user_reviews:
[{"Name":"EV NA","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkrFEYUDX56vJrEozPX61XeE38WxjNbtQFPsVaCY2-cAwrUA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Simply gorgeous location on one end of the mall, with views over the parking lot and we were fortunate to arrive here in a very warm day, hence seating outside on their very comfy areas, with hardly any people around - it reminded me of one of those restaurants you find in Florida.  Well, I was in holiday mood!!!
- lovely young servers, very friendly and polite, taking our orders straight away
- very clean toilets and clean cut place altogether
- excellent food  with the chef paying attention to my requests
- not far from the ferry terminal (maybe 20min by car), if you prefer to eat in a proper restaurant, rather than in the small and many cheap cafes at the terminal","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOeOjnAIdoEVVCVYoXXUT6GPWpzYx-uVrvgq3EN&fid=0x0:0x7036a98cb704d7b9"],"When":"2024-7-8"},{"Name":"Wayne Lav","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUk880jfctdjiDn4tRAvocN5rCVUdtgArCHWFDiv2yxg-QvIz4L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This restaurant, located just outside the mall, offers both indoor and outdoor seating with a pleasant ambiance. The menu features a wide variety of dishes, and the staff are friendly and attentive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvJIgJru6E_tyHr3PkzsGEQyWMUHjOspVxNx2T&fid=0x0:0x7036a98cb704d7b9"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"James Hopkins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI7pWUJCXAZ3TFKPOMmqiGEYyfSlYMeW4NeUBtiEZBMRXSEuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently dined at Milestones and had a wonderful experience! The food was delicious and perfectly cooked, making every bite enjoyable. Our server, Whitney, truly went above and beyond to ensure we had a great time. She was attentive, friendly, and made excellent recommendations that enhanced our meal. Overall, it was a fantastic outing, and I can't wait to return!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kaili Hagel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1yzsrk8SwqNNuCyYuKlRn3_9eHqDoZ4DHy3of0cmYzrn0vXPe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Usually really enjoy eating here but had a horrible experience today. Very slow service even though there were only 4 tables in our area in the lounge. Had to keep asking for refills, my husband order a burger with no tomato's and I ordered the spicy Korean. When we got out meals my husband's burger came with a tomato and my burger was completely the wrong burger I got a beef burger with bacon instead on the chicken. When we asked the server he said he totally forgot, if he can't remember orders he should write them down.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Olivia Levesque","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUb4zZbV0YXKhHkU2F_3dwx03KNXKQqTHdsRQyeSWJ9SjDYl5kv3A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always such good food and drinks, service is great. Still my all time favorite restaurant","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWhB5mTOuu8Nu--rZKhOcPF7dobNAxYq5law35&fid=0x0:0x7036a98cb704d7b9"],"When":"2024-9-3"},{"Name":"WILLIAM REN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKRmqUVmhhErGGqKi-Bzn0et1-EnBX9lgvZO2NQ0f1pzZpZEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This restaurant is always one of my favorite restaurants. The foods are always excellent and the service is always good. I appreciate the elegant atmosphere. I love the box seats, which are very suitable for friends to meet and chat. Todays foods were still delicious, cook well and beautiful presentation, especially the steak sandwich. Today ETHANthe serviced us, very considerate and thoughtful, and he is very handsome. I wish his service gets more compliments from customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhtKfwaNue2wc2XxbSd7Aq9KvWtYR2KiJvwgGz&fid=0x0:0x7036a98cb704d7b9"],"When":"2023-4-7"},{"Name":"Carlo Thirtytwo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbR_vlyW79qWuGGVcDHaz7U0_HyYvsOHMhgJmUWxIJEKzvVQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Really enjoyed my experience at Milestones the other evening; they've really stepped up their food game. It's been a while since I've been to Milestones so I was impressed with what they've done with the menu.

We ordered mostly handhelds, but I was enticed by the portobello chicken dish which seemed to be popular around other tables. We ended up with the Wagyu Smash Blue Burger with garlic parmesan fries, the Caprese Chicken Sandwich, and a standard veggie burger. California Spring Salad on the side was a fantastic addition as well. Quality was really impressive on the Wagyu burger, chicken sandwich was a little bland, and the veggie was above average.

Our server was super friendly, made thoughtful suggestions on the menu, and was attentive. She was great. Only qualms were the small beer selection that evening (they didn't have a few beers available) and the inability to use our gift card (which apparently ceased applicability in February). Other than that, I'd swing by this Milestone location again next time I'm in Tsawwassen Mills.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjTKk63tf4I3Q9K0jnxecBYvkVVgUgX9O-SQEz&fid=0x0:0x7036a98cb704d7b9"],"When":"2023-7-26"},{"Name":"JB CHU","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgWSLLs0R--vY6HThjK4A_oQpcCL09XMjbjMMjW_zVqw3j73-u=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Wonderful service and awesome food.

It's Milestone! I'd say this is one of the best franchise restaurants in the area. The quality of food was great, and the pricing was reasonable. The portion was generous, and the selections were wide.

After a long day of strolling in the mall, this might have been the best decision to end the day with a happy meal!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAdk4CbqQh1AE0bUFaTDoTovETIp8_WKIr1s9s&fid=0x0:0x7036a98cb704d7b9"],"When":"2019-3-7"}]

[{"Name":"Jordana Howley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLcyXBlLdHydYsF_Gj7ansJBTnASxt14ZYfUHCYEyBPCyl3vQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Brunch Chorizo Bowl was amazing the first time we were in! Hollandaise was perfect. Quite a wait the second time we were in as the ticket machine malfunctioned. We are service humans too, so we get it bit would have been nice to know. Food still tasted good though.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO89grvHZ5cJAwoiQrBSc3inoz3pB7Uniu_xiQy&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Fernanda Coelho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVedTXYXr1zyxhZdZOPmfv5AfLwGhLcGc5suzn7a9G_hXu7LFla=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"LOVE this place, I drove 20min to get breakfast here lol, photos are the traditional breakfast and a cappuccino. So cool to see that they started a pay it forward program, so I bought someone a classic breakfast wrap! I also recommend their roasted veggie panini if you're vegetarian, it's delicious!!! The only feedback I have is that there is a lot of foam in the drinks sometimes, so it's a bit tricky to drink at first lol but very good nonetheless!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYmZQx0CdTMmNoKuE-Kj2ONBSeq2_hROVV2GVv&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Linda Hansbauer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbhYntSwrf3fPiWmrNihB_RxxZEX6epZ6NkhTpeBuOWgHv5aaF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am visiting my family for a week. From Australia 🇦🇺 🪃  - this new Southland Community has a lot to offer. Went for a walk and spotted L'aromas - nice "pitstop" to energies you for the next couple of km of walking. I had no food - the Matcha I had was delicious. Interior modern and pleasing to the eye - clean - staff friendly. I will be back, willst I am here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqNAmfTvp-3eQGO9gnRfm4VShwuU8L59RB61Bw&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2024-8-21"},{"Name":"Malani S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLv2sekt8bQvCrOL6j9X6m8xvp17ZCvNYrMy0rl1w80IWruAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I ordered a chicken curry salad. Like most chicken curry salad, it is mayo based, but this is clearly mayo stew. The crunch of celery and apples are missing and only 1/2 of a grape is present. After taking my first bite, I went up to the till and tried to explain to a worker that there’s too much mayonnaise. Her response was that it’s the way they make it. It’s their recipe to have your curry salad drowning in mayo. She didn’t offer to adjust or correct anything.

They received  2 stars as my husband and sister-in-law’s breakfast were decent. Overall, I wouldn’t come back or recommend this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMDYgatG7rgRo0IwMmZDUCEr8YKxQcqJJRJh03m&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"Jamie Glennon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLOjs5-jqgyQWUX_yOuzgUG9TpUgCo3VZBWVH5vnxr8HdflLs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a really great place to go when you are in Tsawwassen looking for a coffee shop that also has breakfast, lunch and dinner.

They have expanded their breakfast menu quite a lot recently and are priced very well against other places.

They have beer, wine and spirits and live music.

A large south facing patio with fire pits and plenty of seating makes it a great location to meet friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmRjb6p9ZV4kxJ2mtzZ4N7DClfiDnTVaU4sOY3&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Eddie So","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISSdmRal6WEYNToT2BfCZQ0cdumKRhmtyRM82KD93UMkc0-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A really good coffee shop and restaurant in this area. There are lots of good seating area indoor and outdoor. The staff are nice and friendly.
Usually we come for coffee or tea with some baked goods.  But we are late this time,  we decide try the pizza.  It is good too.  We can have more options later.
They also offer happy hour drink and food too.
There are more menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAqnPs8Gtav8n8y6dKUDQfEGcJqmRcocje4RhA&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2023-6-13"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a nice time here; cozy atmosphere, not too busy on a Good Friday. I absolutely loved the blueberry danish, could tell it was fresh with delicious cream cheese and juicy blueberries. Avocado bacon wrap took a little while to make but that seems to be because they make it fresh as it was nice and hot, and it was deeelicious! Like a sit down restaurant style. Definitely coming here again to try the wide menu selection.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNktMPXK3EiTgxwdxipCNPxZXdiyhssOtCvM5qP&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2023-4-8"},{"Name":"Jeanine Manley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsiCSl_kDu5HLPcil1hcAWowgG5wYruXebcQF0I1lDL6C3XA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stopped by early afternoon for a bite to eat. Hubby and I shared the Roast Chicken Sandwich 😋 and Carrot Cake 😋, drip coffee for me and English breakfast tea for him. Service was friendly and polite and the food was amazing. We will definitely be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmj5c_IEOJaexSjVu_k-TvrZT2HpAH01IQL_m3&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2024-1-5"}]

[{"Name":"Neil King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1Q0EM5pZx9WHzCr_pTn-6Omi-lDPJuUwZruVKPcLT89Ccy0-h=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down the best Sushi in the PNW! Every dish is served fresh and made with such care and perfection from the owner/head sushi chef! I highly recommend asking for the Chef's Special whatever it is as it is always the best. And they have always taken such incredible care of my 3 year old daughter. This is her absolute favorite place to eat and has been since she could have solids. There is not a single bad dish on the menu, hot or cold. Definitely visit and enjoy your favorite Japanese cuisine.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwoNBbh4BPJ8ksW_6VPrlJcshKLefj61I8y_P0&fid=0x0:0x2e5cef454a459987"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Dew Low","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIWRsVIHVBRgzu4BVKN_-yKVWvjyVlDF_H_GDiV_pudumLtpw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an amazing dinner here, ordered the dinner bento box and everything was delicious. Authentic Japanese food with fresh sashimi and perfectly fried tempura. Staff were friendly and vibes of the place was relaxing. Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMxQJlZ0fqh6jOP5Tk-ZJjnFGHjEI55tOHSO07N&fid=0x0:0x2e5cef454a459987"],"When":"2024-7-25"},{"Name":"Micaela Robinson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2QksgdiepfAQ10tl72lYcRqkt6l1FugMIhmMIfzOnP4rJ1IYySg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My son and I enjoy coming to Bistro Peekaboo!  We try and make it a weekly thing since it is super yummy and conveniently located across from his Taekwondo classes.  Sometimes, we even able to get in 10 mins before they open when his class is over.

Their sashimi, sockeye salmon is Very fresh and delicious every time.

I've enjoyed a bunch of different rolls here, and they are all good.  A few of my favs are Mango cream cheese roll, crispy pineapple roll, spicy salmon roll, yam tempura roll, miso soup, salmon sashimi and of course saki and Asahi beer!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRproP8xpnKhZKPN7PCNdG0F6LR2Iz54rgxh9X&fid=0x0:0x2e5cef454a459987"],"When":"2024-5-13"},{"Name":"Karen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXl4Bs2i46X0UBgHBYM6tmfxeFCxnxMn0HyiqFjx8gCCPLCyH7FFw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was good, and the staff were very friendly. The Peekaboo roll was delicious, but the plate it was served on wasn’t ideal for eating. However, it did look great for presentation.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMrsQaPMSo8NDqyBrpq2OceZdPC0h-Il4N5s6l&fid=0x0:0x2e5cef454a459987"],"When":"2024-9-17"},{"Name":"Ben Ho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHpMEx1fjmmf3AWQzf5DR-kr-pRDEx7TvKvnONf8OCMN1eqpeDFg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just pass by this afternoon and have a wonderful lunch. It definitely the best sushi restaurant in Tsawwassen.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfdGU2pQPf2tIbaX77W0MLEPs7wQfdz-TDTVdp&fid=0x0:0x2e5cef454a459987"],"When":"2024-9-19"},{"Name":"Anne D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcpvA-h-AyBmANCHdhhrDOmLepgyc7gk09U5rqfGXZ7NBfzhU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Years ago, when people kept telling me about this place, I had trouble finding it. If you get lost, first locate the BC Liquor Store in Tsawwassen and then look across the courtyard. It is a cozy little place, decorated with beautiful architectural drawings and usually playing jazz. The meals are always presented artfully. Personally, I like the creative fusion dishes; just like in many restaurants in Japan. The service is consistently excellent, and I often notice the chefs behind the counter taking time to chat with the clients. My son especially appreciates the vegetarian rolls; very few places combine all his favourites of avocado, cucumber, AND sweet potato in one roll.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLIEwz9kIk0N1M4VMQF_NwBTz07QlbUiuH9m8M&fid=0x0:0x2e5cef454a459987"],"When":"2023-9-2"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered takeout from here. This was my first time trying oyakodon, then I also ordered the chef special sushi, which was a surprise. The staff was welcoming and the order was very fast, 20 minutes. The employee was also mindful to ask if I would like chopsticks.
Every bite was a flavor sensation! The oyakodon chicken was so soft and there was a savory sauce with tasty onions and egg. The sushi was incredible! I was fully prepared to expect to maybe not like it. I wish I could know what it was exactly, because it was a great flavor I'll never forget.
Both dishes were very filling and satisfying.
Will definitely come back again and recommend to my friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVjvnd4PKO-VTllNME5m55m_oPWSkmXhgaOG-3&fid=0x0:0x2e5cef454a459987"],"When":"2023-11-12"},{"Name":"My Dang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuX9KoQSNoXxWT2plnTBiOSoGxIN2IfRotXosxr5iuLPzIRMw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Small and cozy Japanese bistro restaurant with excellent food, wide range of menu and reasonable price. It is a hidden gem in Tsawwassen. It is a wonderful place for solo, or just small group of 4 or less as the space is small and can't fit for larger groups.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrsGqksrhk03quMKnaaKgKkAOmqfhHWFqTo_iy&fid=0x0:0x2e5cef454a459987"],"When":"2024-1-7"}]

[{"Name":"raechelle bishop","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWp3lLax-Ic4Pxkoex821fO7o43NmBPDrnvvciGvnHqgK_ujxsD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My husband and I love this location. Their food is always amazing. They staff is polite and the service is quick. We always bring people out for dinner here when they visit. Most of the time we order takeout.

My only complaints are on the takeout.

The portions are a lot smaller than if you eat in, tho the cost is the same.

The lids for the dips always melt and shrivel up causing whatever is in the container to spill all over the food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMsLZaKZhiacIRtWd1wYnhHFdI63AYUgqIv7VyN&fid=0x0:0x62dbece1fff9c912"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Tony Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPKcy0N8L_e03kCanD-kbqBYJvghgec1_Wu16Qs-S8YjI-PLg2nw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"When you crave for chicken wings, Wings is the place to go. They have every flavor you want. My favorite is the dill pickle, but ask for more seasoning on the side if you want the saliva to flow. The classic Buffalo sauce is great too. And if you want sweetness, both the Fuji and Jakarta heat are delicious. After 3 years, I finally tried the Bobby Wing that practically burned a hole in my tongue. After getting over the heat, it was actually good. Complement it with calamari and have the dip nearby. You'll want to douse your tongue in the dip, and not the beer. By the way, the tacos are really good. Get a mixture of meat if you can.

Update: Been there for lunch several times and noticed how quiet the place was. Unfortunately the place smelled more like a pub than a wings restaurant. I also think more emphasis can be done on trying to promote wing nights rather than trivia, hockey meals, etc. - all things that remind me of pubs than restaurants. The updated lunch menu is great and happy hour bites - all tasty and good value. Only the decor and smell of the place can be adjusted.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOYXHEtrPcSZdiN36U7wq2aqy5bqhQXZwvgIbH&fid=0x0:0x62dbece1fff9c912"],"When":"2023-8-1"},{"Name":"Daniel Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAxFTfz_ZYgM60gsStYArKOb4YgmHuHArMEsVm-TJD2WcKuo33=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The service at this is average, there isn't anything particularly noteworthy to mention. We placed an order consisting of 2 kids' meals, Chicken Alfredo, Meatballs Marinara, Wings, and soda.

We ordered chicken strips for the first kids’ meal and pasta for the second set, which were satisfactory. The chicken strips were tender, and the pasta was decently prepared.  (Kids’ meal come with drinks and dessert)

My wife had the Chicken Alfredo, and she mentioned that it was good. My daughter particularly enjoyed the garlic bread that accompanied the dish.

However, I was quite disappointed with the Meatballs Marinara. I'm a huge fan of meatballs and often order them when available on a menu. Unfortunately, the meatballs at this place were lacking of the smoky flavor I was expecting. They were among the worst meatballs I've had in years.

The wings also left us disappointed. We opted for a half-and-half combination of lemon pepper and honey garlic flavors. The lemon pepper wings turned out to be dry, and the taste of the honey garlic wings was unclear.

As for the soda, we ordered Coke and Sprite. My son mentioned that his Sprite tasted like water, l  believe that the soda lacked sufficient carbon dioxide.

Overall, the experience had its ups and downs, with some dishes meeting our expectations while others fell short.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOC4bKrUklfBCqJ9xhJf3bKbqquKqCLN-eaPQmg&fid=0x0:0x62dbece1fff9c912"],"When":"2023-7-1"},{"Name":"Shawn Corkum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxtAysqj7F2p6bXglsUmRm5orOep5UPFSzANo7LTK_LKMLPrMwoA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Stopped at Wings for lunch, it was my second time here.  I really enjoyed the Beef Dip I had last time around, so wanted to give the namesake dish a try.  The wings are very good, if a bit pricey.   I had the Peri Peri with the house ranch, and it was tasty, with just the right amount of heat.  The wings are coated nicely, and are meaty.   My wife had the quesadilla, which was pretty bland.  They need a better lunch menu, imo.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNP6D9hBO-t9lFU5Lcehthb09hOXtmD_CLjaHi9&fid=0x0:0x62dbece1fff9c912"],"When":"2024-3-17"},{"Name":"Krazy Mitch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUI7e00_EMxMC5lRcA9LNPHxr6Mbxl-ctUbXYQxIXvNjX2guHtK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Well that was a dismal experience.
Never been to wings before,  won't go back.  $50 for a starter salad, a 14oz beer, and wings and fries combo.  The cheese bread was missing flavor,  the sweet potato fries need longer in the deep fryer, the wings we meh. I asked the waitress for a "fruit" beer, she said "we don't have "fruit" beer, I asked what the stanley park rotating was a Peach Lager, last time I checked peach was still a fruit..

I won't be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elmira Nazari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUS8psOPde-fgvVYsglTVKj-j9hpNdB1347mGr_T9d11yAStREO4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious food. The Southern bowl, spinach dip and wings were all delicious. Went for the UFC fights and our waitress was really awesome and made sure she checked on us often. Recommended for sports events and casual outings!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyO7GQChxe8Q0fF0fqHcHx_Tu70fmNAAIMliAY&fid=0x0:0x62dbece1fff9c912"],"When":"2023-4-10"},{"Name":"jason wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAr7OPM3u3i7bBkh0r7Q9kS7_8Gu_88Crv223BgydShD66TQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Service was excellent, Hamburger was dry and need more mayo.. Wings are better than most place in Vancouver..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLOwBvpfETiHPlsVYopSh1Zsyaf_2LNe48lRa6&fid=0x0:0x62dbece1fff9c912"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Janet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJLdrp4_-PzGWs8I7cbVIruptxWktGjE-_19gAKtYsnjV7T8DB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came at Happy hour so it was pretty loud and busy, but the staff saw and greeted us right away. Given the crowd at that time it was understandable there was some wait but our server made a point of checking in on us so we didn’t have to wave multiple times. Food was decent, wings were a bit small but tasty enough.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmugq2dGK8I5BuROfk_kvAIBjAJ5TiwtvQgtTx&fid=0x0:0x62dbece1fff9c912"],"When":"2023-2-20"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"larissa sandoval","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHMsnNOyQ-dDeoTnqKIXCM1pOeSc3Hn8eBLvjCMupM9LsN7CuRvA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The customer service was exceptional from the moment I walked into the restaurant. The atmosphere was warm and inviting, and everything was spotless. My food arrived almost immediately and was bursting with flavor—one of the best pho soups I’ve ever had. Plus, it was very affordable. I highly recommend it! Don’t forget to take a Vietnamese coffee to go. You won’t regret it.!

I visited Canada from South Texas for work and discovered this restaurant on my first night. I loved it so much that I returned every day for the next six days, trying a different dish each time!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyj7lFmxISltInSiPPdk6ulOcLIaa3OeJdTLIW&fid=0x0:0x6e9eb54daa4159d7"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"sandra lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJKnH1o2AEeZGgKmELOGnQMyc7MzehItqcwPsLlvsBp4hAp1Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A hidden gem. This is the BEST Vietnamese restaurant in town.  The food is authentic, delicious -  fresh ingredients 👌🏻 You can really tell the chefs and staff care a lot about the food. The team is also super friendly and attentive.

Highly recommend—10/10. Also got extra springs rolls and another BBH to take home 👸🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyohww9C_HzcvtrCJnq5cX-hTdcFvzskI7IQC0&fid=0x0:0x6e9eb54daa4159d7"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"Kimiya Missaghi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJb2lDM_w29lxt8nTu2BYewMDuVlnwacYth1DYiBlerwGgsuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our new favorite Vietnamese spot! Perfect for a meal before or after the ferry. Great ambiance and amazing food. The owner is super sweet and hospitable. The Vietnamese coffee with fresh coconut juice wow 🤩","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOSheKC1VLjZs1Qyv9rLJ2vyttGf_YBLIfeDJdq&fid=0x0:0x6e9eb54daa4159d7"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Steve Leong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzFeTX1xzGFbNlSVZoreAyWYbXUkrUozWhYo5D0t4fKe1zvzvnEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pho Fresh is an excellent Vietnamese restaurant in the neighborhood, offering a spacious and welcoming environment. The hospitality is top-notch, with friendly staff making the dining experience pleasant. The lemongrass grilled noodles combo and the special house combo are delicious and served in generous portions. The pricing is reasonable, making it a great value for the quality and quantity of food. The vibrant ambiance and comfortable seating add to the overall enjoyment, making Pho Fresh one of the best dining spots in the area. Highly recommended for anyone looking to enjoy authentic Vietnamese cuisine.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtsySdIr0-Xq25O7mhRcvU_aYfpyy_gLuMYTW2&fid=0x0:0x6e9eb54daa4159d7"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"y sa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFngQqa2F90OIpbxkUL3vQVcASx5xoE2gyFjE4kMR1ydjk_2M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You can enjoy some delicious pho there! The homemade broth was especially amazing! Steamed prawn salad rolls and the dipping sauce were also good, making for an enjoyable experience. The staff were incredibly thoughtful and kind. I definitely want to visit there again with my family. I highly recommend everyone to visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0pwqrrOi8ANgHSc3w8bRlzXj4Xx6cX2HP47Au&fid=0x0:0x6e9eb54daa4159d7"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"Robin Clements","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9PmsLxITJmMMeaAz28FAyYktWqAc6468HB42trXKaraHdb6JS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We came here on a whim as we were early for our ferry reservation, and it was the best choice we could’ve made. The restaurant has a warm atmosphere, and we were greeted as soon as we entered.

The food was fantastic, and satisfied our cravings for pho. All the ingredients were fresh and the depth of flavour was perfect, and every time I thought I was running out of meat in the bowl, there was even more than I originally expected!

The owner of the restaurant talked with my boyfriend and I while we waited for our food, and served us directly. Although we only interacted for the hour we were there, we saw how much of a kind and thoughtful person he was through his interactions with other customers and his regulars.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTdvLq6VmgOJLqtEsJCSacgnYxO3oIDJR7-nCw&fid=0x0:0x6e9eb54daa4159d7"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Jungyun Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGp0on-U3-UWh9MA5CmYGPw4gLbO_Ew26nJYGOjF6hdC1QFQKG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The broth was very rich and clean. The service was also amazing. Additionally, the interior was very cozy and welcoming. I would definitely come again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYsf6mb7S2SseGuN0lcFJCzdJbZgx4g-m56TuS&fid=0x0:0x6e9eb54daa4159d7"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Tickets Canada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL0SLPz52bqTWVqYYEKCPdR-8-5YcNqhnfjmebE3sqxMOr0bQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been here several times now so I can say that the level of service and food are always fantastic. From the moment you walk in the door, the owners greet you very warmly with a nice smile. They make you feel immediately welcome wanted and appreciated which is something most restaurants seem to fail to do. The food tastes so fresh, so healthy, so tasty. It’s also quite speedy as well! I make it a point to stop here every time I am in town. It’s just one of those feel good moments.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Andrew Giassa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKs2M8Lm_fO5YMx6QeBO4bPk3OR_tJ-4_oCO6-v2DtArGT_4g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time going there this morning... Americano and bear claw were so delicious that I had to go back for lunch too! The coffee had such rich flavour to it! The sandwiches and desserts were very tasty! Nice atmosphere and friendly people! The staff were very polite, accommodating, attentive, and kept the place very clean! My new favourite cafe in Tsawassen, which I will absolutely be returning to!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1XsfVfdEQM3AlTzGmkwA5TaRQsJ8Odu3YARVk&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Christine Kelly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViXAovH45MnNLisSYPlbAdr50-xqpXW5iVtG6G2pYCk32fQOB_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is such a cute little place! Close the ferry, we stopped here for brunch before heading to Victoria. The English muffin sandwiches were delicious as was the yogurt parfait. Idk why it is but all yogurt in Canada tastes better than in the states. My friend ordered tea which she loved and my latte was delicious!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtOzY8pSi0G7i9sHHpze27FfzvCskVrdjj2VoL&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2024-10-10"},{"Name":"wah chi yip","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKBykHMUbkrtJ4cwRRXsjOnAzAcOzwrpq-XVjovUt6A3trFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A hidden gem in this small town.  It's a small family restaurant.  The baked goods are homemade. I think all of them are good. I love the coconut cake.
The staff is super nice to us.  Since we only order one coconut cake, she cut the cake into two and serves us by 2 plates.  Thank you for her caring to seniors.
We always come here only for afternoon tea since we live in Vancouver.
We didn't try the sandwich and soup.  But the sandwich looks good from the other table, we have the bagel and it is always good. The coffee and tea are good.  They still offer the pot for the tea and I love the tea set.
They always have great services, friendly and helpful.
I think they have reasonable price for their customers too!
If you are in this area, this is the place you should not miss.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOInc5bUVJsDxWi-GB6RnbyTMSAGphovRYCCCgb&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Celi Ribet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoYG5slbals5vHoHXxhmSpAKY1SRqjtLQwadcKXsFpTDJ0esn3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was so fun to stop here and see all the frogs! Also it has a very cozy, homey vibe. Friendly staff will greet you and it is clear that they take pride in their service and products.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmY7UtlX1fZmzfpH_xm8IJRCdP9NQkvxn59P04&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2024-8-3"},{"Name":"angel lo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1IzL3-IELA7R7E3oFObEFF5jKqUJ8mIkFOIr338r21pBTPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a nice breakfast place in delta area, and it called Frog in restaurant title, then I ordered the London frog as my drinks of the day.

Plus, they have varieties of the breakfast to choose from, and we choose the avocadoes toast and the chorizo breakfast wraps, these 2 items were so delicious!

The london frog and cappacino were very nice and yummy also.

The environment is very good as well.

This is recommended for everyone in delta to try it out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlScBHkrRW3YmZy7D8d9UfUnrQIjVWpQ7AoJ0D&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2024-5-21"},{"Name":"Maria M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmuhUB-INQ3XCbE2M9HT-MdzILSuqxW6ls6tLvy0JgUoxl1f3wCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great spot around TSW mills area. The Gingerbread hot chocolate was delicious, the eggnog latte and the muffin were just okay. Lots of options of treats and merchandise. Nice place to sip on a coffee while staring at the rain outside, nice vibes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVy4cLh4udfq61IKbbllHLJhrRF7O1dXbS0gnG&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2023-12-16"},{"Name":"XJ Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7WcjqVdoNPNDRqOZSiFSZHUDbel5oDzpy4rSaDZj54EOkAa5x=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a huge cuppa great oatmilk cappuccino and the best roast beef sandwich I’ve had in a while. Love the place too with the funny little frogs as decor - a great place to stopover for breakfast!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFi7iVKUBhkHM7gU4NS-YNWXVX0GaYFzWWWdNe&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"Eddie So","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISSdmRal6WEYNToT2BfCZQ0cdumKRhmtyRM82KD93UMkc0-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A small lovely place to enjoy the coffee and cakes.  The staff are super friendly.
My wife loves this place and she loves the store baked goods.  She still remembered the coconut cake that they made years ago.
Now they offer a really good outdoor eating area.  They keep the place so tidy and clean in and out.  As before the owner and the staff are so nice and helpful.
If you come for afternoon tea, you must try their baked goods.
The indoor is a nice area too.
We have the coconut cake again in January 2024 again.  It's as good as before.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZIqAQvyssAgnAPyUGhWIUVg2VZGAlVRWEiJHY&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2022-8-14"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"석가래의 음악공장(석현준)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDfbHcLQTbwm-ItWF-lza8n8hO-hy8Pt2bCpNPLfd-pvbf8k4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Best Sushi Spot!
Everything was exceptional, from tempura to sashimi and rolls—nothing fell short.
Dining at the large wooden table with the artwork on the walls made the experience even more enjoyable.
I especially recommend trying the Volcano Roll; it’s a must!
I think I’ll come back every time I visit Vancouver. Absolutely amazing!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLWPbGg2PChFRsordhyFo7BpiPd7CLOTYPQfJf&fid=0x0:0xd68d74066199f0be"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Zion Park","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViRCXnP7OExL_OVOTf32hSSWTtr5MEJGsCRa4BiqUZLUC7IB2Efw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All the dishes were fresh and so nice!
The tempura was perfectly crispy and flavorful, and the Volcano Roll was a standout.
The staff were very friendly, and the food was served quickly.
It’s the perfect spot to grab a meal after visiting Tsawwassen Mills.
If you’re visiting Vancouver, Canada, this sushi place is a must-try.
Highly recommended :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOY0PldIDMZ_Zlz3sUzIQcjH-qC_Bh1OlrNhmfF&fid=0x0:0xd68d74066199f0be"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Arturo Ibarra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXc6k9am_h6r9ca5OgUH7qEKHLP1lIjfBwL_jh8IRhfExCKJN_y2w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was so good I forgot to take a picture before I finished my food 😅. The picture was their jalapeño bomb, which I highly recommend along the rolls royce roll,  both are delicious dishes that I have not seen at any other place. Unique combinations of sushi in general.  The staff and service were superb! Two times I have been here and now for sure it will be our go-to restaurant when we go to the outlets or towards the ferry terminal.  It's one of our favorite japonese places in the metro Van. area now.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOe-dZ8S-LLtg9YxcwGvUINZGtGatHpGtEL49XL&fid=0x0:0xd68d74066199f0be"],"When":"2024-12-1"},{"Name":"Dennise Cecena","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8rG5Z4MVHxQqol0KkBJ511tOPvYKQi7De74fI3KiylLW-9IYI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our favorite Sushi place in town!! The sushi is fresh & delicious! Our favorite is the Dragon Roll, beef/chicken teriyaki & the chicken/beef udon soup. The service is amazing and the servers are friendly. My family and I are always welcome with a smile and greeting! :) 100% recommend trying if you’re in Tsawwassen!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOE2PEnVFlbxCWTevdsmhvvlR7l1WYxqjs7e7aX&fid=0x0:0xd68d74066199f0be"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"Tony Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf8VP49ZjSvgG0JnhT1tc6Tv6OzLL9YEi_yNvwH1rW_K8-7VE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Looking for a Japanese restaurant with a Korean twist? Kamome is it. There is KFC, Korean Fried Chicken and Kim Chi fried rice on the menu. You'll also the the bibimap, rice bowl contents cooked in a clay pot. Recommend the lobster roll or the bento boxes for lunch. And give the dinner for 4 a try. Delicious food. Only thing they can improve on, is the substitutions. Need to be flexible and better priced. People have allergies and may want to swap ebi shrimp for salmon but not for $3 more on a nigiri.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_xYNJHOh9w6gm5mymZDNUEFrvbq9KznjyP4ba&fid=0x0:0xd68d74066199f0be"],"When":"2024-8-20"},{"Name":"John Stick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLwA-jpzGraYUo7jr1qY95bukP2m4mzjWDFk6-stxq5hpHJcA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We went to Tswassen Mills to see Santa at Cabellas...which BTW, is a hidden secret, great set up and free photo....

Afterwards we went to Kamome which is about a 2 min drive in the next complex over.

Lots of parking and a big place. The three of us, 3 adults and our 6 yo easily got a table. Service was attentive and good. The server felt we ordered too much food, but he never met my 6 yo either.

The best dishes were the sushi tower and the yam tempura. All the other rolls and items were good, nothing I'm going to rave about, but filled us up.

The food came fast and was fresh.

If you are in Tswassen and craving Japanese food, this place will give you what you want and a decent price point.

$$","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPS42_c2cGl4al3EqHlN4ca6nqhNNC2ncj_sEs6&fid=0x0:0xd68d74066199f0be"],"When":"2023-12-12"},{"Name":"Paula Kor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCCckh4f87jBroNxUDIpqu4Q7EezAD-0DmaNXgqRVCjwxqjfsh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Found this hidden gem by chance while driving around Tsawwassen Mills. We were looking for something with rice and noodles, and this one came on the signboard. The menu is pretty good, covers all basic Japanese food you can find in Vancouver, and taste is great. I will say is a comfort food for Japanese food lovers. The highlight was sushi tower, with tuna, salmon, ebi, imitation crab meat, avocados with special sauce.  Ambience is quiet and spacious, and the staff were amazing, attentive and polite. It was a good experience overall. Thank you Kamome staff!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbiW1ob11UTN5-xzqI8EI1fSnj4433giAuxowX&fid=0x0:0xd68d74066199f0be"],"When":"2024-3-4"},{"Name":"Narim Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyob_Wh1Q36QKhWsXQXfBtdoiDeEdbzfEo6aeDKIZgqyg9lz1f=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We were the first customer in the restaurant and we ordered 3 menu and we only got 2 of our menu first and when we asked for the other one they said they’re making it rn but I I think they forgot about it and made the new want after I told them.  I ordered rolls with cream cheese and when I got my rolls after waiting they forgot about the cream cheese so we waited again. They didn’t apologize properly and I got my rolls after eating everything else we ordered. They still charged me for everything. Never coming again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmcWcTn_hfmMp2E4smAGf6TIuLcnb30RpqrPaU&fid=0x0:0xd68d74066199f0be"],"When":"2024-6-9"}]

[{"Name":"tease69666","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfCDNnaDyUdqQO787NHuRKytnlKGA_aYQlxxQ4lU5tO3Td63xB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"my boyfriend and I went here with a friend of ours who is a regular costumer, and...oh...my....God....this place was so...good...the food was amazing. the service was great even tho it's cash only and small its still a good place to go when you just want a home made male or sandwich and meat.cant wait to go agin.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO10SBn_yJZH5p-eXGr9PzSncFv4VC7UfyVNUJ8&fid=0x0:0xb8a3fd710275a869"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Louise Yeoh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKn6H1v99edwzRk8pxHxqcfGWgIZaHgZyHlx8FsGc__i8U2ig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"While having a pedicure at Bay Nails in Tsawwassen this morning , I smelt some delicious food. After my pedicure, I found myself drawn to a deli which was full of people . I ventured in and was amazed by the menu. It has been awhile since we has schnitzel burgers , cold shrimp sandwiches, etc. The split pea soup that 2 ladies were having looked really good. So told hubby to park the car when he came to pick me up as I think we found a new place to have lunch. The 2 ladies were super friendly and welcoming when I asked if our fur baby was welcomed at their patio table.

We ordered the Shane burger which had schnitzel and corned beef , chilled shrimp sandwich and split pea soup . First bites were heavenly.  Looks like we stumbled on a hidden gem.  Pricing was reasonable and portions were huge. Will definitely be back .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTmkatfYiZ8PlCD7C1oMlg_gThhqscVvUROb5u&fid=0x0:0xb8a3fd710275a869"],"When":"2024-7-2"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Shepherd's Pie has no business being that good. Why is it so good?!
The atmosphere and interior is cozy and old-fashioned. The lady who serviced me was lovely and gave me warm smiles all around.
The burgers are absolutely massive and hot. Really liked the Dave Burger. They are all so good.
Definitely recommend and will come back.
Btw, there are "cash only" signs all around the walls and windows.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhFD5c7TSEDWL26fTbFLwuBZrSS9sDHkbGPVIA&fid=0x0:0xb8a3fd710275a869"],"When":"2023-10-7"},{"Name":"Ps H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWZH4u5uxDfJNhnL_l8W1S4uIzr1H4HDeoj_eCHzg7xFQspTGN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best. Roast. Beef. Sandwich. EVER.
My whole family feels the same way - we just get it how it's made, no special requests. AMAZING.
Cash only, but there's an ATM at the 7-eleven a few doors down.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEqC7wsj0cdQZZLNDIIzUixwNiB5C9ozHvUh-F&fid=0x0:0xb8a3fd710275a869"],"When":"2024-5-29"},{"Name":"Drew Meikle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJouGVykfUCqec0xQBo-ea8IIIqdcCFU3ZRS_OZlsR60YLITw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ozzie's is a step back to a time of quality food and outstanding service, not to mention fair prices.  I never go in without feeling welcome and appreciated.  It is Tsawwassen's jewel.  Don't forget to try a few of their homemade cookies, too.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"AJ R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLo4tIvUrcwNXdNPm8MhPpZgzsQXb-_lGpW8MEceFXJ5buZ1dI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just went here for my first time, and I loved it! The place is run by two wonderful ladies - the customer service was fantastic and the food is delicious, filling, and very well priced. I’ll definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOOAyIJ5zkh_foYb7nH4nM5HMlU63w2sg3hcBm&fid=0x0:0xb8a3fd710275a869"],"When":"2024-4-15"},{"Name":"Jeremy Hannaford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJh4gJaa4fTCJIngBRIGMrmmqMdx4ZxIh5c_eHCdtOqz7VOAFhyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Before I ordered, three different people ordered the Steve Burger.
Can definitely say it was a good recommendation.
Great portion to value ratio. Just remember to bring cash.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNOXqhKnfMo_gE3_IPqYxYc09bRODcKrG1XkHVD&fid=0x0:0xb8a3fd710275a869"],"When":"2021-6-22"},{"Name":"Dan Lorenz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVa_eC-U0kV3zmKzI4E1osV8_z7ABPGLuq9fXQNAmdOuVhfXvuZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Turkey and Beef are my go to for about 20+ years now. Great small town sandwich shop that serves great soups as well. Spilt Pea being my fav.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Bradley Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQSjOdt_NCThfrgQQSPCAI9c1m2q4Cia70lWTZMyAGLNwKu8R3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We stopped by Browns Socialhouse on our way to the ferry terminal and were pleasantly surprised by how much we enjoyed the experience. The atmosphere was lively yet relaxed, making it the perfect place to unwind before continuing our journey. I opted for the Spicy Ginger Beef, and true to its name, it packed just the right amount of heat. The flavors were bold and balanced, with the perfect level of spice to keep things interesting. Pairing it with a crisp, chilled Pinot Grigio was an excellent choice, as the wine’s refreshing notes perfectly complemented the dish.

Our server was fantastic—attentive, polite, and genuinely made us feel welcome. It’s always nice to have staff that checks in without being overbearing, and she struck that perfect balance. Service like this really elevates the dining experience.

Whether you’re in a rush or looking for a place to linger, Browns Socialhouse is a great option. It was the perfect pit stop before catching our ferry, and I’m already looking forward to coming back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5mXhWow9kivaMbpj3Y17Q4QYlioKH-GjLJOIg&fid=0x0:0x7ceb3fe94e40acff"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Wayne Lav","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUk880jfctdjiDn4tRAvocN5rCVUdtgArCHWFDiv2yxg-QvIz4L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Browns in Tsawwassen is one of the few spots open past 10 pm, making it a solid choice for late-night drinks and dining. The restaurant offers both indoor and covered outdoor seating, with a pleasant ambiance throughout. There's ample seating inside and plenty of parking available outside. The staff is attentive and friendly, adding to the positive experience. The menu is straightforward, and the food is flavorful. TVs above the bar provide a chance to catch some sports while you eat, but the atmosphere leans more towards a restaurant than a bar.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUX1fIVQUgoi3RX8zjIwyqv0wmK6w7yDoyEikN&fid=0x0:0x7ceb3fe94e40acff"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Trevor Moore","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUwW9-UDVr0ZHxqbBSs5pfX74SSAUW25zvwcLqgNHWCSwKlj4M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ended up going earlier on a sunday evening and there was lots of seating. We ordered the Blackened Chicken Cowboy salad and a burger with yam fries, both tasted good. There was an issue with our order, but it was taken care of quickly.
The location, while attached to the Coast Hotel, is not accessable through the hotel.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPK3oTxITnPt8PEbHL7gLlZtsygYZUT1Vh5sGK-&fid=0x0:0x7ceb3fe94e40acff"],"When":"2024-7-24"},{"Name":"Anthony Cooper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCp3vRQvxR895Kdykt6EtzWcDiPpiIUgZ_b2lDj2Bq3nOjUuFY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Calamari, Dry Pork Ribs and Hot wings were amazing! Even had a personal touch with my name on the take out bag! Thank you chefs and hostesses! You guys are awesome!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK42E2QGIhGIbhXbF-hih0k9Xo5rh8B_sd8T3bpl0r9T0JBvRg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Just got done with happy hour nachos and a single amber ale...

The happy hour nachos are very very small...i get it to some degree...happy hour is tidbits...but definitely expected more substantial than this

$23 total with 15% tip for a beer and very very small serving of nachos...

Would have been much happier in the $15 to $17 range.

I evaluate every place i go and ask myself if i would return...probably not, just a bit on expensive side for simple snack","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laurie Rankin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUY_vttpoD4NVvddZfoKf53X65GbQUu156AJtSk0jSr4E1qRntVnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had dinner at Brown's Social House which right beside the Coast Tsawwassen Inn.

We had never been there before and were a bit overwhelmed by the loud music and numerous TV screens.

However, we were very happy with the prompt attention from our server, Michael.

We started with yam fries, served with a delicious chipotle sauce. For dinner we chose Southwest Chicken Bowls.

The food was fresh, colourful and nicely plated.

After we relaxed, we did not notice the music so much.

Having a professional server like Michael enhanced our overall experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMr32qaZ6i25jBp4lVCZd6eBtrdV00EQwDT_CnZ&fid=0x0:0x7ceb3fe94e40acff"],"When":"2023-4-12"},{"Name":"Chris L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlo27yi0c3tMg1MEFW8gltVROJwlBrQGtk927fnMS7KkAAA0UJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I frequently stop here for lunch if Im working in the area.

The food is great. Although this time I tryed the dry ribs, my only complaint is there wasnt much rib lol.

The service is top notch, the ladys are always lovely and helpfull.

This is also one of my favourite patios to enjoy a cold one one.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnFMKjTCUdUB-2jXjFbEsLaNss5S8AW0vmCx7Q&fid=0x0:0x7ceb3fe94e40acff"],"When":"2021-6-24"},{"Name":"Brian - TGR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzC6iHnlfyEU-aB2UYUDobSOZA5Wfs8E2KRx4-J5jcYpXSPaQ2Zw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Exceptionally friendly service, really good food and the indoor patio was very enjoyable.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3OLZfPss1zuZHY6jPl0PjPSABnPN-A5UoySUw&fid=0x0:0x7ceb3fe94e40acff"],"When":"2024-2-15"}]

[{"Name":"Emilia Tam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgfp9u2yzyy8HUI4c13oDqO8lmhh6nx7dy4FtdX8yKSFhFbDi4rQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Food tasted great but small portion. My husband ordered the baked tortellini with Alfredo sauce. The tortellini and sauce tasted like store bought and it was very heavy on cheese. Server constantly seemed like she was on a rush. Big portion of food makes it worth your buck. Everyone there seems need to pack their food home. The serve is awesome! Our server observed and not interrupted the meal still having. Loved that! I felt relax and had a nice chat there with dim down atmosphere. Starred this location for my choice of Greek food. Even though it is distance away, it is definitely a place to go if you are around there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWGWDIVnLxf5j3r6e4GA-Fd9dSUkQHJwF_7Jql&fid=0x0:0x5eeafa1a7ed01608"],"When":"2023-9-5"},{"Name":"Indy Virk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLoeoRUuBv6iGVh8ojWW2AawuN-5SRQ7HjGXshYVFDCEo8xWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely delicious authentic Greek food! It was our first time there, the chicken souvlaki was a 10/10. I highly recommend going and I can't wait to go back to try the other dishes. Extra shout out to our server and cook! Overall we were very impressed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elmira Nazari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUS8psOPde-fgvVYsglTVKj-j9hpNdB1347mGr_T9d11yAStREO4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Was craving greek and this place was close by. The service was great and the atmosphere was quiet and relaxing. We got a few things:
Calamari - super fresh with tzaziki dip.
Greek Salad - nice portions, and a generous amount of quality olives for the olive lovers out there.
Roast lamb - slow cooked, the meat deliciously fells apart. Comes with greek salad, potato and rice.
Chicken Souvlaki - Chicken was a little dry, the rest of the dish was good.
Share platter - had a good variety of everything and would feed 4-5 people.
Cesar drink - really well made compared to alot of other places.
Favourite dish - roast lamb","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO23Gpd72Qhc1xl9qobY3Iq2cKQnpaYE3bGVp-t&fid=0x0:0x5eeafa1a7ed01608"],"When":"2023-9-17"},{"Name":"Heike Reinhardt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQu13xA_sdCrrCEzybl4Mb_Gnyu8_KDY2hb0kmgRKtEpDaH70=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super sweet service, calamari with greek withe wine is great.
I had so much leftovers, which I brought home for the next day for lunch ;) I will ge again ✨️💓","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNOSOFcS3oqj--oATIR1cqesDAt8DXwlKgLR9Ce&fid=0x0:0x5eeafa1a7ed01608"],"When":"2024-10-8"},{"Name":"Jeff Boulton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwWomyzjheqZXm1ssNiqtjC1h17ofWn10zQqMCbIBk5xqgw48e=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had lunch outside on deck, great service and food.  The moussaka was fantastic!!  Lots of food and great flavour.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMpQsNzv6hZ2-3eM5BpM7ufTGqzTz73MJMJmbKx&fid=0x0:0x5eeafa1a7ed01608"],"When":"2024-7-16"},{"Name":"Ronald B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_Mt0SdyzppT58qLdbbzj1sY4Nva9W-LpB9qFPiHaoQT6MHG0H=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This place transported us back to Greece! We only ordered the Chicken Souvlaki, but it was still really good! The skewer ends were a bit dry but the rest was juicy chicken! I ordered a 6 oz glass of Tsantali Retsina. I would only recommend this wine if you’re feeling adventurous and have a palate for a dry, fresh pine and a saline finish. If you can get past the piney notes you get on the nose citrus, pear and apple notes.

Definitely one of the best Greek restaurants in the lower mainland we’ve tried so far!

Price: It’s priced the same as most other restaurants of this caliber. But you get what you pay for! Great Food!

Portion/palate: Portion is decent for the price you pay and the taste is so good! Minus the dry ends on the skewers. The wine was a delight because it is nothing you have ever tried! (I bet)

Place: Location is nice because it is on main street and parking is decent if you come when they open. We dined on the patio so I didn’t see much of the inside. A bit of a drive to get to, but if you’re in the area for the beach or an event definitely come here!

People: People were great! Good service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuv1BkZAiE_m0srnHDc5TL6GX05c6M9Tmv7x_X&fid=0x0:0x5eeafa1a7ed01608"],"When":"2023-7-5"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Melanie E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUR0bJcxqNkJt-i1wxCH3EaQXevncA86panZszfT__NAs_0KWRp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I was underwhelmed about this place. A friend invited me here.

Food: 3/5 - the breaded chicken almond was average, not greasy. The chicken chow mein had few veggies and lacked taste. The butterfly shrimp was average. Lacking authentic Asian food.

Service: 3/5 - slooow getting your food. If you’re not in a hurry to eat, and you have patience, then it’s okay to come here.

Atmosphere: 3/5 - clean","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-owsUSuhBLQL70y_NZLWvDhF0fMVg2GKtzPoZ&fid=0x0:0xc6c6e136ffbdb874"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Devon Phelan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXorWAedHbb59VsAXuR_js0R_xERF5lT44CmILYrHhE3b98PaXr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ocean Palace has been my go-to place to eat Chinese food for years. Having local business owners run the place has ensured that they maintained the trust they have with customers. If you are conscious about MSG, just know that you can ask for no MSG with your whole order!

Be sure to order when they open (~5pm) so that you don't have to worry about a potential 1-2hr wait time for take-out or delivery late at night! The long wait goes to show that the food here is made authentically and tastes great!

It's also great to know that they make their spring-rolls in house!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"steve “Steve here” garnier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8syJgHRb0oL04Zsxzk5A8o3zGjkPiKanrBaAkjiMlFwFoULbA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Missing items from my order and It took over an hour and a half for me to get my order. I did order through skip but the order was received by the restaurant in about 2 minutes and the driver was there before the food was done AND it only took him 6 minutes to get to my house.

All I ordered was 2 combo meals and 2 pops. They didn't give me any drinks or cutlery or napkins.
And when I called the guy had the nerve to ask me to drive there to pick up my drinks they forgot AND tried to blame the wait time on skip the dishes.
Wasn't until I told him I was going to leave a poor review that he offered to refund me for the 2 pops that I never even received........uhm yea I'm deffinately not paying for the items I never got buddy. Thanks alot. Meal should have been free.

I also thought the meat portions were quite small.

***I'm not sure how to respond to your response so I'm doing it here.

Again your trying to blame the skip driver. You only offered to have the drinks delivered after I said no to picking them up myself and only offered the refund on the drinks after I said I was going to leave a bad review.

My opinion on the matter remains the same that was poor customer service and not taking responsibility. If you apologized right away and offered the refund even for just the drinks I wouldn't have givin this review.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"mike hagan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvUqJb3JaTqllEtEnlhNA7LGjD22b8O1McJFccS2HHP1Cc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Went Aug 03/24 to dine in with another couple after it had only been open for take out for years due to Covid & staff shortages. We ordered 6 items and every one was very fresh and tasty!  So glad to have this dine-in option back open!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brock Aura","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJnr_sEMDNfoDwSGZD53SzjLC3ZDNthshJ3gL532nCm4kTy9w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Decent portions, but steep prices. Taste was good.

One strange thing was that I ordered a noodle dish ahead of time and about half and hour before pick up, I was told they only had 2/3 of a portion left and I was asked if I still wanted the dish. I stumbled a little bit before asking what I would be charged and was told that it would cost 2/3 of the full price. I kept the order and it seemed fine...I’ve just never experienced this before.

Buddha’s feast was good, rice noodles and beef were tasty.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMiNMyyek6gNNEj6nLYSccm4-EkyQntccmio1X1&fid=0x0:0xc6c6e136ffbdb874"],"When":"2020-10-24"},{"Name":"Linda Robertson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYuGuxPHkbgoM_-l_wB7xGXgjppRNnhe3SJGQ6XK3-vWK3VdiM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Wow!!!! Dinner I usually get for two has gone up in price. Now $89.00 for what I would have paid between $50 - $60 not that long ago. Great food but pricey","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Morgan Strohan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNvuq4FfbgLeZ4Ln2fBU_295Y8TusQxWL4Qm-sMIQZhzEM7g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Order here every month- no issue at all like those below. Food is consistent everytime and very good! Phone ahead on Friday and weekend nights expect longer wait (they’re busy because they have good food) but they are very accurate with timing. Will always be a go to","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"karen ing","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUFcYN-FLw5wWMf-K2skISaZsFKnGxzP9SXfJsb_LBZZN84jw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our only Chinese food choice! Gluten free options available for our celiac family member. Worth the wait.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Sarah Wigglesworth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMpIyRLQQVHzkoZxweOof_jd7F2xMKXHLApVdDC8gb4iN9lEE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came in for lunch and had a very enjoyable experience. The food was great tasting and delivered fast! Would go again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPiVdDy_AULrVhMUUoID6jTw3MvmSeROgxk6Xky&fid=0x0:0x17943d6bd3047396"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"Reece LGraham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8-AA2N7wEgPWzGE5evRj6WzuMJ0cqmKgcAYSIU5WmnNkFCLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went with a friend for brunch and the service was wonderful. I should’ve gotten the girls name but didn’t, we spoke about how she was part Japanese. She was super kind and attentive. It was such a wonderful experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Inderjit Kaur Johal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJS3BRB_NIdOpD-bBNwkOmi3-ZXk2Dxc5dOozpsVaPrN6KJOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"White Spot Tsawwassen is a must-visit restaurant if you're in the area. The atmosphere is vibrant and colourful, setting the perfect mood for any occasion. The menu offers a fantastic variety of food and drinks,
**Delicious Food and Exceptional Service, The food was great, with excellent vegetarian choices. Definitely will come back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"chsnwun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4P9KCaYveOCkTXiolanHwrE7k7jyl5DMR1IQhcDM5jPKzpelh5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"GREAT experience  met Jas and not only did she make my Dining experience awesome she  took my order and cooked it

Awesome doesn't get better then that

Zucchini on point just the way I like it!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNVHwshyLbUQjZwSkfQdnOy01dxjXz8o7-6p4cH&fid=0x0:0x17943d6bd3047396"],"When":"2024-5-13"},{"Name":"Victor Law","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpnZPh7heLHnvp3JcjErTq9VzUaFB6LA67FBNyLyGHNyq0kA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our friends invited us to a beach outing and we were famished by lunchtime. We are happy they suggested this White Spot.

The restaurant was pretty packed when we arrived. Our server was great and got our orders in quickly. Despite the crowd, the kitchen got our meals out efficiently.

I got the Bacon Cheddar Bigger Burger with fries while my wife got the Mediterranean Chicken Burger. The kids shared a Chicken Fingers Pirate Pak.

I loved my burger. It was tasty and delicious. My wife enjoyed her chicken, which was not dry. The fries are good as we come to expect from White Spot.

The kids love the Pirate Pak, but what kid wouldn't!

It was a good meal and we had a great time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJCDFGe0xlnwuW3PU_SSvmyog5uC_degFwgEMJ&fid=0x0:0x17943d6bd3047396"],"When":"2023-5-23"},{"Name":"Mathew Lao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtO7Xiefy5DCdGGQ4Bz-1QO-aissnnVRn_Ycl2AHI76SyQyWE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just as I remember it years ago.

However, it was a lot more quiet than I remember

I decided to go here for a quick breakfast and a coffee and they didn't disappoint at all.

Everything was cooked well and the staff were really nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMpUkTMgiOLMnTc5L1G7-cDGEUOCq1XROKBnVUD&fid=0x0:0x17943d6bd3047396"],"When":"2024-1-15"},{"Name":"Edmund Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHvlF0urWYXIlPfQf5KowC1k-rq0AheQYSkLiZHu_9DBsVZPiP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great, friendly service by our waitress. But I noticed the booths were pretty small compared to other White Spot locations. But the food seemed better. Had the Double Double  and it was pretty juicy with the Triple O sauce and the double cheese. And the Fettuccine Alfredo was excellent. And you can't go wrong with the milkshakes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_-39la0GsZEuuit0kOQfTFP6qUVsrxsg6LXZ7&fid=0x0:0x17943d6bd3047396"],"When":"2018-4-29"},{"Name":"Mud Wings","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXn49esCPdxZCE7lF0ANC3JlIYANJi_nJ_zdre5-CH9la_DzNc3ow=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Firstly... Entered through the exit door. Member of the waitstaff saw me struggling with my cane. Opened the exit door for me.
Thank you kindly 🙏🏽
Ordered the "Legandary" burger. It was okay at best. French fries are too thick-a-cut for my liking. Coleslaw was bland, but crispy and crunchy. Creamy","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODRskF2YfqcT4ThTBqQaRRpl3ntrbMwaRKKfAv&fid=0x0:0x17943d6bd3047396"],"When":"2023-3-2"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"SoulCurryArt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhdI4XBvTt_hb2FS8qvbTFp0uDaG2xUgX_dp11882wvcTrqrEh=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When a local business not only makes the most amazing food but also goes above and beyond in customer service, you know you’ve hit the jackpot!
We stopped at Roy’s on our way from Victoria to Vancouver after a long day of sightseeing. We reached 10 minutes before closing time, they had already closed the kitchen and were winding up for the day. When I told them I had specially come to sample their Bengali cuisine with my family, all the way from the east coast, they opened their kitchen and hearts for us.
The food was cooked to perfection. We celebrated my husband’s 50th with his favourite; kosha mangsho ( slow cooked goat curry) which reminded me of home. The flaky laccha parantha was perfect with it. 10/10
We had the prawn curry with lime leaves and it was spicy and so so delicious. We washed it down with gur-er rosogolla (cottage cheese balls soaked in a sweet jaggery syrup)and my only regret was that I didn’t pack more to takeaway.
It was an outstanding meal, cooked to perfection, authentic Bengali food in every sense. The staff was extremely helpful and made our dining experience at Roy’s one that was really special.
Thank you Roy’s for bringing the Indian hospitality and food to Canada. You made a lasting impression on us and we can’t wait to come back when we are back on the West Coast.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMun4f_A6fXdDsFxDQUlfcNaEYNAC9ls_SVueYC&fid=0x0:0xb7f0a68c89ea8418"],"When":"2024-8-7"},{"Name":"Pooja Chaudhary","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVikZvhBSYSeJHyC2iVE3uoSeiUL7_8Q-E6SrAo6CM8YBBQWbE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"TLDR; average food, got food poisoning after.

We came in with high expectations because of the rating, but were quite disappointed with the food - flavors et al. Between the two of us we ordered the Manchurian cauliflower, the paneer peas and a naan. The Manchurian was ok. The paneer was entirely flavorless - the gravy tasted like dal, which was so weird.

After all this, I chalked it up to just picking bad options on the menu. But 30 minutes after, I had an upset stomach and my partner had full blown food poisoning - that has definitely tipped my experience to a negative one.

Service is very nice though. The servers are super attentive and good come about super quickly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNLHx2eLUo1ZPSAd1tNQ-qWLTwUTOqA815PPjZg&fid=0x0:0xb7f0a68c89ea8418"],"When":"2024-9-14"},{"Name":"Israt Jahan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUGLh9yB2qVdZGIbYpQJ5Mon3-2NjEqAny7q46XimuvNTnMNA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dhokar dalna and Prawn Malaikari made our weekend lunch special. Food was less oily,  that's  why we loved it more. Cherry on top was the happy hour deal. Surely coming back again to check on the rest items on the menu. FYI, From meat side, only lamb is served halal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOaTA_dH6exm13wfzqcji-TrUHuVaWGvzm4SONy&fid=0x0:0xb7f0a68c89ea8418"],"When":"2023-9-30"},{"Name":"Lee Gildemeester","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmwK5TPiyJO9K2BikS-yqaHifl8H0QHLdeDujEGzwKhWsKSXQ7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great food, tasty and consistent. Portions, including the Samosas, are smaller than I'd like. a bit overpriced considering the small portion sizes. 2 people can easily spend $80 with no leftovers. bill didn't reflect the 'buy one get one free' promo on my last visit. should probably be listed as a $$$ not a $$","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Manpreet Dhindsa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhVsf4hqwCPRKlTzCNXAyXqeKlgKKkWoEL8_wr-jkyvsKRNWYLGw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Simply fantastic food, menu options and service. So glad this is not just another Indian restaurant. Loved their menu, it's very well thought, curated and executed. Food was excellent, portions sumptuous and taste bang on! Their naans are a must try,  different and best recipe so far. Loved the potato pesto naan, different yet traditional!! Lamb was 👌 👏,  lentil cake curry delicious, lemon rice excellent , cauliflower Manchurian, a hit . Glad we stopped by tonight as we will be back for more moving forward.  What a wonderful team you all have, they were happy and working as a team, both front and back of the house . Keep up the good work guys. You are amazing!!! Thank you for great experience:)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMEoViXLHjHpyP5gIg4Y1MtjAvzt-wiUG2fQo0G&fid=0x0:0xb7f0a68c89ea8418"],"When":"2021-10-30"},{"Name":"Arun John Varghese","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVoZlTUN4otj58r2juzAQOie8Enk3IWZUtDNKbsBz_OdbDGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best places to have authentic Indian cuisine in Tsawwassen. We were greeted & attended by Ms.Ujala. As her name suggests, Ujala’s enlightening hospitality was really worth mentioning along with the delicious food and quick service. Truly a very good place to spend an evening with good food and good people. Certainly recommend 👍🏽","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOs9GMTi-zI5TPw4Qyeh9TCu9HjaHe6iTCg-riW&fid=0x0:0xb7f0a68c89ea8418"],"When":"2023-7-18"},{"Name":"Rohan Mittra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTan-4gipBjSPNNLq7O6nnDAB6h3Ox83_ealwiawyIVYLWvek=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After a really long trip of BC, I was really craving some good Bengali food. My oh my, did I hit the jackpot. Found Roy’s on Google and jumped at the opportunity. The mochar bora is what I started my Roy’s culinary experience with and it packed a punch right away. Then had the echor chingri which was delicious and finished the main course with some good old kosha mangsho which transported me back to my home in Kolkata. Now comes the best part, they had gur er Roshogolla 😍 I was in food heaven! Thank you so much folks for making my day! Will definitely come back the next time I’m in Vancouver.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO59cFWBcB4fvb3zzlfyy14GoYdf0H1XpHwFupG&fid=0x0:0xb7f0a68c89ea8418"],"When":"2024-4-1"},{"Name":"Ji Luo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJDDlwTdksi001rt6rIhoB59jo2HsOkhb0VH7JlXKVGsRC4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Above average food quality and taste, decent service, but the portion is on the short side for each single dish. Nevertheless counting the buy one get one free (dine-in 2-5pm) deal it's really worth it and I recommend a try if you're an Indian cuisine lover.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvdd3ItBFpEwiw16ge8wvUUTHNiRqTMnQErq6_&fid=0x0:0xb7f0a68c89ea8418"],"When":"2024-4-9"}]
