[{"Name":"Max Voigt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJ7EG7NzgbGGtweKH_4cMuIzP7KBBqWZv2RDcRky6qogzA1mlT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly staff and prompt fast service. About 5mins after ordering food was at our table. Wonton soup, fried rice, chicken wings, fried noodle and green beans all dishes came out hot and tasty. Not Americanized Chinese food - which I would see as a good thing. Would come here again when our family does a trip to the area.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I really love their almond chicken, BBQ pork fried rice, and sweet and sour chicken balls. The breading is crisp, crunchy, flavorful and the meat is very tender, almost creamy. Serving sizes will leave you satisfied and not too full. Prices reasonable. I recommend for an after work dine-in!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHL0WOLHPvm8RLyH7HWc_IXC_3QA5DsEWaYSpn&fid=0x0:0xf1c9434b79ebe56e"],"When":"2023-1-12"},{"Name":"Geoff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIB7GO5SNpE1WIKMrtKsZatBr4-vjVP1je4zsiQTxeZeBqfyw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ive lived all over the lower mainland for over 50 years… and have had Chinese food from countless different establishments, but this was some of the worst Chinese food I've ever eaten. Poor quality ingredients and poor quality of taste. I really cannot think of another place that is this terrible","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Trevor W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyJ9v0nAxuFJWevbjIWIjM7AxUnw8p2XTyXFzmeKsiKCAZF4Nf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their BBQ pork fried rice is pretty good.  Sweet and sour pork, ya I will order it again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jen Olson Kurcz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJS-DSvDCCvB6r4JUDjb-1adsIMbJM3WQfNMZO6jkXwHbXDk4G6g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"When I ordered, I was told 25 minutes. I showed up 30 minutes later to get my food. An hour later, and I was still waiting there....bad service on a $100 order.

While I was waiting, a couple came in, ordered, had their soup, and were halfway through their entree. This was arpund 40-45 minutes after I placed my phone order.

After 70 minutes, I went up to the counter again (3rd time checking in with her), and she retrieved my food from the kitchen...and confirmed it had been there for a bit. A meek apology was offered, but that's all.

I brought my slightly cooled off food home. The fried rice, chicken chow mein, and green beans with beef were good. The szechuan beef and chicken snd broccoli were bland. They tasted like the already cooked veg and meat had been tossed with the sauce---not cooked with it. And our fortune cookies were stale. Bland as it was, we needed to eat.

It's not an experience we'd like to repeat.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPOs6IyUTfvHJeiY3XL9NZ-ZK-_IjGqPta4Qque&fid=0x0:0xf1c9434b79ebe56e"],"When":"2023-6-23"},{"Name":"Isela Galaviz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWp18vcoTvzvwDZAKZBhhxTSioNcKGzYMPItoc1q0S0-JFK7BHzlw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was so pleased to hear a lady coming into the place screaming “finally my favourite place!” And immediately having a good feeling about it that was successfully confirmed after trying one of their most popular dishes and the great refreshing ginger beer. If I would live there it will also be my favourite place!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjNg4AIs9VnvNgs_LRQB2cdWR9bVihNumcIGeC&fid=0x0:0xf1c9434b79ebe56e"],"When":"2022-8-30"},{"Name":"Parker Walsh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL51PSJQ0Ml87PlG5wU8AIkpKT9SdtcC6a0MWDC06P-NTkzrw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great classic Canadian Chinese food. Quick to answer the phone, upfront about time of delivery. Fair prices. Good portions. Tasty food.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"R B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL1uEfq0J-PcMkK-u2eTdRLVRlSVJ4sGA_fCeEivn83k6iKSQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The chicken in the cashew gai ding was unpalatable and we could not eat it. It was some kind of unidentifiable white mushy protein. It does not resemble, taste or feel like chicken. Maybe some way to get around higher chicken prices but this stuff was Absolutely disgusting. The vegetable dishes were delicious and well cooked but I would stay away from any kind of so called “chicken” on their menu","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Steven Legatto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8L2nKw1EPV1ph0AIhYhg-v_kV3CGDAO6pDONWluuSVXOOO3oo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always a positive experience at Freshslice Tsawwassen! Pizza is always fresh and made perfectly to order. Care given to each one made and never just thrown together. It is our go to local pizza as we love the thin crust. Excellent customer service and friendly staff. Recommend to anyone who wants high quality food at an affordable price!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMq_1pR_zAmi3xVw8g57F-exCdxJCpmf3vCcsxV\u0026fid=0x0:0x142d31aeefc8249b"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Louise Yeoh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKn6H1v99edwzRk8pxHxqcfGWgIZaHgZyHlx8FsGc__i8U2ig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were craving Fresh Slice Pizza so was thrilled to find one on Tsawwassen. Lady who took our order was excellent. She checked with us to make sure we were ok with every vegetable topping as we asked for all the vegetable toppings they had on our pizza . The place was spotless. Ingredients ok pizza was meticulously placed and not simply tossed or thrown in like some other pizza we had. It was clearly crafted well. When we had our fist few bites, we were blown away as to how good it was . Definitely the best pizza we have had in years ! Kudos to the lady who took our phone order and who prepared the pizzas 🍕! We found out she was the owner operator as she came out to talk to us when she saw us in the car. We will definitely be Back when we need our pizza fix.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBYqhpzobBFPp4Z8iaNG7-SJqqOXpt6vFSyfjU\u0026fid=0x0:0x142d31aeefc8249b"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've eaten here a lot of times. When the pizza is fresh it's crispy, savory and nice and gooey. Custom pizza or hot pizza slices are especially good and the crust is not greasy, it's more of a thin crispy cut. Love that they do sauce srizzles! It's not very tasty after it's cooled down and reheated but that's how most pizzas are.\nPrice is AMAZING and really affordable! Probably my second favorite local pizza place (sorry, I just love Domino's thicker saucier pizzas). From the times I've been in person, staff is always friendly and helpful. Much appreciated.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSYPZld3SUgQAeRGnpG6T1_qxrQ61j5pNzY6y_\u0026fid=0x0:0x142d31aeefc8249b"],"When":"2023-3-9"},{"Name":"Sukanya Pawar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4kOaZclz4KN-R_APgLcghAoA9eFA1A2nlgOtT-K0kDsFzkUs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have never been to a restaurant but we ordered food many times and the pizzas were awesome.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1GpP_T5T01fISc5yzdyOGzPvIBkAFyKtedt_q\u0026fid=0x0:0x142d31aeefc8249b"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"Tony Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPKcy0N8L_e03kCanD-kbqBYJvghgec1_Wu16Qs-S8YjI-PLg2nw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I've had their BCAA special, a few slices and a XL custom pizza before but Canada Day did something special to the crust because it was extra scrumptious. It wasn't just the 99 cents per slice deal but the pizza was really good. I really enjoyed the veggie slice and the messy BBQ Bacon Ranch slice. The crust was like the pan pizza style of Pizza Hut but not as oily. And there's plenty of toppings on each slice. If you like thin crust and everything on it then get the BCAA special. It's a great lunch deal with a drink too. And for those who love to save money, get a whole XL pizza for under $10 with the Too Good to Go app.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOS4BJzuCS6QGk3hfn_A_PUBl5sOeMWSGp2uSvR\u0026fid=0x0:0x142d31aeefc8249b"],"When":"2022-1-25"},{"Name":"Tony Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf8VP49ZjSvgG0JnhT1tc6Tv6OzLL9YEi_yNvwH1rW_K8-7VE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Dropped in for a quick lunch. As a BCAA member, ordered the medium pizza with unlimited toppings and a pop. Pizza was tasty but the crust was a little too thin for my liking. Not bad though as a quick bite. Tried to scan my rewards card and staff said the points will automatically be added. How? By osmosis?","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lily Lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqPSencBZNBBFb1e2yEiDotI5g1dHjC3MDcibVtf8WHyh0_YE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their staff is incredibly friendly and patient. The pizza is not only fresh but also delicious.👍🏻👍🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6bLePFz0Aj2l-QrREh2tpwcZgHGTVloqtVKD6\u0026fid=0x0:0x142d31aeefc8249b"],"When":"2024-1-28"},{"Name":"Dong Jie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3CmL7wFGWMMiSHLuMIkF-ihmj25L0MtNJmadZ7sDbcFdMJA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered a half half with half Italian half Vegetable, and a Chicken wing. The pizza was great. I can’t tell how great it was cuz my husband kept eating it until he ate the fourth slice and realized that there were only 2 slices left for me. He owes me another one. The wings were great, but I like it with less BBQ sauce. Will definitely order again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIYcKU-qCz663wYZqyLAcJnHXqGobI2TtGA7fB\u0026fid=0x0:0x142d31aeefc8249b"],"When":"2022-8-28"}]

[{"Name":"Jen Kormendy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJDQy6au_XJFirHmuHJJeHBCWgdDdXhrdIyUWojrjzVwcAyqrW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered an awesome vegetarian pizza with broccoli cheddar crust, pesto, sun dried tomatoes, feta, artichokes, red onion, mushrooms, and red peppers. Yum. Nice crispy edge on the crust. Only down side was a bit soggy in the middle but otherwise flavours were perfection. Great combo. Well done Madhouse!  Love the unlimited toppings.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKWcA0d2JlMOlS8bLK6DOwzSpikNORB0pD58nJ&fid=0x0:0xfc3d5a642f26c975"],"When":"2024-5-9"},{"Name":"Chloe Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUypilqaCfFTLWfsuXOd4-sGcdINssz2wFi1Ho6TDg_uSXZ1Rhx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stopped by this pizza place before we head to Centennial beach. Great pizza, my kids love it. Will come back again if we go to Centennial beach. Orders the hot and spicy and double pepperoni, both are yummy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2gbGmudXRL3hpkqBHZOHWha2bZku0Nbuvd1WL&fid=0x0:0xfc3d5a642f26c975"],"When":"2024-8-11"},{"Name":"Andy B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYThHxMVR-pDCIdsp2FkkxbU8XzRoahIp4Rt4mXZ7NqNtD7Awt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am not in the area often. Today I decided to see what the state of pizza was like in the area and boy am I glad I did. I have reviewed my share of pizza places and this one takes the pizza of the summer award.

Great staff! Great pizza! I liked the crust but I know that's subjective.

Anyways why are you sitting there reading this! Get down there and grab some of that golden goodness!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObnHcQuHSFQUmUa6cx5Tdsnb7cXVi7L_NHV9Cc&fid=0x0:0xfc3d5a642f26c975"],"When":"2023-9-15"},{"Name":"P.A. Arthur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuFuIHIFISprfe0xu5oX3MuI_Csn0eVniWo0yeAOYPWSf9tobd6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent pizza; fresh, quality ingredients and reasonably priced. Well run business with top shelf customer service and attentive and friendly management. 5 out of 5 stars ! I would give 6 stars if I could.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Taran Kh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLC5_Ff7sA2PVX3hAiefao95YsLLB-TQ8BUbvs4Cos-rOFVkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious pizza. Worth us making the 40 minute drive out just to get some! We love the hot and spicy with a little bit of house garlic ranch.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"neal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVBOqKYNOTPDyp3NyorVUvkkr5hrjPYOBxfhmnstSB9sVsYj7trg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Happened to be in Delta and was looking for a bite. Checked out Madhouse for a slice and boy am I glad I did. I think it has to be in the top 3 pizza joints in the lower mainland. The crust, the sauce and the generous fresh toppings all deserve 5 stars. They should consider franchising as it will beat the pants off the current offerings elsewhere. Next time I have a pizza craving, I may just have to drive the 30 minutes, it's that good. Good job Madhouse!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dave Chao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL544JfNo-heg8UsP95fr9shcrTY9pTTKZqcIgOMgLc7F2usw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I come in every once in a while for a quick slice of a tasty pizza. Very friendly and fast service. Warm and inviting aromas.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMUA82MUxu1NMARBYRFQNKuaeplHDlKqju2pkhS&fid=0x0:0xfc3d5a642f26c975"],"When":"2024-11-23"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came in today for a slice to go and was really impressed by how tasty their to go slices were! The atmosphere was welcoming and the person who served us was friendly and attentive. I just had to order delivery for later. They have a HUGE selection of very unique toppings, sauces and cheeses so I went a little crazy but oh my goodness it's delicious!! Probably my new fave! Very thick crust with extremely generous toppings. Loved the garlic sauce and steak topping. Thanks so much for the great dinner, I'll definitely be coming back. This place rocks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipORMtoE2Nvwq45PILc_i9l3IhoQaFiTcIvsG8pT&fid=0x0:0xfc3d5a642f26c975"],"When":"2023-6-11"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Grace An","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3EK2a7K177Sf6bXqILIYZjHE92GM9sTU9EFaLTvxP3GPOEiEz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of dining at Sushi Gurume with friends, and it was an extraordinary experience! We ordered the nigiri sushi, and it was nothing short of perfection. The fish was so fresh it practically melted in our mouths, and the flavors were out of this world. Every piece was beautifully crafted, a true work of art that tasted as incredible as it looked.

This is the kind of sushi that stays on your mind long after the meal—it’s that good. The ambiance of the restaurant was cozy and inviting, and the staff were friendly and attentive.

If you’re looking for the ultimate sushi experience, I highly recommend Sushi Gurume. I’m already counting down the days until my next visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJfnBmceB0HdPIGDit41xG2lBWK_5GH627yRYF&fid=0x0:0x167045d44866b380"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"Peter Estrada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVw52Fx60bw34dCukF0QbSF82RCB7ujq7YTAahYaTLdvpQbj8VVtg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Dropped in for lunch a few minutes before noon and was seated immediately. The server was friendly and welcoming. We ordered the sashimi salad, the teriyaki chicken lunch set, and the pork katsu lunch set. I am so impressed with the freshness and generous portions of the sashimi salad.   My wife and I agreed that the teriyaki chicken and the pork katsu sets were just ok. The pork katsu was thin, crunchy, but lacked seasoning. The agedashi tofu was bouncy and tasty. The gyoza was disappointing and lacking taste. Maybe we need to try other items. The miso soup was warm and could've been served hotter. Our server was the only one to handle the entire restaurant, which did create some delays for service. That won't stop me from coming back to try other items which I'm sure will be delicious. Lastly, the atmosphere is comfortable and it is nice to see they have private tatami style rooms for groups. Thank you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZf6LvPlaMH5cKx_97jL8MlcNfQaEu2aejFloZ&fid=0x0:0x167045d44866b380"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Min J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtIPeoqhkFl03jdSzCVlzaTMjgQGC_vY4FoHEuuXhMwN_H016i=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to Tsawwassen Mills and stopped by while looking for a nearby sushi place. It was more delicious and fresh than I expected, so I had a good time! My daughter told me that she’d like to come on her birthday again! May be…I could come again even thoght it takes 50mintutes to come. 😅😊😊

I have only this picture since we were busy to eat after this…","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNrdgK1xjsjDeRl55ENhw7Mt-WZ_FL3WDN7xO4&fid=0x0:0x167045d44866b380"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Joving Kalbo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPbEx34CDXynwER2kXZvyRmV5oUv-dwB_ke3K5wyO82u4FovkVqQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A good place to have your lunch. Reasonable price, good service, nice ambience. I ordered the katsudon lunch special. I will come back if ever im around the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSFSo47etpnxUgyBNJHGquc1iN3Ff7qF9oriuH&fid=0x0:0x167045d44866b380"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"angel lo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1IzL3-IELA7R7E3oFObEFF5jKqUJ8mIkFOIr338r21pBTPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a very nice sushi place in delta. They have the rolls called Tsawwassen Rolls, which has the yam on top, avocadoes in the middle, and made so delicious rolls.

They have the miso soup for the appetizer, and the bento box - sashmi box is a very nice one as well.

Love the saba grill, and is very yummy, plus not much bones, it is very good!

This is a recommended sushi place that if you go Tsawwassen for a visit!

Recommended","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDLuu1qFRY6bzgVQthTHqHPpvu_Hld3Svusgxz&fid=0x0:0x167045d44866b380"],"When":"2024-5-21"},{"Name":"eun hye Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKuoV9-0Xysj3Xql7Lq9Xfl97H18XSz78ZLoHXZi2XbWpVPCA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience ever! 대박! Can't believe its freshness. I've had rolls, sashimi, and other sushi plates so many times from different places, but I can tell this is the most amazing sushi place ever! Friendly staffs, great service, and fresh ingredients impressed me in so many ways.
I could see their passion which I really appreciate it!!(loved their deco on the sushi plate)
I STRONGLY recommend this sushi place ♡ thank you so much for your service today! Made our dinner so happy :) 감사합니다 :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0enbaunS_9KC1VSNJwc8BH0q2wyyq0mhZLKG2&fid=0x0:0x167045d44866b380"],"When":"2022-3-14"},{"Name":"Carmen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7_XzKFE0aHZ9ICJ3wvIpujcc7ckTtZQJfitcVujDUNzE7STI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came for dinner right before they closed last Friday. The staff were very attentive and friendly. Though they were taking their last tables they didn’t rush us. The food was delicious.  I’d like to say it was nice seeing staff work as a team. There were 3 girls out front serving and they deserve recognition for their work. Great job! I didn’t have a view of the chefs but I’m sure it was the same with them!  Very nice experience! Recommend 😁","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nancy Deol","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZcj0j-KSE8pJJOduKFby0tUkthuFEhXCa-SU3qKcHQl97zfn2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We waited quite a while for our order to be taken, despite the restaurant being relatively slow when we arrived. Our server seemed busy with other tables, and it took around 20 minutes before they took our order.

When our food arrived, only my meal came out, my partner’s order seemed to have been overlooked and arrived about 20 minutes later, so we ended up sharing my meal while waiting. We also noticed other tables, seated after us, receiving their food before us.

Additionally, we experienced the cooks openly yelling at the servers, which was uncomfortable to witness. It seemed inappropriate to handle this kind of conflict publicly, and it certainly affected the atmosphere and overall experience.

While I understand that delays can happen, this experience was quite disappointing on multiple levels.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"matt wagoner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjWROtGa0pMQvfSeeyAFH3Wd8YjoUYs1NCTbZYocCsIetg9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I'm not sure why this place gets high reviews,  it was not a good experience for us. The rolls were put together very poorly. Uneven height and falling apart / not wrapped properly. I don't really wanna eat at a sushi place where the chef can't even cut rolls evenly and wrap them tightly. The ingredients were fine but the way they made the rolls was actually kinda embarrassing. The staff was actually kinda rude in a weird way. Not saying goodbye when we said bye and being weirdly silent like a family member just died or something we're just passing through so I'm not sure if there's any good food in this town but there is not a chance we will be back","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cassandra Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgQLgSPpYH1f3LTRKfx7urUyWgCr7ATgQO4mDlzQtLR0Va18kn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice staff and very well presented and tasty sushi. My partner who doesn’t like fish enjoyed the spicy agedashi tofu very much! It had a different texture than other places we’ve been to. I am a raw fish fan and thoroughly enjoyed their rainbow roll, which was fresh and pleasant to the pallet. Would go again and try something more intriguing like the Toto Tower!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkbI0mbxdPCpSWWJ35sKB16R3gsPICSArYYYMZ&fid=0x0:0x706a70c1d2aab9a9"],"When":"2022-9-26"},{"Name":"Deanna Wallace","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKFhbpQidGlBQjnxU2xZT3hD9E8xBMnzWA_TWZY50WDGlCD6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is my favourite hidden gem when I’m passing through sunny Tsawwassen . The owner / sushi chef is a literal sushi artist ! She’s always so friendly and remembers my order ! The food is consistently fresh and you need to try the monster bites they are my favourite thing in the world ! Below is the monster bites and the tuna aburi roll 🥰 they have daily specials as well ! I guarantee you won’t be disappointed in this food ! The restaurant itself is small but it’s a homey feeling 🥰","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOoBA5X_WsDX5WnAfVqOP5M5LQERYval7ME_WDD&fid=0x0:0x706a70c1d2aab9a9"],"When":"2024-2-1"},{"Name":"Martin Jankowiak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_WSOO2iIt47NL02EctJZhW3XjqY-DdgYJoPsl9fCrFLxScj5K4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were in from out of town and craved sushi, and boy did we ever find a hidden gem!  Small and quaint, the food, atmosphere, service, and everything else were absolutely top-notch.  Very fresh and tasty food at a great value.  We will be going out of our way next time we're in town to come back for another meal.  If you want some great sushi, this is the place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCAcy5k1xHTEy8p2uxBZmFKOoFTS4QVjHepmks&fid=0x0:0x706a70c1d2aab9a9"],"When":"2023-12-21"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent food! Such attention to detail in presentation too! I had the Twwassen Set ($16.95) which included assorted Sashimi, California rolls, miso soup, ebi sunomono salad, beef teriyaki, rice, and assorted tempura.

Sashimi: fresh, clean, mellow, not fishy at all

Assorted Tempura: very good, crisp, flavorful, and delicious. Nice crunch factor

Beef terriyaki: just like Edo so average but fresh and good

Rice: nicely steamed, above average

Sunomono: tangy, done right

Miso Soup: generic but with added fresh soft tofu

Great lunch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7ZSjnkWhzfuqiN_m_9eLVemEspPl7cgdToJr2&fid=0x0:0x706a70c1d2aab9a9"],"When":"2021-7-28"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cozy decorated place. Presentation was lovely. I was craving tonkotsu ramen and they did not disappoint!! The pork was so soft and flavorful and the broth is creamy and subtle. Unagi, tamago and salmon were fresh. The roll was bursting with flavor. Croquettes were perfectly crunchy and crispy too. I definitely want to come back soon. Thanks for the great lunch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZKSuHvUfS6j5RSZBdb2BsUv271y9XnZWaBzED&fid=0x0:0x706a70c1d2aab9a9"],"When":"2023-1-14"},{"Name":"Steven","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwhlFiHPSDGYcBNEBZjiV401CUR-8LRwpy-nj0JN_nYZzCJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A small sushi place across from Tsawwassen Town Centre Mall. Seems to be family run. They are closed between 3-4pm for lunch break. The sushi is fresh and has some nice flavor and plating. Tried the monkey brain, a deep fried avocado with tuna and imitation crab appy - was pretty good. The toro sashimi was quite fresh. Some of their rolls do seem to be similar in terms of ingredients but they were good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPYk9xyJIUrpD5ViJUKFaw3tNKew17ZZSK_UiH&fid=0x0:0x706a70c1d2aab9a9"],"When":"2023-5-1"},{"Name":"Jaeger Mah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVt7hXDkFIcG6P61qcK0wBTq3t5gD1ANgzOWhiOupEWI1RBHtWj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very friendly staff. Sushi rolls were excelled. I found the chicken teriyaki a little soggy (I like it when there’s a crunch crust on the outside of the chicken). Over all it was a great experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMEj1Q8AyhiSrRIEr9hRdPBJ5RfnwJqWnO6PyWq&fid=0x0:0x706a70c1d2aab9a9"],"When":"2019-8-11"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Chris Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgN3Ssfvbb1EbijfsAqh9RD9v4HjU3iLte0juEBNWQn45kCyr6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Needed food, so I picked up a donair and fries to eat in line at the ferries. I sure am pleased with my choice to do so. The donair was packed with lamb and the typical donair wrap ingredients; I enjoyed this. Oh, but the fries! The fries are just crispy and pairs extremely well with the garlic sauce dip.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMy5vRnpRS8EjD-RwQ9FX3xrKjvxBOpHW2EqsPL\u0026fid=0x0:0xf5ba066a46548f4e"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Mike M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjCgzb0OJlXCk-WAK9SsEnf3vMl57FpIAZS92vCp5R8BGKs9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Small store but amazing donairs. Best on the West Coast. All the flavors enticing you to another bite. Very large portions if you get an extra meat option. This is the best donair west of Toronto. I am literally smiling from face to face. Don't wait to get to the ferries terminal  ,  stop two blocks away, and your taste buds will thank you forever. Authentic is a word I  don't use very often. This is the place for donair. Awesome food, friendly service, and your stomach and taste buds will love you longtime. The only affair I've ever had on my beautiful wife. I bite of yummynness. Love you and your company....God Bless","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwO2mphCWc71j3Bhk9cN6QqIUsp8BKXKz7av4\u0026fid=0x0:0xf5ba066a46548f4e"],"When":"2024-3-27"},{"Name":"Hayley Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbRZ5Wdk8dqms4dVpG-KvC0dBCKi_SRF-K3IwyxC-laGKk9_e0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All the staff there are friendly.\nThey made the best kebabs for our family. The best wrap kebab I've ever had! I always miss that place, because I stopped there while I was traveling.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8GoxyHx64EhXZ74voadITIdfG1ngiVxwLTINF\u0026fid=0x0:0xf5ba066a46548f4e"],"When":"2024-4-24"},{"Name":"Aaron MacEwen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3Ky6ximZkKg4l7lYD2oaitNzrrzF59AoquM1M8Z4is8xtKGnG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I mean I was working all day and starving.  So why not give a Donair some love.  Service was good your basic fast food.  Flavours were nice.  I’d go back for sure in a pinch.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"K M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJKXwHJh7B8P0DZJcmF7dG-ROfM4k02K_Xc5rcOlL5lGq_4wdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Huge portions for its amazing price. The food and sauces are very flavourful. The staff member helping us was friendly and tried to really engage with her customers to get to know them better and ask how their day was. Her cheerful personality and the amazing food deserves this 5 star rating!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOX1LTQ6F_DurKLX5SZSWFdKl3slxrtRWeoKj_f\u0026fid=0x0:0xf5ba066a46548f4e"],"When":"2020-12-23"},{"Name":"Chris Ericksen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViMdr5qANv3ULulQPLl_g1GGjwndbSbloLmalGzSvO7G73pBQY9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"May have an addiction to this place. The food is awesome. I have been ordering consistently now for about a year and a half. The staff are incredibly friendly and the management is also. I even used them for catering a large outdoor Dinner. I brought them my own catering dishes and other platters, and they were kind enough to put all of their food in them. Sauces and all other condiments were packed caringly in containers. Made the entire event a piece of cake. and most importantly, everybody loved the food.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"MiwitoLikes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9Cp-41jfC8lAGC19XcfHcrNAHhObunbBBMPLUw6S7yon19zyo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Better than any of the drive thru options around - especially since they open late night after long shifts! Solid and consistent portions - service is fast and friendly! One of my favourites to visit in Tsawwassen if you looking for clean food! 😎 rice platter or bowl with extra meat, wraps are easier on the go! 👍🏼👍🏼👍🏼😉","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nell Andrew","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3E0E3F9Zbk8X_ZsoD5u-iFtBxecstcnw5dTMU9Ep6bRtahXMn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The food here is great, don't get me wrong, but the service is very poor. It's a loud environment, so the employee misheard my order; I ordered the Hawaiian wrap and got a Mayan wrap. When I returned to ask about it, the employee very clearly established that it was my fault and they would not do anything about it. Really sucks, because this used to be my favourite spot and I'm back in town for a visit to get my favourite meal and got shafted.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Karen Castelino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7hhw7USB5QEJWbaxhDcx84xG1_szAmojdVvw-2W8v9vRmg6g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We just happened to stop here for a quick lunch and were warmly welcomed by the charming owner.

When taking our order, she warned us the food is already spicy, so perhaps choose a medium and she'd add extra spices on the side - she was right! And it was a great suggestion!

We tried the BBQ Pork Shewers and the Beef Pad Thai and both were delicious!

The Pork skewers were a generous portion, grilled perfectly and were slathered with delicious herbs! SO tasty!

The PAD Thai was very tasty, fresh and spicy and a large enough portion to share!

There is plenty of parking available, and if you are a plant lover, you're in for some eye candy here!

I was highly amused at the way the owner reserves her tables - she places plants all along the table!😁

This restaurant has charmed us and we'll be back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrZH94z6_q9cO5iRNUeMrsni7xGZ3nG64eShf_&fid=0x0:0x283647f8cd72e153"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Elmira Nazari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUS8psOPde-fgvVYsglTVKj-j9hpNdB1347mGr_T9d11yAStREO4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Overall highly recommended for the food. The service is fairly slow, so if you're going for a quick bite - reconsider. The red seafood curry and coconut rice was actually nearly out of this world. The papaya salad and crispy fried chicken were fresh, uniquely flavoured and great appetizer choices. The pineapple fried was alright, nothing special.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_cnwMIIY7cUyPrOKprynAav4yQke62Kk7Lsdb&fid=0x0:0x283647f8cd72e153"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"Ekaterina Spooner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDSglxx2dUJfzmltQnzShmE40EBsZJWhLxAmzj0Z87TKVqZdhB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We ordered pick up for the first time today. The food is delicious, but the wait is enormous! We waited 1,5 hours for our order. It is too long. I could have made it by myself faster. The service is not existent: there are two teenage girls on the front end who is arguing with customers trying to explain why the wait is so long, aka we have a lot of problems and it is your fault. There are lots of great restaurants in the area and I would not give this business a chance, unfortunately.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessie Vo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMevy9XgA4BcCLtVUMn6rX4-CsoOtL-AuhwLDVEclQDLN6HnO0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came here for lunch by recommendations from my coworkers. The owner greeted me with a friendly gesture when I walked in. I’ve tried several restaurants but Thai-Isaan is in a whole new level. Their Chicken Pad Thai is very flavourful. It’s a perfect combination of spicy and sour. Especially it’s not too oily. That’s exactly what I’m looking for. I tried their new fried chicken dish as well, and yes, it has to be a must try item because it’s so crunchy and delicious!!!!! I also overheard how the owner carefully gave instructions for TOGO dishes to another customer. I bet we all can see that she put tons of love and efforts to this place. Prices are absolutely affordable for good food and the services. I’ll definitely come back again!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMRQqAF_g0wZ1Y_1UYNxJww0XHpsIRejXDlZL6c&fid=0x0:0x283647f8cd72e153"],"When":"2023-10-12"},{"Name":"A P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKrx52nE6v95kIA5QUoIqBRqKszeGvzHBNs44ln2jwiBUdhmA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The food is delicious, that’s why we keep suffering through the service. Every few months we order take out from Thai Isaan (eating in is definitely not an option) and are reminded of why we never order from them. Called in an order at 5:29pm. 2 noodle dishes and spring rolls, nothing crazy. We were told to pick up in an hour. It’s now 7:10pm and I’m still sitting here. The 2 ladies working the counter have done nothing but apologize profusely to the 6 of us waiting at tables for our to-go food. Some of us have been here so long people are ordering beers. It’s wild how bad the service is, I haven’t a clue how this place makes any money. Please give yourself time if you’re planning a meal.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cassandra Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgQLgSPpYH1f3LTRKfx7urUyWgCr7ATgQO4mDlzQtLR0Va18kn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We came for the first time without reservations. Not busy but service is slow as they are a bit understaffed. Food was delicious - especially the eggplant pad and the bbq pork skewers! My partner liked the very hot level of spice - he said it’s enough heat without being painful haha. The coconut rice is tasty but may not be liked by some for its sweetness. Overall would order again. :) We ordered more than what we needed but it was so tasty we ate everything!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBi4mAH3mTmglxD5ePEnLvAPOx18o8OdS_22X2&fid=0x0:0x283647f8cd72e153"],"When":"2023-8-13"},{"Name":"Braden Hale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJfnv-j3IVdu4R9ihNCj1_rLpVLdnJ59yrLF3XHdG1ZlKBa_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I order from Thai-Isan rarely because I know the service is slow, but recently it has become inexcusable. Everytime I place a pickup order, the wait time is quoted at 45mins-1hour, but the food is never ready at that time. It will take at least 1hr and 30 mins, if not longer for the food to be ready. There either needs to be dramatic changes to the kitchen to improve the prep time or the service staff needs to be honest about the wait times. The food is good, but I avoid ordering from here because I now know the service is excruciatingly slow.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"J P Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVv-TZdheQ2KRgbv66PStcV7Bg2Aya6_K0c9TCrcSOX10hChF3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an amazing lunch here at this cozy Thai restaurant , food was authentic we ordered chicken lettuce wraps and Thai green curry with coconut rice","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNaYF4_Kbr-ZM1Tnic6wUt2OYfUBIxTU_Mg-nZY&fid=0x0:0x283647f8cd72e153"],"When":"2024-4-6"}]

[{"Name":"Jamie G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4K5nJ1yxY_yvRsH0bM-7wF3ZRgltXkRm5DubSyC4vqkn-2OW-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We got into town starving and I ordered from Pizza Factory based on the fact they were still open and the pictures on website looked more appetizing than the others.
I never order pizza because it always disappoints me and the family.
Well not these guys! The pizza was fantastic! Gooey. Cheesy, great toppings to sauce to dough-cheese ratio. When it got cold it was still great; meaning dough didn’t dry up and the left overs turn into cardboard.

If you’re looking for good zah, I highly recommend Pizza Factory in Tswassen.

More over, there was a mistake on their end for my online order and they were not only transparent about it but also fixed it and had the pizza delivered within 20min.

Support this business. They’re wonderful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULFs4uMqpehzBeGp8XHUvb6uZTSHxz0HmMZTQHlxvUx0atflM2Gw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Tsawwassen staple. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Thedishdetective Lala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKD_tj6k6xpF8R8uVmPtHQuGBgjvefVOKaKmqeE1mkWnmvdyA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Menbow Ramen Tsawwassen
5000 Canoe Pass Way, Delta, BC V4M 4G8

Nestled within the bustling Tsawwassen Mills Mall, Menbow Ramen offers a convenient spot for shoppers seeking a hearty meal. Located adjacent to the food court, this casual eatery presents a range of Japanese-inspired dishes with an emphasis on ramen.

Food

Takoyaki
Menbow’s takoyaki is a commendable starter. Served warm, the exterior is delicately crispy, while the inside retains a creamy, well-balanced texture. The flavor is satisfying, though not particularly distinctive. A reliable choice for takoyaki enthusiasts.
Rating: 7/10

Shoyu Ramen
The shoyu ramen delivers a robust, savory broth complemented by tender chashu slices. The portion size is generous, making it a comforting option. While it satisfies on all fronts, it doesn’t venture into memorable territory.
Rating: 7/10

Tantan Ramen
This tantan ramen impresses with its creamy broth and nutty undertones. The flavors are rich and balanced, though an extra touch of spice could have elevated the dish. It remains a solid pick for those seeking a slight kick.
Rating: 7/10

Mini Pork Rice Bowl
A standout on the menu, the mini pork rice bowl features succulent, well-seasoned pork paired with perfectly cooked rice. Its balance of textures and flavors makes it one of the more satisfying options.
Rating: 8/10

Deep-Fried Gyoza
Crisp and golden, the deep-fried gyoza is a dependable side dish. The filling is flavorful, though it doesn’t necessarily set itself apart from similar offerings elsewhere.
Rating: 7/10

Chicken Karaage
The chicken karaage, while adequately crispy, falls short of expectations. The seasoning lacks depth, leaving the dish somewhat underwhelming compared to other options on the menu.
Rating: 6/10

Ambiance

Menbow Ramen boasts a clean and modern interior that feels fresh and inviting. Despite being located in a busy mall, the restaurant offers a pleasant escape with its well-maintained space. The self-service kiosk system is intuitive and efficient, streamlining the ordering process.
Rating: 8/10

Service

Service is functional, with staff acknowledging customers without any particular warmth or attentiveness. While it meets basic expectations, the experience lacks the personalized touch that can elevate casual dining.
Rating: 7/10

Price

The pricing is fair and consistent with the portion sizes and quality of the food. Menbow Ramen offers good value for a quick and satisfying meal within a shopping mall setting.

Verdict

Menbow Ramen Tsawwassen offers a reliable dining experience for mall-goers seeking quality ramen and Japanese-inspired dishes. While it may not deliver standout culinary moments, it excels in convenience, cleanliness, and overall consistency. For shoppers in need of a quick, satisfying bite, Menbow Ramen is a commendable choice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdJppCTuFoOyKYEiGh_2mEUaLbU5wKqg1tPAIC&fid=0x0:0x5bc528369b8869b6"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"Tony Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf8VP49ZjSvgG0JnhT1tc6Tv6OzLL9YEi_yNvwH1rW_K8-7VE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"After seeing a 2.8 rating, I wanted to go back to Menbow Ramen to see if it deserved that rating or not. If you've been to Japan, you would have experienced ordering your food from a kiosk before sitting down in the restaurant. Thumbs up on that, except when you select the daily special, don't assume I want to order a drink. It's almost as though it is included in the price but it is not. Just don't pick anything and add to cart. I selected take out so when the food came, it was nicely packaged in a covered bowl. Thumbs up on the package. No instructions but its easy to figure it out. Just in case youre not sure, ask before you leave the restaurant. Today it was an Asian guy who served me. He was polite. Other times I've come here, it's been a caucasian lady. She was also pleasant. On their soft opening, there were two chefs. Perhaps they were working out the kinks and they weren't the best public facing individuals minding the store. The broth is delicious. Unlike a lot of ramen joints in Tokyo, the broth is not oily. You can drink it without worrying about the fat. They deserve 4 stars for the ramen. Don't order the chicken karaage. I agree, the taste is off. Squeeze some lemon on it or skip it altogether. And come on Tuesdays when extra noodles are free. If you want chicken, order the Tuesday $3.99 box at KFC. Now that's a finger lickin' deal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQvTTC8SI-gJTFkY2PqkcxYweO0hmwn1D--qFS&fid=0x0:0x5bc528369b8869b6"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"James Gonzales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0unpnU-8mggud0YcgWewTeEH_sT0-3Uzrhx_zm_qDfPS-Nug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"No more need to go to Vancouver for good ramen places as this has great tasting ramen! Ordered the Tonkotsu and it didn’t disappoint. Flavorful broth and good noodles and toppings. Will come back for sure. (Apologies for the photo as I only remembered to take a shot after having one slurp already).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDe10mPlKUouFZs-aytUyvCI5DjUJXMMu_6iAL&fid=0x0:0x5bc528369b8869b6"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"John Weng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKs_ZMy-V1LCA-1Oio_wWVYCOTAIusDw5J00NkliThxbDjhRA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"This is a mixed review, let’s starts with the positive: flavor is acceptable (tonkotsu broth), the place is will lit and looked tidy. Kiosk staff is friendly, the blackshirt(manager?) not so much. The “daily special ramen” which I assumed was some sort of generic sauce to water mix, was extremely salty. Me and my friend both took two bites and agreed it wasn’t paranoia. When we placed the unfinished bowl to the return shelf the kiosk staff asked how was it, I replied a tad salty, very salty. Then the manager overheard that and told me it was impossible because they didnt add soy sauce, and asked whether WE were the ones that added it ourselves. I said no, we never add sauce prior to tasting it as is, and I never claimed they added specifically soy sauce. Whatever they had in the broth was extremely salty. Manager doesn’t even apologize, I shook my head and said it’s alright, never mind and left.

So Mr black shirt whoever you are, you’re giving the staff a bad reputation, because frankly the other staffs are sympathetic and nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6M8dtndA01kooQurJPGx81psflGD5t_8lxU-C&fid=0x0:0x5bc528369b8869b6"],"When":"2024-8-11"},{"Name":"Dave","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_LjB1fIYfyDUjgL_-07doYO2DdqKnjIx6lTxP0wGruUckNw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I just visited this place today Dec 22th which is full of Christmas shopper. To be fair the service isn't bad but the wait time for the food took us half an hour (Miso / Shio and Tan Tan Ramen).

Seeing the review which is 2.8 out of 5 I wasn't have any high hopes of the food, but to my surprise, the ramen isn't that bad at all (Even consider as restaurant quality). Perhaps staffing level would needs to readjust during the holiday rush?","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ben Ho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHpMEx1fjmmf3AWQzf5DR-kr-pRDEx7TvKvnONf8OCMN1eqpeDFg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The worst miso ramen I have ever eaten. Don't waste money.

The cook is definitely not expected.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhABLVYP2IWOOTuSrHEeXd_jbKEzZxiME7wQo9&fid=0x0:0x5bc528369b8869b6"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The ramen here is amazing in my opinion! It's on the richer side, very hearty and big fatty melty pieces of pork, which I personally love. They have self service kiosks which is to my liking. I came back multiple times because I loved the ramen, and there's a lot of different flavors.
I liked the black garlic ramen, the tantan ramen and the spicy ramen. All are great though. Love the egg too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipORQey7vohNQFHHQLSqLm5JRVfdYgZ7nwoksz8s&fid=0x0:0x5bc528369b8869b6"],"When":"2024-1-11"},{"Name":"Mark Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCF24Za25W7mFVKPV1e78m89_C2VOF21rvAAzkauPiCAfdRgr9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I don’t understand the attitude of the manager here… If you dont like people, dont open a business... Taste? what did I expect.. Instant noodle taste better 😖","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVd0uUOwK7TS47oog7t01BOP6oWLvbXudoJu1j&fid=0x0:0x5bc528369b8869b6"],"When":"2024-9-15"}]

[{"Name":"prem Galsar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwPKhm383daEGJm6CHUM8xBELalENP-y6GUU5hbdhMohNKNfb7Gg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently checked out the new Quesada Burrito and Taco, and it’s a fantastic addition to the area. The moment you walk in, the bright decor and inviting atmosphere set the stage for a great meal.

The menu is impressive, with a variety of customizable options. I tried the chicken burrito, and it was delicious! The chicken was marinated perfectly, and the fresh toppings, including cilantro lime rice and zesty salsa, made every bite enjoyable.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwVWXgZ___jV62PquM4nkNcaqhlbTVLZmuCcn5&fid=0x0:0x9066322a0ca4ba96"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"Jennyfer Cassar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVd4aVfS8EqavvsCB7LHNP274bCbTusCOh-WoQpYXUzWRBRXZJq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dine in was great. They had more tables than chairs so we had to stand at the counter to eat but overall a great meal!

We enjoyed it so much that we ordered from their catering package for a family gathering. The 20 person build your own taco bar had EVERYTHING we needed to have a great meal. Everyone was incredibly happen with the options included in our kit. The price was very reasonable. Definitely recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kamlesh Galsar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXl1DcvrnNexhh8SbO-D3uTHBr4yBK8lVrcuLjFMvePBkTpPG2t=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"recently visited the new Quesada Burrito and Taco, and I was pleasantly surprised by this vibrant eatery. The menu features a wide array of customizable burritos, tacos, and bowls, catering to all taste preferences.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUpulog9dSkk4g4S7iXRtSld0foeNiSVpnVJX1&fid=0x0:0x9066322a0ca4ba96"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"Denise Rudsrin- Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhtHdsTvpcChvm08OaSdQ66X6CnWEAEQqKb3VF3zi5CMyLow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had our first take out from you on Thursday evening. My husband and I each had a burrito.
I had the regular and he had the large and they were  delicious and very generous servings. My husband and grandson were going out this evening and he stopped by this afternoon to het me a burrito for my dinner. We lucked out in that you were giving away free ones today! Mine was great and just the right size for me. Thank you so much we will be back again very soon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Danny Ng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPFpxTFJ3u9SzLCSXea0v-aXlg3umR59y0nfTLYbCzwas4amM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The service was good, and the staff were friendly and smiling throughout.

However, the food didn’t taste as good as other Quesada locations or like authentic Mexican cuisine.

The wraps were extremely small with less filling, and another star off for playing Indian music in a Mexican restaurant.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"steve “Steve here” garnier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8syJgHRb0oL04Zsxzk5A8o3zGjkPiKanrBaAkjiMlFwFoULbA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious!! Friendly staff and did I mention delicious?
Deffinately trust their judgement on the spicy stuff. I love spicy food but if I went any spicier than I did i would have been on fire. But there's lots to choose from that isn't spicy so just do your Thang and chow down.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aayush Patel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXT1j82owIGJV6XOggBZvgmDsG8dgpkOAMnq0GWY-8Avpx7Xs-t=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a great experience here. All the staff and everybody were good and polite towards us.

Food is amazing. Must try pickled onions on the burrito its the best part.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"July M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPev1MGk8g7gho65nL58g_fBB-niZ6_zdN_uI9W2I5IhKVkLnN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We visited Quesada Burritos and Tacos and were thrilled! We ordered quesadillas with beef and chicken, and they were incredibly delicious. The kids ate everything! The service was excellent and of high quality, everything was very fresh. Thank you for a great experience! Keep up the good work, and I will be a regular guest.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"C Pedrosa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcMDy4tMBdT1bu6DvBAjbPuH68jW3f1qeeNrDCc5DPFdSftMlu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I kept seeing ads for their steak and lobster , so we finally caved. We were the second couple to arrive a few minutes before 5 PM.
We got to order happy hour wings. I noted that our server was so personable.  The wings arrived really hot and they were really good.

Our main course was a bit disappointing though.
Spouse ordered the 10 oz steak cooked medium with fries and baked beans. The fries were hard and cold.

I ordered the steak cooked medium with lobster , coleslaw and baked potato. I opted for butter instead of sour cream. The baked potato was just that ! No bacon , no chives.

We did bring up the fact that the fries were cold and our server and the manager brought us a fresh batch of fries.

The dessert , Texas trash pie looked tempting so we ordered it as well. It’s too sweet and I wouldn’t order it again. The female server that brought our dessert to us didn’t even bother to ask or clear our plates. She just handed the plate to my spouse. Makes one wonder if she was ever trained to serve at a restaurant.

Her demeanor was such a contrast to our male server who was fantastic that I felt compelled to ask for his name. Matthais. He set the bar really high for the other servers in that restaurant.   They should all take pointers from him.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQgS89goYBvIEA4erL8B64IwP41D2hYPg-KXX7&fid=0x0:0x57f9d87194f4dd7f"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"Ching-Kai Chiu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGbYbS0ggvEFgjque4QRFtJ9y5gnvhUtfu0dvMbXF9kgoqrbF1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It is a good place to eat with kids. The kid meals there are valuable. My kid likes kid rib meal for 10CAD. It comes with a small drink, three pieces of ribs, apple slices, and a dessert. On Tuesday, I ordered tacos. With a drink order, each taco costs 5 CAD. It was a good deal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMFJVdTdlsiZPIYWtPZS_KJ_Lrfe-oeu2o-8kyN&fid=0x0:0x57f9d87194f4dd7f"],"When":"2024-11-15"},{"Name":"leesa tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWsWaHyhzcw7kKPh9V3HkvTK5TTa81TdmCDp9IylYllx4puXIy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Disappointed with the whole experience. Took over 30 minutes for each item to come after ordering. Server was a mess with forgetting our orders, than bringing us the wrong order e.g wrong sauce/flavour.

Our food must have sat at the counter for quite some time because our food was room temperature. I’ve never had a room temperature rib before, it was disappointing. Worse part was that the fries were so stale that we couldn’t even eat it.

Only thing that was good was the lobster spinach dip because it was fresh and hot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOof9qDhGlWOeCXq80fSsim8qsf7Tn95eDzkI8K&fid=0x0:0x57f9d87194f4dd7f"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Cannon Rowe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI14kY3cTXxkzCIBbkX1kFfvrwmLcetgnKrtLpCxa4s_TEwXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I had high hopes, but it all changed after I ordered, the first thing was that there were clumps of dirt or sand in my water, so I decided to order a drink, my friend did the same. after we got the drinks we had to mix them together because we ordered the same thing, yet one had way to much flavour to the point where it was hard to drink it because it was so sweet, and the other one tasted like they mushed a strawberry and threw it in water. Then when we got our food both of us got a small portion (4 wings and such) when I ordered a larger portion (more food in general) I didn't mind it or want to make a fuss, so I just ate it without saying anything. I want to give this a higher review as the cooks did an amazing job, however I will probably not return to Montanas again, especially this one.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPknbAgwk9uD3azZyveHSvnIriNYbOz_1062dCD&fid=0x0:0x57f9d87194f4dd7f"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"chaitanya gupta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWP-Cx-tNwiu90cNABgEGrEB8sTBdVTRvK_y-kZN0OvutQ-s073wg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Montana’s is an absolute gem when it comes to delivering mouth-watering, finger-licking good food! From the moment you step in, the welcoming atmosphere and rustic decor set the stage for an unforgettable dining experience. The real stars of the show, though, are the dishes that come out of their kitchen.

The Antojitos are nothing short of spectacular. Each bite is a burst of flavor, with perfectly spiced fillings wrapped in warm tortillas that are crispy on the outside and soft on the inside. They're served with a creamy dipping sauce that complements the spices beautifully, making it impossible to have just one.

And let's talk about the Cheesy Bread – a true indulgence for any cheese lover. The bread is baked to perfection, with a golden, crispy crust and a soft, airy interior. Each piece is generously topped with melted, gooey cheese that stretches delightfully with every bite. It's the kind of comfort food that keeps you coming back for more.

Montana’s has truly mastered the art of creating delicious, hearty food that leaves you craving for your next visit. Whether you're there for a casual meal or a special occasion, the Antojitos and Cheesy Bread are absolute must-tries. If you’re looking for a place that serves incredible food in a cozy, welcoming environment, Montana’s is the place to be!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNX0pDkwTuuiS5cMOpHrFRC97aT--PpFwztXTzh&fid=0x0:0x57f9d87194f4dd7f"],"When":"2024-8-3"},{"Name":"Pame Muñoz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWK-E6q_CKNcU5arueVpZB-EtqA-TtgCe6O8I-mSmV0JU1uRS3m=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The meal was fantastic - the nachos were absolutely delicious and definitely the best we've ever had. Additionally, the pork ribs were exceptionally good. The server attended to us with a pleasant and efficient manner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOm0M0pEL5v6RoJeh0VoGeXcbtNiwptyW0xcxq-&fid=0x0:0x57f9d87194f4dd7f"],"When":"2024-7-7"},{"Name":"Sam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtX0MUDjCE0-vy-dhnXmKj8wSFb2TYmOdItbTBVjUWBQi-9BN1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went for all you can eat ribs! Our server Matthais was super nice, easy to talk to and attentive! Ribs were really good, I really liked the coleslaw. I wish I took pictures of the ribs but when I went it was close to last call so I had to eat my money worth!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIGhMmyQR5fEQYPNmFQQ6jAf_8iCZTX8-Tw63p0QAlPVLS2Hw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Empty little joint. Went for lunch. Good value for kids. Burger was big for kids meal but dry, no sauce.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8qt4IIQnEDEbh33MxcT2oL1T62Sxen_DpS5Tt&fid=0x0:0x57f9d87194f4dd7f"],"When":"2024-10-24"}]

[{"Name":"Kamal Sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7ugyEGknBNNlILf31u0JAbmLdIgL4MRgEDpq5W7GHR4dnFqyK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst Indian food. Uncooked naan! And no matter what you order it’s the same thing just a tweak of different frozen sauce. I went there I was told it was Punjabi and I did confirm with the owner. I would say avoid this place or at least verify yr food. It was $60 waste and so the food ! Pleas don’t do this, the owner !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOxP-hRUwMAXpkUxqovjd8Fe-2PIDtZvThPE88g&fid=0x0:0x68c8a7d638fd7531"],"When":"2023-5-21"},{"Name":"Lei Ann Shiramizu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYUzucb7SgV-kpKbnzOX0XifHnp5tm5dLeArb4HjzF0s91w6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The mission of Connaught Place is simple: serve delicious, affordable food that guests will want to return to week after week. Mission accomplished.

I live in Seattle, so I'm a couple of hours away. But if I could, I would return week after week, and perhaps even day after day. Because coming to Connaught Place is like coming home, even if I'm not Indian.

After a long day of traveling from Salt Spring Island, we needed a quiet dinner to restore ourselves. I chose Connaught Place from the many positive reviews. We found the unassuming eatery tucked behind an office building and peered in the windows to see it empty. With trepidation, we approached the door just as a young woman was pulling up to pick up take out. I asked her how the food was and without hesitating, her face lit up and she said, "Oh my god, it's delicious! Plus, it's family owned and I love to support small business."

Enough said. We slid into a booth and was greeted by the lovely Satbir. She helped us (Indian-food novices), decide what to order based on our input: samosas, naan and lamb korma. She could tell we needed a little pick-me-up and kindly brought us papadum (a crispy wafer-like bread) with mango chutney.

The samosas were hot and tasty, however, the star of the table was the lamb korma. With generous chunks of tender lamb in a rich and creamy sauce, it was the stuff my dreams are made of. Accompanied by a hearty serving of rice, it was plenty for my husband and me. Even after we were satisfied, we kept on heaping food on our plate because we didn't want to miss out on one more bite.

While chatting with Satbir, we mentioned that it was our anniversary and she surprised us with scoops of mango ice cream! Just the thing to top off a memorable meal. We were definitely happy diners.

Throughout the evening, many people came and went from Connaught Place to pick up their to-go orders. But I suggest dining in the relaxing space because not only is the food superb, but Satbir is a delight, and an integral part of a wonderful experience. Oh, and you might want to order more than one main dish because you'll definitely want leftovers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwDP86BmOkutA77Dz0l0WGT6IKziVi7Vh0UKnH&fid=0x0:0x68c8a7d638fd7531"],"When":"2023-8-2"},{"Name":"Celestial Producer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLcwqfWl1gr39vLtzTdQX1KjMjQn0etzAzDHo-cF4Ad1jRuxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Fish Pakora ever and butter chicken ever...real spices...been coming here since they opened ...you can taste the love in their food...amazing family....who ever complains has no idea about food with amazing flavor or they get paid by the competition shame on you🤔 😋
Love you Connaught family xoxo 😘","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Abhinav Jindal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJM4oZCfhRvIsNadmGhYgIAN02ymUQqZkd-HEyw_g2b22BpSw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered Dal Maharani (Spice level hot) with Naans and Rotis, and it was really amazing. We got a really good portion of Dal (3 of us ate 2 rotis and 2 naans with it), which was surprising these days, but this is the first time I felt authenticity of Punjabi foods in BC. Also, the naans were so soft and not flaky like most of the restaurants these days. It definitely gave a vibe that they care about the food they serve, and I am definitely going to try out other items on their menu.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katie B Kohn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIblYPx-vTj1SiHiq7ul29XcTgXHp0t4YJvp8cUkuqUlix18g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Oh I so wanted this to be good. But I got three dishes and somehow there is *negative* flavor??? I’ve never had curry like this. All grease, no flavor whatsoever. Like none. I also worry a bit about the freshness! Never wasted $80 like this before.

Update: I truly can’t get over how bad this is. Worst takeout ive ever had in my life. Like dirty dishwater. Wish I could get my money back as I’m trashing everything.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patrick Burns","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAssgLe-So5tFzU6uhQzJF29bn_SiEFDR-ANfbxHT4XQ2Re0Cp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It was very good. The Dal was perfect, exactly what I was craving and as good as anywhere. I also got Tandoori Chicken which was very good as well. The Naan was very good. Very flavorful and delicious. The rice was good too.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexander Voogd","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaTUk3xqJzVvRr4_f1So4GR3nta8yXgA6objuo8ac7X7-7X3xvew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome food, we've been coming to Connaught for about 20 years now. Lovely husband and wife team running it. One of our friends we introduced to this restaurant,  an Indian food connoisseur, stated it to be the best she's ever had.
Please support our local people.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paula Jean Lloyd","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbZFu_mGLrykOVNo31ykayvJBF_JZRsYi8V16apprugDNNfg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We ordered. The food came way too spicy. They replaced it with something less than cooked. The service was terrible. Big mistake . This is my first negative review ever.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Shannon Blackmore","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ8pMnRNN5UQrJ1wUEsvfGgtB4YWU8h63doSSpRCEWSkRCEkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great lunch special, halibut and chips for 16$.

The fish was very well cooked with a nice light batter

The mushrooms were a little bit oily but still tasty.

Nice plain simple menu with a good variety.

Service was very good and a nice clean restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwG59doMXWvgobRzSTBtYJC0lmOZ1AX8SpgM8f&fid=0x0:0x1684471f6dd4a3c8"],"When":"2024-7-23"},{"Name":"Riley Ryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5qJQlQZUlr3T7tudhKtAZ_F4oZ6nPr_TS-zgoIXTeJwC3_w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love all the dishes that we’ve ordered.  Everything is very tasty and not greasy.  We loved the tartar sauce very much.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMer0OiZTes-_J6fGBvka3UDXWec8dsp_gto0Uj&fid=0x0:0x1684471f6dd4a3c8"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Eric Chand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIWwIbQtdY6WUaFS-i1AZmEc25ZCY0xVJCasCgn8djMLpSdWUMTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"WOULD NOT RECOMMEND!!, the service is super slow, we ordered took about 30min for the food to arrive.  Once we got the food it was overcooked, placed another order as we had the all you can eat thinking it would better than the last one, however which took more than 30 min again also overcooked. The waiter never comes to check if we needed anything or ask how the food is. I RATHER JUST GO TO MALL ACROSS THE STREET CUZ ANYTHING ELSE WOULD BE BETTER BECAUSE IT AINT WORTH IT HERE.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOEi3BiJQzZ95X4QIgF91ZOotocEobk-uXCU4OY&fid=0x0:0x1684471f6dd4a3c8"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"Jay L.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCQoS8NlWNxDjO6o3kh2TYTZ28b3n0ueXzOO3bzkd8cLzLiA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently tried Harry’s Fish and Chips and thoroughly enjoyed it.   I couldn’t resist trying their new all-you-can-eat option, and it did not disappoint. The fish was crispy and flaky, while the fries were just right — crispy on the outside and fluffy inside.

The staff were very friendly, adding to the overall enjoyable experience. If you’re in the mood for great fish and chips, definitely check out Harry’s!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jordan Martin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUCr0tr9YlhzAUVvUDA0uh1N_E9-qD-QRXTWP98RAIztJCmEjV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food gets 5 stars while the service was very slow.

I do NOT like fish and chips. Honestly, I think the vast majority of fish and chips are bland and rather sad. However, anything made well can overturn that sweeping generalization. And I am proud to say that of all the fish and chips I've had that Harry's  is worth it. The fish is perfect. I highly recommend the haddock. The batter is thin, crispy, well seasoned. Not too oily. The chips are great. The tartar sauce is excellent.

The curry sauce was very disappointing. It tastes like some cheap powdered Curry sauce and I feel if they put the same love into it as the rest of the stuff, it would be a knock out. But most importantly, Harry's does what a fish and chips place should do well.... The fish and the chips.  Having eaten fish and chips on white rock, steveston, Granville Island, Melbourne and across numerous other places, the batter is always too thick so it gets soggy quick or overpowers the fish or is thick and soaked with oil and grease or it is just plain underseaoned which often seems to be the case in The Vancouver area. An aversion to seasoning. Harry's gets it right.

It took almost 40 mins to get food while there were only 4 other tables there so that is a negative and they never checked on us to say that the food was going to take a while. So the girl working the front should have been a little more proactive. We happened to be in a particularly patient mood that day so we waited without saying anything.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"G. Thandi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKK0fbTfKn4oJsVqGQVuttQWILwxEXzV2YpkNcaTKaWAeczLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Harry’s fish n’ chips took me straight back to the UK! The fish was perfectly crispy on the outside, light and flaky inside – delicious. The thick-cut chips were golden and just the right kind of soft. Plus, the service was spot-on, with a warm, welcoming vibe that makes you feel right at home. If you’re craving a taste of classic British fish n’ chips, Harry’s is the place to go!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sofi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-opTzuNthCUcMRRjR05ACdKoDeruLOEirZI-e_FPMXXNiFXs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Unimpressive! Our first time at Harry’s Fish & Chips, sent my mister there to pickup our dinner after off the phone with a lady about substitutes 1 of the fries for yams and pay $3 different. The man took the orders for a 6 pieces Cod Family Meals, but refused to honour the substitutions and charged us a full price for a full yam order instead! The order wrapped as 3 separated of 2 pieces fish & chips orders. The L (Large) coleslaw was really tiny, like 3 tablespoons, more like a portion for 1 person. The tartar sauce is like 2 tablespoons, which barely enough for even 3 pieces of fishes. The foods were decent taste, fish on a bit small sizes, good size chips. Overall, had a much better experience at other restaurants with taste, portions, and prices!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMFLoMR_ci6MCXyfeOUOzz_S4BNwdCzsCcuSmdf&fid=0x0:0x1684471f6dd4a3c8"],"When":"2024-3-30"},{"Name":"jeeven chatha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLBfOmzwVZ3U-hOgo89yBurBlrS_c8n4XH7loEzGr4XL0cCVA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Harry’s Fish and Chips is hands down the best place to get your fish fix. The halibut is beyond amazing—perfectly cooked, crispy on the outside, and tender inside. The in-house tartar sauce takes everything to the next level, with a fresh and tangy flavor that complements the fish perfectly. The fries are spot on, crispy yet fluffy. If you’re looking for top-quality fish and chips, this is the spot. I’ll definitely be coming back for more!","Images":null,"When":""}]
