They only had two employees there… and a big line. Managers, staff better. There ended up being a wait for the food, but the staff was hustling and doing the best they could so.\n\nI was really happy with the food. I had the pad Thai with crispy beef. Really good amount of food, lots of beef… super hot even after I took it home… tasted great. Great option other than a burger for fast food. Will be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZqojHpJ10wLJu6qR_w5x34sqE6cIjFNJUHow9\u0026fid=0x0:0xc433e8ca3cb8209a"],"When":"2024-9-25"},{"Name":"Laura Elout","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBg9fHbXsEgZIbtE51F5pT8QP7WuFEjNo377sVa8SK0tKVAFPE_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my first time going to the Noodle Box. I had the crispy ginger beef with jasmine rice. Sooo delicious!  Such an extremely clean and welcoming atmosphere. The customer service was top notch. Rajveer spent time with me to make sure I was comfortable with the spice level.  He also walked me through the various noodles I could order with the crispy ginger beef.  There is also a section you can sit at and watch them cook your food.   All in all it was a 10/10 experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJ-i-oynVy2lkI8uRI6XSUo3HT7p3Tpo6wcVDm\u0026fid=0x0:0xc433e8ca3cb8209a"],"When":"2024-8-18"},{"Name":"Jen Jackson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuWBLOHPAK5UtFjqk_k6fMLzerE_c_s_XiTG4Zrf9vrRFSamxh=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Have visited this location several times with a good experience but today was terrible. We got the Szechwan bowl and the Drunken Noodle along with some add ons. The Szechwan bowl had a very off-putting sweet flavor and the Drunken Noodle was incredibly bland and boring. The “crispy beef” breading was soggy and like chewing leather when you bite into it. Order very carefully if you choose to eat here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZxkLU6IBCoDiwHbAlYqENRFHGAuAKIcRwpCE_\u0026fid=0x0:0xc433e8ca3cb8209a"],"When":"2024-9-7"},{"Name":"Jesse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSDyGy576NjOpFot9rCBdIpO7u4qZP6Qzr6EXuEXmqpkbcdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"What a disgusting bowl of slop they just sold me.  I can’t believe the difference between what the food looks like on the menu and what they really serve you.  Looks at these pictures.  Absolutely disgusting!!!  You can see in the pictures what they say it looks like and what it really looks like.  Just drowning is sauce.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObwTgj5Vd5_vo7C63SPd24uM33DBQRV_JEUZx7\u0026fid=0x0:0xc433e8ca3cb8209a"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"WWG.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUn78hs1gyPa62w7hNh3K-ZPDxvzydvZVSMCMdGqbbmzV7yyzWs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience here tonight. Greeted with great customer service, food was fast and delicious. Drowning in sauce, but thats what I like. Its quite pricey, but its nice and fresh, if noodle box is what you're craving, this will hit the spot. Bathrooms are clean and the restaurant is comfortable enough to sit in and eat in peace. Will be back again. Thanks guys,","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Percy, Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6g-5jtl_Yq69yPlFaWbeURqM1ztOJz4LoJ0yyO10RQF78nmU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I've visited this place a few times and let me tell you, it's like a circus! The cashier must have taken a crash course in how to mess up orders. And don't get me started on the kitchen lady who keeps running in and out, asking the cashier what to cook. She's so forgetful, she probably forgets her own name! Oh, and the way they handle bowl plates? It's like they're playing a dangerous game of finger gymnastics( at least one finger on the inside of tue food bowl..)It's a total disaster in there, like Hurricane Katrina decided to take up a part-time job at a Noodlebox. IMO you'll be entertained, but maybe not satisfied.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfMDL4djEjVLA9gh3mglu2WgIJbFso4SrMHI0D\u0026fid=0x0:0xc433e8ca3cb8209a"],"When":"2024-7-8"},{"Name":"Parmeet Purba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXhlsGn1AoGnvIIKAlg5yFw8KkhjG6wGTUx6oDOLQVly7nMw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Noodle Box is a fantastic spot for delicious noodle dishes with a variety of options that are full of fresh ingredients and authentic flavors. The stir-fried noodles I had were perfectly cooked and well-seasoned, with generous portions that left me satisfied. The friendly staff and cozy atmosphere made the experience even better. With reasonable prices and top-notch food, Noodle Box is a place I'll definitely visit again and recommend to others.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"steve little","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlSOwLtsdW6HTUdAZldoZAZJsuN6EjI7Iqigq7alDR3a1n3iOp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was delightfully pleased with the food. Lots of taste or flavor. Delicious! We asked for extra crispy tofu, and it was done perfectly. It’s a kind of a fast food atmosphere but super clean and pleasant server.  We’ll be back for sure.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"James","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7dYAF0BBmR0pl-gZdCg6QNbyBu-6C9pD1ZiWYuTCPpcwlwUU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today, my family and I visited Mucho Burrito and had a fantastic experience. Kuldeep and Twinkle, made our visit even better. We ordered the Mucho-sized chicken burrito, which was delicious—juicy, perfectly seasoned chicken with a mild kick. We also enjoyed the tacos and a bowl. Last Saturday, I tried the chicken and chorizo burrito alone and loved it so much that’s why, I brought my family this time!☺️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfruxUIoYW3Vsc2IALhafElf4oyWSaLD2xaFp_&fid=0x0:0x348601124d1e0e1f"],"When":"2024-12-1"},{"Name":"J P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPNOwczxQeYq8Qup51h2PTCgzkWZZqiOeXeOFsoHWK1IWAROM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ate here on Saturday June 8th for the first time, had heard of Mucho Burrito but wasn’t aware that they offer plant-based protein options. There are also no locations near where we live, since we were shopping here, we decided to try it out. Overall very happy with the food, service and ambience, 100% recommend you visit this location if you are anywhere near the area.

The interior decor is really nice and welcoming, restaurant seats 30-40 people, lots of seating options from regular tables to couches, booths and one high table. We were greeted by the employee behind the counter. We used the app to place our order and it was a very smooth experience but also could have ordered in-store.

The burrito was 10/10. The portion was generous, the food was very flavourful and the ingredients looked so fresh. In fact the staff was preparing some meat and vegetables on the grill behind the counter when we came in.

The bathrooms were clean too and the service from Twinkle was fantastic.

Overall, this location of Mucho Burrito blew our expectations and left us with a very good taste. I hope this location gets a lot more business when customers see the incredible value they offer.

I consider myself a fairly tough critic but the entire experience at Mucho Burrito was a 10/10.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkNzurAX4BewBCOI3MbxFxEJwZDGRJI3MPXXay&fid=0x0:0x348601124d1e0e1f"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Wild Wanderlust Photography","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYPQeHy2fRvptt6V1NtTq0t9CdOFiP_rQd_Emm8iYNczU9hCDSwA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just love their monster burritos! Man they are huge!!! It's like a fast food dining experience, as in the atmosphere....BUT it's cozy enough and you're there for the food ..not fancy ambiance. Get the faint burrito....with all the toppings, you won't be sorry!!! Hot sauces and Deliciousness.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kenneth Lai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaxVGYXfpPoTmAfNhLJtbs31BGbuX8DK_7Hj5GOcCBNwv8VjrvXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Mucho Burrito Fresh Mexican offers an exceptional dining experience with its use of fresh ingredients. The vegan tacos are a standout, bursting with flavor and freshness. The service is top-notch, with friendly and attentive staff making you feel welcome. The cozy environment adds to the overall charm, making it a perfect spot for a relaxed meal. Highly recommend for anyone looking for delicious, fresh Mexican cuisine!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCwRRBBDkCy2RT5gpqg07FY6naonO6J86dZSL_&fid=0x0:0x348601124d1e0e1f"],"When":"2024-5-21"},{"Name":"Jared Woolgar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8ioo_99XbpSJIRyn9cRIyf71-v-U8Jja7KTwBzGJjWmOo4_-J=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is delicious and you actually get alot if you order a regular burrito 🌯  which is really nice. [{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Expensive food for portion size, not really worth it for fast food Greek food. Best part of the chicken souvlaki platter was probably the bread that came with it that was seasoned well. Service was ok, they made the plate on the spot and it didn’t take too long. Plate was filled but mostly carbs and one chicken souvlaki.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3TuTi-MrebOogPIkG7ATjJANNTU8HMDwb2fbG&fid=0x0:0x21b1f23020283612"],"When":"2024-9-17"},{"Name":"Jong Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsj66d8DdmBbxiBfPXwcsaGu37_5Q5dlKhqvY11hATgPvGuCHOqw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Fries were good and cooked to order with yummy saice. Nice people working there, but the pita is very very thick and the meat was too thick and over cooked. Greek salad was hand tossed and fresh.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2ND3brPZ6aEQHSKJMzgly2xbtY-Zrr0WOaAYJ&fid=0x0:0x21b1f23020283612"],"When":"2024-7-3"},{"Name":"Fuzzy Nemo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMhjGNDhI-RZYgIiVRXnRDEQCiyyP-dsVjb7EhBkcymNr9MvYi0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I have visited many Opa's and it has always been my go to when in a food court that has one.  The experience was disappointing to me.

I had ordered a meal, the menu said it was an additional $2.69 for a drink.   I was shown the bottle drinks and was never given the option of the fountain drinks, so when I ordered the bottled cranberry juice, it was an extra $3.49 plus 10 cents bottle deposit.  No one told me about the extra charge for the bottle drinks.  That's misleading.

I was told to stand in the back to wait for my order, while everyone else was congregating with their trays right on the counter, so when my number was called, someone almost took my food, because they didn't check the number and just handed the food off.

The food was rather bland.  I had the calamari with a Santorini Salad.  There was no seasoning at all on the Calamari or the salad.  For the most part, it was tasteless.

I never knew ordering food in a food court was so stressful.   First you have to question if they overcharge, then you have to fight over people to get your food. Would I come back?  I highly doubt it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBYQx_INXBRS0ZUU6gCvcO81jk4jjjBEeXrmC2&fid=0x0:0x21b1f23020283612"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"E. Ho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWapxfDmUmneoBwxC1ihDSroK6TaIbvpgMe2GHZhKT4HcESHYsOew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Whenever I come to Tsawwassen Mills, I always grab a pita wrap from Opa. Amongst all the other options at the food hall,  Opa's selection is probably the healthiest. The pita feast has decent Caesar salad, freshly fried fries. Not bad for mall food. Avoid the baklava, however. it's soggy and not fresh, not the crispy mouth feel that we associate this dessert with!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBolG1Xh61aMYOj-APN4DNpKNTDeOX0ahDd7uZ&fid=0x0:0x21b1f23020283612"],"When":"2024-9-27"},{"Name":"Shery On The Move","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmAA3VItm5d-LzZjMzSS_FZs12aHSse1X5w-nXQqVmdbUvhBBJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I always come to Opa and order Calamari with ceaser salad. Greet service by staff. Keep up the good work..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNT8V2vU8G123IfWESUIjfsU4jL9Wlf4ALdPJZ7&fid=0x0:0x21b1f23020283612"],"When":"2024-5-31"},{"Name":"MRD","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVs3AD8byZ8WbxiDuCx06SKC6vjPah01MHg0pn3mF9O-9tEU3xDhA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent food great company!
Like any food service PH is very important! I saw complaint about miss handling food... believe me unfortunately it's happen specifically with FAST FOOD!
SOLUTION: Managers to supervise
Company to have a training procedure with test! And  a mandatory Food an Safe certificate.
Otherwise great food booth and tasty products
Thanks","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pretty tasty! Hot and fresh, especially the falafels and the pita. Nothing like a hot pita with a crispy exterior and soft interior. Don't sleep on this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMepCU_rsrC2zYXyIlSCqZjztNN8x8EyBgrwxvz&fid=0x0:0x21b1f23020283612"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Edward Solidon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4ufShUKSB1-h0YAcv0VpNQPhvTLBKv4_mVr-YY2o5jHLNNg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Small portion sizes for the price as others have stated. I had the olympus bowl with falafels and fries as a base. For $3+ more than the fry bowl you get 4 tiny falafels. The kind you get frozen at the supermarket.","Images":null,"When":""}]

I know everyone has it’s own issues in life but the staff looks so miserable, nit a smile and not even asking. I know what I want but regardless, there is no service at all. Not going for food in this place again. I do not recommend to anyone.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJBqS1FWuAvlKA7mRPTiCWyyz2nPUjrPYjqmcM\u0026fid=0x0:0x2f5507b307d0fc60"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Spring Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMOpz_v4ssMlsZT_0g7sOO22cdL07mWO_x_lTFjjkEzlY4vg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Hire friendly staff please. Otherwise, they will ruin the customer relationship. There are lots of completion and returning customers to the mall. It’s wise to provide a reasonable service to retain the customers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gray K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV197eijb-A_qK8hlE7t9HqXjATzfzrWhoWXPAMMrhYqayE25D8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The lady who usually works here (everytime ive been there) is an absolutely pure and an kind soul. I really enjoy when she is working. Also this pho is great, the 1 star reviews must have gotten extremely unlucky. Anyways that is my 2 cents. Thank you kind pho person! PS. Order extra meat you will not be disappointed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Taz C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ235c-1POJF85QGI4N_CFSzUmrADwRBXdKObCvBIDceTrCYTc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"2 stars for food and 0 for service. We have eaten here a few times when they first opened. The portion size was decent and the food was average. I happened to be at the mall twice in a a row recently and was craving lemon grass chicken. The first time, as I approached the place, the lady at the front was busy doing something, she saw me but didn't bother acknowledge me and continued to do her thing at the other end. After about a minute, I had lost patience and was just about to leave, and she came over to the ordering side and just stood there. Still no acknowledgment. I said hi and proceeded to place my order and the lady just stared at me. I thought perhaps she didn't hear me, so I repeated my order. She just looked at me and said \"No\". Not understanding what the no meant, Im looking for some details, she just walked away. What a bizarre experience. Lol\nThe following day, we ended up ordering the lemongrass chicken meal. This time it was served by the tall guy who I've seen there since day 1. He was nice enough but the food was really bad. The noodles were overcooked and soggy. The chicken barely warm (instead of keeping directly on the warmer, the chicken was in a bowl on top of the warmer - this is also a food safety issue). Thoroughly disappointed by this location. Will definitely not be going back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9E1dVo1F8b6a_tyPYVZx7_X6zLjg_6kXo6Lhp\u0026fid=0x0:0x2f5507b307d0fc60"],"When":"2019-11-19"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got food here and a drink at freshly squeezed. The cashier was very friendly and the lemongrass pork is so yummy. I'm not entirely sure what the food on the top is (it's like a crispy roll with meat inside) but it's amazing and flavorful. I love it 😁 And thoughtful of them to include water!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTxbq6qLOFOG7kPvY3aWYQj-j3VpR0MJbRuLUy\u0026fid=0x0:0x2f5507b307d0fc60"],"When":"2022-5-28"},{"Name":"Martin V.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHUWeLQtzrLwznxOz1qtEg2BlpBpzkU8Lx0nL6UaQRn9ju0mbz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Not only quality of the chicken is down, now even the portion is half size what it used to be!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOaqC7D4F_4mJnvi6_4IgMJBFEWpYlZ3sGpoGUa\u0026fid=0x0:0x2f5507b307d0fc60"],"When":"2024-7-16"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Michael Lacson Ello","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJus38Jm8x4a4FpscwrnNrQTjVBeHPRdqtc6sWQWa80xSZEdw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The taste of the food was great , the portion of food per order is amazing, packaging was ok , price is reasonable and affordable, service is excellent the Filipina lady works so fast and very friendly but needed a little bit more smile and I know she’s already tired and it got busy when I place my order that’s why she can’t smile anymore and I can see that she’s working with the new staff I overheard that she’s doing training for the new staff because of that good job . I didn’t have 5 star for now because the consistency of the quality and texture of the food is failed for me because I got the newly cooked fried rice some of the rice was still hard and it needed little more time to cooked well before serving to all the guest second the spicy chicken that I got is hard to chew it’s little bit chewy and some hard as well then the rest everything was ok but

I still definitely recommended to everyone to visit this branch in Tsawwassen Mill to taste their lots of different varieties of food it’s affordable and delicious. 👍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWIrBC170gEsNzs_NQCvpebQNR22-pWbSeQuae&fid=0x0:0x2258541a2226475e"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"No MSG No Garlic Foodie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-PVOn6GcWxsKb-qqVJDTqvJ5rfua5QVuFocwcMF-ZRwuEIPLm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We first encountered Bourbon Street Grill in Richmond Centre. I couldn't believe it when they told me that they don't use MSG in their food. And they have my favourite food – BBQ chicken, BBQ pork, fried noodles, and of course mixed vegetables. However, we discovered that there is a catch – chopped garlic is as common an ingredient as salt, and there's garlic in everything. But if we wanted to eat a balanced meal with a decent amount of cooked vegetables, that's what's available. We stopped by the mill before heading out to the ferry to grab a bite to eat. I was going to have a simple Chachi's sandwich but would prefer more vegetables, and Bourbon Street Grill is the next stall. But the food was almost not edible because of the amount of salt in the food. I ate less than half and left the rest. We've since gone back again in case there was a different cook. But same thing, the honey mustard chicken was over-spiced and everything was too salty. Even our friend who lives locally and is a fan of Bourbon Street Grill is not keen to visit this particular outlet. I do wonder if that's the reason they are not that busy!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMp2LX-PWUjs1v1GYVHpQW7qQHdPLFe25EuezSF&fid=0x0:0x2258541a2226475e"],"When":"2023-7-11"},{"Name":"Sukh jas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdZXO1s-FXEoal1FhYT-Pim0I2Ssia3Zer5WEGjGTRrnjXDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"rice was mixed with day old rice. The chicken was Dried up. This place is not good. I informed the manager that the rice almost broke my tooth it was that hard. I suggested to her to through out the rice but she said it was fresh. I did not ask for money back but rather get rid of the bad food and she would not. I told her you can not feed this to the public. She kept on selling it. I will never go back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"J Doyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPPny9TtiK51znrVGw_mfnuA8ZqG4xTW9w4c-Vn42z-UkUntwsVg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We are from up north, decided to stop in quickly for a bite to eat. Will definitely visit here again 🤗","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harjeet.S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMJKeEpZcaNiEgRHVKJzDta4pG1eiEwuO7xb_vw9gFztG2SA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Not tasty food, bad service. Ordered the Big Splash Hamburger with lettuce, onions and tomato. Want cheese? Add $2. (Not today).

Does it come with a drink and fries? No

They cost extra. That’s how money is made.

Burger was pretty much Costco Kirkland burgers. Nice bun, but pretty basic. I ordered onion rings which was super greasy but fried good.

I watch two young adults working while waiting for my burger. One girl was filling up dressing into little plastic cups while another was arranging salad. They both looked miserable which made the food miserable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Barista Okina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUjOvY2uGwjb3KxDPyohnKw7C1DrN_aYzj47PSJi2rpbAz4nCj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The pizza was amazingly good!

The receipt numbers are different for each till,so the staff said that the ticket number wasn't a good way of measuring when your food will come. When I asked what was taking so long, they told us that they were waiting for a restock of hot dogs to come in before handling our order and that I could come later to pick it up. This should bring many red flags about the service here.

1) They sold hot dogs even though they were out of stock.
2) They decided to put aside the order instead of informing the customer that there was no stock.
--- I watched my order get covered on their paper list by another order.

I was able to get a refund for the hot dog in the end, but overall the experience was horrible and there was no order management at all, causing other customers to be angry as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"R M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJeUNTo22HXcXcBqqYyA3eUx0AaUrAskGeQeDhJqwTSM8q6pw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What can I say... Service was very slow looks like they don’t care if their customers will wait very long time
- food prices was ok and it’s not bad it’s affordable and reasonable price.
The atmosphere of the store was ok but their dining table some are dirty and their floor was so sticky

I will definitely not coming back again and I will surely not going to recommend to all food lovers this location .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMzpQftR4GQBydJfm0UwflChL9gVrw3XsK1A1Kx&fid=0x0:0xfe08ab308275d736"],"When":"2024-11-27"},{"Name":"Emma Kirby","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLUCBRFq35cMp6DuUPjCYr3huuvOvq9FOWwaORU024UlktyAg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Will not eat at the Tsawwassen location again. Wendys lover since forever, ordered food there last night. Ordered two double JBC, and two large fries, received 2 single JBC, and the fries tasted like mould. Very disappointed. My child who loves fries ate one, and wouldn't touch another. Threw them away.
It really turned me off ever going back to this location ever. Lost loyal customer.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Grant Joseph","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzfLTwRDWmiz8P9LraNx0eAs71Icdpz_urWQcsKQbeeFTpgagY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This Wendy’s location was filthy, there were FLIES in the dining area. The dining area was not kept clean at all, the tables had garbage on them from previous customers. There was also a toaster on one of the dining tables, like why keep kitchen appliances in the dining area? The garbage cans were overflowing, could barely put my garbage in. There was a spill near the soda fountain that they didn’t deal with, they just put a slippery floor sign up. There was food on the floor as well, also didn’t get cleaned up. The food wasn’t bad though, but what’s the food worth if a fly lands on it or if you can’t dine on a clean table. Do not eat here it is disgusting.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWOq3mwjGYnGmTgvXRLyaNX2PQvIpM-xeegeCw&fid=0x0:0xfe08ab308275d736"],"When":"2023-9-2"},{"Name":"richard edmonds","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRhBtL8rhQt1wza-QsGoceLRjvJAB2Cb0mFy_W_X_-XGKGMA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Don't eat a ton of fast food but Wendy's is the choice when on the run. Stay away from this location, if anything they are reliably bad.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wayne Lav","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUk880jfctdjiDn4tRAvocN5rCVUdtgArCHWFDiv2yxg-QvIz4L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Quick drive thru service. I can't remember the last time I had to wait for my burger to cool down because it was so hot and fresh!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPn5FMLslcKh2ODNqXomllj01r2RsXGJ4aeVjMV&fid=0x0:0xfe08ab308275d736"],"When":"2023-3-11"},{"Name":"Gregory van Tol","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxw6QSC8o8XMfCmNcSw6lMeU2PFxE3V8NpWLchAdJ-fO1uclzSIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"What can you say? It's Wendy's food. It's fast food so you get what you expect. Staff could do a much better job cleaning tables. There were maybe 10 customers in the place, and staff were standing around talking instead of checking if tables were clean.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Victor Ashish","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5yDGsHeJgzKstxa8rP4Gv_Fpd2kv7iISSV0cdfsyJ0a6tL6aeAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Although we understand that we came during the closing time, the place was a mess. There was water all over the floor near the pop wending machine, paper napkins on the floor, tables not cleaned, and tons of mosquitoes everywhere.

Felt like I was in a very unhygienic place - not even feeling to dine in. The restaurant was very much understaffed, and the staff didn't even know how to manage and prioritize the orders.

Wendy's being an established place - in such a situation surely wants me not to visit the place.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Shawkrat Bogda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrsOjmCZ5t1t9qzS0-fojDP_RC_lsLL9v2fdkXeKRxhdjA0bM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If you are not hungry and tired after shopping in the mall, AVOID AVOID AVOID this store. Don't throw your hard-earned money into the lake.

In the 5 or 6 years I've been going to MaryBrowns, this was the most disappointing experience. To be honest, I've always liked the juiciness of the chicken and the professionalism of the service, but this store pleasantly surprised me.

1, When placing the order, the front desk staff press the big mary as the original price without hesitation. He didn't look like a new employee who got the job that day. After I mentioned that today was Monday and the sandwich should be half price, he continued to mumble a reason instead of a simple "sorry" and changed it back to half price. This is the first time in many years that I need to remind the staff what day of the week it is.
2, I ordered another box of "made for 2". It has always been served in one box before, but today it was packed in several paper trays. Maybe it's not a big deal, but I still need to confirm with the staff "Is this what I ordered?", and the gravy bowl is also covered with gravy. Maybe it's not a big deal, but this is the first time.
3, Finally, I came to my favorite part of the chicken. The five pieces of chicken were obviously mixed. Two of them were newly made, and the rest were unknown. How should I understand this? Is it leftover from the previous customer? Or is it the same order with different cooking skill? The first time in many years.

So, long story short, This will be my last time here, maybe some people will confuse"just because of a mistake?", okay, let me tell you, in the past few years, I have enjoyed countless excellent services and delicious chicken in many MB stores in BC, they are still there, why should I come back here again? Now the big economic environment is not good, it's not easy for everyone, but don't treat customers as idiots, right🤝","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNMlWjuIZ9y8a1w3wTnRvKkBeMzjVdLdTHu64FF&fid=0x0:0x30da3eb802012ba8"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Peter Estrada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVw52Fx60bw34dCukF0QbSF82RCB7ujq7YTAahYaTLdvpQbj8VVtg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First time here. When we arrived we were the only ones there. We ordered the classic crispy chicken sandwich combo. It comes with an order of crispy partially seasoned potato wedges. It was cooked to order. The wonderful order taker brought out our order out once it was ready.  I'm happy about that. The order taker was friendly and wonderful. The chicken sandwich was juicy but needs some more seasoning. The wedges are definitely super crispy but definitely needs more seasoning. I added some salt and vinegar and that helped. Pricing is right for this type of food. I hope this was a one off. Please season your wedges and chicken better. I'd love to come back and try their fried chicken meals next time. Thank you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXe5gTZXGhDkydM7jfMsNczq_FxStLnb8t5F49&fid=0x0:0x30da3eb802012ba8"],"When":"2023-11-6"},{"Name":"Yannic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiPcmDTwcIkbAuU20IUFgKkCBjFYjG9sUQdPEW0BqDMa7FOx92wA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stopped in to get a quick bite before hopping on the ferry. Highly recommended for some quick chicken and fries if you need a snack  prices were reasonable and the food was hot and well seasoned. Ordered the popcorn chicken and fries combo and would get it again.

Service was  pretty quick and the staff was nice.

Will return again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSXQiuMcx3DzIUN8t9_WWAd8DRqyRguVzFWROu&fid=0x0:0x30da3eb802012ba8"],"When":"2022-6-13"},{"Name":"B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7xBoDZXzB2dAR1aPyzB6D_OyfCRl0KTZjcXntbq7Hug5PH6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had never tried Mary Brown's before, but today was not the day. The oil was definitely old. The wedges were burnt dark brown on the outside, but almost raw on the inside. It was so disappointing, especially since we didn't open the food until we were all the way at the beach. We had to throw away both the wedges and the chicken. I should have read the reviews for this particular branch. There were so many comments about old oil tasting products. Mary Brown's corporate should reassess this store. I definitely expected better quality from this brand name.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"M K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWg_KAqTQxsDLwon6O6f-_8Lc1dsT_DysWASplu1udt_XQYNiNq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This branch needs improvements, and fast.  Firstly, when a client enters, the staff need to learn how to greet clients. It's awful seeing sad faces on the counter. Secondly, there has to be some flexibility to satisfy a customer. I requested a small fries instead of two biscuits, but no communication whatsoever, and request wasn't granted. FYI, Popeyes ALWAYS replaces our biscuits with a small side upon request. Thirdly, they charge an upcharge of $5 if you request either dark or white pieces of the chicken. I have yet to see a friend chicken place here do this, except them. Fourthly, FOUR of the twelve pieces in the order were wings.. again, unacceptable. If I wanted to order wings, I could have done it. I ordered chicken, and I expect chicken, not wings. Also, my 11 year old son went to the counter to ask for hot sauce. He came back seconds later with a sarcastic smile telling us "they charge $0.99 for hot sauce, so embarrassing, no?" What is with all this greed honestly? Are we not already paying enough!? The management really needs to work on this. On the positive side, their chicken tastes good, the location is good, and the washroom is very clean. I remember when this place opened up, things were much better. However, because of these negative experiences, I wouldn't think of going back here. There is a reason my sons asked if there was a Popeyes nearby.. If I was the restaurant owner, I wouldn't have been happy to hear that from a young kid. Overall, very disappointed, not worth the money.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard J Bergeron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZExnbUKFKvplHQ_0M_2nTN2L_GFTHbWz1_5aOGcpxIqn_GckSKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I ordered the Buffalo Mary chcken breast in a bun , tater fries , gravy . Was disappointed.  Way too much sauce in the bun . Dripping all over , bun got soggy , went through about 6 or 7 inadequate napkins . Bit of buffalo flavour in the breast , not that spicy. Enjoyed the tater fries , bit of tang to them , gravy is really good . My partner had three piece chicken dinner with taters and cole slaw . She ordered one piece extra spicy and thought it too spicy ! And she likes spicy . Thought the chicken was greasy . Liked the salad and taters . She have her meal a 3 also. Im going back again in a  couple of days to try the fried chicken . They're having a special this tues and wed . Two piece meal for $4.95 . Reglar $9 + change . Basically half price . Good deal for tryout .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTJA6EZ73sw8Mo8Agp4fNiVquGPtaR0IVQvlUR&fid=0x0:0x30da3eb802012ba8"],"When":"2022-6-3"},{"Name":"Richard Tang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLFUWw11hwMWa1Sk1hj41XH2mlcFHo0UUpVl7eiUsH79LJa=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food is ok but not spectacular. The portions are good. However the potato wedges are sometimes dry and not edible, while other times they are as good as steam potatoes.

The standard franchise situation leads me to believe that they are frugal like KFC. For some odd fact, they give styrofoam Dixie cups of tap water. It's almost as though they are punishing the customer who decide not to buy their expensive bottled drinks.

The chicken of Canada franchise follows the same pattern as KFC of the south (USA)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary Yang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQk0jIsRLjuxxQCKwQrqojoDQ0JITPr57raFYAQmTpBeL4VA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best fried chicken place I’ve ever had in Van. The Big Mary Sandwich is the most favorite dish. All the staffs there are really friendly and professional. Had a really good experience there. Will definitely highly recommend to all my family & friends!","Images":null,"When":""}]

You have to stop here if you're comming or leaving Centennial Beach.\nStopped in for vanilla bean frap after bike ride to boundary bay  , Centennial beach . Lots of products that make for great gifts. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Jesse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSDyGy576NjOpFot9rCBdIpO7u4qZP6Qzr6EXuEXmqpkbcdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Not sure what happened to this place. Haven’t been here for a couple of months.  Used to be pretty good.  Just got the pepperoni meatball sub.  The bun is stale and hard I could hardly bite through it.   The meatballs were dry and rubbery.  This place has really gone down hill fast.  Definitely won’t be back turned me right off these subs.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFwIiMPOnsiSbDO4nrLB-WHZ92epDri8rWeBuc&fid=0x0:0xf3d18fd9288a10ad"],"When":"2024-9-25"},{"Name":"Marcus L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWAm1ka_ESYBlOFfTbfcnGmFcYKuqYakfSxihPN9UkLOeVieLhZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Tried this FireHouse location for the first time. Definitely better than Subway in the same area!
Good flavor, soft bread, and hot meat.
It ain’t cheap tho! $46 bucks for 2 subs!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOC0TWbguundM8ehXDzWTwgCvlZFTd6iyN6i5H7&fid=0x0:0xf3d18fd9288a10ad"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"Lee Gildemeester","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmwK5TPiyJO9K2BikS-yqaHifl8H0QHLdeDujEGzwKhWsKSXQ7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"had some great sandwiches here back in the summer, if overpriced, but todays was pretty bad. tried the french dips, 2 of which ran us over $40 (just the 2 sandwiches, not even a meal). the sandwiches were thinner than any other Ive had here, with the filling being chincy compared to the others Ive tried, at over $20 a sandwich it was much, much too thin. Super greasy, surprisingly cold considering it was made fewer than 10 minutes before we sat down to eat, and the Au Ju dipping sauce was super small for the size of the sandwiches. the container was only filled up about 1/3 of the way, and I feel pretty ripped off for more than $40 for 2 subs. the image of the dipping sauce is literally the amount they gave us, it was not partially consumed when the photo was taken. one sandwich went entirely uneaten it was such a disappointment. this was a 1 star meal, only because of past decent meals is this review a 2 star, but if this is the new business model I don’t think Ill be going back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMa7VBV9lmbb9fKsmu5D7UaimwYiHErRqPcMqif&fid=0x0:0xf3d18fd9288a10ad"],"When":"2024-11-21"},{"Name":"Joey Mullins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjA9hfj_Ijm7nk28n3Pwuv3ZUU8ObFM0Pq6x9qasT5gDb6RMN8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Definitely a sub place that's worth coming back to!

The Italian sub was excellent. Fresh ingredients, large portion size (I had leftovers). The staff were really friendly and helpful too. It's one of the best sub places around for sure!

Can't wait to come back to try the Meatball. Thanks Firehouse subs!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAWJ4DDReXWk6INSiFVTLrv8zbcfKZ-QiRbm9Z&fid=0x0:0xf3d18fd9288a10ad"],"When":"2024-5-13"},{"Name":"justin mckillop","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXycL53shbjuiaMD6urzpkXK-Gz6EEnmXV8W8247HHolXRLn9Od=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"AWESOME SUBS! first time at this location. Was served with friendly Service. Plenty of seating & surprisingly not to busy. I got the Large Brisket Hatrick & my woman got the Large Smoked Turkey Italian. We usually go to the Abbotsford location but found ourselves in Tsawwassen craving Firehouse Subs. The service at this location was way quicker than the Abbotsford location. I've said it before & I'll say it again, Subway & Quiznos is NO LONGER an Option for us! The Quality & Quantity here is so much better. Definitely a better bang for you buck. This location was clean & exceeded our lunchtime cravings. Looking forward to our next visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMx2RCxB9IAFlTHUPXVh4RrICeBPVxQ8POYVRrT&fid=0x0:0xf3d18fd9288a10ad"],"When":"2024-6-2"},{"Name":"Brennan Matharu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLtf-lCZ0-sAH6Kjr__M4ylU-MIv4Is4kMCK-YJ7wc6HMHM0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Heard this place opened recently in the tsawwassen mills area so I had to come and try. We got the brisket hat trick and the hook and ladder sandwiches. Both were pretty tasty, and nothing to complain about, I would say the sandwiches are like an upscale subway. One thing I did really like was the soda machine in the store, that thing had so many different flavours and options it was awesome! Pricing for the food was reasonable you get a pretty large portion. Will be back next time I have the chance!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtX_2KoplfCPqwcLxFHKlvEnCU23n9T64FPazR&fid=0x0:0xf3d18fd9288a10ad"],"When":"2024-5-2"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I seriously never knew subs could be good. I don't know how these subs are so good. Is it the sauce? Great staff? Even just a plain deli meat with cheese sub was a delight to eat.

If you order in store, it will be a little bit of a wait for your sub, but it will come out hot and fresh with melty cheese. Great quality. Lots of different types of subs. Prices feel a bit expensive but what isn't these days. Honestly, just sooo savory and tasty, really not what I was expecting!

Also, they have a soda machine with a lot of different flavors.

Can't wait to come back for more!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQnOvnK_I--vBquNSvPAqkJQpxGA3-rPdsVcUb&fid=0x0:0xf3d18fd9288a10ad"],"When":"2024-5-23"},{"Name":"Dmitri B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdxsyfOxNZ3JROY2TPuZvZYKsy3nqn1s0Pu1pbKehWbCiDng=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time trying their subs. They taste great and the service was fast. Loved the real smoked beef. I definitely recommend. Great choice of hot sauces as well.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Really well cook not dry at all and not raw.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_ONIqHINMAaJtlunBp0lyBfIojFDkxImm6utS&fid=0x0:0x40d689667d96df50"],"When":"2023-7-28"},{"Name":"Cole Davis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAOU6XCX3s_R0vWndse-P-J59JZDVGZbi6kfyG2pJARhX4qsYzZw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The quarter chicken breast is actually a whole chicken breast, maybe a little more even. Manager gave me a regular Fries which was half full.

TERRIBLE Customer Service!!!

WISH I could give thia location ZERO STARS!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNN_pjMrNI7f9-3DmxVSjxWHYKLXMJzRAsQ8DNZ&fid=0x0:0x40d689667d96df50"],"When":"2022-12-29"},{"Name":"Gayla J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXonqVkSyZ0kj4L10z7xgxgHrVwLs1vu7F6PXXTIeflvEXHoYh3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I ordered six family dinners for six and expected to feed 36 people. It did - sort of, we were really short on the side dishes. There was a communication breakdown, so when placing an order, ask them to be sure you have ordered correctly to feed everyone. Thankfully they did send enough chicken, the Owner called and helped to explain the short fall, was due to ordering too many different sides instead of just two sides.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lucy Yep.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWyWEm1iVA5BhD52EO30x5805b5fs28qVCdlDvtJbrD1_d2ndv1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I love Barcelos and I used to go frequently to other locations but specially this food court location has very poor service and products. Last time I ordered half chicken to go, first, the girl that is accepting payment does not wash her hands and touches the food to pack it. Second, part of the chicken break is missing like they took all the meat from the bone. The pieces are already small and they serve the food like that? As owner you are not saving, you are just loosing customers...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUrIQ2JYii7LnXZjGyq9WYL4w94r-rRkwW15YN&fid=0x0:0x40d689667d96df50"],"When":"2022-1-20"},{"Name":"Joe Uppal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLuumM3GoJ92r_B_Agk5l5t0c-BkgeXxmyhF9y8n67x0B-hCA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If there was a zero star, I would definitely give this location one. It was my son's birthday, and he really wanted Barcelos, and we had guests over. I had placed with Uber eats about 30 minutes before closing time. On the Uber app, it said the order is getting prepared, and the driver is on the way to pick it up. When my Uber driver went to grab my order, the restaurant was closed. The restaurant didn't cancel my order or contact me saying it's too late. It's 8:30 pm now my Uber driver calls it's closed. I have no food for dinner my guests went home hungry. Will never order from any Barcelos ever again.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Kenneth Lai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaxVGYXfpPoTmAfNhLJtbs31BGbuX8DK_7Hj5GOcCBNwv8VjrvXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"South St. Burger in Tsawwassen Mills is a must-visit for burger lovers. The highlight of my visit was the super nice manager, who took the time to thoroughly explain the ingredients of their vegan burger, ensuring it met my dietary needs. It’s rare to find such attention to detail! The option to add as many toppings as you like to any burger is a game-changer, allowing for endless customization. The entire staff was incredibly friendly and made the experience even better. And the fries? Absolutely outstanding—crispy, golden, and perfectly seasoned. Whether you’re vegan or a meat lover, South St. Burger offers something delicious for everyone, with service that goes above and beyond. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnIX1xgDfabS5_3QlFs283kfDTq2AekYOSZaxT&fid=0x0:0xbf00fbdb798de4ab"],"When":"2024-8-28"},{"Name":"Davin Kwan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVswJ2-NLO2quiErTaF9hiqRQfT94JwutZOBbqHCI54Aq4Q9VeU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I’ve been a loyal customer of this restaurant for a while, and one of the main reasons I kept coming back was the quality of their burgers. However, during my most recent visit, I noticed a significant change in the patty, and unfortunately, it wasn’t for the better. The patty was dry, lacking the juiciness that made their burgers so great before. It also wasn’t tender like it used to be, making the overall meal less enjoyable. It’s really disappointing to see such a drop in quality, especially since this place had been one of my favorites. I really hope they reconsider this change and return to the juicy, flavorful patties that made them stand out in the past.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGtFdjpf8ihr0u_CMMj2sYNi-m9d4InKZA3m1-&fid=0x0:0xbf00fbdb798de4ab"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Uros Nikolic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqZKUGj61BfmTYu8vecdYC7cNoaJsQnfWJB3zipm50mUOPG3Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don’t remember when was the last time I eat such a tasty burgers  🍔 everything from menu was really fresh and we ordered 3 different burgers with poutine and other fries.
If you’re in Tsawwassen Mills I highly recommend this restaurant, you won’t regret it 👏🏼","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3cCOZUSjEF_ku1zdFkwNJ9U5Mer_O793yS2-U&fid=0x0:0xbf00fbdb798de4ab"],"When":"2024-8-27"},{"Name":"Chan Owen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2m58ulSaNORbkm-gDhzx99iQT7v0dK1KjY8tZMsv_TprAr6-w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I used to love coming to this restaurant, but recently they changed the quality of their patties, and it’s disappointing. The patty I got was dry, not juicy, and lacked the tenderness it used to have. It made the whole experience less enjoyable. I hope they reconsider and bring back the quality they had before.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSgsPGhNIrLk-w4En_Lo4HoDaFhMOjTvaxf8Wz&fid=0x0:0xbf00fbdb798de4ab"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Minipa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLkpsoXCUt-uCoPDrB_Mv40ZqSioejOqdNEdMQaklHEBDE1W1x=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Amazing burger, fresh fries, free refills too. Gave the food in bags though which was a bit cheap but decent pricing","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOooFEY3PS3fFdpfm2Du_he9sdw6eIjYLlO-ScQ&fid=0x0:0xbf00fbdb798de4ab"],"When":"2024-7-17"},{"Name":"Wayne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8QJBi6QcTRAi7AdEdYaGH_JW0AEF7e6HzgNdEU0sa_JSuPyNJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First time visit during a busy (long weekend) Sunday evening. But the restaurant was not busy.

+ Mushroom Swiss Burger was tasty; beef patty was grilled.

* Southern Fried chicken was ok. Same price as the beef burger. Not crunchy but it's fine. I'd prefer the beef burger.

+ fries was good.

- Drink costs $3+ per cup (part of combo); Not recommended. More expensive than fries which is less than $3.

- No services. You get food when they call your number. The payment machine has options for tipping.

- Space not so clean. Had food crumbs left at table and seats.

* Had to ask the staff for napkins.
* Not sure if the drink is refillable.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGwXXquj5NV93v079dMhI4kIHdygJahqqaTjEO&fid=0x0:0xbf00fbdb798de4ab"],"When":"2023-8-7"},{"Name":"Dean Winchester","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQlXwDDY504zo8RECz7OcOc-gAUoIquol-YQOfDwmBK5q4h_VpnA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The burgers are amazing, the patty itself is so juicy and flavorful, and love that you can choose your own toppings. I've been coming here for years but recently had the chance to meet the owner, Tom. He is super friendly, hardworking, and passionate about his work and it shows! We came about 40 minutes before they closed and Tom told us to take our time and don't rush, he also gave us a little back story about the franchise and even took our trays to the garbage for us. He also told one of his employees to take off a few minutes early! He didn't have to go the extra mile especially before closing and we really appreciated his customer service!

We went back 2 days later around the same time and Tom wasn't there but another cook was, and he wouldn't let us order fries and after we placed our order he was making fries for another person? He seemed annoyed that there were still customers coming in 35 minutes before closing. Besides that, everything here is great!

Also the poutine is amazing!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7z5da4u6KStFu-rcLjoMcJTDqNHQUSVXfDdACqwKMPCpmCXXj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Excellent cheeseburger, nice and warm...... french fries were also top notch and very warm.   I,ve been here a few times now..... never been dissappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0XYCZo2bizyNLAkXNS7nq6YK0_fzNsIcbwlG0&fid=0x0:0xbf00fbdb798de4ab"],"When":"2024-10-15"}]

And the longest wait ever...  it was slapped together almost as if they forgot our order.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQJWNseEL76uVII2r96B3hr-0_vilXInHJa1SX&fid=0x0:0xd7238af858a364f2"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"karanvir singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmhSTkwf552ii13luYjLCu_N5AKepHjDsEI26QJqQpG06RylI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently visited Edo Japan restaurant Tsawwassen mills location on Saturday around the afternoon and unfortunately, my experience with their customer service was quite disappointing. From the moment I walked in, it seemed like the staff were uninterested and inattentive. We waited almost 20 minutes to give our order. my experience with the cashiers left a lot to be desired. There was a old lady on there cash. It was clear that she struggled with basic tasks like reading the order correctly or understanding simple instructions. I had to repeat my order multiple times, and even then, it was still entered wrong.
When I tried to explain the mistake, the cashier seemed confused and unable to fix it without calling over a manager, which slowed down the process even more. The lack of basic communication skills made what should have been a quick and easy transaction incredibly frustrating.she doesn't seems professional as at all.it was almost impossible to get cashier's attention for simple things like water refills she cannot even understand that basic thing.It's alarming that a restaurant would allow such poorly trained or ill-equipped staff to handle customer orders and payments.Customer service starts at the register, and if your cashiers can't handle even that, it really diminishes the overall dining experience. I hope they invest in better training or hiring staff who can provide a smoother and more professional experience.The overall attitude of the staff made the experience uncomfortable and unwelcoming.
I had heard good things about the food here, but with such poor customer service, I don't think I will be returning anytime soon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jada f","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBMbFjOAN3hgEEo2BAevmyr4y71okWigCdxsj9jXJ-PgQrPXW95A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"As a former Edo employee I'm pretty sure you are not allowed to deny service to someone claiming you have 0 sushi then proceed to sell the same roll to the person behind me, not sure how you can have no rolls period and then sell them right after you tell me no.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mory M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPs8avgpY6Oe_Ytsg4rqTPRpKj-6YZ9I59NE5Wd6hmPPMEz98=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My son tried the kids sushi and he liked the taste so he had to go for the second one😅

Her attention to detail and warm demeanor made our experience truly special. ! Surely gonna visit again…. 5 stars and highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFXrkRh3OiWzhhBrDJ-ZHUlWXRJbA-kT0th-1V\u0026fid=0x0:0x3276255fe94244b8"],"When":"2024-5-10"},{"Name":"Gurleen Mann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLiPUG0uS2mNXBduiVsY6PVMjHnfxQ7NkDQyzxiXX7WnB_qcg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We placed a mobile order today which was supposed to be ready for pick up at 4:10pm. We arrived on time and went into the restaurant to pick up the food at exactly 4:10pm because the Subway App indicated the order was completed and ready to be picked up. When I entered the store, the worker, Manpreet, was acting frazzled on the phone. When she finally looked up she asked how she can assist me, I shared I’m here to pick up an online order, Manpreet then said “okay, it’ll be a moment” and then she continued to loiter behind the counter and pacing back and forth on the phone. Then after she finally got off the phone she started to make, what I assumed, was my order which was 7 minutes after I Manpreet mentioned it would ‘just be a moment’. This was unacceptable as we had 2 young kids waiting in the car and hence why I believe placing an online order would have been a better idea. Manpreet also did not apologize for the late order or the inconvenience this has caused me. This was the first time I’d ever seen one individual working at subway, during dinner time, on a weekday night. This entire encounter was unprofessional by subway standards. [{"Name":"Erika M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbqk1kFtNPHISF0Ckbr8zNJFaoIrF_gEl48L_0JINECU67_yg1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had dinner with a friend at this location! We both had pastas (Seven cheese ravioli and Jambalaya Fettuccine) with a side of half nachos!

Our server was so friendly and checked in with us frequently to see if we needed anything or more food.

For the price, the pasta and nachos had large sizes which was perfect to share with a friend","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOPCn2KRDCJiJsEVR2RJdc_70DqOZaFBgX7p3ml&fid=0x0:0x7317904699150095"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Hailey Jang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGHzTNWFVEMOYPCgsQqixyQ6UFFIGKdXAQzO83IrNsff_lMg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great overall. Their pastas have big portion. 2 people ordered three dished and we packed the leftovers and had them for lunch next day.
I liked the Richard’s Red beer on tap.
The bolognese pasta with italian sausages was really good. Also the chicken caeser salad was so so good I would re-order this. The classic small sized pizza was okay. Lots of tables too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAiy8i2-vRsYMO9mA7EbQiP8WRQRAkpA8ZMqLI&fid=0x0:0x7317904699150095"],"When":"2024-7-4"},{"Name":"Tamara Edwards","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8ZuKpeL4Ih9QmrhtK2oyH2KDZknSThZMMt5EgoJQcRNpWYw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fresh, fantastic! Excellent service, our server was totally attentive without being obtrusive, friendly, knew the menu, checked in at perfect intervals. Had the fiesta salad - flavourful, delicious; and the Thai chicken wrap (grilled chicken), just a hint of heat in the sweet Thai chili sauce, nice chunks of grilled white chicken and a bit of crunchy noodle. My new fave thing","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIvkjHnLwQn0b1o6609ZMKeUJpxbjENUKClL8l&fid=0x0:0x7317904699150095"],"When":"2023-11-16"},{"Name":"Alysa Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJcgTm0ud5IEy5AFweNCtfAx_NW6IUKANq244urxoakJ5YPzw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I'm sorry to say that my review of Boston Pizza may disappoint you. I ordered takeout, but I wasn't very satisfied with their pizza. It was a bit salty and not very tasty. I was disappointed because I had heard a lot of good reviews before. Additionally, I ordered a side of sweet potato fries, but it took 20 minutes to receive, which made me a bit impatient.

However, I think that Boston Pizza's service is still good. Their staff is very friendly and enthusiastic, making me feel valued. Also, their takeout packaging is very good, keeping the pizza and fries hot.

Overall, my experience was not very good. I wouldn't recommend their pizza, but if you want to try other dishes, maybe you could consider it. The service is still good, but they need to improve the quality of their food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5VO66BsBjMCWVVRiutNvTO8X84Fftg37lco_p&fid=0x0:0x7317904699150095"],"When":"2023-6-11"},{"Name":"Joey C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVONws43kRXQQZVKUY_4MVYuG_XVH3tG7L-3VGHgoEAT3rINBjk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Came here for dinner with my family.  We were seated right away when we arrived.  We had a party of 12 people.  My daughter's pasta was really runny with barely any noodles and when we asked about it the server, she told us that it was the last of it.  So pretty much got the bottom on the pot stuff.  I ordered the ribs and when I got it, did not look appetizing at all.  It pretty much looked boiled and lighted sauced.  It should have been browned a bit to make it look better.  The wings we ordered were really good that were probably the best dish out of the whole dinner.  The pizzas were decent nothing to special about them.  My daughter loved the worms and dirt dessert.  Boston Pizza has changed their menu and I think they are trying to upgrade their menu.  The pizzas seem to be gearing to the more gourmet side.  The pizza looked good but was lacking flavours.  Not sure if it was the crust or the toppings.  I would rate our meal as average.  Think they could have done a few more things to make the meal experience better but failed in a few areas.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEA47NgnmYQHIkhJlVZ98sfPSJo_yHGGojHgxz&fid=0x0:0x7317904699150095"],"When":"2019-7-27"},{"Name":"Kalvin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYzAZd-0_JeniSNljNxgImCwzlXWbe6PzaDeAXT6_nhg5vP5E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Food tasted good and came out fresh. The hostess made us wait for 45min for a big table to tell us she can sit us in a split table which they had available when we walked in the door. After 45min wait then a big group finally leaves. We assume that would be our table which would been ok to wait but the hostess offers us a split table????? And the split tables were available when we got there. How do you guys train your hostess","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPR43cWIirMSpRIV72iRbKWj2sy71sFr0zCjgxv&fid=0x0:0x7317904699150095"],"When":"2022-3-6"},{"Name":"Susan H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIzyhWUuvO0u5SHQXJCItJV9VkX0Jmt-Ui6-FYM3gaPiKpO1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The place and seating is spacious. Friendly service. Food is okay. Pizza crust is a bit dry. Vegan power bowl was tasty and filling. Unicorn lemonade taste meh. Kids love their food. I guess we will go back again just for the kids.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAO-2B7NHVcob-DGTh7hbzO5wECPZhTDh1C80x&fid=0x0:0x7317904699150095"],"When":"2019-11-19"},{"Name":"Mas Rostam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXn9N6jo_YK6Nshi-kTKKBlL6s75IIqo4-4Z0DhozzunRxm2uG_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Dinner - connected to the mall, seemed like they were short handed and busy with the few staff who were trying to do the best they could. Greeter, delayed the flow seating guests by being overly polite asking all of us where we wanted to sit causing a few to go back and forth amongst themselves. The server took care of us and was polite, the drinks (quenchers) which we free refills came with little flavour otherwise overly syrupy. The calamari was quite dry almost like reheated frozen calamari. The pizzas were great. I had a chicken salad quinoa bowl which was decent tasting.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLXidiUay1Kgu0nCydGil4KbXLLhCMh60oIKHl&fid=0x0:0x7317904699150095"],"When":"2022-4-30"}]

I can't speak for the hot dishes but overall pretty happy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_o7QI9wwipAFm9mQdsvGZWzgVBlkiNE8Iw-BQ&fid=0x0:0x992886a809fc679e"],"When":"2021-1-3"},{"Name":"A F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2iTrJszKnOcVhaa1e58UFNYfDr104Vsfh-lMQyoAuxyXXhAux=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Food was very disappointing. Please spend your money elsewhere until they drastically improve.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Relatively healthy, affordable food option among the fast food stalls. There are bento boxes, individual sushi roll sets, noodle soups, teriyaki rice dishes, and even bubble tea. I bought the beef bento box and saw the person at the counter cook the beef on the hot plate and it was nice and warm when I got my meal. The bento box came with 4 pieces of California roll, a salad, some sweet potato tempura fries, white rice, and some sort of teriyaki protein. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Tony Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf8VP49ZjSvgG0JnhT1tc6Tv6OzLL9YEi_yNvwH1rW_K8-7VE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I'm a huge fan of the Grinch so when I heard the Grinch meal was here, I hurried down to get an adult happy meal and a child happy meal. Was I ever disappointed with my Grinch meal! First of, the cashier didn't even know I could choose a Big Mac instead of chicken mcnuggets. She had to turn around to see the big screen advertising the Grinch meal. Ok, staff wasn't aware of the new promo. When I got the food, it wasn't in a Grinch box. I was disappointed. The Grinch meal wasn't cheap to begin with. At $16.89, you get a Big Mac combo meal with a pair of socks. When you add it up, its not a deal. You're paying for every item in it including the socks. You can't buy the socks directly but you can buy the toy only that comes with the child's happy meal.

I noted they had a stack of Grinch boxes behind the cashier and yet they did not package my Grinch meal in it. Why tempt me and charge premium?

The child happy meal was in a regular box with no Grinch advertising at all. Another disappointment. We grabbed our meals and found the napkin dispenser was empty. First time, first McDonald's that supplies were depleted.  When we got home, we noticed we had the shaker bag and dill pickle package but no fries. Blasting mad, I jumped back into my car, drove back to McDonald's and complained. There was no apology. The cashier grabbed some fries and gave it to me. I told her that the rest of my food was now cold and all she did was shrugged her shoulders. Poor service. Poor attitude. Not returning here, Grinch or not.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqSbE2_7IdKJiTTbrnPDKW8P_Xz1uqlZ4iJGhe&fid=0x0:0xde2bdf2901b0b7"],"When":"2024-12-4"},{"Name":"OVO6","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWyXOvdNyUNZpAWB2xPkw0KDrh0AySj0B-o9Y20rJaGYmyKt43h=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Simrin (somehow a manager) & her staff were completely rude & disrespectful rushing us to take our order saying we were wasting their time. Also none of the kitchen staff were using gloves or using any sanitary precautions. Never leave negative reviews but just had to share this horrible experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kamikaze Digital","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIHs1Q_XuT0SrensVjICNSGvWLexmem0hVqJ-mE5kC2M8cboje=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Food was prepared well but they forgot items and for some reason McDonald's refuses to give napkins anymore. You'd think if I order food for 2 adults and a kid you'd give us a couple napkins, especially now that we pay a billion dollar corporation 25cents for a paper bag.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shinn Inagaki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpF1gPQ6II9FjL7HoACMWpgmrVznxivHZdomkvTJ9wRIkWHw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"No wonder this McDonald’s is so empty.
I had 3 issues with my visit.
1. It started with no receipt paper on self-order computer.
2. Employees are so busy making drink lid and straw to make a drum kit at the cashier and not helping me.  Then he forgot to serve my food and had it sit 5 min  until manager realized that I have been standing for a while.
3. When I ate, my chicken wrap had minimal lettuce and also over cooked chicken.(see the pictures)

Manager had to keep telling employees what to do.😭😭😭
She needs to fire these lazy ones that she needs to tell what to do.

Definitely I am not coming back to this location.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhPwN8ioh0reMTA-ppwTNWAmdR49nKwkUsdUQ&fid=0x0:0xde2bdf2901b0b7"],"When":"2023-6-18"},{"Name":"jaja twins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVioOpD7ZxV4B5M1Whof5_vCJ04Ro3TCSWprMtJR6UnYqpe4GoA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have been going to this McDonald's about three times a week and the quality of customer service I received today was atrocious. I left my job for my lunch break and when I ordered my usual meal I realized that my wallet was left in the school where I work. After doing the lineup (because I couldn't back up anymore I told the customer service representative that I had found some cash and asked if she could help me, she agreed but then her manager told me that there was a lineup and I needed to go lineup again. At this point the manager made it obvious that she did not care about me as a customer and that other people were more important than me. I offered to move out of the to the special drive through area but she did not care. I cannot count how many times I have waited on orders that were not ready but today that I needed great customer service; I received a horrible experience that has made me rethink my choice of restaurant","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pascal G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLwhl3cvs4iFJlsGpEEvBQuO6yFuS3rvDKX-L2PKKxPZriqnOEy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"One of the worst McDonald’s experiences I’ve had. The wraps were very poorly filled, and the service (takeout) was extremely bad. We ordered takeout, but they served everything on a tray. When we asked for a bag, they made us pay extra (not much, but still). The staff member was unpleasant. Paying $35 for 3 people to eat poorly and get bad service? Definitely the last time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"qian lu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPpRjLjrDmBemH5k5i2JLQYffNLqpFDAtf-jeL9OvgR-AhUQs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have never encountered such a rude manager. After repeatedly confirming whether there was sauce for the McNuggets when picking up my order, I received a definite “yes.” However, when I got home and opened the bag, there wasn’t a single packet of sauce inside. Even the toy for the kids’ meal was missing.

When I went back to ask for the sauce, they told me it was a minor issue and said, “Just take the sauce and leave.” They even blamed me, saying, “It’s your own responsibility. Why didn’t you check before leaving?” Furthermore, they claimed that only those who pay their salaries are entitled to reason with them. The service attitude was the worst I’ve ever seen.

This isn’t the first time something like this has happened. On many previous occasions, the number of McNuggets in my order was less than it should have been.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harmandeep Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8wV6X6c4fwv5bbjWD3rfJqQAVaYG9vuWHWz6XrJ5UMa91y9eTUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I was excited, especially since the staff were polite and welcoming. However, my experience quickly took a turn for the worse. As I was waiting for my order, I noticed something absolutely unacceptable in the kitchen. The sandwich makers and other kitchen staff were preparing food, including burgers, with their bare hands. Not only that, but they were also touching various other surfaces and items in between handling the food.
It was both unhygienic and disturbing to watch. I couldn’t eat my meal comfortably after seeing that and ended up throwing it away. I am extremely disappointed and disgusted by the lack of proper food safety practices here. I won’t be returning, and I would advise others to think twice before dining here unless they address these serious hygiene concerns.","Images":null,"When":""}]

The pizza was soaked with who knows what, crust was dry and overcooked, no sauce, and where is my bacon? I tried to call the store to rectify the issue, only for them to pass off my complaint to door dash who in turn decided I only deserved an $11 refund, even though the pizza was $45 after everything said and done.

Panago is definitely the best spot for pizza. Arjun should be the manager one day

A life time customer was made by Arjun! 😍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHGJGqxZAGCgWh6eesMqIYcgEkFyKubFwzcKvN&fid=0x0:0xf1e66614ebe774e1"],"When":"2022-10-20"},{"Name":"Maria M.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDRG-yUxmCRTeMbgMR7M_AtJoVP10dGVk-ujVbXfA_LDZYf_QKOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Yummy. I have try all pizzas around. PANAGO tastes the best. My kid likes the chiken bites with cucumber and garlic cesar dip.❤","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_hwlzxXosAKZgXpPfBqfGPetnRg_h4VeUDPIO&fid=0x0:0xf1e66614ebe774e1"],"When":"2021-4-30"},{"Name":"Derek V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRFoyHN3CFgRDZUccMDKFlr3Y5ff3IemN9Fd1NwIkY2UQD5jcbsQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We had a taste for pizza Friday night and decided to give our local Panago a try because I used to love their Chicken club pizza. First I'd like to give top marks for the person who took our order, she was very pleasant to deal with. The pizza however was very disappointing. The pizza was lacking in both sauce and tomatoes which when done properly makes this pizza delicious. Some pieces didn't have any tomato at all.
Sad that trying to skimp on a couple of toppings will cost this location any of our future business.
There are a lot of other choices in the area.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matt Wood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7XWx2MRzHt81gm3hRVPXTJJv5-0JmskWSRNNdLpXkD47IIqek=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tasty pizzas, good service, reasonable prices. Can’t ask for much more than that!

We specifically choose Panago because of their community outreach and support. Other commercial pizza chains do nothing to improve the community.

Thanks local Panago owner and staff!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIloBNU8BqrMXEu-c0fToNelRGoBG-Xq5zGAs5nrI9YjYWKmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Long overdue review as this is by far the best Panago location I have eaten at . The staff is all very friendly - owner & employees;  I am always greeted with pleasant smiles even before I walk in through the door. What’s even more amazing is that my order is always custom and not once have they let me down. 10/10 every time . It’s ready within 15 minutes or less , tastes amazing and is always hot ! It is because of this amazing service and consistency that I’m eating here pretty much every other day now  and I will continue to do so until I get fed up of pizza haha  :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Glasner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlFSX_UUx6rW0lix6i7dkX9lVOSyBZB-F5xxqlskw_ZqxWVSPR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Just placed an order for over $50.00 it was online for pickup. Waiting outside for 20 minutes then went to the  door its locked not a sole around inside. So I called 1800 and they had to call the shop still in progress it said 2 guys wander in from out back. Finally I was put to customer Care now its 20 minutes late still not making the 2 pizzas.
And I was only offered $10.00 credit for the next order.  Needless to say I just canceled the order.  The tsawwassen location is the worst for mistake orders .","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Henry Luan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJV3o9ovKjC50gaewyyVx644uNJMEvGGzEfe11dsssYdY0hBw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I really like the taco pizza with chicken. The combination of the sauces, meat and ending with crunchy cabbage was a nice touch. The glazed pepperoni was rather mediocre and practically had no difference compared to a regular pepperoni. The fried chicken was total wack as the baked pickles made the pizza almost inedible and the cabbage did nothing. Feels like panagos pizza design is very hit and miss but their smoky cilantro sauce is to die for","Images":null,"When":""}]
