[{"Name":"Shery On The Move","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmAA3VItm5d-LzZjMzSS_FZs12aHSse1X5w-nXQqVmdbUvhBBJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm a first-time customer to Nat's Coffee  House. My husband ordered caramel macchiato, and I ordered ice mocha and blueberry lemon muffin. We were so happy with our drinks and nothing to complain about.

Meanwhile, about the muffin,  I was attracted to the blueberry/lemon combination, but unfortunately, i didn't get the combination taste.
Furthermore, the muffin was not fresh (probably not baked on the same day), and the staff didn't offer to warm it up.

All staff were friendly, but the mistake was that she didn't offer to warm up my muffin. I don't mind eating muffins at normal temperatures provided if it's freshly baked, but the muffin I ate wasn't fresh.

I will definitely come again because i really like the atmosphere. The last time i came here, it was a Woods Coffee. So when i came yesterday, it reminded me of Woods Coffee because the management didn't change any indoor seating.

Next time, i will try another drink on the menu, but I'm not interested with bakeries anymore.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBRKK8aS7njRgSXVnofgRMTCdYr4C31jX96APS&fid=0x0:0x41ce6f043a990a56"],"When":"2024-5-21"},{"Name":"Ravneet Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGzmrD1cHYpATlUMH47NlKB0BDLL0MfGLBo2b5dzUPZNB42R9f=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I came here like a week ago and tried their chicken strips,they were really good. So i brought my husband today to have that good taste but the first order that we got were burnt chicken strips and they were so stiff that i had to give them back. The staff made new ones for us but same issue, stiff again. I dont know if its just today or what happened. We ate them anyhow and did not even feel like ordering anything more. Also, the staff today seemed not interested in serving the guests. The other day a tall lady with black hair served me and it was wonderfull.
FELT Very weird today","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sean “Seanwiches”","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnTzFWGQfJQMbbpjucIHtu1smaGLNpsJGa5YTtcfzP5sTrd0k5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my go-to spot when I’m in town. The service is great, it’s got a great atmosphere if need to do a little work and you can beat sitting at the tables out back.

I haven’t tried the new flatbread, but it looks pretty good. I did try the gelato and let me tell you, it was amazing! Do yourself a favor and try the cookies and cream, maybe a double cone. 🔥","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrOTN_Sc7_qFpSLYP57MX5J8pydsdEDJ6pqsF-&fid=0x0:0x41ce6f043a990a56"],"When":"2024-5-15"},{"Name":"Dan Lorenz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVa_eC-U0kV3zmKzI4E1osV8_z7ABPGLuq9fXQNAmdOuVhfXvuZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place serves fantastic coffee, and bagels. It also serves as a place where I can grab Powerade and water before my gym session!!! Keep up the good work Nat’s Team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daljit Bains","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdA-hMsR_2SCDC3RksfT-_GWaGnswzYErwlgBNeNz1TpmQ9tbs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went for the first time in drive thru.  A girl named Iliana was so amazingly wonderful.  I asked her for suggestions because it was my first time.  She told me what she really liked and she made it for me.  It was a modified white mocha with less sweetness with Irish cream and Cinnamon.  I took a sip while driving away and immediately stopped my car, backed up into drive thru, knocked on their window and told her it was the best coffee drink I have ever tasted.  I don't really write reviews, but this experience was exceptional.  I'm hooked on their coffee now.  It's sooooo good!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bradley Dougherty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqgGwHhnGDE0p20s1bs7ju-N01GgzCaA_vBAarBf3FDMzl3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"To the employee that was annoyed and grumpy that I had my SERVICE animal with me and was visually pissed off because she told me to take her outside and got mad when I told her she was a service animal, shame on you Karen.

As a local, I probably won’t be back for that reason.
Management please inform your employees that service animals are allowed and it is unacceptable to get mad at the customer for having a service animal.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jason wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAr7OPM3u3i7bBkh0r7Q9kS7_8Gu_88Crv223BgydShD66TQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good coffee.. wish there were more locations.. Great place to hang out and get some work done on my lab top..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdpJDiBtGutF2kMJIPhahn8ul9zT5BClQd9a8A&fid=0x0:0x41ce6f043a990a56"],"When":"2024-3-2"},{"Name":"Sally Chae","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKIrMOZBorysV9LFGtDjWGmlbuifIIYKfb6HSAS-4aTe2ZVZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visiting from Seattle. Dropped by on the way to the ferry terminal... what a perfect little place! Really cozy and nice atmosphere  and the staff is extra friendly. I had Chai Tea Latte and husband had hibiscus tea. We both really liked it :) I want to come back on the way back :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPY-_idUmwc8kSdeSBaMllyP4V7ueF0-v-jOtJG&fid=0x0:0x41ce6f043a990a56"],"When":"2022-10-19"}]

[{"Name":"Tania Arora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTM3cK0Tza8sQADEGxXloyJRDpBZYkaTTxxRbwY3aPKKl7pqbW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Omg the most amazing food I have had in Surrey so far…. Very unique creations. Staff is very nice & professional - service is as quick as it can be. On the weekends they have a 2 hour dine in limit - there might be a wait so make sure to check if should get a reservations.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQA5W2pqC0Id9ErFZ4-o2bcWL6Rau9SyLCGC2w&fid=0x0:0xa3ae60553b040e35"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Videesh G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhwNGfq3r6NW4xapwGlC05lcGIwtehlR0cWbDA5XMl2N8bqM_i=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The ambience of the restaurant was inviting, and the customer service was exceptional. We tried two appetizers: the butter naan with garlic, along with keema and paneer curry. While the naans were decent, they didn't quite stand out. However, the curry was flavorful and had a nice level of spice. Overall, it was a pleasant dining experience, but there's room for improvement in the bread.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMNUGFezLrCmQv6Gi50WqlVN3Nl_fJM3iv3EKgZ&fid=0x0:0xa3ae60553b040e35"],"When":"2024-11-4"},{"Name":"Tav Dhillon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrRGAiccrCPtDxnsbL4iLIukwM_7N5NEOQxwb3h34PPRTBKpXk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Visited for breakfast and brunch for the first time, but unfortunately, it fell short. The açai bowl received was far from what was marketed. The granola was just raw oats, and the toppings were noticeably different. The base was incredibly runny, more like a smoothie. Overall, disappointing and not recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBG2TuhSuwDkgQpogi1dVkwXpKig2NaiEa11rr&fid=0x0:0xa3ae60553b040e35"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Gaganpreet Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWS6CRVqFqr0pKuY5BtNvJvQAzqSCn7OZw-ir7-rgecN3Nga8w8hQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Great Dinner at Tasty Indian Bistro

We just had dinner at Tasty Indian Bistro, and it was such a lovely experience that I had to share. From the moment we stepped inside, we were welcomed by a cozy, inviting atmosphere. But what really made our evening special was the incredible service we received from our server, Jas.

Jas was simply wonderful. She greeted us with the kind of smile that makes you feel right at home. Even though she was taking care of several tables and handling all sorts of requests, she never missed a beat. It was clear she’s incredibly hardworking, yet she made it all look effortless.

One thing that really stood out was how much Jas knew about the menu. She didn’t just take our order; she helped us choose, offering suggestions that perfectly matched what we were in the mood for. Whether it was deciding on the best appetizers, entrées, or the perfect drink, Jas had great recommendations for everything. Her knowledge of the cocktails, whiskey, and bourbon options was impressive, and her suggestions made our meal even more enjoyable.

And speaking of the food—it was fantastic. Tasty Indian Bistro really lives up to its name. Every dish was packed with flavor and beautifully presented. You could tell the chefs put a lot of care into each plate, and it made the whole experience even better.

But honestly, it was Jas who made the night memorable. She was so friendly and attentive, making us feel like we were her top priority, even though we knew she had plenty of other tables to look after. It’s rare to find someone who’s not only great at their job but does it with such genuine warmth.

All in all, our dinner at Tasty Indian Bistro was a great experience. The food was delicious, and Jas’s outstanding service made the evening special. If you’re looking for a place with amazing food and even better service, Tasty Indian Bistro should definitely be on your list.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCQeqGjvYvdLALA1ahCXbrag7z4jLhNunAsJn6&fid=0x0:0xa3ae60553b040e35"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"sreedevi radhakrishnan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbgXwP26_52lKSsrN3V_BQpBNEYeYagTgwp1HSsvPT4knUcusU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely phenomenal food! We’ve been here twice now and they’ve consistently served us delicious authentic punjabi food. They definitely pay attention to every little detail. Service is great!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8OlZj-KypKYAkcWfH8VODpPLjW9CcyhoYU_xX&fid=0x0:0xa3ae60553b040e35"],"When":"2024-10-8"},{"Name":"Divyanshu Chaubisa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLwycq9sqfcIYjmWvmrsgjiWg5fGw-galqSoUY7mlNY_XKBvTI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"No doubt it’s one the best Indian restaurant in Vancouver. The ambiance is amazing and soothing vibe overall. Somehow I felt the food quality and taste was not at par with other good restaurants we have in the city. They have ample of free parking to accommodate the guests, the waiting time for table may vary on the rush but it’s reasonable.
I went with my family last weekend and had a good time. We tried mini burger sliders, kulcha chhola, malai koft (main course) with garlic naans and aloo paratha.
The food taste was average, the service was pretty good and quick.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNX3AGv8EK7cc4l1cv0zhJc_UByz6zC6S-e1wlK&fid=0x0:0xa3ae60553b040e35"],"When":"2024-9-6"},{"Name":"Amarjeet Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwuqo1tqouoVJlCdwYJ3Yrr0cn0IrKRgbjXwXxz6jc5GaxxI1k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of dining at Tasty Indian Bistro, and it was an exceptional experience from start to finish. The atmosphere was warm and inviting, with elegant decor and just the right level of ambient noise to make for a comfortable and enjoyable evening.

The girl named Puniya(sorry if I pronounced the name wrong) was incredibly attentive, friendly, and knowledgeable about the menu. They went out of their way to make recommendations and ensure that everything was to our liking. The service was prompt but never rushed, which allowed us to fully enjoy each course. Overall, is a fantastic place to enjoy a memorable dining experience, whether for a special occasion or a casual night out. I will definitely be returning and highly recommend it to anyone looking for great food and excellent service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nikhil Patil","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_kaPBj58IwRUgFf0stQWxv34s-JNKYUd5fFrMxzXTGf9TuOkHcA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"'Tasty Indian Bistro' consistently exceeds my expectations. The food quality and taste, ambiance, and service remain outstanding. Both the veg and non-veg thali were truly delicious. In the veg thali, the palak paneer stood out as our favorite, while the lamb curry in the non-veg thali was cooked to perfection with incredible flavors and complex notes. We concluded our meal with the staff-recommended dessert, the 'Cardamom Dream Bar.' It was the perfect ending to a wonderful meal. We will definitely be returning to this place many more times.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNz3w5AfmI9rcR-mTAOiziJ2JvKR0WRnG1pVme7&fid=0x0:0xa3ae60553b040e35"],"When":"2024-10-1"}]

[{"Name":"Tony Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf8VP49ZjSvgG0JnhT1tc6Tv6OzLL9YEi_yNvwH1rW_K8-7VE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Want a quiet place for happy hour to sit and enjoy a very good pizza? Il Posto is the place to go. These guys make an exceptional pizza. We shared a pizza with pistachios on it along with chicken and pancetta on it. Truly a great crust. Nicely seasoned and cooked to perfection. Will be here again next week. Can't wait.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvDJ9jsBeihHY7flFCHtPWe4GEcLve-91B3996&fid=0x0:0xb252e36f93d6a6c7"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Pongo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXT-qQCE1uUwfmES1FGLIpAmkroUlDIcsJZMXejhRkO1uA9CxO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Portions are huge. Kids pizza is the same size as regular pizza! Really enjoyed the chicken sandwich - excellent value for lunch ($18).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaKaMtClcY51VlRjo9OlCxshiXsLxMRZ4uWmC1&fid=0x0:0xb252e36f93d6a6c7"],"When":"2024-10-7"},{"Name":"vineetha jose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUiO8_9JpdCDe3jgHqjk-FxZS9jbtQBw6VZNBdMvoEDuI4P3Vl=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Celebrated birthday dinner with bunch of my girlfriends  there it was awesome have been there with my close friends and both  times the food , ambience , service was wonderful . Will visit again 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXAlE9WICtNjN2z09DRFu30DMABakGKYyC_Msy&fid=0x0:0xb252e36f93d6a6c7"],"When":"2024-7-28"},{"Name":"Linda Hansbauer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbhYntSwrf3fPiWmrNihB_RxxZEX6epZ6NkhTpeBuOWgHv5aaF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am a visitor from Australia 🇦🇺 🪃  and the family decided to  take me to " il Pasto " for dinner. The restaurant was fully booked and it was "buzzing" a sign of an excellent managed establishment. We had various Pizzas - Kid's - Vegetarien and others. Very tasty, crispy crust - it was fun to watch our Pizzas being made from scratch (the kids loved it)! Amanda looked after us - efficient and helped us with the different requests. This Italian Pizza Restaurant would be one of th most efficient and full of atmosphere run places I have visited for a long time. Prices also not out of reach! Thank you for making this a nice experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP7w5C9iYDgD0M-0gjyoeLX6RmdMXt7cUx9NG09&fid=0x0:0xb252e36f93d6a6c7"],"When":"2024-8-27"},{"Name":"Jello Candles","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHi7A-Ad-UZ-ihIVsJVirYVG_GwBefu03JiYiQDIqXUu231g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Love their new cobb salad!!

They also offered kids meal - basically same portion as regular dish but simplified the ingredients and more welcomed by kids.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNMg0736S4HgObzIV1lA3BpdCuyar_N0rqjXjjl&fid=0x0:0xb252e36f93d6a6c7"],"When":"2024-8-3"},{"Name":"Nadia Cornale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL13yIoIH5XqfSc93bqsXlNjKg6p6DdkYP-ux-uatEJv1Rn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I held my bridal brunch at Il Posto on Saturday morning and I can not say enough GOOD about the venue, staff, and of course, the food + beverages.

The table setting we were hosted in was beyond perfect and our server was upbeat, kind, and accommodating. He matched the groups energy to a tee which really added to our experience!

Il Posto really played a role in how special the day was for me. Thank you to the team for accommodating me and my group of 14 ladies!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOmkS7V2X6fbLoejqbFXaJMROhUsLah7bScaSE&fid=0x0:0xb252e36f93d6a6c7"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Munro Stuff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj0Wcuk6ox5dfAeJ4fAaMbhX_F-nzzt3p5oc_f0hBd0NpbGSM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really enjoyed our dinner here. Great vibe and decor. Good drink & food menus, with something for everyone. Our meals were absolutely delicious, and the affogato was fabulous (the nut crunch, yum) and generous in size. Our server Kelsey was exactly what you'd hope for in a server - fun, magically appearing when needed, clear communication, and helpful. Excellent and highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPT015J8W5q9zQe9vbfrlWzPllE-2txto5LBVZu&fid=0x0:0xb252e36f93d6a6c7"],"When":"2023-10-14"},{"Name":"Taylor S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmUbsHvM0QGDaI5zDz_GGDGZWXcR_L6APXCOovUJttHkTLVo6r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cannot rave about this place enough!!! Food, service and atmosphere are 12/10.

Il Posto hosted our engagement party dinner for 16 people over the weekend and we could not have asked for a better experience. In terms of food, there was something for everyone and we had plenty of leftovers! We really love this place because of their staff though. They are the most amazing and make you feel so taken care of.

I would highly recommend Il Posto for any occasion.

Thank you for such a memorable evening! We can’t wait to come back for dinner and drinks.","Images":null,"When":""}]

title: Beach Grove Motel
descriptions: Functional rooms in a basic lodging with guest laundry facilities & complimentary WiFi.
about: null
user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Eamon O'Donoghue","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgT_CyEWLEJDJEnJEy3XYscrUtOM6X9c5CKx8XyGA_dDi_qcV5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The worst motel I have ever stayed in!! We actually only lasted about an hour. Dirty, bed was not level, very loud people upstairs and paper thin walls……I could go on and on. I asked for a refund. Showed them my bill from another hotel for the night. At first they said they would refund me half the cost. Did not receive a refund so emailed them again and they said they changed their mind to only refund me 20%. That was my last straw!! Do not stay here, even if you are desperate. Horrible place and horrible people running it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole Joli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIaIDDnmgB0bNSSZVO4RuVNYDFD3r2TfA4DeNqHtNjgC9H7WnZzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Definitely old , but felt more or less safe. Town of beach grove is adorable, staff was nice. Jacuzzi tub in the room was a good idea but was a bit dirty. Rooms were spacious and price is good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anne Gray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIngNW-jAb68v9UXcyDc3EN_VONZUAzzZ1tFTSCBaK740lJ8A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We have just stayed 3 nights in Room 9 at the Beach Grove. The room was exceptionally clean as were the refrigerator, cooking requirements, bedding etc. Bathroom excellent with great water pressure and plenty of hot water.
The family and staff are so kind and helpful, nothing was too much trouble.
Things I would suggest need looking at are the air conditioner, cool air stops at open bedroom door so lounge area and kitchen very hot. It needs a good clean as well.
It may have been us but we could obtain very little on the television.  We kept trying but were unable to bring up the program list, maybe a print out for visitors on how to bring up the list of available programs as we didn't want to keep bothering reception.
Thank you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristin Bogart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXv0ndrUvKIZnwFlrnGK0Cu3HpaBd6c4Ds_nKG5y6FHuvwVdTwE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Mouse  excrement, human fecal matter on walls, broken toilet seat… still with me? Let me tell you about Beach Grove Motel. We booked the “last room available” before our ferry. We did not last 2 hours before checking out (and most of that time was not spent at the location). The room was disgusting - The room has uneven floor with gaps in the flooring, gaps in the door, table in the kitchenette “steadied” with a chunk of paper. Left over premade ice left in the fridge from god knows when and the ac didn’t come to the front room. The beds were dirty, the back room was gross and grungy, walls and baseboards had soo much wear and tear throughout the unit it looked like it was a “slumlord” special. The bathroom was disgusting, the tub was not rinsed out after there “cleaning”, the toilet seat was broken and holding on by one clip, fecal matter on the walls and stained towels. The utility closet was full of mouse poop and traps. The fire alarm was unplugged and the fire extinguisher hadn’t been serviced in over 5 years (well past the expiration date). Window in the bathroom did not have a screen. There were left over cleaning cloths left in the room.

I have attempted to contact the manager to discuss matters but they have sat on our messages for over a month. This place still charged us for the full stay even though we did not stay.

Overall very negative experience at this location.

Update as you can see from the managements response they are not taking responsibility of the cleanliness of the site and are thinking I am looking for something more than letting others be aware of the conditions. I will expand upon their response -

1) the utility closet was not locked as they stated below.

2) I don’t believe for a minute that they would resolve the issues with the 5 year expired extinguisher, broken toilet seat or the cleanliness of the unit. Clearly trying to save face. However with the numerous 1 star reviews I don’t think they that really interested in that.

Don’t feed into their fluffy attempt at trying to dismiss a poor rating it was rated correctly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jess Hepburn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUFuI3df9WdAhw4oOfRJSgYBTHi6kstIh6bXjsqJLl8Ri76QMq5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If i could give 0 stars and still leave a review i would. I should have listened to my gut and the reviews and cancelled out stay.
Before you check in view the rooms!
Our room was in bad shape to the point where we couldnt even stay for one night because our child is immune compromised. There was literally urine marks on the wall in the bathroom and mold in the baseboards.
If it wasnt for expedia we wouldnt have gotten our money back either.
You can tell they are trying to reno but definitely cutting corners.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPveXJFeopPjtDoULZ22RxxWbfv15z2pjkKDdTD&fid=0x0:0xf8985cc836f8f55d"],"When":"2024-8-12"},{"Name":"Robin E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/local-reviews/AJMZ0QfnSFWXMd1oJu73a6IhdtgibYcjse2HKQTHeghNQd9Cyw8DYQQJZDCyh-TD68ehXuY-FA=s120-c-br100","Rating":0,"Description":"Did 1 night stay here before getting a ferry.  Very close to a lovely nature walk at Boundary Bay.  The room was a classic motel and did everything we needed.  It was cheap and cheerful.  It was quiet despite being beside a main road.  The wifi was a bit slow was probably the only issue we had!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexander Driscoll","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKCo2NNZBEr8hYS5mu08TnBXbBMutIWZnjKIEBJ0vRoYRwCUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Its been nearly 2 months and I STILL have not gotten back my $100 damage deposit.
I have called numerous times, and they keep saying its on the way.
this place is run by Thieves and Liars","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nik Zierik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKcHELAs3ht9PK2II6KFtYonT9U5es0hrqQGOjROLrfJbiAHw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Me and my family stayed here for a golf trip to tswassen springs golf club in august 2023 and we noticed this motel stood out for being cheaper and we booked it. DO NOT LISTEN TO THE BAD REVIEWS!!! Those are old reviews anyway. This place is great, everything you need, quiet, and great location, nice rooms, and great service! We are coming to tswassen in august this year same time as last year and will definitely stay here again!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"DLH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNxoVJChN19TlxEyh2PqXcySZWcsWGp-pw0aGewSStRgeU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Updated again May 2023:
Kids treated us to a Mother’s Day lunch and food, portions and service were very good. We ordered vegan as well as non-vegan entrees (see pics).
Only observation to note is that peanut sauce for the salad rolls wasn’t very peanuty flavoured.
Based on today’s meal, I am bumping my rating up to 4.5.

Update Jan 2023 **bumping rating from 1 star to 3.5: Gave this long time ND local Vietnamese Restaurant another go after an ownership change last year.

One of the owners was behind the counter tonight, very friendly and his partner Leslie, in the kitchen owns a Vanc. restaurant.

Our server was pleasant, albeit some confusion with our order, also due to our unfamiliarity with the menu.

We ordered the House Special Phò (L) $16.99, Deep fried Spring Rolls (2 to an order, $2.50 ea), Assorted Seafood Wonton and BBQ Pork with Noodles (S) $16.99, Deep Fried Rice Paper Spring Roll $4.50 and a Lemongrass Bahn Mi $8.75 to-go.

The soups were hot (as they should be), the DF Rice Paper Roll was greasy tasting and I didn’t care for it but everything else was good.

Make sure you ask for the chili oil, it’s bomb and a tasty condiment with soup and noodles.

My previous bad experiences were with dayshift employees so I hope the new management has corrected that.

Update Jan 2022: Went with friends for lunch to see if the poor service from hired staff had changed at all. Unfortunately it had not, food is plunked on the corner of the table without any acknowledgement. Nobody came back to check on tea/water refills. Requested the bill and same. Food was ok but the service leaves a bad taste in the mouth and doesn’t warrant a return IMO. Doesn’t seem to affect the local customer loyalty though as it’s been this way for years.
Demoting to 1 star.

Got take out beef noodle bowl (Phō)- large #6 well done brisket and skirt flank-$10.99. Soup was very hot but not as flavourful as Phō99 which is our go-to, but closed. Comes with generous portion of beef and the usual sprouts, cilanto, lime, basil, jalapeño and hoisin sauce.
Hadn’t been for couple years, while the owners are very nice, friendly people, the servers have not always been very attentive (to the point of being rude) in the past.
The food has always been quite good though.
Located in a strip mall with a variety of businesses and ample parking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOnZ3Ufs7YsPQXmcMlvLnP0b-99yAaE24QWZ-s&fid=0x0:0x80f8ec4ed8554885"],"When":"2022-2-22"},{"Name":"Ronald Retandy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKiVTWQFKjqXe4UnsBFRIZ7GxF9tGrva9JzQ7uYayyA9RXk6w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been going here for more than 20 years, I heard it was operating under a new owner last year. We've been going here a couple of times, food is still good. Deep fried wonton is still my favorite, pho is still decent.

Price has gone up by double though, and I'm not too sure how to feel about it.

Decent food and good service, might be the last time we come here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbTw75FjErm7R-a_7nB94qQmPqncf4mhCCSU68&fid=0x0:0x80f8ec4ed8554885"],"When":"2021-2-7"},{"Name":"Taz C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ235c-1POJF85QGI4N_CFSzUmrADwRBXdKObCvBIDceTrCYTc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Awesome food, big portions. We frequent this place despite poor customer service because of the food.
Their pho is by far the best I've had in the lower mainland. Perfect balance ir flavours and aroma and generous portions. Customer service is pretty average, kinda makes you feel like you are in Asia.  The staff are neither polite nor friendly or will crack a smile but they are fast and efficient.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1sKj7fxG0xMXQ80l3cn7x3skRhMX4Ay4ujxG3&fid=0x0:0x80f8ec4ed8554885"],"When":"2020-1-19"},{"Name":"Dallas Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMYF_2uOmj792l9EGoe7IgcbejSm4xJDnldT3f_eKAsHBaj3Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best pho in North Delta! Tucked away in the corner of the shopping complex so it can be hard to miss. But once you have had one of these amazing dishes, trust me, you'll never go anywhere else! Food comes quickly and it never dissapoints! Good sized portions for your money too! Whether it's pho, chow mein, or a simple vermicelli bowl, it's all delicious!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMM6lbG1VWiUeM-AtejYlMcL1VV267CqEa6Qv8u&fid=0x0:0x80f8ec4ed8554885"],"When":"2021-6-20"},{"Name":"James H Terre","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQe3cD2OAW2WicJ2iFvBRW7BSYgRuA0F0JJhj-r3nWIlovZFE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"rare steak, beef brisket, tendon, tripe beef noodle soup (15.99) / rare steak, tripe, beef brisket, tendon satay noodle soup (16.99) / butter deep fried chicken wings (14.5)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPrgTxQwve5BJkGgsXYWShL48X-r9EyGaQnOBi&fid=0x0:0x80f8ec4ed8554885"],"When":"2023-8-10"},{"Name":"stephen wilde","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrvNleje5tgYYW4_yJssFvWvErjTDdku1cFBuV2wYdlHLfuh1S=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"sadly we had to wait for a very looooong time for our food. there were only a few other diners in the restaurant and only one server who looked a bit frantic. when the meals did arrive - they were dropped at the end of the table for us to figure who’s was who’s. i did see a number of to-go orders leave and can only speculate they were filling delivery orders and not attending to their in real life customers!!!! i ordered the chicken sub. it was the last to come and not until we reminded the server we were missing 3 of our meals. i took mine to go. now i bite into an extremely disappointing cold cut sub with dry bread. sad.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMDBiV8IWiYrc1EjFrzMuzhl6wYKCpYphTl0Q76&fid=0x0:0x80f8ec4ed8554885"],"When":"2023-1-22"},{"Name":"T Radons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLSlrOzuvgcVDj3aymAbLi78FkANCC9Xc5TtjYnP6GCW8zNqw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Front staff were absolutely awful to deal with, refused to provide any information on allergens in the dishes, infact at one point said they and the kitchen staff had no idea what ingredients were in the food. Asked for a manager or owner, she refused to provide a contact number and instead suggested I eat somewhere else and call back at a later time to see if the manager was in then.  Would NEVER trust this restaurant to eat at or spend a dollar of my money.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandy-Lynn Davidson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlrDRKj5gXrEMDMqfm1JmhzCsZkr9P0sp4JvsPu1nMwv-_YZUe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am very loyal to my usual spot but after seeing the reviews we decided to give it a try. I had the small #12 with the rare beef on the side. I am happy to announce that I was not disappointed!! Priced as usually for this type of dish. This is a great place and the lady who served us was quick but friendly. My only critique would be for them to offer water when you get there as we were only provided with the tea. Tea is nice but I enjoy ice water when I have spicy phò. We will definitely be back as it's so close to our home 😊🍲👌🏼
Cheers to a great phò!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNaPniHMd8GtuQXgcJ4YEPnGbg6_RAH5n_CVBfU&fid=0x0:0x80f8ec4ed8554885"],"When":"2018-11-14"}]

[{"Name":"Andrew Melville","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPE8YK95HJDhY7cASAaoJAorc8OeKtZyg_wZ5oMnnQktmUO1SP1A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ahoy, wanderers of the sea and seekers of the divine crust! Pizza Daddy here, casting tales of the Ali Baba Pizza stand at the Tsawwassen ferry terminal, where each slice is a legend woven from the Arabian Nights.

Here, amidst the bustling throng of travellers, lies a treasure as coveted as any found in the caves of wonder. Each pizza, a caravan of flavor, travels far beyond the ordinary, offering solace to the hungry soul with its bountiful, belly-filling delight. As the Quran enlightens, "And He it is Who feeds but is not fed." (Quran 6:14), Ali Baba Pizza nourishes us, mirroring the generosity of the heavens.

Yet, amid this feast for the senses, the crowd swells like the tide, bustling and vibrant. And like our wise old friend who once faltered atop Coit Tower, the sheer delight of these flavors might just sweep your feet from under you!

Four stars to Ali Baba Pizza, a beacon of culinary mastery in the Tsawwassen ferry's ocean of motion. Here, every pie tells a tale as rich as Scheherazade’s, and every bite is a passage through the gates of flavor paradise. Sail in, fellow mariners, and let your taste buds embark on a voyage of discovery!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEaOlYe9A1p6hsraHj2Yuu0Iv3ZEJ63WxghIYf&fid=0x0:0xc8dde9ead8481237"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"Byron Sheardown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNqxb0c_42J36yKVRNJaOWQgsDJlMUDs94sxLG_b3F9RGXTQ_D=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good size of slices and fair toppings for a locked in market (ferry terminal/airport/stadium you don’t have much choice!)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5k7G81dVOd6BsDjDky4Muj0ujgEMGpIqLyPU7&fid=0x0:0xc8dde9ead8481237"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Grace Tsang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV77q3lDBN8pyeGIjZJpsbYkDymBOHRI6bxP5NZw6IAoley5AER=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"10 minutes wait time for a freshly made whole pizza. Crispy yet soft crust with ingredients loaded on top. Ingredients were a tad on the salty side, but it was overall delicious. Would return if craving pizza while waiting for the ferry sailing again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmLiHEbeNGhH8Rrynt9TMYJNt_kiymQkpCQhxR&fid=0x0:0xc8dde9ead8481237"],"When":"2023-6-9"},{"Name":"Jens Frederiksen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLsrhdCHPY2OrPKIjsdNbpAjF_nXtXu6vGlOOj2CS-je8U2rc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Taste like cold cardboard for 8 bucks a slice. Do your stomach a favor, don't eat here","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMv_LDKHXUDSwPncD-tBOCmES_KHjHXq4znkOzb&fid=0x0:0xc8dde9ead8481237"],"When":"2024-8-2"},{"Name":"FlowChange 54tyr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocICGPrTjhTgGbTQcSAnbtb1J0YUgbAn6naDFjb4mBlhRlbVjA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Gross cheap tomato sauce probably made from green tomato and vines. I also thought you guys had multigrain, why do you never sell multigrain slices, I don't want to eat 'enriched' bleached flour.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ester Toews","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK0lvfEbti3pFbGKEKUkNLb5_iyrWcQnExXZNYtJ6DBEvlJYn4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pizza is pretty good, and the slices are large.

Service was okay. On the slow side and not especially friendly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Noah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMIWXtiOkjovWGo1mbbKniEe1eklCMvUnlzMTTz6YbMYlYj_TO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This place was so good idk why it has such a low rating. Sure the prices are a bit high but the slices are huge and for ferry food this is amazing. Pepperoni with parmesan added on top and it was delicious. Can’t wait to come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPtpMmi-woNPg_TtYnMP9ZmPEDxrDLDsip9mmKk&fid=0x0:0xc8dde9ead8481237"],"When":"2022-7-11"},{"Name":"momentoftransition","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJigyNdUAXTr6SzaLVHnR9mEaUlZkHmTRVXTHXPau6viFta5K8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Zero stars. They had one kind of pizza only and for 6 f-_$#&ing dollars it is half the size of an Ali Baba slice in town. This is a  joke. I want my money back. Never eat here. Totally taking advantage of the captive crowd at the terminal these vultures leave you dissapointed. Other reviews of satisfaction make me wonder if the guys I dealt with were actually ripping the place off by selling twice as much pizza and pocketing cash sales. Either way it was very unsatisfactory.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNKiKY9lXt_kfCjUpdv97Ac52ooCZxoGmqZIfrZ&fid=0x0:0xc8dde9ead8481237"],"When":"2018-5-14"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Parneet Kahlon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqz_l5BzN5_mBY3QC7SEZWEVervEPkE_VocF-ECzkBQsGcdPO6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was craving indo- Chinese food a lot and wanted to try a new restaurant. Came across this restaurant and it had good reviews, so decided to give it a try, must say they did not disappoint.

We ordered
1. lemon chicken- so far the best lemon chicken ever tasted, lemon sauce tasted fresh and flavourful, even chicken was crisp and juicy and no smell at all.
2. Chicken Hakka noodles- so good exactly what I was craving for. Lot of veggies and chicken and plus portion size is so good.
3. Paneer Manchurian- wasn’t expecting what we got, but it was much more.. paneer, veggies, sauce everything was amazing.

Definitely worth a try. Will be going back to try few more things.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNy-9bEGUIa9RuGiQfhCF1ksFMamO1YS5qoiEDc&fid=0x0:0xadd6447877bd9fc"],"When":"2024-5-5"},{"Name":"Asif Asad Jan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-H8QYQjNPnQpvnOIo3aT330ZoDHwOQdzvDzJ5RZh4Z_6p8x_B=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After hearing a lot of good reviews, we decided to visit the a/m restaurant last week.
It was a nice small restaurant with only take-out option. Few seats, where you can wait while restaurant prepares your order.
The owners are super nice people. Very friendly and helpful.

As for the food, portions were huge. We had them the same evening and also the next day, yet we still had some left-over.

Everything was tasty. Friend Shrimp Wontons were nice and crispy with good amount of filling. Tasted great with its sauce.
House Special Chicken was very good, had a lovely kick of spices. I totally enjoyed it.
Chicken Chow Mein was the best. Great flavour of chicken and veggies with yummy noodles.

Chicken Cream Corn Soup tasted really good. It had cubes of chicken which was kind of strange for me as I'm accustomed to shredded chicken. I would prefer shredded anyways (my preference).

Overall, we had great dinner for two days.
I highly recommend this restaurant 👌","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkXRLwtAOvZ5Qs5oqrE8OjPG7LCulJVZuUebUL&fid=0x0:0xadd6447877bd9fc"],"When":"2023-11-2"},{"Name":"Zeeshan Sohail","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQzSgXcEIo5d0fY039IL3LLi7k1i-9eyjB9u0xnur9BQekUdtD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is only take-away but the taste is so on point it's a must have in the BC food scene. Crispy Chilli Beef, Chowmein, Egg Fried Rice, Sweet and Sour Chicken and Honey Garlic Wings are to die for.  Absolutely fantastic Chinese food every single time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNYyvpCBI8bUAXCvVXfONkjl8Qb7osluGxWhWP&fid=0x0:0xadd6447877bd9fc"],"When":"2023-12-30"},{"Name":"Jerry Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7RBlhmiqlmWEVXQb9JHQrpND43nYDVl3HJ7FJRNUCikja0DiP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pictures don’t do it justice!

Curry eggplants has a very unique taste and so perfectly executed. The fusion between Chinese and Indian is surprisingly delivered through the Chinese cooking style, with Indian flavour, and more nuances in between.

Tofu with vegetables and Crispy beef (sweet and sour) are both crunchy and saucy, great white rice pairing dishes.

All the dish you can customize the spicy level.

The owner is very friendly and attentive, shared some great stories about their unique journey from India to Vancouver to North Delta.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_-_wWJJZ5b-uICWkUrJHRyCcWyBIuGZL9VIbm&fid=0x0:0xadd6447877bd9fc"],"When":"2023-1-30"},{"Name":"Amrita Nayak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJgJ3b8LMBlPc7G1Rv8sy6cyH33IeJwYGYkw6c-i8ocBKF5odAKg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We order regularly from this place and they never disappoint. Food is delicious, portions are huge, they do not skimp on the meat and the service is excellent. They go out of their way to make the items to your liking, exactly how you want it.
What makes the food even better is the people who run this. They are super nice and always greet you with a big warm smile.
Some of our favorites - Manchurian fried rice, ginger garlic chicken, masala (curry powder) fried rice, black bean chicken.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTte94SYdZUDHEgZM2OsuRdRIA5Xqz4E8py662&fid=0x0:0xadd6447877bd9fc"],"When":"2022-11-2"},{"Name":"Syed M Kazmi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFPoFab8kRIuO97MoMRl6sTxjS02YjKCGuudVSUEA8Tr-nlg2z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered for take out from Manchu Masala. Their sweet and sour chicken is staple for us to order as it's balance of flavour and sweetness is just to my liking. I thoroughly approve their use of pineapples for this dish.

Their egg fried rice was good and the vegetables chow mein was excellent.

Tried their garlic chicken for the first time and that was a hit. It had the sweetness like their sweet and sour, but more of a garlic flavor twist. It was delicious and something we will order again.

Excellent portion sizes with reasonable prices and really good taste.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWweI4UXOHcqAC8elcTRBs-P_UgrfCc0GJCQ4c&fid=0x0:0xadd6447877bd9fc"],"When":"2022-4-28"},{"Name":"Emily L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwMr5VlKt9ECBUDKUi62kHV2PESObS8EDu0Fr68tChck1Pc-Li=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been here since they opened in 2020. It's always my go-to for affordable and yummy and quick food. Could not go wrong. Love the staff, mama and paps kind of atmosphere and they are so sweet and kind.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jay Morgen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8eQhyjxINm15a8wZ5LZ0QB76sRSJyG8yl9te5yRgVrwsJj8MA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing hakka food. My first time trying tonight and was very impressed
Wonderful flavour, great portions and quality. The meat was cooked to perfection and spices well balanced. Also really really nice people who run the place. They do deliver but are not on skip or ubereats and do the delivery themselves which I really respect. I will absolutely be going back next time I want chinese food and highly recommend","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Treesa Jose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFAcEvrf5W4OuIeuAB0aqqRE5Cp6_m6FulMnOH78o-tGG2Cn__OA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I always enjoy dining at Cactus Club Cafe. The atmosphere is great and the food is always delicious. The menu has lots of tasty options. One among my favourites is the lettuce wrap.

The place is clean and comfortable, making it a perfect spot to relax and enjoy a meal.

Highly recommend Cactus Club Cafe for its good vibes and amazing food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvBckkymuHYevzyFigZWjyhjoyPn1-y6U6Ao_7&fid=0x0:0x4c9e73b53a52ba79"],"When":"2022-3-29"},{"Name":"Maschanka Fernandes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7ToBWhyLBbGLZ9_8uWWhNnrT3Kh2_4kSVOU9RxE3Xv4dVckVdYw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I absolutely loved the food and drinks. We even got the dirty fries but it was over before I remembered to take a picture. The steak and Cajun chicken were so good🤌🏼🤌🏼😍. My only complaint with this location is how loud people can get.. I've been here a few times and I just feel like it's always been really loud..not something the restaurant can really control but it'd be nice if I could hear the person across the table.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZ1I9ff8k7SsvyOuYK_SCS_3ipe_0Q5uoARYk4&fid=0x0:0x4c9e73b53a52ba79"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Jennifer Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFO0fgPBTIA1yxL3IXSghRJ6EmshLC1YB1a72b-xeg3kpjHx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lunch date with my husband. We both got the garden burger, mine with kale salad and his with Parmesan fries. Everything tasted great. He enjoyed his Bellini as well. Service was fine and so was the atmosphere. We had a booth on the lounge side so the televisions had a lot of real estate.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0nTs9r8OkoFwPxQl6OaCYv3lc5HGTVHIOPDCu&fid=0x0:0x4c9e73b53a52ba79"],"When":"2024-6-15"},{"Name":"lakshdeep kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIISZRidimqWboS9maAeYnKcwByIOMiqSw_sC4nCVDC-5ebhMA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Having the best food in town. service was great and everything's really good! love it. Highly recommend to try cactus club anywhere!
Cyra you are best will come to see you again thanks","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_bZOehEo7ohWGo6z7HZpH3aXAXtdKgB2Qp-0E&fid=0x0:0x4c9e73b53a52ba79"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Rakib A.H.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdgGXpXjQ46vmG0qRSPqmRaIuaZRrwz7FYbPxUP82i4D1GWkU17A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Really tasty food. Every item we ordered was great in taste. But sad that they don't have any halal meat options. So some of us were limited to vegetarian or seafood options only. May not be 100% enjoyable place for Muslim customers.

Music in the place is too loud, making it difficult to have conversations.

Pictures of LavaCake and 6 layer chocolate slice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKGqvyucu7lSIVA9HSPThSjZ0Vk0gRMcPw3-oV&fid=0x0:0x4c9e73b53a52ba79"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"Karen Steeves","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdM3Z2sJAFypJ-VonrGDSGhT-1nBT0031AG3gCcRFjn-kVUk2J=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Cactus is a classic! I enjoyed my birthday dinner on the patio with my mom here last night. The hibiscus drink is my favourite and I tried the butternut squash ravioli for the first time and it was delicious! Thank you for the cake ♡","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWbaTVP2Uqm5-G40TrhZNJ1HmZN6CFbSSJ3e0k&fid=0x0:0x4c9e73b53a52ba79"],"When":"2024-7-22"},{"Name":"Shierly Yolanda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUF095OeEzpSqLbe7Rx8sJGnw-Qm4kHB3lenS6Vg0qNm0JBnwBl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Having the best food in town. I always love western food so don't mind me loving this one. service was great and everything's really good! love it. Highly recommend to try cactus club anywhere!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOKXJdKTB6_3HerV2QtxkgtcJMkhgGxmcHoIr0x&fid=0x0:0x4c9e73b53a52ba79"],"When":"2024-6-24"},{"Name":"Amritpaul Sokhi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLeGpAOnTs4MhIDTSFure1fBwjINgZUYyEFf09q8_A581lYuA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We have an reservation for 5 @8:30 fri 27th at Scott road Delta location,we got there 8:15 and the girl ask us to wait. So waited untill 8:45 with my 88 year old mom who couldn't stand that Long  4 of the girls standing there no one offer a chair for her . We were about leave ,my daughter ask them what's going on? The girl then check said somebody else taken our seat ?? We still waited to get the table. And that's not it we ordered two coke and water .One of the coke glass has stain on top edge (photo attached) or some kind bacteria 🦠.They gave us new one but seems it wasn't a big issue for them .After seeing that we couldn't eat and we paid and left the food . You decide if you want to eat in that kind of restaurant.if the glass is that dirty imagine what will be in your food.We will never go to any of Cactus club.Dont deserve even on star for service,food or hygiene.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGXXubJrAS_pawI48qvj0Xjt__rihQ1x11hxgY&fid=0x0:0x4c9e73b53a52ba79"],"When":"2024-10-15"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Marco Ropke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkFcDdZrGOV_ZEyfdKDMOAjSOrXoSHuAfL7QJQtzfZqg2THv13=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sunday evening, rainy day and a really pleasant surprise for dinner at Sharkeys. The Nachos were loaded, chowder was delicious, the pulled pork Mac & cheese was one of the best ever, mussels & frites awesome and the big seafood Choppino was outstanding. The food was very good, you could tell there was a real chef in the kitchen. However, best of the dinner experience was server Diana, who was just a lovely lady who provided service the way it should be. Choosing the right moments to approach our table, same time super attentive with a natural service. Kudos to the whole team at Sharkeys , well done ! We will be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvfZaZhTERBxzHrEaWki63ZIXnjs9SnflPnbc6&fid=0x0:0x14372c4ba9bb6c15"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Spoke Spurr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6SBXwfGoUXIMfCRHI82vggrz0MEiQ4COzIjzyCQuY_w8CfkTv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This is a nice place but I think we came on an “off day”. Servers were very busy chatting with selves but I get it, only 6 patrons 🤷‍♂️
One star for the $17 for 5 shrimp!!
The rings were good as were the Caesar and $5 pint.
$45 for a snack seems unfair.
I’m happy the locals support it but we won’t be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPV-X2I7ffvdaamqkNfrEEr7F3svgv_T_qiyEWU&fid=0x0:0x14372c4ba9bb6c15"],"When":"2024-7-29"},{"Name":"Raymond Campbell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXldjV3i4-BTickKCXNM1ff98zOTT1RjfPjijGIUlY6ZcOfNWAP5w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ok… if you have not been here before. Jump in your car or bike or walk here Asap. The patio is amazing. The food is spectacular. I have been here about 4 times over the last  4 years. It honestly feels like it just gets better every time. The garlic steak bites are a 10. Clam chowder is a 10. I promise you you will not be disappointed. Yes it’s that’s good. Plus the beer is ice cold ♥️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXs3ogNR3amJ6ZsF7dllX2180-jZMX-Qxm7CHu&fid=0x0:0x14372c4ba9bb6c15"],"When":"2024-4-18"},{"Name":"Graham Young","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxN9FUaBPDzGoSAkZd5lDRepWEvNLzTSr9VZyeNWRs12MDuw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As of Nov 2024, 2 for 1 Cod & Chips on Monday with 2 beverages.  Good deal and helps patronage on a normally slow day - smart!  Attentive service, super fast and batter was not too thick.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBbzbJeGxxHZuCq2nflOPd1FlCFroAPdouLiGo&fid=0x0:0x14372c4ba9bb6c15"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Karen Ashcroft","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKOCMzrTEO-OdpEhLtNZWge2eQ0j9FmUbiNfT-8yyUjm011-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was good. I had the Ladner burger. It was tasty but nothing special. Service was great. We ate out on the patio watching a bald eagle or two in the trees. The location was scenic.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6fxUppglbRyjSJZtSyORtOCQ0HTTfjHCXZ1cM&fid=0x0:0x14372c4ba9bb6c15"],"When":"2024-6-9"},{"Name":"Chris Van Luven","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2h20svqHRt1zmTV8Q_6syn8tS3URWzdAtBXtqTx6mx0KnZFDu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Old school pub style place.  Service was friendly and knowledgeable about the menu.  What seems typical pub fare is actually better than that.  We ordered the calamari and was very pleasantly surprised with a very tasty dish.  Followed by the garlic shrimp ceaser wrap that delivered on quality.  Recommend this place when you’re out in Ladner.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Silvia Ramirez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVa6JSptOp2BQVu9z96XMoK9p5Kyo9-2r_Gs3c5u4eE5VGwH9iuAw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love their chowder soup. Honestly, I'm not a big fan of their fish and chips, but their salmon burger is amazing.
The service is great, the staff is very polite and the place is clean and cozy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"T-sky w","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0uEsH9cmoXM44maq4LpVeMX01iq76aPxdjsa_7JuBIb5Y9RZO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place has been one of my new favorites since I moved to lander. I remember only one staff member out of all them and she has the biggest and kindest heart ever when you get to know her. My partner and I just went to the place yesterday because we haven't been there in a while. I love the food for sure.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Edwards","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEP0al1u4j1WWeQ8yd0aKgNYb7za23fm-6OXr32zmpPgsC1t0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff were very accommodating for my daughters wheelchair and we had a great time before catching the ferry. Highly recommend this location!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEC2W2kT3Eqd0njv1NTvGjCguvnBe3VzgFA-3L&fid=0x0:0x9a78f20219c35a07"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"Micaela Robinson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2QksgdiepfAQ10tl72lYcRqkt6l1FugMIhmMIfzOnP4rJ1IYySg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"1st off, the service here was amazing!! Fast, attentive, honest, personable, all that good stuff !!

2nd...the food was fresh and delicious.  The perfect filling breakfast !

I do like how refills on pop are free and they come out of a Can!! Not a machine.
We will go here again! I'm just sad it took us so long to try it !

(For the record...I think our servers name was Izabell? Or something like that)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqycXoD1CmIek7TzEoJKROFabbcA8K5j6aDwoV&fid=0x0:0x9a78f20219c35a07"],"When":"2024-3-12"},{"Name":"Joanna Grayston","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrC7KjOQnUkpDb0o1Z5QoMiOQSSH_WTFV9ongUvTT0mRd6jQpS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The breakfast menu is enormous.  Perhaps a  little too big.  Great service, good breakfast, pleasant and clean restaurant.   Pannekoek was delicious, and my mum enjoyed her omelet.  Food would receive 5 stars if they improved their hash browns.  1 cm, frozen, fried cubes are a little disappointing","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jay A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0RELLdGDmU4mUU2O4splg5RoL3yTJnShh825sqC7IizJnW3IrnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It has been awhile! When de Dutch closed their location in Richmond, that was basically the time when I stopped eating from their chain as well. Didn’t want to go to Vancouver since parking was as bad or worst than what we had in Richmond. But!!!! When I heard they opened up a new one in Tsawassen, I got excited. Didn’t pack my bags and went but waited it out since it is a long drive from Richmond; moreover, prices are a bit high. Anyhoo!! When my family and I eventually went (we took a bigger table), the place look clean and modern, on top of it, their pastries are from COBS BREAD! Support local! Food wise, it was because of de Dutch that I started loving eggs bene! And I still love it! Their serving were still big.. the orange juicer was interesting as well. I should say, our brunch was well worth it! Service was awesome too! Sorry, we forgot our servers name but you know who you are! :D everyone did an awesome job there! Keep it up!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7c5Qv_Yz0n7UclRutxkJTsyNDLWDW6QKMBU8r&fid=0x0:0x9a78f20219c35a07"],"When":"2023-6-19"},{"Name":"Aida Cowdy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYOSMyUOPMwT4wqDue1PDS2-0KlV4tjaFl0JOj2dSBgi8VQ6U8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s nice to see that there’s still a De Dutch that you could go. My pannekoeken is just a bit overcooked (a little toasty) than usual, the ambiance is nice and tidy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzTZn-vz9adBc56AqKw7xacMQPoqqW5MagUBH6&fid=0x0:0x9a78f20219c35a07"],"When":"2024-8-17"},{"Name":"Mike Burge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNAufzm35P7WKYUsGaq4nX78UrH9cF6tcGhMUNx0wZkbgLkg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was really good. Service was great. Very friendly server. They allowed us to sit on the deck and keep our small dog under the table. The hash was delicious. The Boer breakfast was great. Both large portions.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwU8dMXtKfNDebS3DB6MGeEHD-_k3A3qMIE38&fid=0x0:0x9a78f20219c35a07"],"When":"2023-5-20"},{"Name":"Mary Yang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKp_JevLlEsOcZ3N_Dqhy1I4TQ04Cls_o2gejUEW32RI86ZIg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My Mom and I shared the Peach&Rasberry Pannenkoek and the Salmon Breakfast Platter and it was a perfect split of savoury and sweet. Service was awesome and very friendly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carey Barrett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXv8CzCurNTkqM0sswBjR6onA-0bAgLd7UqVm12sX74NcIQwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We were sat quickly, but waited over 10 minutes to be approached by a server. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Donna Izabelle Abes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmbe8krcBH6aWNPHx97hR5NlSV-iP3Rn3nrjA5v7O3c1gJw9M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came in (first time) for dinner last night. Place is quaint and homey. Floors were a little slippery though, not sure if it's really that way. Anyway, the lone server was very soft-spoken and nice and kindly explained the menu for kids as we had our toddler with us. The lighting was a bit dimmer than I liked but they had these little oil tea lights on the table but server did not light it up because of our toddler which we appreciated.

The food took a while even though we were the only ones there. But it made up for the wait as the food was really good. The flavours were amazing. We had the roast lamb, chicken skaras, and kalamari which were perfect. The portions were huge and we still had one container full of leftover after dinner was over.

We used to go to this now-closed restaurant near our place and the flavours were a hit or miss as sometimes it's too salty or too bland. Greek Fellas had all the flavours right.

We really enjoyed our dinner last night and I hope this place gets more foot traffic because it's that good!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMsAyAFsLdPl7gHye0VANspc1qwXv2TgnYOBuik&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-10-23"},{"Name":"Tom McDougall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0J48kC1hZM1V1aRsvHOZVDophlDmEISwqhKMFe94oVeHk06c2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

Greek Fellas in Delta is a hidden gem! This small, family-run restaurant offers an amazing dining experience with its authentic Greek cuisine. The food is absolutely delicious, with each dish bursting with fresh flavors and traditional spices. The home-style atmosphere makes you feel like you're dining with family, and the warm, welcoming service only adds to the charm. If you’re looking for a cozy spot with outstanding food and genuine hospitality, Greek Fellas is a must-visit. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPiVfm1T1AeQA9FFM3RYY3Cp9snp7BYHp0rQU18&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-8-12"},{"Name":"Jonathan Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNgq2ykZbLe2d_u0ExFniyHMucdZBry6o2uBaXifHbvE2ISiM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Possibly the best Greek place I've tried in the lower mainland. My wife and I each had different lamb entrees, which come from New Zealand. There was a saltiness to the meat, but it only enhanced the flavour rather than another it. The potatoes were infused with some sort of lemony zest, while topped with some sort of mustard that wasn't overpowering, still allowing for the potato to be enjoyed, rather than covering it up completely. And the rice wasn't a filler, but rather something I couldn't bear to miss a single grain, devouring the entire platter. Oh yeah, did I mention the salad? The sour and the freshness of the olive oil was so refreshing, balancing the flavours from the savoury bits.

The portions were sizeable. Thank goodness I forgot to eat lunch that day. The service was limited, as it's a small mom and pop type of shop. But the place was full on a Tuesday night, along with take out in what looked like a 2 person operation. And even then, the food didn't take long to come out.

So thoroughly impressed by this hidden gem in Delta! The pictures are nice, but they don't do justice to what is happening on your tongue.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBABiOogJ_3L37sEkPCAIipuQzLK5-YWnikFiq&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-6-26"},{"Name":"Paulina Pedrero Miranda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoiOld2vaC2Dv18bWNi8EDRiykD7MSCRsU3RK7RESh6xQghXxb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We arrived and enjoy the happy hour deals, the place is comfortable and the staff was very polite, the calamari was delicious, the spanakopita was a bit oily, as main we ordered a beef souvlaki, the portion was great!, the salad was a bit bland, but the potato and the rice was good, the food in general was ok.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJ4NtMGzEWyb9KkVu1gMOcKar36IxvcEGI7S8V&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Leslie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMMk25HwUFhyQjoG0usKDYaMIy_Vp018yNzS4uqMl_zDyr1No=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolute hidden gem! happy hour before 6pm. calamari, keftedes, spanakopita, ekmek and pita breads were all tasty. but what knocked my socks off was THE TZATZIKI!! So refreshing and light, I could just eat it alone. Took home all the leftover tzatziki.
Cant wait to go back and try their other dishes.
The restaurants seats less than 25ppl with 1 server, so expect a slower pace or go early.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRQjpoUFpB_LjDy45PTHLzA9_6KIZODU940xco&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Wild Wanderlust Photography","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYPQeHy2fRvptt6V1NtTq0t9CdOFiP_rQd_Emm8iYNczU9hCDSwA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was worth the wait. It didn't take forever but long enough to know that it's made well. Lamb shoulder was delicious. The pasta was also huge and delicious. My moms bday today and they brought out a dessert with a. Candle and it was also.... DELICIOUS LOL. Small place. All tables had 4 chairs, no booths. Each table had a little paraffin candle which was nice.. ambiance is important in restaurants, esp during dinner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtOUAAIeEcxYZdtm-xncw3z9OLAfLknSDGYgnn&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-11-20"},{"Name":"Rod McKenzie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLk7i0CDRtHjxSLOFIM1MJnNG4AA6zjDm6JcBm9lJVvSCWIsA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Since a small family-owned Greek restaurant. Nothing fancy.
We were a table of five sitting for dinner at 6:00.
Two couples each shared an appetizer. One couple had escargot the other calamari. The escargot was nothing special but the calamari was great.
All the dinners came with a lovely Greek salad. I had the lamb chops. There were four of them, a substantial portion and quite tasty. Two of us had the roast lamb which was lovely. One had beef souvlaki and the other the shrimp souvlaki. Everything was wonderful. And we shared a dessert which was described by our waiter as a Greek tiramisu which was also very good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7uu0ratzl5H9ZkOnGAHoRBa0fD-7CHKrrsxEA&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-8-15"},{"Name":"Jeff Hohlbein","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIPlNcDi8i8PzH35XOvMQTzasIafq7V7xqYqm0KIPq1H59B8A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The place is small but it kinda adds. Very homey authentic place with amazing food and friendly service. A hidden little gem that I highly recommend","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMW_7DA-Q3yT-Prcx3GcXhW1qSl47CQglENsIs2&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-8-11"}]

I love the tacos, great atmosphere. Not a good space for larger groups. More of a 2-4 people kind of place. Few seats. Would recommend getting the refried bean tostada 👌🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtU6qaK7W7zRJQFz4ECsolXl9PzOLmrbCmpXMu&fid=0x0:0x15866ec4c70b949d"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"Giancarlo Sagastume","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVudspcS1irgBZJQESSNdRKc2axTVFpv6bBW-jBfiYsnKYJ4n6q0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The beer was cold and delicious, blown away by how good the food was, stopped in while visiting from the east coast of the states. My sister lives locally and always talks highly about this place. She has brought me a handful of brews back to me when she came to visit me. I'm glad I got to stop in person myself this time. I Would definitely make it a point to stop here if you happen to be In the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVROuX7I9aHi2kh1489WTexyXLlzxJo_y6B2qd&fid=0x0:0x15866ec4c70b949d"],"When":"2024-5-31"},{"Name":"Marcos Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrIx99K0w17o1_jz1_EhQur2HjhBKK7Idj_Dw1mjT3aruNUbguXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I tried El Diablo Burger, and it was sensational. Paired with any beer, and that's going to be an amazing dinner for you. I really like stouts, but unfortunately, they had none, I ended up getting a german style pilsener, which was pretty good, but I hope next time there're some other options of the dark side.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWhEHSixzldYr2IAFIxBr51CUyIc1qFfx8YbXu&fid=0x0:0x15866ec4c70b949d"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"Redwood T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKi8BxE8SywOnxg7xf2JWjo4tQzJgEEsYHi9F8iXpNvqnZzIg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super friendly staff, comfortable place to hang out. The happy hour three tacos and a beer is a deal!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrea Cosi Villalva","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBoMQFJbbx9QzLLbwhkjs92uV4pggDyUiO9c0dYJ0RDxehyxie=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing beer. Birria dumplings and refried beans tacos were amazing. Service is 10/10!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrdu8JpxUdnqUaEzhq9xSAdTcnHMWiVo9oPKaF&fid=0x0:0x15866ec4c70b949d"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Yeseul Rachel Park","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVq_DXRTaHaz7GKDg7IoJa8nS8imqLxCsxz1LLKpDj4JKhQp0PF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We visited last Monday afternoon to try their craft beers and some tacos. Few people were there, so it was very quiet which was nice for us🙂 We were not that hungry so only tried a chicken taco, and it was declicious. We love their IPAs😍 Also grabbed a few of IPA cans to go. Will visit again to try other beers with tacos.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgZatIepHN12_Qm0qGaYBJrF3pwijBErEwGe4c&fid=0x0:0x15866ec4c70b949d"],"When":"2023-3-30"},{"Name":"DLH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNxoVJChN19TlxEyh2PqXcySZWcsWGp-pw0aGewSStRgeU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As ND locals I had heard and followed this local brewery for some time. Hubby is the beer drinker, I am not so it took a @welovedelta #dinearounddelta Instagram contest win for a $50 gift card to bring us for our first visit.

There is a nice outdoor patio area, good thing as it was already a full house on a Saturday (5pm) inside.
There is communal, 2+ and bar seating.
We sat at the bar, fun to watch the action and talk with the servers learning more about the beers.

We ordered a flight ($8) that they picked for us (4 light) after hubby was asked for his preferences.
Two were fruity and I really liked those. Hubby enjoyed them all and they went well with the Jerk Chicken Taco ($5.75) and Rajas & Mushroom Tostada ($5)- they are starter sized and the menu changes monthly so check the website for current IPAs and food menu.
We both had the House Burger w/house-made tortilla chips/salsa ($16) that was one of the best burgers we’ve had.

Highly recommend. We’ll definitely be back, gift card or not.

Located in an industrial/retail area along the Fraser River.
Not a lot of parking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMqpv8qVhhb7RL8ECwnI4zff5UOwvn6H8kcH5E&fid=0x0:0x15866ec4c70b949d"],"When":"2022-4-12"}]

[{"Name":"Amy Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvtm7hBqZHDYxXgP_oxkelx2FGhwfW-EuwTv9rdyjxo-_-_8Nq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I’m not that picky with poke but this one was not good. I got the Peruvian Spicy Citrus. The sauce was too salty, there was too much of it and very little fish. It was a lot spicier than expected. Portion was also quite small.

Overall, very disappointed and would not come again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOanZBdpFdTtvdYhc3NVIt66FZwcLNJ_s4kpf2B&fid=0x0:0xb32e11462bfcdb7"],"When":"2024-7-31"},{"Name":"Rubel Ahmed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcFyV0UnGjUg5eJnWh4zaitP2fi78AYcoftqix22diqKzGMwE1qA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Here’s a refined version of your message:

I'm a regular customer at Hula, both downtown and Tsawwassen locations, and I’ve noticed a big difference in portion sizes between the two—it’s like night and day. Today, I ordered the Tikki and paid for extra salmon, but I was stunned at how few pieces of salmon I received. It was very disappointing. Not worth of $21","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2aMon0SzhLu9AVzjvyfk7yfhzQEkiVxcvWGqp&fid=0x0:0xb32e11462bfcdb7"],"When":"2024-9-14"},{"Name":"Jeroen Stout","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6mbN0-4i-7Hiy53rXUS_QQOBj0N4Lv-VJYrc-yp2ho_33mNi5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time ordering a bowl here. Very satisfied with my order: double salmon, coconut rice, ancho smoky/sweet. Service was decent and fast. Atmosphere of the food counter is good, sitting places in a mall not so nice, but these are not Hula’s.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMUoXFhWqYAOjzjqv5TrAsTvvAmMsuzVz_BL4Ab&fid=0x0:0xb32e11462bfcdb7"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"Sandra Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUS3d7aZA4lMhkB4lrjOTrDjB_p6PvngmeWQeM0VFHPfzqli2Uc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We were surprised at how few pieces of protein (raw salmon for both orders) was in our bowls and how small the overall amount was. The taste was good, though.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJZPzfWmb0ZbpsorQuswzwa7i1uf4wfFzK7Edk&fid=0x0:0xb32e11462bfcdb7"],"When":"2022-5-4"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend the Ancho bowl with ahi tuna and coconut rice. The savory sauce combined with the soft hot rice, veg and tuna is perfect to my tastes. I am not the biggest veggie meal lover but there was just the right amount of greens for extra flavor and texture.
Yuzu bowl is good too.
Expensive for the portion, but you get quality seafood, fresh veg and a uniquely delicious meal. Overall one of my fave things to eat, would eat more if I could afford it.
Service is polite and fast even in busy times.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPosMNrOc9UT0GjaiceHk7X5OJgcfQBMHvJcYYT&fid=0x0:0xb32e11462bfcdb7"],"When":"2023-7-20"},{"Name":"Shanice KO","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbAiJ8WffchhFHCc7nWHUGhokAijkg1PLmCSqnL8cAc66U9E5F=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"My husband ran in to grab us two Yuzu poke bowls with tuna before we boarded the ferry. The bowls weren't even close to filled and there was the most pitiful amount of protein I've ever seen. I've been to hula a few times before at the Guildford mall location and never had this happen. I'm guessing it's a training issue or active shrink-flation. The only redeeming quality is that it tastes good but for $34 we won't be going back. Steve's Poke Bar is way better and they don't skimp on the amount of fish or toppings.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jo Zamora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRiQ0k2aipqLBzmIfT4DfVFgMtoFZ8OzkduSv0IOT7ZMof6If0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Stood here for 5 min no one seem to work here and when the person in charge came back she did not even recognize that there is a person waiting to order. She was wearing headphones   i guess she is busy listening to her tunes. This is a very bad experience and costumer service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAOv04jvYTi9C83I-P6yBpk-i7-BvZdb6Fe3ws&fid=0x0:0xb32e11462bfcdb7"],"When":"2024-2-23"},{"Name":"Ms. Fancy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBQaNfblq64oqWShq2FuM-_BC-1ScwkOJu_eYkfqvQy0DjNuPb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Service was a bit chilly but food was fresh and very tasty!
