The grilled burrito was also tasty. The person who took my order was friendly and chatted with me while I waited for my food (which came out quickly despite the rush).  I would come here again if I had to wait for the ferry.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP682wWYlglsjcWuKtvVLgFz6KoDAW67ZGz_yan&fid=0x0:0xfad1578e12b30ee6"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Cailie Crane","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOnYu3kRaeJ8J5LnpIFXVCmY9eR_qoaWzx73VJe8Z-N7brVhaorw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I told them that they forgot the guacamole, as shown in the photo. They said it was extra. False advertising.
Furthermore the toppings were so sparse, only scattered on the top later, leaving the chips underneath dry. But I didn't notice until after I ate the top layer of chips. When I pointed it out the lady rudely said "Oh they were fully loaded and you ate it and only now you complain." Ah well. Tempted to order again just to post "before" photos of the pitiful nachos.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNro2bNd941WFEVd8jm3p_rvdqnlfJS2uM8Dyz3&fid=0x0:0xfad1578e12b30ee6"],"When":"2024-10-23"},{"Name":"Bradley Scott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdXDtocJBcwGBKwHclqp33UOHzIlIwPQfgTpnHX-sfguLC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Not satisfied with the quality of food. We ordered 2 enchiladas that were ice cold. Not even the rice or meat was heated separately before assembling. They substituted shredded cabbage inside the enchiladas instead of lettuce as advertised. The tortilla was cold and stiff. Salsa was not spicy at all. Cheese is liquid drizzled on. The new operators don’t know what Mexican food is.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Davesito","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLcJPCrI3jSn6uWx0opCkW78_1UORJ3MUCjvk7ZGRzPHJ7Vqg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Get snack size for the price of a full meal! Had the burrito bowl. Portion was very small for dinner. At least put more rice in! It’s inexpensive and might help you get better reviews.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sam H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWc51YkYLzoVzVn7vYgihiJdmbFAOjiSt3Gg_AosBwjSJv5WQ9M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Contrary to most other reviews, I found the food here to be just as expected. Quick and cheap Mexican fare. Don’t expect fine dining and this place will exceed your expectations before the ferry ride.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sayesha Saleh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWRcNGGsGlYVMXhW1eWwdAI9jbWt0eXaH44abP5Vb3D6nr7mM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Terrible food i have ever seen . All the ingredients were cold . We ordered sunrise burritos and let me tell you, it was just sucks. I would say rather take a water bottle from somewhere else than ordering from here . unprofessional staff. So called maxican food i bet they don’t even know what actual maxican food taste like . Staff just only know how to say hey there , literally annoying.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christian Gregory","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhLdvrCZvC_ZLWS5-IUWrBX6AQ9pVbqh_N_vb97KyKu65zTm59=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"To put it lightly .This is the worst so called mexican food I have ever had. I had the burrito and let me tell you .....garbage . Chicken dry, terrible salsa, the tortilla was as dry as they come way overpriced for what you receive.  DONT DO IT. Do yourself a favor and get anything else.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julianna Raeburn-McCormack","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIn_6IIJVsIVV2dXu0O7Ni-agnAYQLaEPFyfKUApgB1hn_UTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Holy hell – what a horrible food experience. Now I totally appreciate that this is fast food and I am at the ferry terminal on new years eve but still… I ordered a vegetarian quesadilla with guacamole on the side. Not especially challenging. (Or so I thought.) What did I get? A dry tortilla with a thin layer of corn, tomatoes, and black beans that was warmed up on a grill. Sounds like a quesadilla, right? No - it wasn’t. There was NO friggin’ cheese to hold the contents in the tortilla, so every time I picked up one of the tiny little bite-size pieces that the woman behind the counter chopped the quesadilla into (why???), the contents fell out because there was nothing to bind it to the tortilla. Couldn’t dip it in the salsa or the sour cream - OR the nonexistent guacamole that I paid an extra $3 for but that they just never gave me. I’ve attached a photo of the contents left at the bottom of the take away container. My hand is next to it to give some size context. (I can’t believe I paid $15 for this!)

The Icing on the cake was when I dialled the number on their website to try to arrange for some sort of refund and the recorded female voice said very unenthusiastically “Yeah, you can leave a message” - but no, I actually couldn’t because the friggin’ mailbox was full! (Of course it was…)

Even though the four women were behind the counter were very sweet, just avoid this place. They are really unclear on the concept.

(For the record the reference number on my receipt dated Dec 31 @ 6:26pm  is 633596 and I paid $14.69 on my debit card should anybody care to reimburse me…)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5fJQ7dCqHVmGPkedDjON0g2ywzSFghI9YghJO&fid=0x0:0xfad1578e12b30ee6"],"When":"2024-1-1"}]

[{"Name":"Jane Vida","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW26hBCqx9OlyNdZYB77-V53rLV_usXZGpWH-UvURxKc5B1Ox0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely the best brunch around! Beautiful scenery, beautiful atmosphere, very nice waitresses. Ask for Eva if you’re there. She’s the most kind and amazing waitress. She gave the best recommendations for my taste. You absolutely HAVE to come here for brunch on Sundays! I will come again and again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNzoOdFSV6OMU9NGUmjIQP-eYECD76KWk1PxZ_V&fid=0x0:0x42a99f3de216085b"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Chris Stayko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYRNGI3ckBx5pVWutLy32EJ_hk4EUEuXeGn5Ht5f-pIzjbwg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you are truly looking for a challenging course, you have to play here it’s a must. This course was amazing to play! Traps that look like WW1 artillery zone, wind that blows from off shore, water everywhere, greens that have more curves than a model. It absolutely made me step up my game, and with beautiful scenery.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXTtArSsUgd8-saLe9EHlxchjBYHES0Bb9K7vP&fid=0x0:0x42a99f3de216085b"],"When":"2024-7-31"},{"Name":"Dominic Hung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocInSidPLNnQy5LZKttrr9YhEgZlFDXSc4uXSAVyllReHY5KOg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time playing Kings Links Golf Course by the sea yesterday and really solid fun track with wide fairways but also lots of spots that can get you in trouble if you aren’t on target.

The winds definitely wrecked some havoc on some holes where you definitely need to club up 2-3 clubs.  One example is par 3 hole 15 that has a stiff wind only 125 to pin and 115 to front of green…colleagues played their 130 clubs and hit it short of green, I said ok 140 club then and closer but still short of green 🤷‍♂️

While the driving range balls are a thousand years old lol they do have a nice simple grass driving range available to warm up.  The kitchen does close early at 5 on weekdays so that’s something to plan if you have later tee time as not much around for dinner

Plus had a chance to play with regular local player there nicknamed Froggy, and his son.  Froggy is 80+ years old and still an absolute beaut hitting a solid 77 and regularly giving good tips & tricks throughout the round.  If you get a chance to play with him (and looked like he was well known by the staff and other regular players) super fun to play with","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpiioC9vGpmboSp13YtvQ8mEj8onD4-bt8wKvn&fid=0x0:0x42a99f3de216085b"],"When":"2024-7-16"},{"Name":"Rob Bartlett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJsWXnM7aD8cOtehyZMyZtUrlXOW340mlCDEnDkp9uQcBeZ0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time around Kings Links today, dry and mild in late December. Course in excellent condition, greens rolling pure and staff very friendly. Easily my favourite track in the lower mainland.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMsKfw6Y-TIbp5E73t3v2VEk9IFlAzCzzEr65O2&fid=0x0:0x42a99f3de216085b"],"When":"2023-12-30"},{"Name":"Jim C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeuwmlBzBhnV1Tf-TNLGsR1BbNcShFl0KgSKNZR06d5EfGBCHh=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Nice golf course with great drainage while unhappy in the restaurant. We dinning after golf and the waitress is so rude  and she added the highest tips to our bills and we just ate a burger. The tip had three options while the waitress picked the highest one for us and don’t let us pick one.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Big Nate","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFQe5Mbd4SuXaq3CgIz6-90V4NY3lNOtLVWdRLAoVVOY6yt-Nr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful course in delta, near the sea with well maintained grass. The holes are often placed well enough to see your flag or green, bunker's are absolutely ridiculous but if you avoid them you will be able to do well here even with less skill. Busy busy course so expect to be pushed for pace. We walked it because it was too wet this time of year and that was no issue. Lots of water hazards and fast greens with slopage. Truly a links style course. Highly recommend this place for great food and excellent service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYywyb06I0PysWllDcyu52RP8VSRz6IeEBElCP\u0026fid=0x0:0x598db8e999254468"],"When":"2024-6-26"},{"Name":"runny maan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWs3LSkqGf3mzpywlSo_WPoreouYvBSuhH3FUJFD98VTVT5LupO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Delight Street Eats offers a decent selection of street food options in a casual setting. While the food is tasty and reasonably priced, the overall dining experience leaves something to be desired. The menu lacks variety, and the portion sizes are on the smaller side for the price. Additionally, the service can be slow during peak hours, resulting in longer wait times for orders. The owner's warmth and friendliness added an extra charm to the morning. The simple yet spacious setup of the restaurant made for a relaxed start to the day. The breakfast options were delicious and satisfying, offering a perfect way to kickstart the morning. The kind service and pleasant ambiance made this breakfast experience truly enjoyable. I highly recommend starting your day at this place for both the delicious breakfast and the wonderful hospitality!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2kkKwvzotYxkd94w2arfLISirb_cGPjkCOzfQ\u0026fid=0x0:0x3b16da3a2de176e5"],"When":"2023-12-9"},{"Name":"Jeff Astle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqpBD1la32QOHRh35fAqT7JCPqLBjqkr5aE2XHbEfgBcBEOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food is delicious all around, and fairly priced. Their business model is making it difficult to justify going, though. Between 11:30 and 1230, expect to wait up to 30 minutes in line. Then after that, they're out of food. Spending more than half my lunch break up waiting because they don't want to pay another employee is a bit frustrating.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joseph lieu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrHfDzsFsRShVEzr2PKE2oX1jaG4cxkhU0kHD4Zh7Fh-yAowEa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Gem of a Restaurant with Amazing Food and Stellar Service\n\nI can't say enough good things about this restaurant! The food is consistently delicious, with a wide variety of options to satisfy any craving. Whether you're a regular or a first-time visitor, you'll feel right at home here. Don't hesitate, give this place a try – you won't be disappointed! P.S try the wonton soup with everything included, it’s delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNVN7gJsAftUBN0o70WDtUcZ392f4NzKI5yJKIz\u0026fid=0x0:0x3b16da3a2de176e5"],"When":"2024-2-22"},{"Name":"Ron Chandra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMUKEp9NFVbFVKFyxQlhQ50VwTmMMSQVQjHTfLly7PyXiMeq63Vg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a hole in the wall kind of place in the industrial area in the Tilbury are of Delta, the breakfast is great, the Asian food is excellent, nothing is greasy or super salty, they take pride in the fresh food they cook. If you work in the area it’s definitely worth checking out, the food is quick and fresh. They are even open on Saturday for the hungover sat morning blue collar workers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kyla Peck","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFsRFGfQBc04cvbiKLoX0cfV9VneZU54J-Ub276gHLYJVuDqEN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This diner is simply perfect. Staff team is friendly and caring. Menu is rotating, options are different each day of the week. Food is home style cooking, tastes delicious, with clean and great quality ingredients. I just love how the overall experience reminds me of the good old days.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Damian Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzJt2mshcCmJU9XbBU-uZyGrPK7lWS4Jkqj1hy8k8U9GBIdJ4L=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had some spicy chinese dish, the company I work for treated me to. Best I've ever eaten was very satisfied. Can't wait to visit again !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alan Iwaasa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnN8rfrxsCESPI1UU7kLxqgkgZsqh2ZmYA_xlfP5C_3nI3Yw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place! Feels so local and family run. The food’s delicious and the staff are very friendly. So good, planning to come back here often.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_akhPyZpjBXSArXS2v5SmFX65jK8ZZuxzHln4\u0026fid=0x0:0x3b16da3a2de176e5"],"When":"2023-7-25"}]

[{"Name":"Zeeshan Sohail","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQzSgXcEIo5d0fY039IL3LLi7k1i-9eyjB9u0xnur9BQekUdtD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the most authentic Beef Bihari Kabab and Beef Nihari places in town. Wait times can get challenging during peak hours but the food never disappoints. Make reservations and order ahead and you're in for a treat. Recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPno9Y4IJST_1Bm5zkfxeuHjDnRrwTuW3rmbI0k&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-12-10"},{"Name":"Mosammat Sayeeda Islam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIL7Ridsklhzy0F-dTiRzeKjJ1HbiLtsL3eJWxmOsn450zj3DIo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We went to village BBQ last night and the waitress didn’t even say hi to us. I read the notice about 45 minutes time and understood but they didn’t even gave us water or said a thing! After 50 minutes I asked for water and then they gave us water. Ever since I asked for water that waitress was giving me an angry look. Everytime we said thx she would just look and roll her eyes and walk away. As if going to that restaurant and asking for water after 50 minutes was a crime. After 1 hour and 25 minutes we got our food and it was cold as if it was left out for a while after cooking. The beef bihari Kabab was good but would have been better if it was atleast warm. Most of all, we go to restaurant to eat not because we can’t cook but to feel relaxed and treated like guest which was missing there. I donno what is it with those girls that work there but they have some bad attitude .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4S43dXrVQOIZCuqu2QXZX0quW75IQRFRAPDBR&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"Zargham Amer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtEmcSO4oM1MO7tkZvkh3DG6vThWmTpDErildoA6Q32y1qOw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of dining at Village BBQ Restaurant and was thoroughly impressed. The food was exceptional, with the tikka boti platter and beef seekh kebabs standing out as my favorites. Both dishes were perfectly seasoned and cooked to perfection. The service was equally amazing, making the entire experience delightful. I highly recommend Village BBQ to anyone looking for delicious Pakistani food and outstanding service. Always a great pleasure coming here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkaLxu60FXxgZVE2ZEomUU_Wzd9caARZJzyD03&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-5-24"},{"Name":"Ali Jaffer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxBuzDsninlt9GBGcwFVCC48Wjy59DzbkKFiPBRKjZ81qqviGf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Enjoyed every bit, great music, best food in Vancouver, surrey. Staff are amazing. Farhan and Shahbaz. These boys are so welcoming and always with a positive energy. The onwer Mrs. Irfan Ali is so hardworking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9szUYp7W8TxRIUBiogpVztyUjNK1jR_3m6bKr&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-8-25"},{"Name":"Muhammad Khan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIV0jbJl9FA6bA_RfKt_nsNRMXRmlNEFPuiEyShHhH1LmeWP-d7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food. Tried the Bihari kabab and Nahari and they were both amazing. Naans are fluffy and very tasty. Will for sure be coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4-Bpux5UzwQTR2wNVZrHQXg-wmbDiuzvCahZF&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"Shahzaib J.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhpzuDBP6wQm6OsAyV_ouA2XY93EeHvr2Uq9kXaQt2rnrq7A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Authentic barbecue. We had the chicken behari and malai boti with the puri paratha, and both were really good. The overall package with the chutney and salad makes it perfect. The ambiance is also nice. I am looking forward to trying the rest of the menu on the next visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7ClnhO8MTsb4aYTVSOet4EtHGmTUKAxDSh3-P&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Saami Zee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-w_OK7ySRR9lB0UkR8VKffsmBtc7M_TSWrJrw-fiTDuKJrF1n=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A must place to visit for authentic Pakistani cuisine which we hardly have in Vancouver.We ordered chicken behari roll ,chicken tikka and chicken seekh kebab the food was cooked to perfection and everything was so fresh .
Though we came to eat at 10:45pm but we got good service .
The server was very polite and doing her best to keep the customer happy.
I wish village bbq best of luck in their venture here in Vancouver","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNi8pmIAAXCRTzzrliZYF5UhX-s8475t7NItCKx&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-5-23"},{"Name":"Nadeem Zia.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMvuVKaJ5RspKjafdw7NuycDlSlwvLOTMgiMvYKB8ZcmZ9sQ7d7w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Woo‼ excellent comeback; we have been missing delicious and traditional Beef Bahari Kababs, Beef Nahari, and fresh Naan.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhqzIsqvzuX_G7GHGeby5eMxbclu_bcrM8PPlK&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-4-27"}]

[{"Name":"Munro Stuff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj0Wcuk6ox5dfAeJ4fAaMbhX_F-nzzt3p5oc_f0hBd0NpbGSM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"New to the area and have been trying samosas at local places, including some well-known/highly rated. The veggie samosa at Delta Indian was WAY better than any others we've tried - excellent flavours, crispy pastry, not greasy. I didn't like the chicken samosa as much, though my partner did. We're definitely coming back to try more of their food. Friendly service as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhaUBuXspLVUpupXMmA3G1wBTtExkmYjCvQ5gH&fid=0x0:0x5306a4347950c7f7"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"TG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULhqU_yLPB5ZAPCEsV5nl0xiZrNbTJqxBrKjH-leYiaFJ3899K=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Stopped here for lunch and ordered from the Lunch Specials. We had the Amritsari Kulcha Plate and Non Veggie Combo. The stuffed bread and Naan were greasy. The butter chicken and chickpeas were tasty and good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyyEgHohbJbLYVD1nAeccGx_zvQhArkJGIuNwg&fid=0x0:0x5306a4347950c7f7"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Chia Ching Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwe2GGT3rdI6ALckS6UIqajkjqJBCpxGDpeE1RlxKE9CKicjp7fA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I ordered Butter Chicken (reg) take-out today. I think the food taste is good, but for $16.49 (before tax), the amount of meat is considered little.

But I still be willing to try more dishes when I am in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_29uTi-LyBP0UlIqnJD3d1moh5ieOyjgViWcq&fid=0x0:0x5306a4347950c7f7"],"When":"2024-10-10"},{"Name":"Wilhelmina Bateman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLy2k0C7Bj9ygMsmApx4UCd2IxlQ2pmcYnMHZAXXFlSNy3_Nw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delta Indian Cuisine is a superb eating experience. The ingredients are fresh with perfectly blended spices. The Mango Chicken is velvet and the Shahi Paneer perfection!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9nHoRMiUYL5Tu2qjjgDIT7NHvG9Hm4iowUTrS&fid=0x0:0x5306a4347950c7f7"],"When":"2024-7-28"},{"Name":"Aphelia R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiujnnp-r6a54qfOz_Nt8RloZYO2XV2hm9eIG0_31zoxJ1jlrG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered fish pakora and the eggplant curry for take out, and both dishes were really tasty! The pakora still has a nice crunch to it even though I was delayed 15-20 mins to pick it up. Price is fair, would order again and try other dishes as well**There were more pakoras than the picture shows;they were being eaten on the drive home👍🏼**","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUAc88ztHANTBTifOXse6udeHgBzLP1XxfO9ky&fid=0x0:0x5306a4347950c7f7"],"When":"2024-8-13"},{"Name":"Angel K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXki7lSOZ8eGdsXwy5XDEH06JQyFv66wnh1_34j8OAQdytKSQk-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We got the lunch special which included pop.
Delicious butter chicken. Just enough portion for a good price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0CdO_ON6VqUUPUw4JIdEuTNj582iENxr8TYkK&fid=0x0:0x5306a4347950c7f7"],"When":"2024-10-17"},{"Name":"rajat wadhwa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKV4aA2M-diDjHp_F6a1ME3IszmBqop0JwpuwNYQjGytAbwqA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"5-Star Review:

This was my fourth time visiting this restaurant, and as always, the food was absolutely delicious and amazing! Their Manchurian is an absolute must-try—one of the best I’ve ever had. The Dal Makhani and Karahi Paneer are equally outstanding, packed with flavor and cooked to perfection.
Every visit here has been a wonderful experience. The quality of the food and the consistency of flavors never disappoint. Highly recommend this place to anyone looking for a memorable dining experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Victoria","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJAO4yPpx0p9iLW4iLWQ3P4gHSOyfD1COujQXpjOtVn931Fdw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"At first when I opened this was already very disappointing barely any sauce.. then took a bite and it was so dried out it was awful. Very disappointed. Butter chicken always good but the wings were absolutely AWFUL!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOnnRlCXKV7H7af36RY3rCc-28k1vEznFIl_8on&fid=0x0:0x5306a4347950c7f7"],"When":"2024-7-3"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Kylie Gayon Woo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbxaF6A7WGi_ORpIehjp6sKn8x_LA2CUlDHfin8e218U-8eh2Iqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best Thai restaurants I’ve been! Everything was great. We ordered Pork jowl, papaya salad, pad kra pao muu, and mango sticky rice. Highly recommend the papaya salad and pork jowl. They go perfectly together. Cute interior and clean.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOO2gnHrpUXbNEZPE23YYUEPV7-L0DLHCHgU8EN&fid=0x0:0xa1ccf70607323eb4"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Sandra Leung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxzPjHNR60FtVdbK8IRtw9xCOLCbXchw0PqhcTgltEFJNNYSgQFA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stumbled into this place after playing golf nearby and saw all the positive reviews.  They have a great lunch combo for $23 which includes a drink (I chose Thai iced tea) and appetizer (opted for the spring roll) and a main dish.  This is a great value for a lunch set and I left stuffed and satisfied.  I chose the hat Yai fried chicken and the bowl was huge with very generous portions of perfectly fried chicken.  Will definitely come back and try the rest of the menu. Also thoroughly enjoyed the 90s vibe of the place.  The decor was very cute and loved how the bill came inside an old cassette tape case.  Extra touches that just added to the overall dining experience","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5zCZxmSZFkQaFprrp_gderVdLgkWKBV--DG8u&fid=0x0:0xa1ccf70607323eb4"],"When":"2024-7-12"},{"Name":"Jasleen Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJq_mX4JcS2qCxDJUdxLM5cEoBdw7wYfyUdfHLGfdunsmqsnw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best Thai food that I have ever had in a long time. The service is quick and efficient. The flavour profile of each dish was unique and amazing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCyS1VldO8DrVeiEX4h84cKCBRvKpsvSDt4FIS&fid=0x0:0xa1ccf70607323eb4"],"When":"2024-8-5"},{"Name":"Jamie L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIsaaODpzZi62wV-93lE__3OFGYxafaFgdJgxMDBfyIfS_ESBX0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Thai I've had in lower mainland.
We had papaya salad, pork jowl, pad krow pao muu, and finished off with mango sticky rice.
Pork jowl is a must must try, the meat was so tender and flavorful, with two sauces that went so well together. I wrapped the meat with green papaya salad amd it was out of this world.
Must try out this place if you like Thai food.
We will def. Come back to try their other menus.
They even had the sinus-clearing thing in the bathroom! Authentic.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNemDpU_njCp4pjkr3kp5g1_dlbDpancqfxIujl&fid=0x0:0xa1ccf70607323eb4"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Pauline","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJGkluLFawzRkcvB0xy93FJ2AGT8gSexVqXi8tpT0shbwpkvB8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Craving Thai flavors in a cozy atmosphere? Their dishes are bursting with authentic Thai tastes, and the servers are super friendly, sharing their personal favorites to help you decide. It's like a little slice of Thailand right in our neighborhood.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNMpH6a8SynKVwK_m5JRNgWejXNsW_-D9x_K3Od&fid=0x0:0xa1ccf70607323eb4"],"When":"2024-2-22"},{"Name":"Sieu Ngo (SomethingN)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKIolnpeHK_Fih9cjGEHkA4wfLWBN6-uwLZ0o_InC0i9vNg8A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was recommended by a friend to try out Soi Ram for the first time and it's absolutely amazing!  The restaurant was super busy towards the end of our meal and I can understand why.  So glad there's an authentic Thai restaurant  near our home.  My family and I loved pretty much everything we ordered.  We had the Soi Ram Fries and Muu Ping with sticky rice to start.  Followed by Prawn Pad Thai and Red Curry with Chicken and for dessert, Mango Sticky Rice.  Definitely coming back soon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXH8x56ssYAXs3gW9ZoYj9bE9XOe1eJErfmOJi&fid=0x0:0xa1ccf70607323eb4"],"When":"2024-5-13"},{"Name":"Winnie Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWeJPpw7ILy-eSHYtnntg0W05T0QO_JdebWvdeaLSSnFbNMBo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family and I visited the restaurant 3 times in February! 4 - 9 people on different visits. We loved the setting, the food, the value and the service.
We particularly loved the fried chicken, garlic fries and chicken pad Thai!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5z3CYjuKrzXjeri4sInkLby7UBsnlG2FYyKKn&fid=0x0:0xa1ccf70607323eb4"],"When":"2024-2-25"},{"Name":"Steven Huhn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjPgKgZCO5PZiQnT0cs9yON3NEoowbu1SmDyHWquv1i9Z5rrCk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My co-worker brought me to his son-in-laws restaurant where we met Brian and his wife and they are amazing. They started this with a childhood dream and the dream is amazing. The food is exceptional and like nothing I have found since my trip to Thailand. Cool vibes and great atmosphere. And authentic ideas that make your culinary experience next to none. This place would out do any place in Vancouver bar none. I highly recommend eating here.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Aplih A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_G0R4WDpsPBUSLZ2seXB0kdjihBFkT8PA-Y802ceSx6fDyw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Boundary Bay par and beach is absolutely stunning and one of my new favorite spots in B.C.. The soft, sandy shore is perfect for relaxing, and the breathtaking views of serene mountains combined with glimpses of the city skyline create a unique and beautiful atmosphere. It has walking, biking, hiking trails, horse riding and many more. Something for everyone. One of the best parts is that they allow bonfires, which makes for a perfect evening with friends or family, watching the sunset and enjoying the crackling fire by the waves. The whole vibe is so peaceful, and it’s a wonderful escape from the everyday. Highly recommend for anyone looking for a picturesque, relaxing beach experience in any season..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbVfdvUNBrDKpA4BxtsTN_yiDJXftXapj8dRYA&fid=0x0:0xdb7a949eb6a591d7"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Kanako Sakurada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYybgPjG_d3LYq66Ui47Ocd_2PMrfkKaju5V_L0IyVTR19lQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful park with long sandy beach and picnic/bbq/play ground area perfect for family.
We enjoyed walk on the gravel trail that had different sections; seaside, boardwalk (temporarily closed right now), and through grass/marsh. Flowers were in full bloom and you could hear lots of birdies chirping. It was peaceful and pleasant.
Whole loop was flat and about 5k long. Some path were shared with cyclists.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMr8DOKwKp4JJhpbkttBFwsBgoCGmNSlJ6TFkXp&fid=0x0:0xdb7a949eb6a591d7"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"Shonna Morgan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7JPOL6ol1-bGinFh8yA1wtxyNTPhprrW64A4E2h0XPIKwregqbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Boundary Bay / Centennial Beach never disappoints! Tide in or out, weather and skirts of any season, it’s always an awe inspiring place to walk and take in! Sandy beaches, paths to walk, mountains and cityscapes to view in the distance. Washroom and cafeteria service in season.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgnY4hePUCzkG9b_KAkBINwgA08UNqg0mOgcPc&fid=0x0:0xdb7a949eb6a591d7"],"When":"2024-7-19"},{"Name":"Kel Shaw","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxlG7dSzG0XCaRucFdzjLtGXMN3t4REtRn-uT0qJZlGy2kASSN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful park that stretches for miles. Hubby and I rode our E bikes out there. What a great ride. Nature in its absolute glory.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAxG2KtjA9Knj7oc4lLn-ybOKC__Edj1gFwRk&fid=0x0:0xdb7a949eb6a591d7"],"When":"2024-3-25"},{"Name":"Denise E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQbJ_L-TxI01ySLshWA7uc6C1q3KvM8JxAkqWoe9pUzobw4pkm5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Any season this park is beautiful. The trails are easy and lots of access to the beach. Parking was plentiful but by noon in hot summer days it fills up so go early!  When the tide is out you can walk forever on beautiful soft sand.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0d_AvLFuTN3KKjHgjgrN2LHrutaeLNx54YMMw&fid=0x0:0xdb7a949eb6a591d7"],"When":"2022-7-23"},{"Name":"Russell Toopitson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzZTFazrfUDRzOfCAmXm_e0kwjYMt5ikeVrrerf-k3NZRtoCaZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This ocean side park is stunning!! It's large and goes for as far as the eye can see. There are nice fenced paths leading to look out over Centennial Beach, I seen many types of birds including bald Eagles, blue herons, there is large covred picnic areas, a large pond on the right side of the park. There are alot of huge logs everywhere u can stand on to get a great view of the mountains and the beach and the ocean. This place is a must see if your in Tsawwassen.💯💯💯","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIlTtttDsOcVJugDE77boo-0ppAwN-XsHQitJG&fid=0x0:0xdb7a949eb6a591d7"],"When":"2022-4-16"},{"Name":"Tia Dawson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWF6ZjgZVjVVjDC-Tue9DLRmJg5qAnMHh1jg0YyfcF88i8h898=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a lovely place to go watch the sunrise. There were so many Eagles too! I wish I would have brought my DSLR to take photos with my telephoto lens.

This was a very quiet place to watch the sunrise- just my daughter and I and another two friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMq8zji8iTaPO6PsYxBFyhmrKiHjTtWXH0fbIan&fid=0x0:0xdb7a949eb6a591d7"],"When":"2023-3-21"},{"Name":"Nadeem Zia.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMvuVKaJ5RspKjafdw7NuycDlSlwvLOTMgiMvYKB8ZcmZ9sQ7d7w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Quite and relaxing beach site, sandy beach  and family park in Delta BC. Good picnic, BBQ, kids and youth play area, wheelchair accessible, washrooms available, lots of free parking dogs welcome here, open 7 am to 10 pm.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjieuciW0EDsnXR8_DaNyLwdGRd1xzQuWZ7fIL&fid=0x0:0xdb7a949eb6a591d7"],"When":"2022-6-21"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Monique","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQcAgOL4v2U_VirmCaadFrb2IzIMWiSeW-tX_pA5B7GcJn2vN8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of my favourite places in the Surrey/Delta border to order sushi rolls from!

I absolutely love their special roll menu. It is definitely on the pricier side, considering how much you get for what you pay. But with that said, the rolls are delicious and full of flavour.

I highly recommend the Fantastic Roll and Amazing roll if you like things like aburi and oshi and want that garlic umami flavour.

The crispy roll and yam crunch roll were great options, but the Crispy Roll was a lot better flavour wise if you were debating between the two crispy options.

Their lunch set (available before 3PM) is a fantastic value if you do order around that time!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMr33KzXn3OIRHo9rm1iYf1Z8wk92kFHH-hAAe-&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2024-9-7"},{"Name":"DLH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNxoVJChN19TlxEyh2PqXcySZWcsWGp-pw0aGewSStRgeU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Update: Sept. 9, 2024
Even though we are within walking distance we don’t go for japanese often enough so it’s good to know that the quality is still A1.
We made a tatami room reservation and our Special Dinner ($27) and Akari Dinner ($28) Combinations were excellent.
All staff are Japanese here.

Friendly staff in this cosy neighbourhood restaurant, tables and tatami rooms.
Booking on-line is easy.
Vaccine passport/photo ID checked.

Menu is large so we ordered far too much. Everything was delicious and nicely presented.
Highly recommend the Awesome Roll- crunchy bits and popcorn shrimp, suits the name.
Tea refilled a few times.

Over the 20+ years, we’ve eaten in and gotten take-out many times and quality is consistent.

Located in a strip mall (Scott/72nd) with ample parking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgZuRKeheynAs5d0XcRJpPNo6WWJjrsuTqN2A&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2021-12-26"},{"Name":"Ben Moreno","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbXIQA5QNY2om_rvFeJhZDcAcErydWjpf8dpxFoZ8JJurbSZgE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious sushi,  friendly and fast servers,  bento boxes are great choices,  reasonable prices,  recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOc9Vb9U5wjij4Jhw7N7xvZnVNwq5wxxouvmziF&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2024-9-7"},{"Name":"Ueli Hartmann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7Fd4w8RA0hoxJvIo4cVNTkMMMVZflfjrD9cusB0rnaVp3t4T_ug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing Sushi, quality was extremely good, I can only recommend this place! Good service and always going around with tea!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMK03wIwT7jW1iU1c00XbfeUk8sD7uoxNzDk1Mr&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"sng1002001","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTfKdGFrJyL8jc4znhIMXimj1BkuJ1S_SEthxZmoeo2Gf8Rg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Long time sushi establishment across from Scottsdale Centre. Good variety of sushi, sashimi, special rolls, and lunch/dinner boxes. The seafood ingredients used are fresh. Really like the various rolls (e.g. Fantastic roll) - good size and good blend of different fish. Fast food service. Apparently they have a sake sampler during the Christmas season - 3 shots for $7.50!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGOjEx74RpX5u3_OCN8pF6GRj0t6RYRAe-MBa5&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2023-12-26"},{"Name":"Ethelyn David","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXK4VlApGUESMpUmHtkuNaKascPX1JKNkMvVUC-VoUsoOtTyUJ6IA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a faithful client since they opened. Always felt welcome and the items I ordered never disappointed (whether eat in or take-out).  Good size portions very tasty, great presentation, fresh sushi and sashimi, and the service is always great. Pleasure doing business with you Julian and staff!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1JnJFCZ-GzpnpFSpITvTLhxRci-gSRmGDvWwg&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2024-3-25"},{"Name":"D SAM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAPZJhKwbwofRMAxzu-Q9mFomEMmhsUcyi8-_CMghvFMl0UXMbEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This place is busy. Reasonably priced. Customer service was good but not excellent. Hard to call waiter’s attention. We had to get up and no one checks in on us. The food was fresh except for the stir fry veggies and black rice. The veggies was overdone and the rice was dry and obviously not freshly cooked. Otherwise the chicken and tofu teriyaki and the prawn tempura were perfectly cooked. It’s a good hang out place for family and friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhaXqQpnUmguN9ivS9aS5wDQ2dSDqNMa7Kfiqg&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2023-6-1"},{"Name":"film by lily","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUSiIn37gm0M4cUD38_C7-DlPW8VoGO46izDz__BjLERifsXLSAw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was bomb! Our first time here and we will definitely come back:) If you’re going with a group of friends definitely do the deluxe boat!
Must-try items: Akari House Salad, Tempura, Agadashi Tofu, Crispy Roll.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZFTU289eU_YZsBaJTLO7sGc5pIlaxMSftDcQf&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2023-12-29"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"nadine Horwood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX444VqGhqsb13DWSE8cS2NTZfh0UetAK47_g5--7ZIkaW0Awfu2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Salt and Steak is an absolute gem! From the moment we walked in, we were greeted with friendly, attentive, and personable service that made us feel genuinely valued as customers. The attention to detail was remarkable, from the perfectly timed check-ins to the thoughtful recommendations.

The food was nothing short of exceptional. Each dish was a masterpiece, perfectly seasoned to tempt the palate without overwhelming it. The portion sizes were just right—generous enough to leave you satisfied, but not overly indulgent. Every bite was a testament to the chef’s expertise and passion for flavor.

The atmosphere struck the perfect balance between cozy, classy, and casual, making it an ideal spot for both a relaxed dinner and a special occasion. It’s clear that every aspect of this restaurant, from the ambiance to the menu, has been designed with the customer experience in mind.

I highly recommend Salt and Steak to anyone looking for a dining experience that combines outstanding service, delicious food, and a welcoming environment. This place is a true standout!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOfBrT-Ysex42YZ36PGFv526MR-CkSJcYaoHvIp&fid=0x0:0x4f9729eea2d6fdd3"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Zahid Hossain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIryPjidW1ZBvazYBWd-8cwUlTBR_aj1lknM1ct4ZVsHcg5WQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I recently dined at Salt & Steak Restaurant and had a very good experience. We had the rib-eye steak, which was perfectly cooked and paired with sides of mushrooms, mashed potatoes, and asparagus. For dessert, we had the seven-layer chocolate cake, which was a delightful finish to our meal.

Our server, Shahrukh, provided attentive and friendly service. We were very impressed with both the quality of the food and the excellent service. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHYyXt27Z7HTn0IpVW0UxZErFOMpFHrZn2xR2U&fid=0x0:0x4f9729eea2d6fdd3"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Aamir Bajwa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFZcT4ZtqNrAjIj78GQfx5nBrWP0ezsiibA2jOCDaMj9tV6ovN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Halal Dining place for memorable occasions.  Outstanding atmosphere with friendly service and Master Chef’s class of food.  Sharukh served us on our table with exotic care.  Highly recommend it 👍👌","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdBYApabm1j0GAlzgIRTCfovzI1mgs6nxQ5rEO&fid=0x0:0x4f9729eea2d6fdd3"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Tayyaba Omar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOnbL5d4TacOaGi2tmt32gV3GfwXDcSagH_8GTDAwwGM4ti1e1Kw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Firstly, HALAL Steak in Vancouver!! All food was really great and superb! Great taste, great ambience. Our server Nancy was exceptionally nice and very thorough, made sure we were taken care of every instance. [{"Name":"Nina Gonn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYgtJKjrCSOUlyi9_4PJDFRUUPLSNGQKERGyBXxgT7s2s0z-VX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have never experienced Afghan food.  This restaurant was recommended to us by a local person in Surrey.  We met my relatives at this restaurant and had a fabulous meal.  It is a small cozy restaurant.  Good food and service.  I live in Washington, state but if I am ever up near surrey again I would go back for sure.  The picture I am including was a 2 person sampler plate.  It looks like a lot of rice but under that mound was also a tender delicious lamb shank.  We chose this because everything sounded good and we could not choose just one or two dishes.  We had quite a bit leftover which we enjoyed the next day.  Worth a try! We 🥰 it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhF299bAIRSI_D_0BE1PTfzspckRCM52g_TzSe&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Jennifer Robin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL7gaaybLnNaTPGBnNOIeI5Ft_r0k4bSz0f4paXDTD087upxg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We tried mantu for the first time, they were delicious! I didn’t want to share them with my husband, next time we will need to order two. The staff were also very friendly. It was all around a great first impression and we will be back! :)

It was our first time trying an Afghan dish, please reply to let me know what to try the next time!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMW4kyLG2a9oJqXc4v8fjyxaytqeADJ-pzCdcue&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Hillbillytc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV833YeKMKJfxtYeKhRHVRSrikZoFOcCapKBwyEFBOnxiCMeXAZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The atmosphere is cozy. The three dip appetizer, chicken korma and vegetarian mantu (like a gyoza). The waitress was not sure what gluten free meant but she said most of the saucy dishes don’t have flour so they should be gluten free, either is or it is not.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXEhKBvd4S6JSy5c6nZ3E6Gv-dQUUpPl7wVHHX&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-11-15"},{"Name":"Asad Raquib","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7rtU11CxT0fodBl73a9UEIvQjIX5NMHx0OoO5M21-KUs2CVye=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered a platter for two. It was more than enough food for two people at a great price. The food was really great. I forgot the dishes' name, but it was worth it.
Highly Recommended !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4tHVkTBedU7z_idwNIYx7Q8247X2jq1nkb5lf&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-11-4"},{"Name":"Macho Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWToXpU3H3YB3xkMOp6uUKU5gePr0KH9w6w89u7rGCD3siyx0IX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Big portion and the meat is ok with reasonable price
Servers there are nice👍🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmVHipvlg47H9ioGWS6OziEDNULNIz-N3uFEdi&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"A & L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgVx9_IdtWK_-ZI3dVJlsTixCRpCT-hautNr97y_a12jkyWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We really enjoyed the potato bolani and pakawra (which is a bit potato pakora or bajji in Indian cuisine). We eat a vegan diet and are fairly picky about where we eat; we were missing authentic bolani like the ones our Afghan sister used to make for us when we lived elsewhere; the bolani here tasted just as good, and is quite large too (see photo - wider than one of the chairs). The hummus was average, and had too much garlic for our taste but that's ok. The wait staff Mushavar and Tanu were super friendly as well, for which we're grateful. <3","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuvkW4r8lV6Y2KQxWDa4Y2S5XZtukP6TZgNfl_&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"Kevin (KC)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrZpzDcm4xbgvb_oOynyP_bQvwIe7l-wMoPIs8L4UeVZ-waBkO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great Afghan Food in Surrey!

Decided to try out some Afghan Food for some post-workout dinner and found Pamir Diner nearby. It wasn't too busy during dinner time on a Sunday and I was able to get seated right away.

I ordered the following:
- Kabuli Palaw & Lamb Shank
- Beef Kebab
- Qaimaq Chai (pink tea)

The Kabuli Palaw & Lamb Shank was delicious. The lamb meat came right off the bone and complimented the rice really well. The flavors and texture of the dish were great, it reminds me of Biryani which I also love. One Con I would say about the dish is that the side of potatoes and the sauces could be a bit more generous in my opinion.

I also ordered a side of beef kebab which I thought was great flavor wise, but it did seem a bit dry in my opinion.

To top off my meal I decided to try out the Qaimaq Chai (Afghan Pink Tea). It does take some time to prepare since it's made to order, but it was definitely worth it! It was creamy, refreshing and hot to help digest the food.

Service here was great, and the staff were friendly. Interior was clean and cozy with good lighting. Only thing I would mention is regarding the seating - the tables are a bit on the taller side, so unless you're a tall person then it might feel slightly awkward when eating, but honestly it's not a huge deal, just something I observed while dining in. Also they do have TV's inside the restaurant but I noticed it was just being used to play Spotify music - would be pretty nice to have a variety of Afghani music videos playing or something or maybe just have it on the sports channel.

There's plenty of free parking in this lot, so you'll never have to worry about finding where to park. The place is relatively easy to get to as well. It's just along Scott Road (120 ST).

Overall, this is a nice place to grab some Afghani food here in Surrey. Do check them out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWmwe5LuEDl8A9IbgaY3r9POZ-RJsi9i2Ny9Ao&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Tiana Brw.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDDTCg5k_MkV2Y6s4oTsX_2MLY-4KNX5OYzIqD2obObePTyqQf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time having Afghan food.. For 2ppl we order Pamir Platter.. that was amazing and delicious. It’s pretty big portion for two. Server and service is great 👍🏼","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOo8jO7KRPqOw7PlG3WFuptgBb32SDe1VSi_jhi&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-10-7"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"a Natu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkkJyNgnmmp-MozHsEh9Z4IsHH5-V_MXErSphecFoISVhBbrQD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went in during happy hour at 8:30. It looked pretty busy. However, we were seated quickly.

Absolutely phenomenal service by Olivia. Very attentive and checked on us frequently! Very kind and nice

The drinks were delicious, especially the bellenis. Nats lager was smooth and wasent bitter

The food was pretty good! However, I am a bit peeved at the portion for the new home style potroast, could have used more beef. The cabanara bacon and shrimp were by far the best dish we had. The double patty burger was good and bit dry and saucy, causing the bun to get soggy towards the end.

The atmosphere does feel a tad outdated, and it was odd that there wasn't anyone dining in the patio despite the propane pyramid heat towers being on.

I would recommend dining at White Spot Scott & 72nd","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTID8O7SHL6gm-EMkUk4aEe7_j2WGAzHsHEJOr&fid=0x0:0x7800341a68048ef9"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"P Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlXs2TzM2uknqo2ufsT0wYUNB2JKpkK3UD6GmafGZl0UHRXQ4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The waitress was all alone most of the morning today and did an amazing job. Thnks guys for the lovely service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfYO2sjFoZ7AMZcwpB6OXCt9jjCJo58ALQ74oJ&fid=0x0:0x7800341a68048ef9"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"Amy Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUamHxgbXpYwrJI1uE5cJUYfe1wmxOQk5ygeSabzKwSDEQZmU3C=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The dish I order is a bit salty and hard to continue to finish. I sit down 5-10 minsites and no server service me instead service a couple come in after me first. Piss me off. I never have this type service like this at this location.  I suggest this salmon bowl should have rice or pasta on the bottom of the dish otherwise if the taste is salty still have something to cover salty taste.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP7DyCfLW_joZrJCNTqMUN3ISuaMFUZ785bDG45&fid=0x0:0x7800341a68048ef9"],"When":"2022-3-17"},{"Name":"Elaine Krieger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqca55JKLo2CtLPs0ypMqXymmEJvPpJYLTfqpCdUCMeqJ2Jw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Went for breakfast on a Saturday, was able to sit with in 5 to 10 minutes. Staff was polite. Saw only one large table which appeared to be almost completed eating. We ordered and had a lengthy wait for our food. On arrival of our breakfast the Benedict egg was cold and a film had formed on the hollandaise sauce. I requested smash potatos and what received was hashbrowns. Had to wave down server to inform and she went back to get the proper potato request. At no time did anyone ask about how either ordered meals were. My partners orange wedges on his fruit plate was old and shriveled. He also indicated his meal was luke warm. The coffee was poor. First watered down then next strong. We were disappointed in the meal considering we haven't ever been disappointed til now at this restaurant. We ate, paid and left. Don't like making a review but quality of food was not on point considering cost to go out now a days. The food this day was a two star at best and service people were polite but didn't check in on meal quality or ask anything else but brought bill when we waved down. Don't expect much but do expect to have a better meal then going to fast food take out place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIT00CLWcaOpcQpmT__3s14Pusgfk_TfBSYLMAr81DWz9ThVA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We came here for late lunch. It wasn’t really busy at 4:00pm so it’s very quiet. Great food and decent price. The service was okay, servers were not really friendly except for one who came to asked if we’ve been helped. Our server didn’t offer dessert until we asked. Overall, not so bad.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOxmFX6Kipfkp-ztnph47zubguzQuy1qvHv4Jey&fid=0x0:0x7800341a68048ef9"],"When":"2024-4-20"},{"Name":"Mounika P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlrnW_AFUjRmmd7lKhMq5nZT_eiPE-cEtUlqvjcjDqoy9no7qI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I loved their Nat's Caesar drink and Zoo sticks. Rebecca, who served us, was incredibly friendly and went above and beyond to make our meal enjoyable." 😊 Over all, we ordered Zoo sticks, sea food fettuccine, Caesar’s and Teriyaki Chicken Donburi Bowl for our lunch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyE0iu9JGb1JBg61F5gF57z6Fc9r7N5b6nj2rO&fid=0x0:0x7800341a68048ef9"],"When":"2023-10-8"},{"Name":"Sid Gautam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhQ-Qq3dP0Pl0ECbL5cG0WCU5h5SIOalcy_m_m0chxYSw3KuprxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Standard as expected, service staff is polite and accommodating.
*Post review update*
Initially I had given them 3 stars, which I thought was fair, as the service and food was as expected and nothing over and above. But White Spot team reached out asking what they could have done to get 5 stars, I didn't reply to them, but bumping up to 4 stars for their consideration. Shows they care about their customers.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMiGoY1toDaO1ki1Xh-YUfPQQaciIah-PnYqHbI\u0026fid=0x0:0x54e43a6f835f4e15"],"When":"2024-10-11"},{"Name":"Devineah Prasad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXX1DFa9bRk6bvv1_M-orvwe0-273w8OFGry_kkVxXgLnOAtjdI1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've always wanted to try this place. Five out of five.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMNAKJIOVlwUV5MJZEaFIuemr_IL2UcDVhoAyYx\u0026fid=0x0:0x54e43a6f835f4e15"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Jennifer Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKeHq6efxrFSAyroSTTkRIy4WdmXQ6sOHOJQgpn6iifK-ai1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love the design, its so cute! Parfait was good, but waffles very crappy presentation, too much ice cream. Not going again . We waited too long, even so people before us came later and got their food first. One plus- lots of parking, maybe because it’s pricy and not what expected based on photos…i don’t know how they got 4.6 rating","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5w8iZ75SoetebPbSqsURduIA54gVV0MrULIx9\u0026fid=0x0:0x54e43a6f835f4e15"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Shabbir Hasim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUH8xK9SlJsdoc5DfEoB5FlFoU9-aoRbJheLKUaqIAfjk4NlYPF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I have to say, the lotus milk cake at D Spot restaurant is hands down one of the best desserts I've ever tried. The desserts are truly out of this world, and we absolutely love going there. Thank you!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKHnBmbC5cpzrnfg0ot2NjDTUjFvgIcVFAldZm\u0026fid=0x0:0x54e43a6f835f4e15"],"When":"2024-8-18"}]

[{"Name":"Ronald Lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1AA0COaI7rivDW2feSPCNyXG0VQ-phrOsoMTKHPA9vE24xGU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice restaurant for casual Nepalese dining. Highly recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5TzDAHNxcGHoIOapQXkd3FNDMKZwoNy0Tuym_&fid=0x0:0xa0203bd6c5b9e93a"],"When":"2024-11-8"},{"Name":"Beatrix Cendana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrgEz8zi1JhWvuye6FwpWxBtelZ_X_lIGR9nTlf8HQ6_8C9mu0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time I came here I already liked the vibes! Nepali garlic noodle was also good!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_kglwgCoQKTgd_B8f3fVM8YSdl16g4ScBol9u&fid=0x0:0xa0203bd6c5b9e93a"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"soumya rastogi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoOSf5EEwUectWj3FTSaat7hv9FbQGSvRLEa5sv_VJj63pc71U_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Momo Factory , The menu offers a wide variety of options, catering to different tastes, and the food did not disappoint.

[{"Name":"Traditionally Modern Food","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMpQ_rffdB1oRpx4JBtbwY9ZnneLVTrtetaX6pnc7nm39hssP8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of the best South Indian restaurants in Delta, BC. I'm not sure why this place has so many negative reviews. We just had dinner there, and our server Shruti was extremely polite. The food came quickly, and everything tasted good. We are definitely coming back for this food","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM20zZFsAUvI1fOLiRl1xi1qFWk6sG-LhscqBPQ&fid=0x0:0xa4c824edd008d273"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"Apurva Shelhalkar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhHoVKXEOi9H6a9TLWDbt3vYQbM1IQy-PEvGXNrQa1vEMaKeKZNw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am maharashtrian but I like South Indian food hence my friends introduced this restaurant to me. Food is really yummmm authentic taste.... Payasam is my all time favorite South Indian desert it was perfect...all chutneys and sambhar authentic... And the bestest thing was the coffee and the service....thank you Salman and Navroop for friendly, kind service I really appreciate it","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPdB7ZBQRLofl3tZLMJoIQL3mmWsovMeueytNHR&fid=0x0:0xa4c824edd008d273"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"Zollstock Mueller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBw0Z4GAdwRUgaxWB9Zu8Za1vWYf1-lUYtwt_2pYVjzMeraQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dosas were super tasty! Salman was a super nice server as well :) will be back! They even had a buy one get one free dosa (Thursdays)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLF4dbQM3GGPvm63IvKTowA76E_spLOxEvKMVO&fid=0x0:0xa4c824edd008d273"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Ram Umasankaran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKftpdQ02WG9ZhMAlO0WB7DyxRXKLOpEhwdKywabYT3UrIZ2w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The buffet was outstanding. Especially the gulabjamun. Felt like my Patti's style. Perfect taste. The Broccoli Kuttu was outstanding. We loved the food and pass our regards to the chef.Thanks to support staff especially Ashwin and Neha.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3Q7-8WA1MFnbF13qe9oJZsEOQN9tMxGDE9oKH&fid=0x0:0xa4c824edd008d273"],"When":"2024-10-6"},{"Name":"Ashley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVS35_N_eP6M2t_lCqCwBnzwAbbUNDMpkhHxKNDdR7yLzAbQpe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family and I were craving dosas, and I've heard many good things about this place. So we made our way here, and we left satisfied.
I got the masala dosa, and it was delicious!! It was the first time I enjoyed having a dosa from a restaurant. All the chutney and sambar were great. I would definitely come back here again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBLsPRXFBV9VlJCJerSkRWYnGcSGAW3kjL6h3Z&fid=0x0:0xa4c824edd008d273"],"When":"2024-7-12"},{"Name":"Snigdha Sadanandan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhvf4BlpGhcWOCjLLD3zSdAipdqUHf8J88XN4wyEb-g1lsKr3J=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a decent overall experience with ghee/paper masala, and kids' meals. The staff checked on us throughout the meal. The ambiance is quite good. There is quite a good choice of vegetarian items. They have tried to make it a South Indian-inspired dining experience, but the authenticity fell short. Prices seem reasonable and decent. Overall, the place is good to visit once in a while. I hope to visit again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMzGthBCN9GQK46eyadg6IOO4K0nwFwKfSDIXgH&fid=0x0:0xa4c824edd008d273"],"When":"2024-3-1"},{"Name":"DEE","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUE68QQugYwIrGbHoSG7JAoZIp7yHKFKTnMFleiKIHnRsp_FxG0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Exceptionally well service by the team.
Not taking names cuz everyone was great n did a fantastic job
(All the ladies and my dudes)

In fact, One of the best service I've experienced here in Canada so far.
Be proud of yourselves
💯🔥👍

The food and drinks were amazing too
I think I found a new favourite spot. 🙂✌️

BUT. what's with the MANDATORY  GRATUITY??
Common guys

Change your policy
Not cool
Gratuity (tip) should be a customer's choice

I personally would have tipped more than the 11$

Definitely coming back for more
💯👻

Mybad, didn't click pics of the food.
Will do it next time 😜🙃

P.S. the sambar was too good 👍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPH9Nren6m3cSFTOw-8j774XfBjSUdUGCqkpIhY&fid=0x0:0xa4c824edd008d273"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"Jayanand KV","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ300Yeb4iZG-kKuVhK9gX6deBVBJYl5e792S9p7AKCEsTgpA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been to Saravana Bhavan at this location numerous times, however posting a review for the first time.  There were 5 of us, 3 adults and 2 kids. Went for dinner Saturday night at 8.30. Place was not too crowded; we were seated immediately. Medhu vada and podi idli were fresh and tasty appetizers as always. Mixed veg parotta, pav bhaji, and tomato onion chilli uthappam are reliable dishes for adults and have been consistently good. Kids got chocolate dosas, essentially ghee dosa with Nutella spread inside. This does not come with sambar and chutney on the side for some strange reason, previously it used to. Kids didn’t seem to be bothered.  Kids had Shirley temple, adults had mango lassi and filter coffee, both were good. Food is not very expensive in relative terms. $116 with taxes and gratuity, the latter is included in the bill. Shruti was warm, friendly and quick to serve.  Overall good experience. Certainly recommend if you like South Indian veg cuisine.  For those with big appetite I have heard their buffet is good, though we have not tried it much.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMHCx-pfZor4XPF7B6JEpC4wzRVOgFjP00BhNHM&fid=0x0:0xa4c824edd008d273"],"When":"2024-4-29"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Safesaif_ 21","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdWJ6aoYbvHsfGcXWimREVk4QyQMSCYyeceILzMwqjvtobBR28=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a chill spot to have some really good halal food. The double crunch burger and the loaded fries are the best. And don’t even get me started on the mango milkshake 🤤","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUVy9C665ejA3OLMfP_0F_05rXxSWNpkyMTzKU&fid=0x0:0x74e48e7000e7ef20"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Hamza Hydri Syed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXQMloeZZXC5acdLr6-P3HFLpQP_ZypzL4n0k4ALz2HPa4qXyHkg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have stopped here to grab a bite couple of times when visiting Vancouver. The food is typical Pakistani cuisine - good selection of burgers and Mughlai. I loved their Chicken Karahi (which goes well with their Butter Naan). Their Biryani is good, very tasty and typical Karachi version. The kids love their burgers and chicken wings. Ambience is good and family friendly. Serving could be improved, the single person taking orders, serving and cleaning up was difficult task.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgjFTf6Z4oyF06stNGL8GmmfMJk6i4glkfuhCc&fid=0x0:0x74e48e7000e7ef20"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Shery On The Move","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmAA3VItm5d-LzZjMzSS_FZs12aHSse1X5w-nXQqVmdbUvhBBJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I didn't expect I would be so impressed when I come and dine in here. Here are the compliments that I want to highlight. ⬇️

The restaurant is cosy, with a nice atmosphere and a beautiful table with a bell/call button attached.

I ordered loaded fries, cheese bombers, mega crush burger, and philly cheese steak burger.

Loaded Fries
If you are familiar and favourite of loaded fries American style like me, you will like it here. Even though the portion is not big like American style but it's full enough for two people sharing. I very much like the combination taste of sauce, cheese, cilantro, etc. It's a twist of South Asian style, and overall, it's flavourful.

Cheese Bombers
I expect cheese bombers to be like a chicken popcorn size, but it came with a huge size! 5 pieces are good enough because they're full with cream cheese inside it (with jalapeno).

Mega Crush Burger
I don't know how to comment about this burger. Double thumbs up 👍🏻 👍🏻.

Philly Cheese Steak Burger
It's good, but the meat is not that much. I totally can understand the price I paid for this burger.

I went to the ladies' toilet and I'm very satisfied with the cleanliness but my husband said men toilets are not good.

Kudos to the waiter who worked that day because she's amazing, friendly, and attentive. Please keep up the good work whether it's on peak hour or not.

Date of visit : 2 June 2024
Time : 9:00pm-9:52pm","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLak-R-gpv1NqeLVAGVVY3j5UuNaP0xeWgUMu5&fid=0x0:0x74e48e7000e7ef20"],"When":"2024-6-5"},{"Name":"J. A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYN8Bfqly5qLcn9ccU2neEREXryexnxM7M2bRJCuWPZG91P4jN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Spicy Fried chicken is better than Chicken world. Worth every penny as it’s halal.l and amazing in all ways. Every dish tastes fabulous. We are regular here and will continue to be. Our go to place and its affordable too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO40T34rEMTbXgyK-i6_wIBbBTHUeOJsKpcGAHe&fid=0x0:0x74e48e7000e7ef20"],"When":"2024-7-7"},{"Name":"Nimrat Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJOrza_eWiJ_hv7LqrqFD4wRzWp8oOdk8QSaOUN0Q502AutVA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This restaurant is a hidden gem! The food was absolutely incredible — the goat karahi is a must-try. The balance of flavors was spot on, and the ingredients were clearly fresh. I loved the creative take on classic recipes. The ambiance was cozy and perfect for a relaxed evening out. Highly recommend for food enthusiasts!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mahadi Hasan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfiL2JeXUIO6XBft-JLtjCK1lreoojcMtT3EjzAFDLFxK9ccQHKg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"With all my complement and excitement I went there couple of times more and found out that the quality has been compromised drastically. The biriyani which i loved mostly lost it's charm. Yesterday i went there and took the biriyani.  There were 3 pieces of meats in total but without any leg pieces what used to be with 5-6 leg pieces. They dont have fried chicken anymore. They only have chiken wings and look at the photo. The shape and size of wings. I dont know why they withdrew regular fried chicken. Totally disappointed. It was my 5th visit to them yesterday but it won’t happening again. I am not going there anymore.

It was my 2nd visit to them. I went there in brunch buffet and that was pretty good. Last night it was not a buffet but we orders one full chciken biriyani and  4 pieces of fried chicken. I added the photo and you guys can reffer to it. I have got in total 7 pieces of chciken with biriyani alone. It was so satisfying tbh. The fried chciken price is a bit high though (13$ for 4 pieces) but it was worthy enough overall. We have also got a complementary gajar ka halwua from the owner. Its a straight 5 star for them.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMqBH6lqSJURP59AmwaR0tmr1mQh79IoTk2cF1S&fid=0x0:0x74e48e7000e7ef20"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Zeeshan Sohail","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQzSgXcEIo5d0fY039IL3LLi7k1i-9eyjB9u0xnur9BQekUdtD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic addition to the local karahi scene. Black pepper heavy Chicken Karahi which has a different kick than a tomato base one. Arguably one of the best Karahi spots in BC. They also happen to serve great Fried Chicken, Karachi Bun Kabab and Fish Burger. Friendly staff and a spacious comfortable dining area. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfvOEqGejLHiBx0wcMoJuJybIbxJoS-TDOy63l&fid=0x0:0x74e48e7000e7ef20"],"When":"2023-12-13"},{"Name":"Adhham Farook","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjlk1T4nE85S8cF73uGl6Bcox-MpnOySZS44DlC3EXuJDnJwJz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Unpleasant experience!
We dine-in for the Saturday buffet.  There was very little items in the spread.  While eating the chicken Kadai . After noticed the blood in the half cooked chicken,  we all stopped eating and informed the waitress but she seems to not bothered about this! Someone walked up to me and told that they can change the chicken for me but we all lost appetite after seeing the blood. When I went to pay the bill , the same person ( who walked up to me) proudly told that they have given me a 10% discount to compensate the unpleasant experience that we have to go through. Even though I told them I did not eat and they can consider not to change for my meal but they seems to be only happy giving 10% on overall bill. After I asked for the printed bill , the guy told me that he can give a coupon for my next visit. They should had a basic curtsy to say sorry for the experience we have to face and they spoiled my wife's birthday dinner. Thank you for your wonderful service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkfGKk6UopJ4BbzWcqRDohVLdKE_cwQMekNNQT&fid=0x0:0x74e48e7000e7ef20"],"When":"2024-10-20"}]
