[{"Name":"Phoebe Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVG0xd2xYnqZIp_umMyZOBb0ks9m0ApyoWjwxAds2lAqLSGAshC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited this Indian buffet restaurant during the year-end holiday season, and it was a delightful experience. The festive Christmas decorations added a warm and cheerful atmosphere, making it perfect for holiday celebrations.

The food was excellent, with an impressive variety of curries—chicken, beef, lamb, and more—all bursting with authentic flavors. The dessert section featured many traditional Indian sweets, which were a bit too sweet for my taste, but I appreciated the option to enjoy ice cream and cake as well.

The ambiance makes it ideal for family gatherings or company parties. They even have private rooms that can accommodate groups of 20-30 people, providing a more intimate and enjoyable experience.

Overall, this restaurant is a fantastic choice for both food and atmosphere, especially during the holiday season. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOPA66OJAdy5G8gMZbJlNfkaNA8QZzIgmLCkvE9&fid=0x0:0x591cca86b95caa3e"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Praneet Raj","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-I5iB9QpG5eztISNYObvNJI9swIkyqnUB25NJVMbN3zDz8_-1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely loved this amazing Indian buffet restaurant. With over 150 items to choose from, the variety was incredible, and every dish I tried was of top-notch quality. The food was flavorful and authentic, offering a fantastic range of both vegetarian and non-vegetarian options. The cocktails were another highlight—unique and expertly crafted, adding an extra touch to the dining experience. The service was extraordinary, with attentive staff ensuring everything went smoothly. It was a delightful experience from start to finish. I highly recommend this place, and I will definitely be back for another round of great food and drinks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkq3HOa0ZwVl0aaeiobaXWtH0z_3agV9w4tZL0&fid=0x0:0x591cca86b95caa3e"],"When":"2024-10-10"},{"Name":"Emma Tolly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHRCBdZMx6SLHNyCO59Sh5fGUMwyy5tM8toUXrcDcdcp4sIyRj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We came during December and they are also open during Christmas. The service was fantastic (better than most places), food tasted amazing (there were no bad dishes and a good variety to choose from), and the price is reasonable for buffet (approx 45 per person without drinks).

The interior design and atmosphere of the restaurant is lively and cozy. Would definitely come back again and recommend to friends and family.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2jpFo-WHtW98eQZXCbiXTdyIzvcHDlsXdbeR1&fid=0x0:0x591cca86b95caa3e"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"John Dreyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJORpLiVTZLOTQ4ZSaEs8r3tBWR0ha3zIf2xPszyRTLu_SWs7Y2g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my favourite Indian Buffet. High quality, good service and tremendous food. Everyone in our party could choose the food that suited them. Some liked vegetarian dishes, I am keen on tandoori meats, the kids chose a plateful of cakes to start with. Nice ( but expensive) cocktails. Plenty of free parking. Not too busy in the week, busy at weekends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2jl9tjwuH7m-OXrEmzpvAaIJGR6bBZu0TvEDE&fid=0x0:0x591cca86b95caa3e"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Ada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_tT85lO7aZKFfq17wWpo8ldgI_n0GJFJfBhG1nWiEa2zXCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From my limited experience of the Indian cuisine, the taste seemed authentic. My favorite was the butter chicken, which got a little spicy near the end. The seating area was spacious. Lots of parking available outside in the plaza. The place was decorated nicely.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPNk8NSoaNv7MBZGAa4JRkh-cXmqdOTnmJhAn04&fid=0x0:0x591cca86b95caa3e"],"When":"2024-11-13"},{"Name":"Rajesh R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAtkYip3pIVP-ZJS7hPA_V6eSNoACvvmp34LIZmlC_HP9d_CM2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow! What an amazing experience! Living in a remote area of Washington State, we were excited to visit Canada for the first time and dine at this restaurant. With modest expectations, despite hearing great reviews, we were blown away! The food, service, and atmosphere exceeded our expectations. We'll definitely return in a couple of days. Cheers!"","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqBepo6FHti2n4_rVtKNu7g2LrWfbiNcGZL4ls&fid=0x0:0x591cca86b95caa3e"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"David CM Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUu9wKhvbfbXcUv3ddzu6Zbl9103spVjAaDikUakjLqFoCJejT0Fw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Not bad for a buffet place.  Price is alright.  Ample parking as it's at a Mall.  Not too busy.  But service was a bit slow....had to wait almost 30mins for simple Mojito drinks for my
table.  And also gave me the wrong bill for the drinks and i didn't even realized it till after we left the restaurant.  We were at company lunch function there whereby we pay for our own drinks.  Food is good though.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMlxoA71TKWOV2YuSu32by5V0MslYtBJUEsFJ2R&fid=0x0:0x591cca86b95caa3e"],"When":"2024-10-30"},{"Name":"Yix Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-J7BhURjrSxg0zehj9vV5_srUXqps-aWwLMecYw1PxcaNrD_qVw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great value of a fantastic Indian buffet! So many curry options, with delicious chicken and fish choices. Vegetarian friendly.
Snacks are sweet and fresh, although it is way too sweet for me...
Drinks sold separately, but still with a a good price. A huge bottle of Evian is on the table, but keep in mind if you need normal ice water, it is available upon request.

Located in a mall, free parking available, both in front of the place, and the back.

Friendly feeling from the beginning of the dinner, treated well with the staff here.

Gonna come back soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0X2XrqNDnkFOxVXiR7w5z3N1-2VTTY-KzRRx2&fid=0x0:0x591cca86b95caa3e"],"When":"2024-8-18"}]

[{"Name":"Shibu Rajan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIz_kKAATx_i2c_nrvy_zHkQjCRhqVBiAvNKpGM65arMKjwg3XWw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very delicious food. Loved the ambience. Went with family and we had ordered Chicken Dum Biryani, Schezwan Noodles, Garlic Naan, Goat pepper fry and double ka meetha. All the dishes were so yummy. Looking forward to going there again.
Diya did an amazing job and was very accommodating.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOI3lTbngtA3JFqtFzRhTwThATIC804oXNow2a2&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-10-3"},{"Name":"Reviews by Sammi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISDh89r6cb4qraK-PQHcAYlErtdTLP1KdmJhJ7Ok-e4HGOlA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an amazing dinner here at bahubali today😍😍😍 we ordered a mixed tandoori platter with butter naan and Hyderabad dum goat biryani. It was awesome, I loved the biryani, after a decade I had good biryani.
We ordered Paan as well and it was good I loved its cute packaging, definitely coming back for more dinners.
Food, Service, Atmosphere 10/10","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbcyfJnZNHibQxgYNsBcoqsDpB41J8gmKRuYc7&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"actionj007","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL3vSkBAqKJl0vg8_AMzQD5EEGhEVeYS2de8UbzcFClZ51w9xM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came to Bahubali Biryani House from a recommendation of my co-worker who said they had the best Hyderabad biryani in GVRD.

The inside of the restaurant looks very fancy and clean.  The service could be a bit better.  For example, the waitress took away the bucket that had our utensils and paper napkins to refill but didn't bring it back.  Another situation was when our water jug was empty but none of the waitresses (3 of them) just stood around by the bar and didn't offer to help refill it.

Now to the food ... my family ordered the Chicken 65 Semi-Dry Appetizer, Veg Hakka Noodles, Roti, Parantha, and Hyderabad Goat Dum Biryani.

The Chicken 65 was ordered non-spicy but it came with a punch.  It was super tasty with the spices and spicyness so luckily we ordered the noodles, roti and parantha to help offset it.  Noodles were delicious however the roti and parantha was just alright.  the star of the meal was the biryani.  It was our first time  trying Hyderabad biryani and it didn't disappoint.  The goat was very flavourful and spicy (even though we asked for non-spicy) so luckily the Raita helped cool the spicy level down.

Overall I would highly recommend this restaurant.  Will be coming here again in the future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNxCZp8Gq2LgBhl2te25S_9XFEKz666DZQENrk_&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"prakash reddy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXb2WRqNb5f2Tgpd1sO4jH5VtFZFQPVCPvbnhXcb3wVT6qPFWIk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bahubali Indian Restaurant offers an authentic taste of India with a wide variety of delicious dishes. The ambiance is warm and inviting, with decor that reflects Indian culture beautifully. Their butter chicken is a must-try—rich, creamy, and full of flavor. The staff is friendly and attentive, providing excellent service that enhances the dining experience. They have a great selection of vegetarian and non-vegetarian options, catering to all dietary preferences. Prices are reasonable, especially given the generous portions. Overall, Bahubali Indian Restaurant is a fantastic choice for anyone craving authentic Indian cuisine in a cozy setting. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHyHyQp_67CoZxCqd2pYXvXuTGTUUiz_NeCVX3&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-10-15"},{"Name":"AMD AMD","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzPVmRQNMQ2YAQxy3zniqjil09YepOShmsliNT69loAl5-o6RZ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am writing this review about the goat biryani I received. Unfortunately, the dish was completely inedible. The goat meat was tough, dry, and tasted as if it had been cooked months ago. It seemed like old pieces were mixed with fresh ones, which was very unappetizing. I paid $64 for a meal that I wouldn't even consider serving to anyone.

This was extremely disappointing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPxGIaAp6Pfkl_smCGQdv208-jV6v3x13FXjI-l&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Sheetal Pandita","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwnHbG10zg7YaAEo0q-LJeaWwbii4P2pYJmElXSwqAMfP0nWsj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently dined at Bahubali and it was a delightful experience. The flavors of the dishes were vibrant and authentic, showcasing the rich diversity of Indian cuisine. Each dish was expertly prepared, from the aromatic biryani to the flavorful curries, all made with fresh ingredients.

The ambiance was warm and inviting, making it a perfect spot for both casual dining and special occasions. The server Navjot was exceptionally attentive, ensuring every guest felt welcomed and satisfied. Their knowledge of the menu was impressive, offering great recommendations that enhanced our meal.

Overall, I highly recommend Bahubali  for anyone looking to enjoy authentic Indian cuisine in a welcoming environment. I can't wait to return!
Music was good too 😍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLoDflJFt6NWO_dUjx46DuboeM1pBd-PKYa7Iw&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-9-20"},{"Name":"Himaja leo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLK0o1E84JQ_7M4M0-c1DK4VdNjhiwqQw03r2q5r0k8sRTADA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bahubali Biryani House, located in Surrey offers an authentic Indian dining experience with a focus on biryanis. Known for their generous portions and flavorful biryani varieties, the restaurant brings the richness of Indian spices to the forefront of every dish.
I particularly love their Hyderabadi Goat Dum Biryani and their Rumali Roti with Butter Chicken.
I also enjoyed the Vijayawada Fry Piece Chicken Biryani and Paneer 65 Biryani, which come with classic sides like raita and salan.
Also try their appetizers, they have both veg and non veg options.
I loved some of their mocktails too.
The family pack biryani is huge and a good portion for 4-5 people.
End it with the double ka meeta dessert.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDzCuKrOUhVS_Qi9uJ2zTscGmzJb9jhyBDAxLc&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-10-24"},{"Name":"Khushnuma Baria","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4h6CCK0EQax6SgHKx94NIQAhlZyc0o6HPMdFK6gESLKX07dEzag=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The portions are  huge. It is value for money. One biryani can be eaten by two folks.  Biryani rice was very smooth and the appetizers are also very interesting , made well and huge. Try to ignore the loud music.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMo9IX0SqWut928oTMVoYatyKHpUsmlQyuP2fUT&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-9-14"}]

[{"Name":"Shaifali Mittal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxOs2Oo1ooPVg1oGTC-uLTS9zXgxYb87JCjG1hUWsE9AQfGKcn6w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Poor Packaging and Declining Quality at The Yellow Chilli

I recently ordered from Yellow Chilli, and unfortunately, my experience was far from satisfactory. The packaging was inadequate—there was minimal effort to secure the food, and it arrived in a messy state, with items spilled and containers damaged. For a restaurant of this caliber, I expected much better care in how the food is packaged and delivered.

To make matters worse, the quality of the food itself seems to have declined. The flavors weren't as vibrant or fresh as I remember, and the texture was off, indicating the ingredients weren’t as fresh as they should have been.

For a restaurant with a reputation for excellence, both the packaging and food quality were major letdowns. I hope The Yellow Chilli takes this feedback seriously and works to restore the standards they once set. Until then, I’ll be reconsidering future orders.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNgcWAhOSkBQZk1jNzSoTlAVc1IS0Mj81PMCogh&fid=0x0:0x59e2c461f803f0ec"],"When":"2024-11-14"},{"Name":"Aswathy Suresh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKR4DNly6qkrVukYEpwNeGLo6K3j-A3IXF_3S8Thv5C4UG9m5MDg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best authentic Indian restaurant that captures the amazing flavours from across India. Regretting that we missed this restaurant before and that we never got to try Sanjeev Kapoor’s authentic recipe before. Every dish takes you back home and the flavours are so perfectly crafted. Would definitely want to go back and try every other dish.
The servers were very great and friendly as well 😊 perfect for a celebration as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONTQSbFzB75IfC5rDFC5XbY13eHjc5Q1YD0Juz&fid=0x0:0x59e2c461f803f0ec"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"discovery sonu ali","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_b2reRKsjtiT_HffF8-yN5QM1sqqpXd5OaoIUa8-ff3hRWT7Gdw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The restaurant had an exceptional atmosphere, with a warm and inviting ambiance. The staff were incredibly polite, enhancing the overall dining experience. The food was truly remarkable, offering authentic Indian flavors that were both rich and satisfying. It's definitely a place worth visiting, and I highly recommend trying it at least once.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2L9y5fGKX8ekh7Gjvk4NjDenh5dABvBe2tdJV&fid=0x0:0x59e2c461f803f0ec"],"When":"2024-8-15"},{"Name":"Kevin (KC)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrZpzDcm4xbgvb_oOynyP_bQvwIe7l-wMoPIs8L4UeVZ-waBkO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My first time eating at a slightly more upscale Indian restaurant...and it was amazing! 🔥

Came here for some late dinner with my Indian buddy and it wasn't too busy so we were seated right away. Originally we were seated at a table for two that was quite dark because of the lack of lighting in the area, so I had requested to our server if we could move to a brighter table behind us which she granted. The main reason for this is because I am not of a fan of eating in the dark, and as a food critic/reviewer, I like to see what I am eating clearly so I can provide better feedback.

We ordered the following for two people:
* Tikka 3 Ways
* Bhatti ki Macchi
* Garlic Naan
* Missi Rotti
* Puran Singh Da Tariwala Murgh
* Dum murgh biryani
* Falooda Kulfi

I ordered the tikka 3 ways for my appetizer and it was really good! I love that it was done 3 ways so I can taste which one I like the most...the spicy one was my favorite. The cook on the chicken was perfect and not dry.

For our mains we got the chef's special Puran Singh Da Tariwala Murgh and Chicken Biryani. For my bread I ordered the garlic naan and my Indian buddy ordered the missi rotti. Everything tasted delicious! The gravy was rich, savory, with a bit of spice and the chicken biryani was piping hot and cooked perfectly! 👌

The garlic naan was soft, flaky and fresh! The texture was really good and perfect for dipping into the curry. The only con my Indian buddy said was the missi rotti was slightly overcooked.

Overall though the appetizers and mains were delicious.

For dessert I ordered the Falooda Kulfi and all I have to say is...WOW! The ice cream dessert was bursting with Indian flavours...I felt like I teleported to India when I ate a spoon full of this delicious creamy dessert. This was definitely the star of the meal tonight! I am not a huge dessert guy - but this one I truly enjoyed...I also like that it wasn't overly sweet. 🍨🍧

The service here was excellent. Our server refilled our waters regularly and even educated me with some of the food I was ordering and eating. She also made sure we were getting new plates, silverware and napkins for each course. 👍

Interior and seating was also good. The table is a nice height and the chairs are padded. The only con is that some of the tables here are placed in darker areas of the restaurant...I guess it's fine if you prefer candle light dinners, but in my opinion there should be a bit more lighting that stretches across the wall where the tables are since they are further away from the glass windows and get blocked out by the higher booth seating which makes those areas feel less important.

Overall though, I enjoyed eating here and plan to eat here again to try their other menu items. I am a big fan of Indian food since I grew up in Surrey, so it's nice to be able to treat myself with some indian fine dining once in a while. 🙂","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMH7Apd1e8CNCeuPqPQ0X62CSoitNmB2nZ6-8Eu&fid=0x0:0x59e2c461f803f0ec"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Gunjan N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKnGgkA1elJAwarcjcQNB0nZVdXLX3uwLu0NnIClSVktMj-5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Being an avid follower of Chef Sanjeev Kapoor, this place did not live up to its chef's mark. Service was good, ambiance was good but there was no oomph to the food when it came to taste or presentation. Nothing was appealing enough to make me wanna go back. It may be because we had high expectations, and others may love it if they don't know the Chef.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEbZDDye6aiT3Vkwc4P6gOmBc0nD3vaEXD4aNw&fid=0x0:0x59e2c461f803f0ec"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"Nikki Paash","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUS1GPSPm9ymA5-pGC3kbNDX0EgXOG9Tr3DvBXx813m9sPBSfpY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I must say, it was a disappointment  at the start, found hair on the cultery and asked to change  that. The first dish  tandoori  lamb had hair in it ( look in picture  below).   The manager  Amrut, was  very apologetic  and saw personally  to all the main courses , making sure we do not find any more hair.  The dessert was on the house and repeat order of the tandoori lamb at no charge to take  home as a sorry.  Taste wise, the batter  used for prawns was too salty. Other dishes were very tasty. It was a let down  for me as I was expecting  better than what  I got at Sanjeev Kapoor  restaurant.   The ambiance  was dull, the place was empty, and the food presentation  was very mediocre. Not the Sanjeev Kapoor  flair that I expected. Check out  my review of Clove-the art of dining, look at their food presentation  to compare.Furthermore, it was a birthday  lunch which was spoilt by the unhygienic  situation as  well.However, the  manager  and the server both were  doing great jobs. The chef.. well... Let's just  say I won't be returning...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOd5cPs-Xw9hQTyMz5fdM3DMrW4OvV3AQvYSN4M&fid=0x0:0x59e2c461f803f0ec"],"When":"2024-7-16"},{"Name":"Roy Pavithran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUisVEx1KPdsNvsiDSaj5xrPz4-TDKiLVGBnR6psffAhZ3qSzUY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Found it looking for a breakfast place. This place is a gem in Surrey, the quality of food is always amazing. They don't hold back of spices and flavors, Kulcha is served is almost all punjabi places but the quality is unbeaten here, loved the harippa paneer tikka as well.

I regularly take advantage of their breakfast offer!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOpARqquBetHZ9ekud1O7aQmVMQi7fILZXUHllF&fid=0x0:0x59e2c461f803f0ec"],"When":"2024-7-29"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Jacqueline Kinuthia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEf8DTwHB3_eKgWgcdteQxXAat-nw7g5sdztBtnifcli4_RbTt=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited this ice cream shop for the first time, and it was such a wonderful experience! The older gentleman behind the counter was incredibly friendly and welcoming. He took the time to explain the different menu items and even shared some recommendations. The ice cream was delicious, with unique flavors that made it hard to choose. The shop has a cozy, inviting atmosphere, and you can tell they put a lot of care into both their products and their customer service. Highly recommend stopping by if you’re in the area!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNM4IEIfkervspgWzTuvq7Vxp3buQEzmq1L2IvG\u0026fid=0x0:0x23b9ed9c0ec125aa"],"When":"2024-10-27"},{"Name":"Amrita Nayak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJgJ3b8LMBlPc7G1Rv8sy6cyH33IeJwYGYkw6c-i8ocBKF5odAKg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This late-night gem is a great spot for satisfying ice cream cravings, staying open until 3 AM. Parking is conveniently available right in front of the shop, making it easy to drop by. The selection of ice cream flavors is impressive, and what's even sweeter is the friendly, welcoming service from the person behind the counter. We also tried their karak chai, which was spot on — strong, flavorful, and perfectly balanced. It’s a fantastic place to unwind, especially when you need a late-night treat.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTTMBZ7wIPDdJxnp1kleV5iTKZ2Em0losbzYoo\u0026fid=0x0:0x23b9ed9c0ec125aa"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"mbaisheka","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1jUVoX1Q1cFDu0YCF6WUyqzT8JiUsAOfV363X86N7z_4OzV2Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"IceCream Wala !!! Best ice cream in town . They have a vast variety of ice cream choices and desserts ranging from scooped ice cream to Falooda to Kulfi  to Paan. They also have a variety of yummy cookies . You have the option to also taste their different icecream choices . We ordered the Karachi special falooda , it was extremely flavourful with a fireworks of a variety of flavours that were utmostly delicious and satisfying at once . The owner is very kind and friendly . The staff are very polite as well . Great decor , music and ambience . We loved our experience and definitely recommend . You won’t be disappointed.  We will be returning customers . No questions asked . 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdu6n3SDGyP6IcRSSsq7BiKHTinw09v_g-rOxh\u0026fid=0x0:0x23b9ed9c0ec125aa"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Tanisha Sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQLOvZMBMpbuULuR26tfoj4Ur1VRgXpWfMk7HGW3J9yK0RNa8KCA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ice Cream Wala is the ultimate late-night spot! Whether you’re craving something sweet after dinner or just hanging out with friends, this place hits the mark every time. The vibe is nice, the staff is so friendly, and they make you feel right at home. Their ice creams are amazing, but let me tell you—THE FALOODAS! They’re on another level. Creamy, refreshing, and just perfect. If you haven’t been here yet, you’re seriously missing out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMR-cUXE6QW5qxgdNlC6MkN57cqGSfji9TIrN3o\u0026fid=0x0:0x23b9ed9c0ec125aa"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Muhammad Shaikh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQdjWdse-YfR521WDC20Axq29mXN4Dhyt3fqivYTAjlsaQ3qxXyw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Simply amazing in all quality,customer service and on top everything is Halal means(gelatine is plant based). Keep it up !!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuh4s3c66EvX404TvV2ihDlUQc7cvc_aVi1Xg2\u0026fid=0x0:0x23b9ed9c0ec125aa"],"When":"2024-8-14"},{"Name":"kamran rehmani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1b1-4oMe3sxwGDT4xlqF3X2foYnTMfE71pSJgxniW_8Vdnw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love everything they have. [{"Name":"Munro Stuff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj0Wcuk6ox5dfAeJ4fAaMbhX_F-nzzt3p5oc_f0hBd0NpbGSM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Enjoyed our lunch here. Friendly service and good menu. Both the combo B and C were nicely presented, fresh, and tasty. Appreciated that they request customers ask for wasabi/ginger in order to minimize waste!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWJYF7lvrUMY0PELN6VFLv5kwNgRKdIJ0yrBKH&fid=0x0:0xf6bddd82220ada13"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Diana L.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIW2kdRGGLj1j8iotZR8u_6cJvN47azaqWmh-dWmP_2e6mQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"3.5. Never been here so went for the basics just in case. I like how in their Dynamite roll they had two prawns (vs only one with a lot of batter). However the batter or fried ness of it, tasted like it hadn’t been deep fried in fresh kill. Had that darker look where it has been re deep fried twice or thrice over.
The yam roll was so so, the yam itself was still crunchy and not soft or thoroughly cooked. The rice and seaweed are fresh.
However, looks like a nice and clean place. Staff are very courteous. I’ll be back as prices are reasonable! Oh and lots of parking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3z8Ixd3uVop-M0vJP_d2o60i0zVUuuBmHNSU&fid=0x0:0xf6bddd82220ada13"],"When":"2017-11-2"},{"Name":"Mori","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzjNclSLYHoLurDMy1z6lBJJfgC1i3gQXUk28JpQQw8EIfuYkF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered from this place through Uber Eats and we ended up ordering:
Assorted Tempura
Chicken Yakisoba
Chicken Katsu
California roll & Chicken Teri roll with Black Rice
Dynamite Combo

It took about an hour to get our delivery and off the bat, we had a missing item and unfortunately it was the Dynamite Combo - which was what I was looking forward to the most since it included nigiri.
Aside from the missing item, the tempura was great, the batter on it was a perfect ratio to the veggies and prawns and the chicken yakisoba and katsu was up to par with most Japanese restaurants we've eaten from.

The cali & chicken teri roll with black rice was a bit of a miss for us as the rice was moderately hard and didn't taste like it was fully cooked.

Although this place wasn't terrible, the missing item and the high prices for what you get was a bit off putting for me. Not saying that we wouldn't try this place again, but we will definitely try other places before revisiting.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPiVV3SThl7KnscwJ29KU9gFhR9WXieHHDOMCXJ&fid=0x0:0xf6bddd82220ada13"],"When":"2022-9-9"},{"Name":"Alex","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjFHGtwIzveQOQjqcUkPmPkjaJlaH08sYYGOWsca-S0Ncj9A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"It's about what you what expect from a "sushi" run place like this..  The staff are actually pretty rude, it's all about turning tables per hour with their mediocre food.  This place sucks, there are better places near by that are beoetter value.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hailey Marie Hartman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-hNTxh2UYMvVaHJkaD6_G2Fjmuiq56y_dqbMawQvIBYfgn6k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been coming to this sushi place for almost 7 years! And they are the best I’ve found, everything is fresh and tastes amazing! Service is always friendly and they even remember my order when I forget to ask for no ginger or wasabi lol you guys rock!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kyle Blake","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJNFcbCQ39fGXxRQtPXHo2eBeLhsWLS92wriEf_ty70muDA_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Tiny avacado roll like you get at a gas station... the smallest nib of weak wasabi. Ordered 3 rolls all together and got 3 packets of soy sauce","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSJRSgO-utvy1HFRsp9eFE2eqIo1PsVBn6Q9Ro&fid=0x0:0xf6bddd82220ada13"],"When":"2024-4-28"},{"Name":"Scythian 77","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTCZVi8qUH6MixmE15xPL0-_3rz_xNDLzk8xuiwECIp9MYhLV4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"ive ordered before from here they sell fas staion style sushi they will go out of business soon give it time theyll eventually collapse","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dhruv Anand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5no7BGOEmOfFvCM2Og4Ox2wgvigMevZFPDxw0o5I3WeRqKuh0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice food, amazing vibe, kind hosts and amazing food. It is also really cheap.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPr1ZY5zaFusM3NrJ2QZi72SeGuS-ZMPLHDJPUF&fid=0x0:0xf6bddd82220ada13"],"When":"2022-10-30"}]

[{"Name":"Anne Bandejo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpzaJELo0GxrfTA0EO0Gpgr5MHPWoIDk-eZWKz5286ue3SlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have been here so many times before this review. Me and my husband consider this restaurant the best Filipino Restaurant we have been to in BC.
Food is good but presentation is excellent. Meaning food per se has some room for improvement but how they plate their dishes is well thought of in my opinion.
I would say it is a gem every Filipino and Filipino dish loving Canadians need to discover.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuwDcCA2ELKewJYxtY0v0JAGzHBV4aPBDe1sL2&fid=0x0:0x5e00bc0bd8602a01"],"When":"2024-2-26"},{"Name":"Michelle ROQUE","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVD5Ft2yZYkozXs1swLhpIu0nnpqHjqQIX3ls8oMAIBKwcM8hbs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All the dishes are good!!
Clean environment.
Servants were nice & polite.
Prices per dish:from $13- $20","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqTfHd4__K05ZtMgZOMWruL7IwLjGeTvOwYkIf&fid=0x0:0x5e00bc0bd8602a01"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Daniel Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuNUvmwvw8AcLQ688TX5PDDz6FyvOl-76asYWzHQaFu9x2IzjvAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Lumpia Shanghai was fried in old oil. The rolls were dark and slightly bitter

Tapsilog was so dry it was literally the same as beef jerky with no flavour. The salsa that came with was clearly a couple days old because the tomato’s were all soggy and chewy

Chicken sisig was so salty I got nauseous 1/3 of the way through. The meat was brown from the extreme amount of  sauce they used.

Kwekwek was absolutely over fried and the batter wasn’t fresh.

Avoid at all costs…. Considering that other restaurants like epic grill are nearby.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNEqDZEdG2e41ynMBF7m1alsWCdobjku1XwL1eB&fid=0x0:0x5e00bc0bd8602a01"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Edgar Ignacio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7oexz4qXoBKr6ujKuYxwMvlf16ckv-ovFMKFmC4nzUqeMSoelFA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This Pinoy restaurant is truly exceptional! The customer service is top-notch; they promptly replaced our undercooked barbecue without hesitation. The servers are fantastic, ensuring our water was topped up before we even ran out. I highly recommend this place for an outstanding dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuxd-S2GXLR0KDvzzo6kP3QE_8h85jp7NWoQPQ&fid=0x0:0x5e00bc0bd8602a01"],"When":"2021-2-6"},{"Name":"Robert D. Serrano (Dombet)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLR_5ygdPJ2yTk5BPVoia-A-wQcfDBneny4142q_0o9TVyh1yU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The service at this restaurant was excellent.

La Mezza Grill is a great restaurant!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Glasner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlFSX_UUx6rW0lix6i7dkX9lVOSyBZB-F5xxqlskw_ZqxWVSPR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just went to the attached store to get my wife Filipino foods and decided to  try out the restaurant as we are looking for good food from her home land. The eggs are always done nicely. The chicken strips are fantastic here, highly recommended as they are light and crispy!! Been going to this location for years and have always had great customer service, good food and hot coffee! Nice its in the little mall as well if you need to do a bit of shopping. One of our favorite breakfast and family places to eat at!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqgGtygocqY02E8OB7Ec4iDRZ184fMQ82SiaUA\u0026fid=0x0:0x27d17b9c7307c597"],"When":"2023-9-8"},{"Name":"Rick the Sensei","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpixu8L3sNOw6nYNwAcLYVzSPD64H-rZ377kHFRZeipNdMRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've never been here but I've seen it around. We were trying to go somwhere else but it was closed so we took the highway 10 and ended up here. It was already 1:30 p.m. for my kids were starving. Honestly I was expecting a greasy diner  like Danny's but I was wrong. Maybe I was extremely hungry but I was really satisfied with the food. My kids ordered a breakfast set that included pancake sausages sausages and eggs. The pancakes were really good it was not too fluffy but not too hard and not too sweet and not too salty. Just right. I ordered a cheddar bacon burger and it was pretty darn good much better than what I expected for a diner. The patty was not dry and not too thick (I don't enjoy too thick it overpowers the other ingredients) and a good slice of tomato, lettuce, and crunchy bacon. It wasn't soggy or drippy. Man all in all it was pretty darn good food much better then I thought it was going to be. I'll be coming back. And oh the fries and gravy were good!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jay Why","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf6qVrRB2FWSP3f_QpdYqgSMlmFo0fYvO9JkGkahstgPZxGBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Staff was very friendly and there was always someone coming a round to top up our coffee. Everything tasted pretty good though my burger was kind of small and the bun was stale. Ever had a dry piece of bread and then try to toast it? My bun was crumbing into pieces as I was biting into it. Overall it was a pretty good experience. I would come back in the future","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtBlJDEaIAnPJhbtPwjcdhV3aIVoX_4W3-am3Q\u0026fid=0x0:0x27d17b9c7307c597"],"When":"2020-11-9"},{"Name":"Filip Pulpan (Filipos)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQkzrR62le0PjlAmlvrGxMxeXfeixrbfKMP3Xa1-icknONYe_dEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered chicken schnitzel with shredded hash browns and red cabbage. Chicken was tasting weird like a processed meat. And taste of the whole meal was very plain. Cabbage tasted … well… not quite good. Very disappointing.\nOn a good side…. Service was great 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPxHO23kE0fuZ3rea7iKe1CTbqW-RXmtkmwO8YQ\u0026fid=0x0:0x27d17b9c7307c597"],"When":"2023-12-1"},{"Name":"Cassidy Starchild (Cass)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3rhlkFMpL-mxsowKvaMcnyEAb4M_1cLgDpp0VCtOdSBmb6DKyjA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Had the Big Brunch breakfast. Food was good and hot, service was friendly and efficient. Nice, relaxed atmosphere in a clean restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPzZM7ZlOAPcVL6FBXLRo1TkfB8JPeX-oPV9Rz\u0026fid=0x0:0x27d17b9c7307c597"],"When":"2024-2-29"},{"Name":"Monika","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbWWX5dAR4sTlmZWeglXfzxOXvz0yb2CgdnfdM-c3BKRcsoDxn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I’ve been going to this Ricky’s for years now and have never seen such a short-staffed day. I went over the weekend with my family and there was no one to greet us or the people waiting behind us. We only saw one lady doing the entire seating and serving. She apologized the whole time, even though it wasn’t her fault, all while running back and forth to the front and to each table. With an entire queue of people waiting to be seated, you’d think the restaurant would employ/schedule more staff. Don’t burden a single employee to handle the entire space by theirselves! We were so disappointed and felt guilty just being there and adding more unnecessary stress to her day. Someone in the establishment needs to refer back to the Employment Standards Act before an outsider complains.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Debbie Jennings","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMR8hqytR0EJVY6GYBiVyCCEsiXxk9wbUaRyQvoOy_I29wr_MqzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Well, I must say this was absolutely  the best food I've had from any Ricky's the service was amazing. [{"Name":"Marley Mckenzie cook","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5n4XAwgV26WrtDQFOwKexjEHrP8ok0rq2RztGWysEOnM29r4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Avalon chocolate milk is one of my favourites even thought it’s expensive. First time checking out the Avalon retail store / restaurant, food isn’t bad but isn’t the best either, I was hoping it was going to be very good with all the hype but was disappointing. The cranberry sandwich was good but the soup was mediocre at best. I ordered the soup of the day and was told it was chowder but I don’t know what it was.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIeacDaRgm4fGxiMFBb1FjkVT0ehX9KtO3wWc&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Jenn Barnett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzqUWXbP6zEojwPISobVMwfU_yJ6gYFAzXSwx30ZfFRB-hR2aprw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You can purchase milk, eggs, ice cream and all sorts of dairy products. Also bread, cold drinks and snacks. There are daily lunch specials. Plus coffee and muffins.
The staff are friendly.
Plus seating inside and outside.
A real gem in Burnaby","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOV-1oHvZzP1lvYa94mi_6fjn0HnZEGp-h89i_A&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2023-7-2"},{"Name":"D M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuH80L8_wM6G7Idu7S0eKOFlHvGcslndhZ413VSdhWvBY9nw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"They should really consider, lowering their price a small sandwich with bare minimum ingredients and a side of small bag of chips with a drink should not be 17$ !  Very over priced ! And to think they ask for tip on top of that is insane.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0uB2KyLwozflrhdHHOE8KGcmXe8WsnkAalRbO&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"J Chow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5nTjAm8gcoM8KEoMc5sPDIPLKdZEtk_2xDDFiiYwdxxyp1qQ7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Honest and affordable food served here! They're not winning awards for innovation or amazing luxury ingredients but the simplicity is part of the charm. You're just eating in a cozy store. Kitchen is open and people are friendly! My chicken pasta special was great on a rainy afternoon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMoY2ExAsBLCrBRpThTFPEIXp1Ndvd5gWDguPgn&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2023-11-13"},{"Name":"Y. Cherski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-7SLlKKRW0Rqcp9wRXFlvt6gbh0rtI7PMIroLgxETtGiPwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After walking along the Fraser River in Burnaby Fraser Foreshore Park, we decided to have a quick bite but quickly realized that being in an office/industrial area, we don't have much choice. Luckily, Old Farmhouse Kitchen was still open and very close. Since we came forty minutes before closing, I didn't get to try food items I was interested in since they ran out of them. We still got a few things, including vanilla milkshake and latte, to highlight Avalon's main product, which is milk. I tried Avalon produce before, so I was delighted with both items. The milkshake was simply perfect and not too sweet. The interior is pretty cool and cozy with lots of great decorations. We ended up getting some milk produce to go. Overall it was a great experience, and I can see myself coming back. I only wish this joint was located somewhere more accessible.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0t5eUGwQjR3t3Mx5aFApNwoYDr2Of-iPuf2aW&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2019-12-2"},{"Name":"Tami A.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXlJNR4R1uitr082NvPNP_ir27Y4tUaJxwY3uezJWRMn0aqL2I-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice cozy little restaurant with fresh local food and Avalon Dairy products for sale on site. Good daily specials, and an outside patio area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMiQwe2BJaQv_-nPdoL5noBdjqUlxuRTz1leYyK&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"Rae Nason","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLrCw7M-pseb2AZi8wT9Qnwdaq2jr_70LDDM9v2l_e5mRJVMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ok people coffee is good when it's hot lol but I've never had a chef salad with zero veggies 😅 come on guys","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMT4_mS_RBABUYp3TPxQPPNixli_IMB9rkvkSPC&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2024-6-7"},{"Name":"Vee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNqo7GsNEXpPBVCqGGWsNLS6BGEH4QfuZNVx2RABtSfESedQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The cafe is located near the industrial area and hence a little out of the way. It is near the Fraser river though, so a meal before or after a walk by the river is always fun!

The servers were friendly and food was served promptly. The food seemed fresh and I also bought a chocolate cookie. It was great! It wasn’t too sweet; just right for my taste buds!

I’m not sure if there are discounts for the diary products sold here, but they do have a variety: milk, yogurt, ice cream, and even homemade soup! I purchased one to try and it was savoury, but it is still best to have it in store.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdnNOk8kE6n_zCpEbhVLa8N8gKvnvIFUSL0Ox2&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2019-8-25"}]

[{"Name":"Shaeli Finnie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9swc8R2K-WPKeSpodeW9gMPefWym8hWzzaxuYb_8dEHf-eO8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I believe I tried the plain cheese pizza and the rest lovers yesterday.
I'm a very picky pizza person and this place is okay 👍
Try spicing the meat really well or sauce or add some type of kick to the pizza for a more unique pizza in the future.
I'm gonna shop around for that specialty zaa place that's to die for.
Overall it's a small shop, looks mom and pop run, a single booth to sit at, polite friendly etc.
If you wanna support local business,  go here and not a franchise place. I might be back to try a more specialty pizza here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMV6Og1zVwN4s9_5ji85xyK7GMrxyMusgOIIPYO&fid=0x0:0xec0cf41da8385ccb"],"When":"2024-12-25"},{"Name":"Simran Gosal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPmqYJW7o1Cey3OqfluBQCQ162C7WOlyuz7zdVwj7G7Zn0Ug=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered large Pizza from their store. Half Shahi paneer and half butter chicken. I asked the employee to make chicken side spicy (to add green chilis) instead they added jalapenos. These are the jalapenos that came out of one slice. I literally took out 2 bowls of these from 5 slices of Pizza. After then I called the store not to get refund just to tell them that this happened. They were arguing that they didn't put jalapenos at all. I used to go to this store regularly but after what happened today I will never go to this place again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZHk0eEpBoUNm2LX2_mrpcO6GZPQ4uWzeba5lP&fid=0x0:0xec0cf41da8385ccb"],"When":"2022-7-3"},{"Name":"Vida Corvus","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqINKLe9b1hKofrDcCLAKEL-6hQV6fdy1HehcGnPVwrDjBQXY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been looking for a good pizza place in surrey for sometime, and this place is it. The trick is to order well done. The crust has the perfect amount of crunch/texture","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKSQBXAzBzCNTRUBTqEWZPM_tWW0HrtofnRzzp&fid=0x0:0xec0cf41da8385ccb"],"When":"2023-4-29"},{"Name":"Zain Shyanne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwljMDRLcobSHBOYATSkUfyA8eUV6IQqD-3N5acOVGljmLFao=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been ordering here since I was a student at LA Matheson at least over 14 years. The recipe is unchanged to this day and it's the best pizza in Surrey hands down. There are lots of places that make Indian vegetarian pizzas but Prime Hut does it best. The crust and cheese is just perfect and flavourful you can actually taste the oregano. The owners themselves are extremely humble and nice I wish more people supported them they haven't even changed their prices as much in years. Back in the high school days some kids wouldn't have money and they'd still give them slices.  I recommend this place whenever I can.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Damanpreet singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLuk02oj_BxJheWLjV-KgR_DTVu1qUELQ_w4OXU60cFY4xGdA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"one of the best places in PG ! 100% recommended ! Staff is so friendly and polite ! always smiling faces !! Thanks prime pizza team 😊","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Ming Lui To","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUEnpNKEVxnP6-lBlHcK5NFcIkPpx3EuMdI9qk5Miv4GOofSrn_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Prime Hut Pizza is awesome.  I run school programs in the Surrey School District and whenever we have a staff event or student event in our program we use Prime Hut Pizza.  They are local, they went to Surrey Schools (awesome) and they're delicious. We never have ANY leftovers.  Their Gluten Free pizza is also amazing - some say it even taste better than their regular pizza (which is also amazing).  I really encourage anyone in the Surrey/ Delta area to give Prime Hut a call!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Kish","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7ycvrk6h2EgX33KYv5Ceieh7bFehxG3h5f_c56EQetMf0PNdbrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious. A nice balance of toppings to dough. We tried a pepperoni and mushroom and a veggie pizza to test them out. Everyone loved it. We’ll certainly go back to explore other ‘za","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lucky Bryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLnBe66fzAP1HI9HURHb9zcqHbrYN9fymWk6YX7-QXKqfTZds=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going here for 15 years. There pizza is very thick and juicy. Easily the best pizza in surrey by my standards. Try there chef special my favourite, hawaiian, supreme, house special. It is amazing. I live abroad and i crave this pizza when i am abroad. It is that good! The prices are only 11-12 for a large.  You just cant beat that in the city.  It is a family owned business and the couple are extremely nice and humbling.  They have a couple of tables inside if you want to eat in. It reminds me of a indian street food place.  A great feeling.  Love street food in india. Make sure you tell them to.make it medium spicy and add cilantro and garlic. I always recommend this place to my friends. If you seriously dont like this pizza.  Something is wrong with you.😂 Thanks ! They have been in business for so many years for a reason .  It makes me quite angry about the complainers.  Definitely not deserved for an amazing business that has been here throughout the pandemic and well before.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Amy Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXqddZyajPNoFhSfeKC0jxyRc2Om1n2-N6OKu8IHOhfMDJ3cE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First to use DoorDash to order food from this restaurant. The grilled lemongrass chicken vermicelli was so small portion. I ordered same food from other Vietnamese restaurant with similar price, the portion was much bigger.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTpWZ7i_SuLRM6m26G35pr7bgjLI2riLsdXRkY&fid=0x0:0x909964153c312c90"],"When":"2024-7-12"},{"Name":"Con Chronicler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILXHCRtdvFXgn0tTM0h8ev_q8sKeKrNAJG8b_jtfVRSIcGpg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is definitely a good local, almost hidden eatery for your occasions. The food is tastier than your average pho place. The service never fails to impress, and the atmosphere is classic. Good local pick.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdGhiMyU57zwF9W6rPccuTqm453LI99hD-vpFE&fid=0x0:0x909964153c312c90"],"When":"2023-12-9"},{"Name":"This food","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUaxcCslaGrcC0u202g67ni7XJGWWGyPYtSKkUjWo5gpcXXO0Yv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious broth. For 5pm it was not busy, which was great until 6 pm hit. I ordered the house special pho (number 14) and a rice plate (number 62) with grilled pork chop and chicken. The chicken was a thigh only. The rice meal was smaller than I expected, but it was still delicious. Overall great service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNf4u1dcKzFRycLcxA8x8yOkOZwJ7mdwngEdKIc&fid=0x0:0x909964153c312c90"],"When":"2022-5-27"},{"Name":"Sheena Chandra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUR3p0C7A3HRi4N9KLcpFSMzefABROoXAyx8Eabt7Fead-uz_M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We got great service from the young guy working but unfortunately our tea cups had a long black hair right in it. They quickly exchanged it for us but when I went to pick up a spoon it was dirty as well. Pho broth was nice but sadly I was already turned off.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5xjTrkMW7Yr2BKUU5tF5H7qEQMlnIk6ATmRlv&fid=0x0:0x909964153c312c90"],"When":"2018-2-4"},{"Name":"eduardo0","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2doVpQGldcyxWFXT6quW54ugCUNmn5RMVpSuGqlS2jzmv_g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I'm so disappointed that all noodles are broken into pieces when I pick them up,( I ordered No.6), and the man who served us didn't say any sorry or apology at all when I showed him that.
Will never go again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuP01z3PYKHYwA5epy7SqcoptT8YmYDNgGkaTg&fid=0x0:0x909964153c312c90"],"When":"2023-10-8"},{"Name":"Paul Ng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWUZ49Ul-3bVyJjJAjiIzsDwRpD0pREaGPqHRlWfDN0XxY4lrGiA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Clean, spacious restaurant located in the plaza with plenty of parking.  Price gone up but the portion size remains. Soup is very hot with a very thick layer of oil but a bit salty. Meat looks fresh. Overall is good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4afomF0XOYZjZ3irvwLWsX0IGl06D-9rR0Uge&fid=0x0:0x909964153c312c90"],"When":"2022-7-4"},{"Name":"DLH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNxoVJChN19TlxEyh2PqXcySZWcsWGp-pw0aGewSStRgeU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Regulars here since opened. Kim, Johnny and all the servers are super friendly, know the regulars and their orders.
Food is consistent and prices very reasonable. You can definitely get a good cheap meal here as lots of variety. Phō is always hot but does contain MSG for those who want to avoid. However the won ton soup and beef stew with noodle soup does not. Too many tasty options to list. Tea is complimentary and their own special blend.
Vegan/vegetarian options offered.

Busy during lunch on weekdays. Service and food prepared quickly. Would be 5 star if more attention given to cleaning the walls and booths as noodles in soup splashes. 😆

Update(June 2020)- prices increased to reflect current food costs.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvrW95FLAX8CyDznhdvGAPQAhQB_3l---vuXQ&fid=0x0:0x909964153c312c90"],"When":"2020-6-22"},{"Name":"Jason Hale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKcIIL_X2tX-dj2FeQITrAXMnZDDnnpAP2sIZG_Ttu-IMw9Gg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered delivery, bad choice. All noodles for soup had clearly been out for hours, they all clumped together even in the broth. The shrimp in the vermicelli bowl were leathery, threw them all out after first bite. Would not order again. Brutal!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Anurag Sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLuNWZNGEXcZYuxJm3PAALeRt53oSt1Pks2yfZ8cIUcOqDeBA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This was the worst experience I’ve ever had. The girl with glasses at the front desk was extremely disrespectful. I ordered food, but we weren’t even offered water. Meanwhile, the table next to us received friendly greetings and prompt service. They were served their food before us, even though we had ordered first.

I had ordered one plate of chole bhature and one gobi paratha. After waiting 15 minutes, only the chole bhature arrived, and the paratha never came. Frustrated, I decided to leave without finishing my meal. To make matters worse, the girl with glasses charged me for both the chole bhature and the paratha.

The service was absolutely pathetic. I’m never coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM47rULbtWwz2tpUrb2mzQDX5bQtXnIazAoJjZz&fid=0x0:0x3f418a1902bbb472"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Alyssa Jade","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVP3BT6QCtKzYrodkNhl4oehDqhZVLsZk1_86M1pnEIZ3rC6PVmBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We live in the okanagan but come out to
Vancouver a couple times a year and we will now add this to the list of stops we make every trip down to Van.
I’m not Indian but still received amazing service and suggestions aswell as education. Their cashews are soo good, easy to bring home and store, the aloo paratha is so fresh and perfect for a road snack. Prices are good and store is clean.
We will be back 100%, thank you Baba Sweets 🙏🏼","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNer_-rZOz1NxQcVhx0r_Z4mRQiIo0gF-hSFClw&fid=0x0:0x3f418a1902bbb472"],"When":"2024-9-6"},{"Name":"Simran Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNClaMWehPTTWtbhjwVN9uXg1xejwqrwQN6zcDewXYBIiw1A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"One of the best sweets shop on Scott road. This is our go to place for samosas and sweets. Owners are very nice and also give good customer service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNlr3_ykpciP7plZ6OYmuCb3Knkjga6ReibQsyJ&fid=0x0:0x3f418a1902bbb472"],"When":"2024-3-18"},{"Name":"Jagmeet Gill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLpl2yHu2NPa_ZPuw0wSfaCJBFQk6gDqSfsAQe86QeGL9OWSUM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I  ordered samosa chaat from them  and i am really disappointed. The samosa chaat arrived without chutneys and onions. It was take out and when I called the staff they said you can come back now we can put chutneys on like  what is this. I hope the restaurant maintains the taste because their taste is getting disgusting day by day.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Latika Kanojia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKDqaRp4nVNlNki1EjFLCYLxJ-5juRVmQjBKTPx9lAwnlxEhE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food was really good. Customer service could be little better. Overall I give rating 4","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBGE3FDj9ajaDnTsSvX7MiDpRiGaCE5VpsBLK4&fid=0x0:0x3f418a1902bbb472"],"When":"2023-11-22"},{"Name":"Kisha Heart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZRtkuBuqVnxRNThLjiWF8tU2-iDtXMckIJjKrhICh53X5p0o=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of the best restaurants that we visited recently for sweets and Indian dishes, the service is excellent and the staff are very supportive. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNLJumKfOy-8yJhMH2y1L5yj_k8buLB5zvt44iP&fid=0x0:0x3f418a1902bbb472"],"When":"2021-8-21"},{"Name":"Jasmeen Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIkMNk2HXtLI1NYwbjuLnerUbbULgQZH3SXJd3SpB4UgFn0o7w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I tried their chole bhature, they were really toooo good, mouth watering,fresh.

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Sade Hanslip","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdgvsoM2_p-8YmjyT1SQ8DaeO7YrEGvpY0U2ElC-uzOSqn5g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I never bought raw pizza before, may as well sell them frozen.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ruth Hawkings","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKcnGeLIrpQJp4TlVtJilq_EoEoKj6NecgvfZcDXAOg89ZtrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We have ordered from Delice several times and this time around the chicken wings came and they were quite cold to the point we weren't sure they had been cooked. I called to complain and was told by 2 employees that there was nothing they could do about it and that they felt it was the drivers fault for not delivering on time. Pizza was hot - why would the chicken wings be that cold. user_reviews: [{"Name":"Ayesha Goonesekere","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWGmgkdQEbWhbfzpAU_EjOXM0Mcy-oGBte6ptZvh_UTzLpzg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you're searching for an authentic taste of Mexico, look no further than \"Dos Amigos\". This gem of a restaurant offers a culinary journey that tantalizes the taste buds and transports you straight to the heart of Mexico. From the moment you step through the door, you're greeted with warm hospitality and a vibrant ambiance that sets the stage for an unforgettable dining experience.\nNow, onto the main event—the food. Prepare to be dazzled by a menu that boasts a delightful array of Mexican delights, each dish bursting with flavour and made with the freshest ingredients. Whether you're craving classic favourites like Tacos and Burritos or eager to try something new like Baja Fries, \"Dos Amigos\" delivers with authenticity and flair.\nIn conclusion, \"Dos Amigos\" is a five-star dining destination that combines exquisite cuisine, vibrant ambiance, and top-notch service to create a truly unforgettable experience. Whether you're a seasoned foodie or simply looking for a taste of Mexico, this restaurant is a must-visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNJKVo0-8v2FuR8zVsvFREJUtXuuXjzWWpIsOg\u0026fid=0x0:0x9b3267e69b167c65"],"When":"2024-2-15"},{"Name":"AJ R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLo4tIvUrcwNXdNPm8MhPpZgzsQXb-_lGpW8MEceFXJ5buZ1dI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dos Amigos offers a taste of authentic Mexican food as well as a few deliciously unique items. I've only had one issue in 10 years with quality and they sorted it out immediately.

Great family business.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"J. F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvnPrghjIIxyliVLQ5qdXC_aHHLxKWdRLtv7_c0XpUi4UfZmBiFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Apollo pizza always has pretty consistent delicious pizza. Great tasting sauce, lots of cheese, nice firm cgewy dough but not tough, you can choose your own toppings or from their creations. We love the ham and pineapple here! The combo deals are excellent value, we often get the two baked pastas with 2 pizzas meal deals which gives us multiple meals! Our pizza was ready in 20min for pick up, we decided to picnic out at the park last time....One of the best in North Delta!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2QHjEd9pY0jufX2cLrgltPLcdBurfHOx0CQtO&fid=0x0:0xfae1f7f5a3c56cda"],"When":"2023-8-22"},{"Name":"DigiBean","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXePsrpkERI_iUcybU_W5MOatvNSCdqvUlTRysRiu0ESPsEHGxZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My favorite pizza in the lower mainland, i wish there was a pizza shop like this closer to Maple Ridge. Fully loaded "Italian delight" worth the drive, in my opinion. Thanks, fellas!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"B Bajwa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHGC1tR35aeo6AlQ3Brr-A2rlzqGmFcI36aF_DFECFBPPUZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Apollo is without a doubt the best pizza shop in North Delta. You'll get a pizza that is made with quality ingredients, always loaded, and cooked to perfection.The sauce has a great rich deep taste to it, and the cheese is always plentyful. At Apollo, they aren't cheaping out on toppings like most pizza shops or using measuring cups to measure how much cheese to use.
They truly live up to their claim of being "makers of fine pizza."
My personal recommendation: cooks special with ginger&cilantro","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8z5jnaFfsmOCPI7gy6A8L75RjdaUaf49Vbumr&fid=0x0:0xfae1f7f5a3c56cda"],"When":"2023-9-5"},{"Name":"DLH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNxoVJChN19TlxEyh2PqXcySZWcsWGp-pw0aGewSStRgeU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had to order the Italian Delight after reading rave reviews for Apollo pizza and wanting to support local business.
We ordered 2 of the same but you can order any combination of 2 with price adjusted accordingly.
Order was for pick-up 30 min.after placing order right at 3:30 p.m. opening.
This pizza was loaded (12 toppings) and delicious. Would definitely order again.
Located in a small strip mall with limited parking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNyB1e_hGoK_yN5U_JeoqTm8ploFJFxLrPBWJs&fid=0x0:0xfae1f7f5a3c56cda"],"When":"2021-4-28"},{"Name":"Kathleen Belliveau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUSFxhb1dgOJx2BcNirnB2G-MBBHCrXykDjykAP776RqjxWOUOEA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best pizza ever. They stayed open a little late for us ordering for 11:25pm on a Tuesday. Epic service, unreal food!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNm-tUUqTf9ZenO647lRDxeQvaeTu2QOuw49a5d&fid=0x0:0xfae1f7f5a3c56cda"],"When":"2024-5-2"},{"Name":"George Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLeuNnxEuJ8_sUj1Nrpb9wyS8wp9g14WltOkYOOJFp-kFphgw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I used to live in the neighborhood and Apollo was my go to pizza place. I now live on the north shore but still travel to delta for Apollo from time to time.  It’s the best.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Crystal Daignaullt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVj6x_7UZ6E9GHa-IMyBT2qTpudaLtpYXOFJQbwBhnKVD4zogF_yQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My Sons and mine New favorite Pizza and Pasta place to order from  .They have so many toppings on the Pizza its stacked .Way better then any pizza place around ! The Ravioli and Lasagna was so good .The sauce was so tasty and the Garlic bread went so well with it 😊 Thank you","Images":null,"When":""}]

..poke bowl was delish with a good amount of Tuna, edamame, mango, rice etc etc.$8
Skewers were delish too $7

Friend had a sandwich which was a triple decker with salad.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0cPyFd4Z9Isyj_nlVEjr6CorEUw1YhFcztuzj&fid=0x0:0xff652bf97dac55e1"],"When":"2024-5-7"},{"Name":"Ravinder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLkPloS5guSgzrcPyY4emO5BrXTqYyFfYe_2yvQHJjiKU7UVFI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Some people have bad experiences but I’ve been here 3 times now and it’s been pretty decent every time.

This place has a decent beer selection, typical pub food, and an ok vibe.

They not the best in any category but it will due for a quick bite and drink with friends.

One huge thumbs up here is the size of the salsa and sour cream that comes with the nachos, finally someone gets it right.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMEZT4MDd3bm_iT_ZEv_MOfiP-w3AQGDoAON12M&fid=0x0:0xff652bf97dac55e1"],"When":"2024-5-19"},{"Name":"Kristen Spanza Pedersen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwMYGtMaY38AyOIyeZrSjTZDF17egD_3KNJBhIZHF7YSCyq7gTtg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow.  I need to become a regular.  Dog friendly patio and great service.  15% cheaper than white spot for exceptional food.   I've been a couple of times and you can tell that the kitchen really cares about food quality all the time.  Huge smash burgers, beef drip and salad were all the best we've had in years.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"DLH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNxoVJChN19TlxEyh2PqXcySZWcsWGp-pw0aGewSStRgeU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Update Aug. 15/23:

We’ve been several times since I first reviewed.
Here is the new menu with the Summerfest $5 menu now integrated into the regular menu, note new lower pricing too.
There are also $5 drink deals that are not on the menu, ask if they don’t tell you about them.
We returned today for the Loaded Smash Burger ($11), comes with 2 Pattie’s, bacon, cheese, lettuce, onion and fries. This is a full sized portion, not the smaller Summerfest burger.
We also ordered DF Pickles and Torpedo Shrimp.($5 ea.) before we knew the burger was so filling.
See new pics.

Have eaten in years ago, received good service then and great service today when ate in on the patio. They are taking Covid precautions with staff now wearing masks for the public’s comfort even though not mandatory, social distant dining, sanitizer at every entrance, wipe down of pin pad before/after use and name/phone # taken for contact tracing.

On a week day it was not too busy on the patio or inside. Service by Sheila was friendly and attentive. Shared plates of Fish and Chips and Beef Dip were excellent. Individual containers for ketchup, packets for salt, pepper and vinegar were provided, as well as our request the au jus be split for 2 sharing. Cutlery brought after ordering.

Already looking forward to returning for the fish and chips which were flaky, lightly battered and crispy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5Gc6SXCWYuX9Rrl5LcW25IM70W1SUsEtWY9Y&fid=0x0:0xff652bf97dac55e1"],"When":"2020-7-14"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Ms Mama bear","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLWX5Jxdcwj2wHgBV-1-8EZaNxwhCM_H5mxOtG_pdo6jDTOTR2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Small little pizza joint in Delta but was always known to our family as awesome pizza with amazing crust which is very hard to find around here. We’ve been coming back to this joint for many many years now however, tonight we were extremely disappointed to the upmost the toppings were not fresh and the shrimp was freezer burnt if you look in the pictures, it’s very noticeable, I didn’t want to risk my children getting sick so I threw out their pieces and the remaining. When in doubt throw it out, I will always stick by that nothing is worth getting Yourself or your family sick. I just don’t understand how this went unnoticed at a restaurant and in this time, and we spent so much to having food ordered in is such a luxury that not many of us can afford to have this experience to the upmost disappointment. I really hope you guys check the freshness of your food more often, if this is not corrected in a timely manner, I do not think my family will be doing business with this establishment again .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3GhZkMTiGP9xhciKT1ADL1-OPigNgKPiuw2Fl\u0026fid=0x0:0x629afbf3037977b3"],"When":"2024-4-5"},{"Name":"Damanjot Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3Byp7mXm4JHjz3HPnNEZRRHe8TVRCpk5fZd5i4qFb4dnECw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We ordered 2 large tandoori chicken pizzas. I am going to complain health authorities tomorrow.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMeMZSSXGFAdjDxBkFp-8ENmCjQaZct7JsDDmt2\u0026fid=0x0:0x629afbf3037977b3"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Jaeger Mah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVt7hXDkFIcG6P61qcK0wBTq3t5gD1ANgzOWhiOupEWI1RBHtWj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"** Pros: Fast delivery. Make sure use fresh ketchup.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Church","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuh5tX_wAivpgwi0sGjc57xo9boqIWL2XIlbJMmWwuKpv42HBEbA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Quiet atmosphere but the people and their customer service are top notch.\nDelicious fresh made to order food","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anzal Yusuf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZaDFbPVBccMzEN5edlxNiePs-h9No_clG0okjJrpzNzWDYtUs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"So today, I went to this restaurant and ordered pizza. He rudely asked why I was drinking there, saying I can’t eat or drink from other restaurants in his place. I was drinking a Tim Horton drink. He even questioned if I had ordered yet, and when I confirmed, he went to the kitchen to verify with the lady. When she confirmed my order, he returned acting angry and left. I felt disrespected, so I left I’ll never came back to this place ever again I was a good customer and used to eat from there a lot but from now on it’s done","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Profillers Staffing Solutions","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzty6_ClebXpAWspUk76Ns64RcT30G6yUA_GEPKoIBYKyuIRVj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"For the past four years, Perfect Pizza has been our go-to for Christmas party catering, and they consistently deliver an excellent experience. The pizzas are always a hit – flavorful, with fresh ingredients and perfectly cooked crusts. What really sets them apart is their outstanding customer service. They're always friendly, accommodating, and make the ordering process a breeze. If you're looking for great pizza and even better service, look no further than Perfect Pizza .","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"RAVNEET CHEEMA","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvhwO6Uci6AjBqW7baZKiJu-JAGC4lBWykF7q10awaP8GImw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Pizza on Scott Road - Must Try their new Shahi Paneer Pizza \u0026 Chipotle Paneer Pizza!\n\nIf you're looking for the best pizza near me in Delta and Surrey this place is a hidden gem! Their Shahi Paneer Pizza and Karahi Paneer Pizza are absolute game-changers. Packed with rich, authentic flavors, both pizzas offer a perfect balance of spice and cheese for a truly mouth-watering experience. As a vegetarian, it's hard to find good options, but their vegetarian pizza selection is vast, and the quality never disappoints. The staff is friendly, and the service is quick. Whether you’re craving something traditional or looking to try something new, this pizza joint is a must-visit for all pizza lovers in Delta and Surrey!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGZrsznZBLN-y6KFiHGHPXQYvuIPxtRrCt1e1a\u0026fid=0x0:0x8dd5bb037ff7e814"],"When":"2024-10-8"},{"Name":"S.S. S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIqnlpmS2LqkmFx3GKnagT0peZM_wzsT02yD9iVdMiLnjtA_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I got a pizza ( ordered toppings specifically) and an additional topping was added to it … didn’t ask for it… and when a call back to query the scenario was told it was added to make it taste better. Huh ? Are you eating it ? What happens if someone had an allergy / dislike ? Threw it out. 35 min drive home and we get this ?? Been ordering pizza here for decades and unfortunately the level of empathy has changed with the ownership . Owner couldn’t understand where I was coming from. Was very polite about it when I called and felt disheartened.  I wasn’t rude and felt low listening to the lady.  Please don’t mix me up for another customer. I’m sure you help many people as you are a popular place.  I didn’t call right away.  This owner didn’t value people’s time and money with getting orders right.  Now the gentleman owner there provides great service.  Keep it up !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Xinwen Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_lPXtoBU_PNOnrlu1KYZTSIHYynMDsK4a2zkUOhUlboCruw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently tried both their pepperoni and Hawaiian pizzas, and I was really impressed! The crust was perfectly crispy, and the toppings were fresh and flavorful. The pepperoni pizza had just the right amount of spice, while the Hawaiian pizza was a great balance of sweet and savory. The service was quick and friendly, and the overall experience was fantastic. Highly recommend this spot for anyone craving delicious pizza!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aston Chaboyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ9luQ1RKtVKiYrPxpVcLMEPHxOngYc7TgW7ZzhRDbCwOYKbg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We order from here all the time. Love this place!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gurpinder Sandhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKU25eeovpfhQq2mSXG6gu_pBzQNnPM3XWk-p8DbutADrrozA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited the place yesterday, and it's a wonderful spot to relax and enjoy a cup of tea.
