I’m definitely looking forward to visiting again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dalbir Bhattal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKI3vo8RDVsJQyNVvjDBuubXqBEnUCx-uOFPLPRQrlC0B6DLw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They have a very nice café with a great ambiance. As using your palm/hand to wipe off the excess food from the counter top to the floor then proceeding to prepare my burger wasn't quiet sanitary!!.. felt disgusted","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennie H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPNtzJqMkXpM_yl5Xcpp4sVRpDlXELrNOIdb5rE1olC4vT6ifG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Frequent this location whenever I feel the occasional craving for McD as it is quiet and very clean. The fries are always fresh too.

This time, I ordered curbside and the staff member was very nice, had a big smile and very polite!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Review Truly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1r_p5CbqF95zJ9gAkSPraeDU5TCpW6jzLmdNlgbvA3ye31A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Dear management team,

I am writing to formally lodge a complaint regarding the poor service and unprofessional behavior I encountered from the Manager Ravneet (I am not sure if it’s correct name, I don’t see any name batch on them) at your McDonald's store located at 1285 Clivedon Ave, Delta, BC, on November 24, 2024.

I placed an online order (Order #2106) and went to the store to pick it up. When I received my order, but upon reaching home, I discovered that the hashbrowns, a water bottle, and the Happy Meal box were missing. I immediately called the store to report the issue but received no response. After several attempts, the manager, Ravneet, finally answered the call. When I inquired about the missing items, she told me that they had been left on the counter, implying that it was my mistake for not picking them up.

Despite explaining the situation, Ravneet did not make any effort to resolve the issue or offer any assistance. She spoke in a dismissive and rude manner, which I found completely unacceptable. As a loyal McDonald's customer, I expect better treatment and respect, not only as a consumer but also in my interactions with staff.

I request that the management team review this matter and provide an apology for Ravneet's unprofessional conduct. I would appreciate a resolution to this issue, as I believe customers should be treated with courtesy and respect at all times.

Thank you for your attention to this matter. I look forward to your response.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOfO6YwjJOzKDQsGCnAzmmas3OQPV-8e7Z-cv5p&fid=0x0:0x1750ee8f431c31c2"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"CriticalBeee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUf9vcBYCB2s0D1bzgz2NSuPZl2c3ejXsXj-abxr-eQaUZcTMs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This is one of the worst mcds to order delivery and for dine-in. Reading past reviews, the reoccurring complaint is the watered-down orange juice and the constant wrong orders.  My wife ordered here because it's the only location popping up on doordash. We spent over $50, and we received no eggs on our sausage egg griddles, and all our orange juices had to be thrown out. Whoever manages this particular restaurant does not care how the staff are trained, or they are purposely making wrong orders to save on food cost. I've stopped going in-house, as my orders are always wrong. You'd think with the mcdonalds warehouse being on annacis island, they would have fresher products. As an ex-shift manager, for Mcds of 10 years. Never again would we order from this location.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jarrod Barnes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIeceTJmLEsKqP3iHvd_c-fehr0LcThFXSXyKK1RGkHIPBo0A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I go there often for breakfast however the shrinkflation has hit here to! Dont get the OJ!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ashley Ford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJzg2RBJZaohk7hmO1_bzLlthUJHQ1LXkGlEaQP1PQGtYu0JA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Order burgers with no onions. The food is delicious. I’ll be making this my “go to” from now on. Fabulous sandwiches! 💙","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"DLH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNxoVJChN19TlxEyh2PqXcySZWcsWGp-pw0aGewSStRgeU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly recommend this family owned and run local deli. Shopping made easy as Sandra Till runs front of house with cheerful, friendly service. She knows her regulars by name and what they like. Stephen Till, award winning sausage maker, makes most products, with high quality no filler ingredients.
If you have food allergies/sensitivities shop here. Too many favourites to list all: brats(various varieties), thueringer, homemade deli meats, french pork, garlic sausage, pepperoni, liverwurst are a few. Homemade sauerkraut with bits of sausage is yummy.
Many items brought in: Grimms, breads and many canned/jar items from Germany. They bring in limited supply for Christmas such as Glühwein, german gingerbread cookies, etc. Buy early as goes fast.
Located in a small strip mall with lots of parking.

Update (Dec 2021)- For an easy, relaxed Xmas Day lunch we pre-ordered a sandwich/bun and charcuterie tray.
As usual, owner Sandra did not disappoint.
Everything was awesome and we’ll be enjoying it for a few days.
Also pre-ordered rouladen cut (raw) beef to make a special dinner.
Note: only available at Xmas.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPCnhKtXx8KHzAFJsAKIeHIJ5GB3XCu0faquHw&fid=0x0:0x5c77f941345b9f0f"],"When":"2021-12-26"},{"Name":"Tom McDougall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0J48kC1hZM1V1aRsvHOZVDophlDmEISwqhKMFe94oVeHk06c2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic local deli in the heart of North Delta.   Great made to order sandwiches and deli meat.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtf5ySishJiRxQ1qkfid42iPrMXrzMBvvZ7ZH2&fid=0x0:0x5c77f941345b9f0f"],"When":"2024-5-11"},{"Name":"Jerry Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvvBpZoMjueQB2J1i0SQDP1pCBU-HRcyxN-CW8114Ou5CuSCkJYg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The smoked meats and different varieties of bratwurst are the best that you will find anywhere. In addition to buying meats they are also a full service deli. The sandwiches are made using their own baked rolls. I would also recommend their homemade soups. They also have a nice selection of food products from Germany. Pay a visit and say hi to Sandra who works the counter","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marla Poirier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoDpdYy6WqLMWS-vpCYoFbHM0FyrBp8z4L6hQh_XL7dkOt0cda=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you really want the full experience, walk into the store, and close your eyes. Take a deep breath. The tantalizing aroma of smoked meats will draw you in.
I've been going here for 50 years. It's been owned for almost 15 years by owners who have even made it better, as the unique and vast array of their home-smoked and cured meats are beyond delicious, and in some cases, can't be found outside of Germany.
You know you're in the right place when you see that everyone who is also shopping is a regular. The sandwiches almost always sell out,  (made fresh for you), and I've yet to sample everything that they offer. I always go for the smoked hock though. It makes the most delicious soup, whether you just add dried lentils or peas, or throw some carrots and leaks into the hammy broth. If I could give this place 10 stars I would.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ian Tait","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVPpmPEXY_YylhA0SM-Us5Nb8-HtL1X6QAjcyREGTwY4YgtskU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A range of delicious, hand-crafted, small-batch, homemade, gluten-free deli products. You've got to visit this North Delta family-owned business to experience what they offer their customers. It's tasty ... and much, much more.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOiwlY0xB4P9l7CiNBvawfPPzKNgtusvDCrLOmE&fid=0x0:0x5c77f941345b9f0f"],"When":"2020-2-26"},{"Name":"Oliver Kester","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-UfeV1ayCnU0_MDuaABWNR8gPhup5pFNx8-rIcopBVHzJAniV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great German specialities, delicious sausages, ham and many other goodies","Images":null,"When":""}]

They forgot to deliver the main dish- rice. It was around 11pm and we obviously ordered through Door Dash for convenience. We kept calling and no one answered the phone so I had to go in and asked to speak to the \"manager.\" He said that they gave the driver 3 bags (rice was in this bag with attached receipt) but the driver failed to deliver it.  We had already contacted the driver prior to going to the restaurant and the poor man was adamant that the restaurant only gave him 2 bags. The manager even said to show us camera footage but didn't think that was necessary over rice. lol. Also, why would someone lie about that so I believed him. I got to find out when I got home that the manager contacted the driver (while I was waiting for my rice to be cooked) and admitted that they didn't give him the rice. The manager lied to my face!! The manager gave me my rice and also gave an extra order of butter chicken but didn't apologize for any inconvenience. Customer service is horrible and its too bad because the food was really good. They were willing to allow Door Dash take the negative criticism for their own fault. It's okay if you make a mistake, just be accountable for it. Never will I order from here again and I will be sure to spread the news to all my friends and family. [{"Name":"Tom McDougall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0J48kC1hZM1V1aRsvHOZVDophlDmEISwqhKMFe94oVeHk06c2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fresh and tasty. Great choice for a quick healthy meal.
Friendly staff and they had a well maintained facility","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNg0S65g5UjyMme_E-Sq_FKywKxPuohFsehtlIt&fid=0x0:0x1454995701ca095e"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Anmol Dhillon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQKCh0cXaNiQlvZx0lWw1nr0yooVHZrtoqseVJVMyFeBsuIaU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Giving one star for their terrible service . I have been their regular customer from long time. But one of the crew who was preparing my wrap put lot of buffalo sauce and my stomach got hurt . Even i told her why you put extra sauce and she just said ok , no apology even after making mistake . She didnt bother . Thats not the service you expect after paying 15 bucks on a wrap . She forced me to write this review","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ember N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAOVVSRZSBJ6e5O5jUUtiBAq23q-FcEx-8tVq1hmthlfDRNYcfgw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered for take out. a bit expensive but a very very good option. portion is a bit smaller than dining in.

We came here while cycling from Burnaby. Ambiance is good. It would be better if there was some dividers when i was there. Place is clean!

I would come back here again.

-2 because of portioning.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN6vzmVDPafnCdh6wCAbtxoAgt9A-IIVO8nnuzm&fid=0x0:0x1454995701ca095e"],"When":"2021-5-22"},{"Name":"Tim Dovey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3hRqeSE1Ni6xzm8x3OJSAQIB3dlLAWPvVYWaVVzqKwaqg4vs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ridiculously small portions. Paid $13 for a wrap I finished in about 4 bites. I understand portion sizes can very between restaurants, but this was unacceptable. Save your money and go somewhere else.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Roma Setia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKopzAyiUvpZzQOtX_VTXCXx-PwBX4F9XWzyVU1XlWuU15AAoY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I do love the food but service is a nightmare. We were told that we cannot order for atleast an hour because staff is busy preparing catering order. I do like the place but would not come back again or will suggest anyone concerning the attitude of the staff.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Clarissa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHucsI2CeByMOdetMrELLicLCRgBagHzWBTkigcJ_31eEF8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I used to love Chopped Leaf.. But today the quality is the worse. The food is not fresh, no sauce for Bangkok salad (which is essential and can’t eat without sauce). Phone calls were not picked up (I wonder the customer service might be same like other reviews that mentioned the worse customer service for this location). I order this for to go during my lunch time at work. Now I don’t have time to go back to store to get the replacement. This is mean I don’t have lunch today and starving until end of my work. Thanks to poor quality and no customer service from Chopped Leaf 😠","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmYRFPxPCEDpM0QbRHF3LY_C_Doh3Y-rxTHrlK&fid=0x0:0x1454995701ca095e"],"When":"2021-11-27"},{"Name":"Mary Nekouei","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIv8Xb7KTjkaZ4fQRcOXzfkASZied89_V_VbQ7eWAvtuqQMWA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Unfortunately , they didn’t put the ingredients as shown in the picture and mixed them without asking .
I ordered Power spinach and no apples ,no feta cheese , very small avocado…
It’s not acceptable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Evan Strain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2fqOdAnhxaiemFQS4XyDFhbiKrZRy07FxpcL2GXjAWO1I4RSA1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love coming here for healthy and delicious food options.

This chopped leaf I probably go to the most, the place is clean and looks pretty cool. The staff are super friendly and the food they make is fantastic. I would recommend my favourite thing but the Sunshine, Caesar, (wrap or salad) and quesadillas are all top choices of mine.

This specific chopped leaf is also very generous and active in the community. They have donated food to a local park event that happens every summer called Summer Fun @ The Park.

The washrooms are clean, the prices are good for what you’re getting and you can order your food online for pick up.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN5AXXjupzfdihrvw3ZEClANLnENxLmCAVafA5C&fid=0x0:0x1454995701ca095e"],"When":"2018-9-9"}]

[{"Name":"Vanika Vanika","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWi-xsR_M07Zdm4atI_oW8JYZDaYaRBghyEWsVUcQkN2g6ZAAI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered through doordash. For noodles, ingredients said - bell pepper, broccoli and cilantro. While placing the order, I made a request to remove broccoli and cilantro and add onions instead. Also to make it spicy. But all I received is stale noodles with just bell peppers. Where are the onions? No spices either. They shouldn’t have accepted the order if they were not comfortable adding onions. Or could have given me a call to ask for extra charges if that was a case. Dumping the noodles as such. Waste of my money and time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN4zgdLxolGZH-YnA1ttZKlzHt33cnuwxAwKezk&fid=0x0:0x558e4548dfee9769"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"Kamal Deep","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISsNx8-BOMzVsNID4P8cWoYB3mnthbkgojc38Yc4VDZw1gQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Today, I visited the store and ordered two channa samosa and found hair in my food.
I asked the lady for solution and she asked that I can only get same order again but here the thing is if they can’t make my first order with proper food safe measures then how can I trust them for my second order
She say that they can’t do anything after this I asked her 50% refund still they refuse
Also they didn’t wear a proper hair net just using normal cloth covering head but still their hair was showing up
So, I wanna recommend people not to visit there if you are conscious about your health","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Omesh Parkash","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhudgZBx87532WPIacVdXCMhOug70inEjzbyWcrgLC71XRm_ZK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This Store provides with various delicious food items and its fully Indian touch. Me and my wife love their Kulcha, Burger and Noodles. Taste is awesome. Good customer service, polite behaviour and reasonable pricing.

Recommend everyone to visit and taste their food items.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuE0Av4ECpjouVeYHXzFpyx5Sv0BDBcOzc3-ku&fid=0x0:0x558e4548dfee9769"],"When":"2022-2-27"},{"Name":"lovepreet kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKL-gCSXPqgf75q0g5x11ATBXnVD7QKP2G3Ln0KIJ50s2Vv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The worst place to visit yesterday i visit tat reastaurant and ordered some food and there is one hair in it
Satff didn’t follow proper guidelines and didn’t wear hair net
Overall serivice was not goo","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ashish sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL15EUvpvpbYdiwkRSUNgiSuMNzQ2WPWqojpoRzGC6J_slcWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Misleading Prices and Dishonest Practices – Avoid This Place!

I went to this shop specifically for their advertised $3.99 Paneer Burger deal. I called ahead and ordered two paneer burgers, as that’s the only one on their menu. However, when I arrived to pick up my order, they charged me full price, claiming that the burgers I ordered were different from the $3.99 deal. To make it worse, the “different” burger they mentioned isn’t even on their menu! This felt like an outright scam to lure customers in with a deal, then charge more when it’s time to pay.

This kind of dishonest bait-and-switch tactic is extremely unprofessional and disappointing. I won’t be returning here and wouldn’t recommend this place to anyone. Stay away if you value honesty in your transactions!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Winnie Yu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvghP3098IkIAe4kkjFWSk_6u2OsZ74hqmPaAghKEI06X6JQo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love the food and everything about it.  Personal favourite is Kings Wrap! You get your money's worth! Foods are at a very decent price, allowing us to purchase multiple without breaking our wallet. If you are looking for comfort food on  Friday evening, or if you are tired of cooking and want something quick, reasonable price, and delicious.  This is the place to go! We come here almost on a weekly basis, sometimes twice a week. Yes, it's THAT good!!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTo_DrRmmjulVt07GZ9hPkwXTBNGCvirErzmSb&fid=0x0:0x558e4548dfee9769"],"When":"2022-6-4"},{"Name":"Ikram Abdullahi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDmvQYDvJi9X4DB4U3orgGun_aKfyiZyh1OnfGJBaN3dPBUjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Decided to try something new and got their aloo tikki. Disappointed would be an understatement because I could even take more than one bite. I’ve had aloo tikki before but never like this. The description is very inaccurate and it’s doesn’t taste good at all. So sad that my money went to waste and that I waited so long for something that doesn’t even taste good but definitely will not be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vivek Bhatia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEJfc3bFfutRnZtX2BKo2u5q_AftdVmBbIYHpYLbT_8q8t6ddT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Food here is the worst I ever had. Disappointed taste. Bad experience. Waste of money. Never coming back.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"D SAM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAPZJhKwbwofRMAxzu-Q9mFomEMmhsUcyi8-_CMghvFMl0UXMbEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ordered Tofu Pancit for take out which was not on the menu. They happily accommodated. I enjoyed it very much. The aroma of garlic was really strong if you are fond of it. I would’ve much preferred it though if there were more vegetables like broccoli, snap peas, mushrooms among others not just carrots and celery. Food always cooked fresh. The staff are friendly in person and over the phone.

Came at another time and ordered sisig and chopsuey . Food was freshly cooked.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7T1-eLpsT2XiZlp4f7nGzDqJM2Ve7pmvwePnN&fid=0x0:0x82b70a1f6fc39e88"],"When":"2023-11-27"},{"Name":"Rnie Javier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWHBJV1K3x0Py3tvNiDVtisKTRGCoVAv4fDYdGg2N10daP8wS2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"If you like Filipino food and would like a restaurant that is not ‘turo-turo’ style then this is a good place to come try. The menu has a lot of different options to choose from. The sinigang and pork bbq are generally my favourite Filipino food and the flavours are on point with how they should taste. However, I wouldn’t say anything is pulling me to come back. Also, the service is not very attentive.. they do not come and check in on you at all. If you need something you have to go up to the counter to get their attention. Overall, this is an authentic Filipino restaurant that I would recommend to others if try if they never had our cuisine and don’t already have a Filipino friend to feed them this food at their home ;)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwKAv-tRF0HQOZQudhcFOOdGFNKWzp7sSo6jEN&fid=0x0:0x82b70a1f6fc39e88"],"When":"2022-7-18"},{"Name":"Rupert Cruz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXt8ml-zyELcJn5n7mbMObX0OVwwAVyqI04N4IqTyH4TJ2dVGE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I will be as fair as I can. We dined-in 6pm Sunday evening as we are in a habit of supporting family owned restaurants in our city. There were only another couple at the restaurant who are almost done and are about to leave. So in short, my wife and I are the only customers in the restaurant at that moment. We are courteously given 2 glasses of water together with the menu... would be better if it was followed by a nice "hello/good evening" gesture. They are not rude, but not pleasant either.

We are starving and ready to order. Unfortunately, we have to catch their attention to let them know we are ready. The servings came in not long after. Food is okay but the portions you get for what you pay is not acceptable. Expensive to say the least. Isang platitong inihaw na liempo costs us $18.75, Pancit Canton for $16.50 (good for 1 person).

At this point we are THE ONLY CUSTOMER inside the restaurant, yet our glasses of water wasn't re-filled and not one crew passed by to check on us if everything's okay.

When we were done and ready to pay, we are waiting if they would at least take a glance on us. I guess we can just storm out and they wouldn't even notice. I finally just called their attention and paid my bill shortly. Again, WE ARE THE ONLY CUSTOMER PRESENT THAT TIME.

Food portions and service really need to improve. I dont mind paying a premium so long as it is worth it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdKx2wqThbm5z88AO5ox9A8V-Q99z5LeTdzq3y&fid=0x0:0x82b70a1f6fc39e88"],"When":"2023-10-23"},{"Name":"Cheska Ferolino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiXbF7Xn7d5rwIp_rXgYIbDlVgBfLQEe-Wkodr7Do6Mr3l80Jq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered sisig with pork bbq thru doordash today . Everything taste so good until i felt something was sharp and lucky didnt swallow it .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNputaqr9uqlll7PZ4Caxkx2NDncfBganc2-Fvy&fid=0x0:0x82b70a1f6fc39e88"],"When":"2024-5-12"},{"Name":"Liane Villarin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJb99wshYftg9gkbUpPO4Xfy9DjJeZ0hQzGJpXD8gNW0Phq_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We just had our family dinner here tonight and we are the only customer at the moment. Unfortunately, the food is not good as before. The red flag is when we order the whole egg pie for our dessert, and when we're starting to slice it to put it into small plates, we noticed MOLDS on the top of the egg pie. Like it was from their display fridge with lots of food inside. Was thinking, isn't all the food in there is contaminated? Nasty. Horrible. Unacceptable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Desiree Gache","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMZ4KiKCrQ5mJQ089Xq8HgurbxXWSxUZe08xGwBK16BUbL5EpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I usually order for takeout from here and my favourites are the lumpia and dinuguan, a little pricey but the food is so good it’s worth it. They also have a big variety of different dishes which I like so I would definitely recommend","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cristina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoN4uAgedw6IPp-TuJoYuwBVPII_f6vTjOwYXgMMvIHnobRtM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We dine in here last sunday and about to order the server gave us the menu with a paper and pencil and told us to write down our order. No eye contact with customers if we need something we have to stand and go to the front and ask them. Food is ok nothing special. The Richmond location is better than here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maxxie Espiritu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7Shst6JzjmLm6iM_c1vcFzXQtk1wIK_Uz4u4sm-151ZyR7w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We bought pancit palabok small party tray cost of $65. We send back the palabok because you can taste the used oil,dry and bitter after taste. We ask them to taste it and as per the cook he said it’s fine.We requested for refund or atleast half of the price but they said it was already half and I said yes it was because it was thrown on the garbage when we try to eat .According to the staff still under review by the owner to decide for the refund and they will call us back still nothing. They have new cook now no wonder their foods taste different. I don’t recommend this restaurant.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Thanks for a delicious and easy dinner Pita Pit!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bim S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZCEq-tjjAo_wFnCNX4kq5apTkVAiAoWVMqTwK5JG2VPcaBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came in yesterday after so long. I especially like the loaded fries with chicken!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNEFKZjfZoiPN7x1b0X4_ZiQWKDcjxXQ7BzJLp7&fid=0x0:0xe37b370126f705c9"],"When":"2021-7-27"},{"Name":"Vijay Riar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPd9po4cB1CJ3ept2LkvkCmEk03wyrzAdGKYNXmkToSW4WHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve tried pretty much every Pizza place in Surrey/ North Delta and this one is by far the best.

The entire experience from placing the order , picking up the pizza and then finally sitting at home and enjoying  it, was absolutely exceptional.

I strongly recommend trying it if you are a fan of real ol school pies. I ordered a small house special and could only finish half and trust me, I can eat!

Great Pizza, great customer service and very fairly priced.

All boxes checked.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Masuma Mehri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLw9qMlBP7sweufBcFidbM2cK8cQCePWNlkTXptFtsoqzXGJg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pizza was amazing! But the fries were pretty dry and the Cheese wasnt much or melted. Pretty cold.. Said 30 min till pickup and I live 2 min away, picked up and fries not what I expected. But over all pizza was 🔥 highly recommend. Hoping next time itll be different. Also friendly advice when answering the phone, itd be more professional and kind to say, "Hi, how can we help you?" loll it just felt like (the person that answered) didn't really care. But ill be back for the pizza ✌🏻","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jasmin Gill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5SGNnU2xs7KApiWC0KGMdZIhVf0UrF6rYRgTgyWlxfitdVA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a relatively new place that just opened up and I was a little hesitant to try the pizza, but it was amazing! Definitely my go-to for pizza from now on and I'll for sure be trying the indian food on their menu as well!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gurleen Sandhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5cSOy3CVZ-kx8Ftkj0XkAXWH9_gxBwReZDF8R5s989R-rxA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have tried various different foods and it has all been amazing, especially the chicken pakora and loaded fries! The pizza is also amazing and all their food is definitely worth trying!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harman Sandhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL0yJeEbJufuvgUBTVqlVih5r4H8HmjifJ8qF0jAcwTHy7uXw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Zaika houses food is honestly just amazing and the customer service there is excellent. This restaurant is a must try!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ruby Tiwana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlqpFQQvlDC04fhVtQRNkFXT09OA1Hj1AsJK0_pGoTPNeEUw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love mogo fries! And i havent been able to find a place in surrey/delta that has them so when i heard about this place i was very excited! We will be returning.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sunil Khatri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIM5WABMoknsFnpGC-_ar5zGjM6Vtuvzy_OjEHga5OYoZfgno4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you are looking for amazing Pizza in Delta, look no further and try Zaika Pizza House. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Myra El Masraya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeJJxwenHWklXoTEl9q8Yi096pDR_ziSwJ6U00VvkKFXeK12yb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food here is so delicious and has a big portion. The servers are very friendly and they helped us take some pictures of our party as we were celebrating our girlfriend's birthday. We also had a room for us to have our party there. The restaurant is very clean and we use the same restaurant for all our birthday celebration parties. They also would play the birthday music and they bring a special dessert for the person who is celebrating her birthday. We just love it there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOLw0rLUAz7kYu-QxFV0I3gjnLEzdUnNaawuBf&fid=0x0:0xf69be2afe19b00bb"],"When":"2021-1-5"},{"Name":"Jay Why","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf6qVrRB2FWSP3f_QpdYqgSMlmFo0fYvO9JkGkahstgPZxGBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First and foremost, the service was great. I recognized the lady that served us from the last time we where here and that was almost 5 years ago. I know that management have changed and I am glad they kept most of their staff. She made it a point to go around to all the tables and took the time to actually talk to everyone. Most restaurants nowadays you'll never see the waitress again once they have taken your order.
The food, on the other hand was a bit of a let down. The ribs were dry and bland, and the lamb was inconsistence. Some pieces were perfectly cooked while other were overcooked and very tough.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDpHR1MYaiZvxmDnpuGKDA6aV8o66oSLN6hDrG&fid=0x0:0xf69be2afe19b00bb"],"When":"2022-12-12"},{"Name":"Kyle S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAHrv12m1CC3kTdgJJdn2Ti6FOCLWHmeg0867bmV2m8DUkHyHW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very good portions food is full of flavors, very fresh and delicious. The saganaki is amazing. Very big open restaurant. Super friendly service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8H0TsgWgT9Gb-Y6IVgPuDAgKzR-n_t12QJs22&fid=0x0:0xf69be2afe19b00bb"],"When":"2023-9-27"},{"Name":"Ebo M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJkGD-0dNKN-6VRV0xdkoDDzwv5oQSqe3xuMLUK2URhYLKK4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I came to this restaurant years ago and I had such an amazing experience. The food was absolutely delicious. Coming here today the atmosphere and the service was  very good. The food on the other hand was  good but I felt like My roast lamb souvlaki  was missing something(I still ate all of it though lol). The staff is very friendly. The pricing is no different than any other Greek food restaurant and portions are generous. My son enjoyed his chicken souvlaki, I thought my Roast lamb souvlaki was ok, I definitely will be coming back here to try more dishes though .

Thanks,","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOb_pyQUTxwzDpGz8zfdn7RoXSO_-8_FdlAPWQL&fid=0x0:0xf69be2afe19b00bb"],"When":"2023-12-10"},{"Name":"Rehana Ali","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKGe30Vbwwr1MgfFIcOA2wcccIVe7cC1kRrdz_ir2zhbDVyo6WWw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"After reading everyone's reviews I decided to go and check it out. It was my birthday dinner that my friends and I went to.
Just as we arrived the waitress brought us in to our table. It took them 15mins to bring us menu's and water. I had asked one of the waitress can someone help us and she abruptly said u just have to wait.
I was not happy at all!!
Finally when the waitress did come she did not very happy. We finally ordered drinks and appetizers.
There pop is horrible it is watered down.
Ur better off with water. We had to complain about that again our waitress seemed irraterd. Finally our appetizers arrived the chicken wings we're very salty and the cheese had a weird taste. Only thing was that the Calamari was decent.
At this point I am not happy with the food and the horrible service that we we're getting.
We all finally got our main courses that was decent.
I eat at alot of restaurants and put in reviews.
This is one restaurant that I don't recommend.
They need better customer service and the price they charge for food and drinks should be better then what we got.

My girlfriend had to ask the waitress if you do anything for birthdays and she was rude about it and said no we don't but I will bring u something this time.

I would like the owner of the business to contact me at there earliest convenience so we can discuss this further.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFkqvjFow9mD10ajtILzC0ROKVmvTWcndu6RJj&fid=0x0:0xf69be2afe19b00bb"],"When":"2021-3-16"},{"Name":"Hemanjot Grewal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWim9Hu81iRvZGkfkh7wJuu43nsSaASxaHoEIOlrgfrtzj-7ao=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love their chicken souvlaki and the dip woth it. O my god and there rice😃❤️. One of my best decisions","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPx-4X0nZ1vjgRfmCeDIXpOHIFPugopZVY3kds7&fid=0x0:0xf69be2afe19b00bb"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"D SAM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAPZJhKwbwofRMAxzu-Q9mFomEMmhsUcyi8-_CMghvFMl0UXMbEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I love this place. [{"Name":"Raviendra Madugalle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4uSti5RtYJISGgBTK64N3UvnE0RQMNNyvHQyHnJXUNKlh6o9k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried a flavourful Indian Thali. Packed with Indian spices. Great variety of selections to choose from the menu. The staff is very nice and pleasant. We were recommended here by a friend. And we greatly enjoyed our dining experience.

Highly recommended !!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqHl3ucILf94pdv3W5gl4jfShEnYbjEh9ziuHO&fid=0x0:0x5a590360d726859a"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Shahan Taneja","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKmIBYY2kL3VGe-r_FhrX08WYXS5iI0zJsrAH5UGxV9oFRQnsec=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was good and personal favourite is veg thali. I also like dosa and coffee here. The portion size is good. Service is also nice. The decor is very soothing with good vibes. It’s worth a try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_SDATgvNEZR2q4POIme1W6JQuaOEAyx2r5fBN&fid=0x0:0x5a590360d726859a"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Abdul Ali","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6A-2UkJSQuzxRI3b5SiNokbRUgJ6lOWebAPsInCI4BZY1eRdJaA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A hidden restaurant in Delta, BC. Absolutely delicious Masala Dosa and Fish Thali. Affordable  , Large Portion and mouth watering delicious.

Also we ate at there another location at Henderson Center Mall in Coquitlam.  Was delicious food there too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2Bsi4hyjgVkVAsM72BSIkrJYHKkV1yS_i4nEi&fid=0x0:0x5a590360d726859a"],"When":"2024-7-22"},{"Name":"AWAIS THE BOSS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFR2cYPf0wPxYiA1s-uSEkyon-hcTMvm8LJq6BY3cw9K_NYCzp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Desi Dosa Madras is a delightful culinary gem that brings the authentic flavors of South India right to your plate. From the moment you step in, you are greeted with a warm and inviting ambiance, coupled with the tantalizing aroma of freshly prepared dosas. The menu offers a wide range of options, from classic masala dosas to innovative fusion varieties that cater to every palate.

The dosas are perfectly crisp on the outside and soft on the inside, complemented by a variety of flavorful chutneys and a piping hot bowl of sambar. The freshness of the ingredients is evident in every bite, making the meal not just delicious but also wholesome. The standout for me was the Mysore Masala Dosa, which had the perfect balance of spice and flavor.

The service at Desi Dosa Madras is exceptional, with friendly staff who are attentive and knowledgeable about the menu. They go above and beyond to ensure a pleasant dining experience.

Whether you’re a fan of South Indian cuisine or a first-timer exploring it, Desi Dosa Madras is a must-visit. The combination of authentic flavors, excellent service, and reasonable prices makes it a standout spot for anyone craving a taste of India. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTPrra21pRW_5YVMyI08rgnSby-SvdPSwwMhTb&fid=0x0:0x5a590360d726859a"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Jasmine Jasmine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIAMYJt7r_I9uLzj_L5_Ayv1BM6ZSUnB0izETrjD06CDNEyww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Terrible food, staff and seating. When you enter this place they wouldn’t care about seating you to a place suited for your group size. We ended up changing our seats 4 times cause our group was not satisfied. The seats were either too tight to comfortably sit at, or literally outside the washroom. The food served was cold and tasteless, one of our items was undercooked and almost tasted like old food. We were brought the wrong order twice and our beverages were forgotten about. Finally when we just wanted out of that place we were charged for the food we had sent back. Instead of feeling sorry for us and giving us any alternatives, we were handed a bill of 50$, for the food we barely ate! We had to book another place close by, to eat our dinner. There was a time when this place was good and food was worth while but not anymore I guess.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gurjot Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8a-bEYf2tOjO3X0uunG1i72NDQmDvedMGhMYubzV2uJfhiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"They are good. But now they are decreasing the quality of food and increasing prices. I got fully burnt dosa.
My last experience was not good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-WjoFDvvI6iYyQXHYKdLX6UfC8N6yA537iPuU&fid=0x0:0x5a590360d726859a"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Justbeing Sam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWM9hiJK-AfVP-qSHlK2ogC-KKU9aHv9jB-f8Zpy8fNkox9PG5e=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Went to this place after long time with family. We had great time delicious food. We ordered masala dosa platter and fish curry thali and veg noodles. Food was really yummy no complaints there. However, when we asked for extra sambar and sauces ( 1 time extra) we were charged for it as sambar quantity was less and 1 extra should be given as courtesy and 2nd time shuld be charged. Prices are genuine but paying extra for sauces n sambar hurted.

Update: Went there again had a great time but food and customer service quality has been decreased","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOSUCEzYT2thWnrLiWyNSfqhjz2CYD9aSQAm_09&fid=0x0:0x5a590360d726859a"],"When":"2023-2-16"},{"Name":"Manik Passi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVH_gfcPHOChMCHRzzmQffU138Sko8LLUzb68J8nqVpFeIuoVHb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Today we again went there. Last time my gf put a review about the soup and today when we order soup again there they saw us and get offended and the staff was really rude. Today they make the soup full of water intentionally. I think they dont want us to come back because we put a review. Here are the pictures of the soup full of water and it was tasteless. Really unprofessional thing. They just want to take a revenge. Very very disappointed and we waste our money here. The sad thing was that we came here every three to four times a week but now not at all. We would be happy if the owner of the restaurant saw this review and taught their staff to behave themselves.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNU6ZiE78LJ1u4McKemEddCbhwt8uu7JGencL3i&fid=0x0:0x5a590360d726859a"],"When":"2022-9-26"}]

I’ll definitely be coming back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuG489ecVLLOuJva8shLFRgWdqjxURjpA3xaK8&fid=0x0:0x7d819c908ae2141e"],"When":"2024-10-12"},{"Name":"Cindy Rose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXh0Mb2aZNKSbCg3ecIqP5jBLg_O2xXbsUeepw6K_Oegut6R9ZuHA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"2024-July.

We were here before noon and got seated right away.

Service was fast. The food was delicious. The servers were nice and polite. The price is good!

Authentic Filipino breakfast!

You should try it!

Bon Appétit 😋","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNz0R9cjeJ-JvE_TKhc3IFT4bE4RTDHhRQtHnVg&fid=0x0:0x7d819c908ae2141e"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Mark Ranges","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqC34bwyQmEaCqU17TT41PfEGWaSmPBBGc9HbxiPptGekAAg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We’ve been coming here for years, and every time we leave, we’re stuffed and satisfied. The food is fantastic—I’m always ordering the tapa and wings. Prices are super affordable, and it’s my top spot for authentic Filipino silog meals. Highly recommend, 10/10!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLRXV2TTxpSN_e8G5bkF3zMJY_1t0_9djZyJXk&fid=0x0:0x7d819c908ae2141e"],"When":"2024-10-28"},{"Name":"Sarah Love","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW10_PKOS624ix13nj8YKTo4TAQBtxqwAyn-GvxxaJgFFQ6c7ib5A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of our favorite place!!

We recently came by to bring my sister and my niece who is visiting in town. EpicSilog is me and my husband go-to for Authentic Filipino food in BC so my family must try it during their visit. The owner was really nice and approchable, we get to chitchat to found out that she and her family was from Winnipeg, MB as well. It was so nice seeing fellow Winnipegers. She gave us a sample of her Mango Mousse. She was thinking of adding it to their already delish menu list and ask us to send her a feedback. I wanted to send her my input on it but I didnt get her contact. Hopefully this will able to reach her? The Mango was so fresh and big chunks was a real bonus, which I am sure people will appreciate because I certainly did! The cake layer was soft and not dry at all, and the buttercream/ganache/creamcheese, not sure what the cream was made of, super delish! I found myself kept on scooping until its was just the empty cup left. It was not too sweet nor bland. A perfect taste of a great dessert. I see myself ordering this type of mouse if she ever decided to make one for orders 😍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWFKsf8e7lAG8Ff8Vlfc1yrXXCejM69mcAmfO8&fid=0x0:0x7d819c908ae2141e"],"When":"2024-7-3"},{"Name":"Tearna Salvesen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_A5qweBOzpqxR3-rNhjGapVyg_fFMEktwqcm_lRq1vNUpevSGfA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Epic Grill Silogs was highly recommended from my friend in Texas so when we came to Vancouver we had to try it! We were not disappointed. We were greeted with the warmest welcome and felt like part of the family as soon as we entered. It was our first time trying Filipino food and it was delicious! They helped us know what was on the menu and what  we’d like when we ordered. We came with our 2 sons 5 & 2 & they were so kind towards them. Thank you Epic for such an amazing experience we will be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOK6CqPdP45c4fvLVwJ5Db8YnOUoHLjpIzWs9w5&fid=0x0:0x7d819c908ae2141e"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Lois Currie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxx2Cy3OtPnIV7ATZ8jN12pCE5duu7FrrOsh2g0unMKYijMl7F=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Called to have a bite before the long drive back to Abbotsford. [{"Name":"Munro Stuff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj0Wcuk6ox5dfAeJ4fAaMbhX_F-nzzt3p5oc_f0hBd0NpbGSM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Samosas were a good size and pretty tasty, but on the greasy side. Dipping sauce was just okay. Service wasn't very friendly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOx4e3fy4Wbwuc_R2AVFxKnOc4xOJbVkVJGJHZA&fid=0x0:0xeb80e44cf0ad9cde"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Karan Verma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWihmhxBivvzIZnhihtWNCltuvgnwqnp8QHTn_L10JQlGd3LQbhA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The overall experience at this restaurant has consistently exceeded our expectations. We have become frequent visitors due to the consistently exceptional quality of the food. Each time we dine here, we are met with flavors that are both bold and satisfying. The dishes are expertly prepared, showcasing the chef's skill and attention to detail.

One aspect that stands out is the remarkable speed at which our orders are served. It's impressive how quickly the food arrives at our table without compromising its quality. This efficient service adds to the overall enjoyment of the dining experience.

Furthermore, the staff at this restaurant deserves commendation for their attentive and friendly service. From the moment we step through the door, we are warmly welcomed and made to feel like valued guests. Their knowledge of the menu and willingness to accommodate any special requests further enhance our dining experience.

In terms of affordability, this restaurant truly stands out. The prices are more than reasonable considering the outstanding quality of the food and the level of service provided. It's refreshing to find such a combination of excellence and affordability in one place.

Apart from the savory dishes, we have also explored the sweet side of the menu, and we were not disappointed. The desserts offered are a testament to the culinary skill present in this establishment. Whether it's a delectable cake or a mouthwatering pastry, each bite is a delight to the taste buds.

In summary, this restaurant has consistently impressed us with its exceptional food, speedy service, friendly staff, and reasonable prices. It has become our go-to place for a satisfying meal, and we highly recommend it to anyone looking for a memorable dining experience. Whether you're craving savory delights or indulgent desserts, this restaurant is sure to leave you thoroughly satisfied.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1k6_nBE3ii_KwfumUVZ3ovO0cIkDhyrY6qdvX&fid=0x0:0xeb80e44cf0ad9cde"],"When":"2023-5-15"},{"Name":"Emily Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5bA-Xs_JlP7CP18cRm7Tdhg7AlD6yMRzCOimrSNOFT2zx4A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Diamond sweets has become one of my all-time favourites. Every time we order the food is absolutely delicious and the left overs are just as good! Definitely one of my go to comfort foods and will be a customer for many years to come!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAiC3_QBi5QSvfnTdexqetfNLxCtRkv-2LNaS4&fid=0x0:0xeb80e44cf0ad9cde"],"When":"2023-8-23"},{"Name":"Lorraine Clement","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKN2aaC3dpWM1PjjhRmZ0XmNC-R_fOAMbas1Bej8qGsLb5aCg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Bought 12 pieces Samosas take out, 8 chicken samosas and 4 veggies samosas.
For 12 samosas they only give 2 small tamarind sauce. I asked for another one but apparently I have to pay for it.

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Praneet Raj","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-I5iB9QpG5eztISNYObvNJI9swIkyqnUB25NJVMbN3zDz8_-1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered grilled chicken burgers from this McDonald’s location in Delta, BC, and the experience was satisfying. The restaurant was clean and well-maintained, which added to the overall positive impression. The service was quick and efficient, with my order being prepared in a timely manner. The staff were courteous, and everything seemed to be running smoothly despite a busy environment. The grilled chicken burgers were great , meeting my expectations for a quick and tasty meal. If you’re looking for fast service and a clean spot in the area, this McDonald’s is definitely worth a stop.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIZTTJ8zDeP-klDe-YsViJIdk45VaduhBMF2TV&fid=0x0:0x6cfb50410b1b5274"],"When":"2024-10-10"},{"Name":"Rocky johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-qbKTqm7jXjeR4bNESCYCbiBB0D1S1kiuff4Q-7RrKgiVG--a=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Stepping into this McDonald’s location, I expected the familiar consistency the Golden Arches is known for. Unfortunately, what I encountered was a far cry from the brand's usual standards. The food was presented in a haphazard manner—burgers seemingly assembled in a rush, with cheese sliding off the bun like an afterthought. To make matters worse, the burger buns were stale around the edges, further diminishing the overall experience.

The dining area itself was no better. Tables were visibly dirty and had not been cleaned in some time, with trash scattered around. To my shock, some individuals were even laying on the floors, creating a chaotic and uninviting atmosphere for guests.

What truly baffled me, however, was learning that this location does not honor complimentary drink refills for dine-in customers—a staple of the McDonald’s experience. It seems this franchise has chosen to deviate from the brand's norms and impose its own rules, leaving customers frustrated.

Adding insult to injury, the manager’s demeanor was outright rude when I inquired about the refill policy. Rather than addressing the concern with understanding, their dismissive attitude left a bitter taste far worse than the stale bun. I’ll be contacting corporate to seek clarity on whether this practice and approach are acceptable.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMFN7h8Qm4g5lUgQvMk6XF4G8xQaSTeyNCWYc5u&fid=0x0:0x6cfb50410b1b5274"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"Adarsh Sivaprasad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4wLIi14ujjNuOiI0zrnXjP7vBI45ELITWJKrDSR6Rnzad9GvH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Dear McDonald's Customer Service Team,

I am writing to formally express my dissatisfaction with the service I received at one of your locations. On [insert date], I placed an order that included four items, one of which was a box of chicken nuggets. However, upon receiving my order, I noticed that the chicken nuggets were missing. I immediately contacted the store to resolve the issue, but the response I received was far from satisfactory.

Firstly, when I called to report the missing item, the person on the phone provided a service that I found to be unprofessional. Not only was the resolution unclear, but the individual did not communicate the order code audibly, making the situation more frustrating.

When I visited the store in person to show my receipt and explain the situation, the staff did not even take the time to properly listen to my concern. Instead, they reacted by criticizing me and were unwilling to address the issue. I expected better from a global brand like McDonald’s, especially in terms of customer service and professionalism.

While the missing item was valued at only $8, it is not the amount but the principle of customer satisfaction and trust that is at stake. I believe that paying for an item and not receiving it constitutes a breach of trust, and the unprofessional handling of this issue only compounded my disappointment.

I kindly request that this matter be looked into and resolved appropriately. I would appreciate a refund for the missing item and any necessary action taken to ensure that this type of experience is not repeated for other customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvNiaHAP01J5-MTpzLi8PhWRxwcLKXsq4qKJsI&fid=0x0:0x6cfb50410b1b5274"],"When":"2024-10-18"},{"Name":"amita Morker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvsZ5qFZb-WRJWkXiKEOAHm9ZqJPpaPiYkMLb4GWEfgDE0Wg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Rude service. Poorly made food. Sauce was not even on the inside of the burger. It's was wrapped around the outside on the bun. I've had multiple issues here. Poutine had cold cheese and gravy. Service was rude. I would not recommend. When I spoke to in charge Harman she did nothing to relieve the situation. Do not go here!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNLcKui0XSm1tRZXuZgbHK5oYa9qSkzKqXKGHVY&fid=0x0:0x6cfb50410b1b5274"],"When":"2024-10-30"},{"Name":"Arjun Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8dzV51dWSvVh_Ew_XKNhFvmXHtngegIoXGetdts7J77ZmTXL4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food part of the place is as usual McDonald's.

On a Wednesday night , I assume all weeknights, around 8-9pm, the drive through took us around 15 or so minutes for 3 snack wraps.

Unless you are in a hurry, I would suggest check if there is a huge queue in front of you when you order.

Otherwise, 4/5 fast food!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Guru Simran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVr0Pfr0xhcbOc2MhI8o0MpcBcHoJteCIa8Cg6tL6YVXRlE7n-i=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst experience here with food and staff. I ordered from kiosk and waited at front counter to tell them make my food fresh but nobody came to ask but a crew member came with my order and i asked if you can make it fresh she rolled her eyes. Later i got fresh food but there’s a hair in my fries. Terrible experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNLhIuRC-hKmrTV3Fk671W-ZzXpBq27RioZ5Xzn&fid=0x0:0x6cfb50410b1b5274"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"Thalia Ventura","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJXUOu_8ijUKMnUaIyiXsE6ykR-VzoroTcEZ_LWdv7Ns6NvEw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst experience of my life . You  need a new sales manager as she will be the reason why you will not have customers returning as there are others around .
First of all coming to the window she did not ask for the McDonald code and when I brought it up to the window she pulled the machine back,ignored me  and took someone else’s order. What kind of service is this??
Then we ask for water and she is very rude about the cup situation. We understand the lack of cups but when I asked for 3 twice and she didn’t make any eye contact or give any indication that she heard me then turn around with attitude about us asking
PLEASE SEE PHOTOS after this mess she repeats the order and we agree then get handed this . What am I paying for ? RIP OFF, NO CARE FOR CUSTOMERS AND WANT YOU TO JUST LEAVE .

[{"Name":"Malwinder Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKtE4fV2M3fW6sJO18IdMP1Kn5pLF-EIwqQO41wFYUP78bLlni=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I went to this joint and ordered two slices of cheese pizza for my son and ordered 7 Gluten Free Chicken Bites.

Firstly, The girl served me burnt pizza slices, I attached the pictures for your reference. My son tried to eat it, but wasn't able to hence he left it as it is. I wondered why and tried a bite of the pizza myself, and it was so disgusting in taste as well.

Second, She also burnt the chicken bites as well, But they were edible, hence won't say much about them.

I would not recommend this joint to anyone.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbKs67rohqc7TeiLpWWbjNgDzykGw9DsGisdpZ&fid=0x0:0x27a0922ad2719de6"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Sukhdeep Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLE-jpLAO17PHNZkFTSaqeG6xpL9k6TGDvXdtXXQoJNs1BWtg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a great experience, i ordered tandoori chicken pizza that,s such a great taste i like from moths. A person on front  iqubal singh dealing with respect.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP40zygbCKITNaYGV6MqWmfJJPnd3g3LN1nBzEz&fid=0x0:0x27a0922ad2719de6"],"When":"2024-7-25"},{"Name":"Charlie Kirk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_7DXLDAAxjcXzwJL5VQRE9dO69UsXuzkjkwo2Zgn6CBemRA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I order the same pizza every week after I play hockey at  midnight in delta. Drive home to Langley and me and my wife each ate a piece and the dough was all raw in the middle. I could’ve rolled it out and made a new pizza. We were busy with the kids the following day so I waited till the next day to call. Customer service said they would give me no refund or credit because I didn’t call same day at 1am? There is also no way to get in touch with the store itself that I could find without going there in person.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO6AQ9tL3GprA-ONtYwZ36e-9LEBPfpZewCYeVa&fid=0x0:0x27a0922ad2719de6"],"When":"2024-2-26"},{"Name":"Arsh Sall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKoXJksDHASduh0qCN4c4TUh-woJeBoHMqJRNqmysgY2hWBlg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I visited their Guildford location for Panwar Pizza, but the paneer was out of stock. So, I specifically went to this location and ordered the pizza, requesting it to be made slightly spicy. However, when I ate the pizza, it was extremely spicy—so much so that I couldn’t even eat it. It was very disappointing, and the staff didn’t seem to care when I complained.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cory Philip","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLefITYIG5ehOvaeYlNpUJ5cxHy48e4ogF4jNkMkk76c0dsg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The pizza is 8/10 good.
The pickup special Medium 1 topping for $9.49 is what I get most times. Half pepperoni Half Bacon.
The Air-conditioning works which is nice and there are a couple places to sit.
I live close by so I go often.
The staff are nice.
The owner Inder is nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTolUFgBFGEGcNYOuHMSOJHjreQpZnKMHxZBIv&fid=0x0:0x27a0922ad2719de6"],"When":"2023-8-26"},{"Name":"Updesh Rampal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYtwhhBEPXJDvv8N-weMS5cILTgWwuem_uDha2Af0Z4KRqs6Gn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went there Oct 27 night best customer service i ever received from a pizza store. And everything was really warm and fresh. Looking forward to visit again and again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harinder Gill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8-X8tP0Uvwb8Jdpw_gx_d9EST4DIITdTEBKZ0x3cj9JXB9Q1y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have visited at their closing time, however they gave us very good dealing and the guy who works at night is super friendly and very professional, the food was also good","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Arman Singh Thind","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ9eYYh9ieSbOLcvurEs8JLqPzJdEXlNVmZA34XQ7y0zV6mxw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best pizzas I ever had in my life. [{"Name":"N T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL0fPxCzYwVmpF7ny4zyQgH9VNWZ2SsZVnPmKq-71dWftNbjg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Walked and the place was absolutely filthy. Only two people inside so can't say they were busy. 3 people working in the back. If the store front of this dirty, I can only imagine what it looks like in the back where people can't see. The people on cash are very polite, helpful, and kind. Will not be back for the sanitary reason.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNOWRT97cGfSo0q-Qu6tMgYvqy36ejtiEqd3oLz&fid=0x0:0x40dd67bb2681cd94"],"When":"2024-9-22"},{"Name":"Jack Nunes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2LYNLmRTbhdeRaRfSSWQfbXW4_0XyT8Wh3w4zVn7-_sIxtWs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered the Big Mary Spicy Combo with a Tatar Poutine.
The Poutine arrived with the lid left open and no cutlery to eat the Poutine. Because the lid was left open the Poutine arrived cold and dried out. I need to make my own gravy because evidently there wasn't enough put on the Poutine to begin with seeing as the cheese curds were not even melted. Horrible service and will not be ordering at this location again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRk6FXY5OO-ENK1DoOmcyzKZ65hVNI2_LYbbXy&fid=0x0:0x40dd67bb2681cd94"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Jay Adalaja","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFoPyCzUynl1AsPhbMBH-A2X8I_h-I-l64fQ5i1Zz08w0HliI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing Atmosphere and vive. The chicken was surprisingly very fresh and sumptuous, and their taters and sandwiches were also above the mark. Customer service was also commendable. Will definitely go there again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"skruee1","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUfWjO8H-_zZEsA5T1jjsMFdmesKtX-kQ-NvFatSyCzvHsBFJ6P=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I'm sorry but, we loved eating at this location till tonight.
Waited over 20 minutes for our food, and then when we asked to talk to someone about the wait...
There was no manager or anyone with any authority.
Not yelling , but just askng for some sort of compensation and the cashier started talking to the cooks  hindi or Punjabi, and they came to the pass, and both were glaring and trying to intimidate...
I don't understand how there is no accountability for for the way we were treated.
I'm sorry but we felt discriminated against....
Both my partner and I, work for companies that focus on diversity, and respect for everyone.
Diversity training needs to be implemented for employees  as everyone should adhere to those guidelines
Everyone","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hadia Aslam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgeHSioMdHCaRYjk1n1Avir3XC4yfHWHDdma9gkyDtzOmcmg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered 2 Sandwiches (one online through app and one in-person ) as there was an offer on the MB App Fried Chicken Sandwich day. I was asked to wait 15 minutes. I don't mind waiting as i believe one gets fresh food if the staff is taking time. However, To my surprise when i came home and opened up the bags, the chicken in the sandwich was super hard to chew, and super super cold. My house is just 5 minutes away so can't blame the distance. May be the burgers were pre made for those who avail the offer. I will never ever use these offers again that just waste your money and time. I feel nauseous as the hard chicken is just strucked in my throat. Not going again definitely.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yuji Stobbe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXR5Akk7izHKA3N-5_TikKoGlhcxqeNMIRk5wkM6_OWHPrO8YIw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I’ve been wanting to try Mary Browns for awhile. I heard they had good chicken. I got a free regular chicken sandwich for installing their app and I got a spicy two piece combo. The chicken sandwich was ok. Chicken was cooked well but lacked seasoning. The fries and macaroni salad were really good and the fried chicken was good with the spicy seasoning. I don’t think I would have enjoyed it without if I’m totally honest. All in all, a good experience, but I wouldn’t drive out of my way to go. If I’m in the area and craving some fried chicken, I’m sure I would stop in.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRWAE6S6_J7ZW3HWwwQaNbMTVnTBLpd-hoEHU7&fid=0x0:0x40dd67bb2681cd94"],"When":"2021-10-11"},{"Name":"Prakriti Kanathia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQHvJQXTkiNWwoL-Ali4rSgJJ9tz53i5kkpcShdgZy4P2cHDcizw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We ordered potato Taters as I don’t eat chicken but there was a piece of chicken in it. And then when we approached them and told them about the situation, their manager acted so casually as if nothing happened.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jay Why","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf6qVrRB2FWSP3f_QpdYqgSMlmFo0fYvO9JkGkahstgPZxGBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good chicken but kind of pricy. First time trying Mary Brown's and I must admit it was pretty good. The Taters was good and nicely seasoned, the chicken was tender and juicy, though I had the spicy one and it looks like they were just the regular chicken with hot pepper sprinkled on top. I ordered online and the order was ready as promised. The staff was polite and friendly. They are pretty expensive for what you are getting. My 9 piece combo was $35. At KFC, I can get a 12 piece with fries and 2 sides for $25 and at Popeye's, a 14 piece chicken, 2 large sides, and 7 biscuits is $39.99.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0Nh7OBE-eExeqrTrrRKDaPcDMFd1agibvb8L3&fid=0x0:0x40dd67bb2681cd94"],"When":"2021-9-25"}]

[{"Name":"Rishi Sandhey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKV7NSGFBgAbPp47OE3oqzvHlSp75VxqcFm5is_gHhqHxTCxw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I have been coming at this location since last 3 years. I came here at 6:45 on Saturday November 2, 2024. This cashier girl has no idea on how to give proper customer service. I tried my best to be polite and not to create a scene here. I could tell by the look at her face she didn’t want to work and was pissed off to see me and other customers too. Didn’t reply to me and started making face when i tried to ask for something. One suggestion, if you do not like your job please quit. A lot of people are looking for jobs. Food is good as usual and other girls did a great job. Cheers to them :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gagandeep Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXiOkW7-IzkR7241ngVsN6Gq-DJesJ_LKrhI1jI3GgL_r5tsq77g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Title: Good Option for Healthy Food, but Staff Could Improve

I recently visited Mucho Burrito and found it to be a good option for those looking for healthy food choices. The menu offers a variety of options that can cater to different dietary preferences.

However, I was a bit disappointed with the service. The staff seemed to be in a rush during busy times, which affected the quality of the orders. They didn't seem to pay attention to the amount of sauces and items they were putting in the bowls or burritos, which impacted the overall taste of the food.

Overall, Mucho Burrito is a decent choice for healthy eating, but the staff could be more patient and attentive to ensure a better dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLtifeNTm6LKJsMCd3MdSpRYuZvLEF_KjpAS2e&fid=0x0:0xf11beeae61b238b7"],"When":"2024-2-13"},{"Name":"bhawna khullar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0SXXLIljG-fcYo6MCkaB51HrbwaqVLzVWorWAx_nE4QPj7w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This store always serves the best. The staff is very friendly. Anshul always greets the customers with a smile. -Aman","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jay Why","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf6qVrRB2FWSP3f_QpdYqgSMlmFo0fYvO9JkGkahstgPZxGBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food is ok at best. The tacos and quesadillas didn't have a lot of fillings. Half the rice in the burrito was still hard, like it wasn't properly reheated. If you ever had leftover rice in the fridge, you'll know what I mean. The service is hit and miss at this location. Sometimes it good, but today I had to wait a while. There were people behind the counter, but it seems like only one person is allow to serve the customers. I realize this is basically Mexican fast food, but for what they charge, I expected better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgMTekGvqRbsS9RT_OPPjYcermqyc3CZAgut7z&fid=0x0:0xf11beeae61b238b7"],"When":"2021-9-11"},{"Name":"Manreet Aulakh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLenyUu5M-FzhmSLndgj9KbOETYzkKpesPXeFFv7s1xVWrTCw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I’ve been a regular customer here for a while, and unfortunately don’t see myself coming back. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Vanshik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4kf7IV3L7GzOeWeSCwC0K2Ccms7H0IiFf_Oy1HASgYToRA-W0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I recently visited here for my friend's birthday, and overall, it was a pleasant experience. The food was delicious, and our server was polite and attentive, making our dining experience enjoyable.

However, we encountered an issue when it came time to pay the bill. There was a scanner on our table that mentioned a 10% discount if we posted a story on Instagram. We followed the instructions and posted the story, but when we went to the billing counter, we were told that the offer was outdated and no longer valid. This was quite disappointing and misleading, especially since the scanner was still on the table.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPoShKbE3yP_pzlxKPGUAaG1wBZ-5RE-Ebe_5r3&fid=0x0:0x8d64d8eea4db2059"],"When":"2024-8-3"},{"Name":"Abhilasha More","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWGt7LPO5T8zSIMQfEqYAtmyFggn7yhYxqzKStzn2UkrBCRkn2Dw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I was so tempted to visit this place after seeing their instagram post. So recently visited their Surrey location. Taste and ambience were not very appealing. Washrooms need maintenance and regular cleaning. Few of the items from their post were not available at time. Chicken lollipop is totally different from the original recipe. Doesn’t taste good with barbecue sauce. No issues with the parking. Plenty of parking available as part of the strip mall. Looking forward to trying food at their Langley location.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXEo0Npc_kJFgXvGrhc8TfSvrIEOpwrBgLSCD4&fid=0x0:0x8d64d8eea4db2059"],"When":"2024-8-29"},{"Name":"Devineah Prasad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXX1DFa9bRk6bvv1_M-orvwe0-273w8OFGry_kkVxXgLnOAtjdI1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It was my first time at this restaurant with my work friends we had a good time here. The food was pretty good. The service was kinda slow at the time we came in because there were not a lot of people at that time. The atmosphere was pretty nice, clean and stylish. I would give this place 3.5 stars out of five.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPH0R9JtbH-6mzK6NkBFfmdwNOy6qXfBtd0HXao&fid=0x0:0x8d64d8eea4db2059"],"When":"2024-5-27"},{"Name":"Jasmeet Panesar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMcW_c7YsWe00hzXLDJ2iEEuUE-CmlYgwh53vkobZL3QO3bow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The perfect Indian restaurant to visit . The food is filled with flavours . I really enjoyed the malai chicken tikka and cream chicken . The service and ambience is top notch. Their Christmas decoration   Is so beautiful .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaKGhCKrhrtjFfwDzEaAfbmHfzkBIn5NtF2W-K&fid=0x0:0x8d64d8eea4db2059"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Kamal J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPtrJUF5Ih34UhFvAmR5C5WZDqD3Oo-SV1XzaS7cVv1WiGar8f=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The speciality cocktails were beautiful and delicious! The appys and Shahi paneer we had were also very yummy!! We will def be back to try more of their menu!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3feD57vepIyBC5MayTFuSRxWFs5IHE3eoEGGf&fid=0x0:0x8d64d8eea4db2059"],"When":"2024-9-7"},{"Name":"Sarah Kaigon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLjjEwjY98ZEuTDXtUHTSbj-wCBC7_WjPiokJYrjyW8CLDt0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The first time I tried the food I had impressive packaging/bags with logos. I loved the chicken pakora which had 2 mint chutney containers as it was crispy fried chicken pieces that tasted amazing. I did get what appeared to be a black cardamom seed in my curry which was bitter & ruined that portion of my meal, however, the naan were flavorful & fresh. The chicken pakora was so memorable that I ordered it again within a week but was disappointed when I opened the box. It was breaded chicken breast chopped into pieces (potentially leftovers being re-worked into pakora??) & although the breading was flavorful the chicken was dry with only 1 container of mint cilantro chutney. Maybe different chefs so hopefully the next time I take a chance it will be better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUnSX3ReUN-1O6Y0nRXENBT4Q1QfgoabDTrcAV&fid=0x0:0x8d64d8eea4db2059"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Nadeem Zia.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMvuVKaJ5RspKjafdw7NuycDlSlwvLOTMgiMvYKB8ZcmZ9sQ7d7w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best Dasi Live Grill restaurants.🙂 It was our first time here, but we loved the delicious food, friendly service and lovly ambience. We got few veg order and all are testy and fresh.
Dikshah took our order, and she was friendly and helpful. Thanks","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYuUY4LTKY7q4FrjkNjzUGSwbsp81D44GkIfDY&fid=0x0:0x8d64d8eea4db2059"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Sandeep Patel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUPXpjfuhMT06CDlElzdABigOc3yyD8mJ_731K4OtRygYmbVPS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The quality of the food was exceptional, with flavors that delighted the palate. Portions were generous, ensuring satisfaction. The ambiance added to the overall experience, creating a pleasant atmosphere. Additionally, the service was attentive and friendly, enhancing the dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOU84emk5O5Wi5pA8fmisZuEcAh4Ar8nphSezBG&fid=0x0:0x8d64d8eea4db2059"],"When":"2024-4-13"}]
