user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Elana Spowage","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLShtrL5KrPHgROVGe-iKsBqQWrzbv-TrlPj3At9vmhz6mJVg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was a super cool experience. Our servers were so nice at the kiosk. Checking on us multiple times if we needed any suggestions. The food was great, explosions of flavour. And their milkshakes are incredible. Will be back for more Indian street food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTf2-tWb_gdGlGk4i5udr1P8OaLq37wTVkZput&fid=0x0:0xb32e17c9b67b82e6"],"When":"2024-10-27"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It's a bit different from a typical Indian food that I'm used to. It feels very modern and bright with digital kiosks to take your order. While the service and the food was good, I wish they had more information on the food and the ingredients for none Indian diners because I was a bit lost on all the different types of street food.

I would love to come back with more research and order different kinds of food to try. The shakes also seem very popular so I will try them next time I visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPxWv96xZA74zOSzjfcCH4d6cOUwcibppuaJcIp&fid=0x0:0xb32e17c9b67b82e6"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"Manali Chanchlani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWezs3pEhIAEx2SzOjW7JtoyqG_GiVGiuXJWHoJHqiGIJBm6o-T=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious food, friendly staff and very spacious place with lots of seating! Manreet recommended us to order their popular dishes and we loved them all!
Their tokri chaat is loaded with flavors and was our favorite. We also ordered the chole bhature, soya chaap and kulcha. Everything tasted fresh and authentic. Would highly recommend this place if you are in the area!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMs-166698wxCYL0eaOvNRub8UgIoul_SYttQU&fid=0x0:0xb32e17c9b67b82e6"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"love kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLj5pRuFSsZMFTmQoHH3vxJtAgbM9b9DTq4749Q7YEevQzGeA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Dining at this establishment has been quite disappointing. While we genuinely enjoy the food, the service—especially from the manager—leaves much to be desired. We ordered the veggie chow mein and waited nearly thirty minutes for our meal. To our dismay, we noticed the staff microwaving the noodles, which raised concerns about their freshness. Instead of addressing the situation directly, the manager sent three different staff members to pacify us, but he never made an appearance to clarify or apologize for the mishap. This lack of accountability and honesty only added to our frustration. They did not offer any solutions. The first staff member tried to offer us another dish, but that person didn't return. After five minutes, another staff member came to check on us, and finally, a third person appeared. But they want to cover-up their mistake.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNyTc__ihH7RD1MYVJlYHY9Cgsk-KadKkKqrMqh&fid=0x0:0xb32e17c9b67b82e6"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Shashank Ahuja","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-fvMxEb4QFhR0YvgVAfCORCcbVvasQUqOuBvJPYqjKVFBfYAe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We recently visited this Indian restaurant and overall, the food was quite good. However, there is a concerning issue with their billing practices.

When paying by card, they round off the total to the nearest dollar, which resulted in us being charged 2 cents extra. While this might seem negligible, it adds up significantly across all their transactions. There’s absolutely no reason to round off if the payment is not in cash. If they want to simplify pricing, they could increase menu prices by a cent or charge the exact amount for card payments.

This practice feels unfair and unnecessary, especially when it’s repeated for every customer and transaction. While we enjoyed the food, this approach leaves a negative impression. We hope the management revisits their billing policy to ensure fair charges for everyone.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMoIYgqybT71ZDFaFdQmtWz4_rw5ruRaz8KY3FY&fid=0x0:0xb32e17c9b67b82e6"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Vijay Purty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUchl-cnLhiNVGqTw5fSimADiSPSqpKzBXu64ANZGyiGYYuKpBokA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing experience......... excellent food
After long time you can find all the Indian street food experience from every corner of the country, at one place with world class hygiene. Add--on what a great selection of shakes they have amazing flavours ..👌👌👌👌👌👌👌👌👌👌👌
Special thanks to Gursheen, Damneet & Taiyab.....","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOW9gR6EldCaIqexOfVff8dqfAO46lfVObTC7oy&fid=0x0:0xb32e17c9b67b82e6"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"swap2188","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwtZRmQRtq48ykmrP2qz6nPKUoV0_lPN_u0lBaDs7e-oz4rcw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is just yum 😋 if you crave for Punjabi street food this is the place to go. Everything is delicious and the flavors are just perfect.
We ordered Bheega Kulcha(must try), Punjabi Non-veg thali, Chicken tandoori, basket chaat (must try), Falooda & Rabri. If you planning to visit from US and takeout they actually do a good job of packing food. Overall one of the best food finds I have had so far in Vancouver.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAzS0sgAykR1N2zDSN0pJQCuIR4V3_2g5p-NnA&fid=0x0:0xb32e17c9b67b82e6"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Sidharth Jhawar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqfvFdclSSlE0wMMqTd7OAs9935GkZqf04JObQ-XgE8pqCZpgI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing tasting food and service. This place rocks. Never dissapointed once. My trip to Vancouver is not completed without stopping here once, sometimes even twice. Try any item of the list, and you wouldn't be disappointed. Little expensive and loud but overall, came for the food and was not disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIxoO_816ZRQZDnwE5Xip9WakiqrJd7RyB_U-r&fid=0x0:0xb32e17c9b67b82e6"],"When":"2024-8-12"}]

I would still go to this place for paratha tho","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-HcEybsyGPveAaKJ07U2Spg3svW1rMd8A1S3Y&fid=0x0:0xe75a008be523fe07"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"Navreet Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNb551TuB4cJVcSu_2ZD2stjRH1phAYzoP8n08uR1VOiMzBWUivw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"⚠️ I am posting this for awareness to everyone to check the food before you eat.

Normally the experience is pretty good but today I had my regular order messed up by one of the chefs and it's concerning how they can send food out like that.

I had "paneer burger" which was partially cold and had overcooked/stale paneer patty. It was so hard to eat that it seemed like I was chewing a rock which led to hurt my gums, causing em to bleed.

I did talk to the staff and they were sorry about it but I think they should have been careful in the first place.

I have added a video clip for reference.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIh95-YN8gikqjTDUVw0OWmYnzAJNoRBhEYTSE&fid=0x0:0xe75a008be523fe07"],"When":"2024-8-22"},{"Name":"Trivikram Kamat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4gPcZ_3IgI2AqqkvQSTkf6ElerU7cZpcZefSZSRJNt7SSAVQnIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I would have given them five stars, if only their chai didn't suck. Chole Bhature was average.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKl3XBCMcFrXFUPTjxvM1n2sK4uoSFMNCG_qQA&fid=0x0:0xe75a008be523fe07"],"When":"2023-12-31"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Raeburn MacDougall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIoXHoCNiCsL0dOjQhl4dr7HXmy8LsAXROqZKdAcT-ThcE0fCn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ok I'm a pizza fanatic. I have tried many of the places between Richmond, Ladner and Tsawwassen. Each place I have reviewed has its own special qualities, and Grizzly Flatbread is no exception. Excellent customer service, big selection of pizzas and a happy hour from 2pm to 5pm even on the night of the Stanley Cup final game. High quality 10" hand made pizza for $10 dollars no limit on # of pizzas..👍. it was amazing I ordered 4 different kinds for our group of friends to go. Each pizza was amazing. If you haven't tried them yet I highly recommend you do. I can guarantee you won't be disappointed. I will definitely be having Grizzly again and again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjvdJW7aSNIyZHUK8OlPS7jkbgdsHI4vI83tLi&fid=0x0:0x13d6b7d52babeea"],"When":"2024-6-28"},{"Name":"Pigpinkx","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWApOQKcUKxk7JjR5oAkq09K5LHCIcyzvXSbNsSeNEYlgx6p8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don't normally post reviews, but seeing such a good restaurant with a low rating on yelp compelled me to set things straight. This is an amazing pizza joint. There aren't many quality restaurants in Ladner, and I would hate to see a place like this shut down due to poor reviews. If you check on Google, you'll see that the majority of people who visited had a good experience. The first pizza I ordered from here was top-notch. I would definitely recommend this gem to others. Please give them a shot and don't be discouraged by the low ratings.

My favorite is the forager (+ bacon). There’s not enough pizza joints doing cream based sauces and this one is delicious!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwMvG9aV3EGnEnAHvGICC5k98GDJn933rWhTh9&fid=0x0:0x13d6b7d52babeea"],"When":"2024-7-19"},{"Name":"Alexandra B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI34csndi8g_W5d38YtSOZDCRjtyMdXHMWvPlV136of0FURsg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried their pizza for the first time and every pizza tried was delicious. The dough is cooked perfectly. Our group tried the figgy piggy, max, forager (personal favourite) and the hot stuff. We were not disappointed with any of our choices. All of the toppings were very fresh. Service was extremely fast. Atmosphere is very clean, simple and the perfect spot to stop in for a quick bite.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mikayla W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrzwUPecZFd0iHu9hL83IJG4wPDLoRyYpqrkvrkbLlIbjS0Nw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"New favourite pizza place in Ladner! (and we have tried them all). Crust is crispy but also has a nice chew. Nice and thin wood fired crust. Toppings are great and fresh. Even the sauces (tomato and alfredo) are delicious and not too heavy. They are also extremely nice and very accommodating. Happy to have them in town and will order again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPxrewLzffKW1-LEbqgU1m32IvL7PCbCZ6zW5tU&fid=0x0:0x13d6b7d52babeea"],"When":"2024-4-24"},{"Name":"Frias Fight Team","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXm2Sdehq7i7pnEbVbcNEui08_LITsNfGUL7YuPoicIubfTxMk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious pizza, great flavours ingredients and a thin crust which I love. The forager pizza and the pepperoni are both phenomenal, I ended up ordering more while sitting down because they were so tasty. Highly recommend coming here and checking it out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMT5oaFOXh9GtRIVV2vijUIg1_-76CwAF4SRaXs&fid=0x0:0x13d6b7d52babeea"],"When":"2024-4-13"},{"Name":"Max Erickson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVz3dwhz2Iz0uC9vQRsiPEcFdDiRVvnC_NMnW4Qw-l_l2eI6_M8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried the pesto chicken pizza and veggie/vegan flatbread.

Flatbread wasn't my favorite but it was still very good.

Pizza was very very good, thin, flavorful and well cooked. Will definitely order another pizza from here in the future. Can't wait!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOZ4Axi1wXaxLGJWQtkYArkfDJR4MaTKVtOVlF-&fid=0x0:0x13d6b7d52babeea"],"When":"2024-3-22"},{"Name":"Kj Deol","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVZtlp5eFyS3gVRRAGabrjFjxQUXx7lFhnEHqMeeY8A4Q9vg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was in the neighborhood after a long time and noticed this place. Went in with my brother and ordered 2 pies which we got during the happy hour promotion. I'm a simple man so I had to get the cheese and the other one I was feeling adventurous and went with the rose. I was blown away with the flavor of the pizza as well as the bite into the crust.  I've got another reason to come back to this area more. 10/10","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicolae Roman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwrXM8xiI7NMfY6vYoUI-_JWhnu0tHltZBV8Xh9UxRwexx5sfL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic environment and really nice staff, the pizza is one of the best I've had from a oven pizza place. Glad to see there is something local in Ladner like this. They do sell slices aswell if you are just shopping in the area","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPeUQUxwkgyx4rUpTpIQ3oXxVtf0feal8xNRKgW&fid=0x0:0x13d6b7d52babeea"],"When":"2024-5-21"}]

[{"Name":"Paulina Pedrero Miranda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoiOld2vaC2Dv18bWNi8EDRiykD7MSCRsU3RK7RESh6xQghXxb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice place to have breakfast, the ladies are very friendly and helpful, but here are a lot of options, great variety of coffee and hot beverages, baked goods salty and sweet, combo breakfast like sandwich and soup, the place is small but warm.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPto4Tcv79zG6wm8-hMzFijXMDbk6VfbBskpuyN&fid=0x0:0xc46381d25939e8fe"],"When":"2024-4-17"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Real homestyle classic foods here made with quality ingredients. I had the turkey brie melt which was delicious and fresh. Their speciality baked bread even had cranberries baked into it and they also added apple to the sandwich which was a nice touch making it both sweet and savory. I liked this place. Looking forward to try their Shepherd's Pie and quiches in the future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1SUtMM-P-A27VadSiRWle0B1kw2uPzjEnHynD&fid=0x0:0xc46381d25939e8fe"],"When":"2021-7-22"},{"Name":"Tiana Gordon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYMz1yUZuEgKHa2uDK3PxaRYn4dyPS_QcB-fy1T_3nxy8-9jZy=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I went here to get lunch while working in Ladner one day.
I ordered a sandwich and told the person taking my order and making the sandwich I’m allergic to dairy. I also asked for gluten free bread (a preference, not an allergy, which I told them).
They seemingly had no knowledge of their ingredients and actually had to bring out their jar of mayo for me to read to see if it had dairy.
The person then asked me if I wanted cheese on my sandwich… I obviously said no.
It wasn’t until after I was back at my work site and took my sandwich out of the wrapping that I realized the gluten free bread they substituted was in fact cheese bread.
I’m not sure how they didn’t catch this after I mentioned at least twice that I’m allergic to dairy.
Needless to say I was incredibly disappointed to not have a lunch that day, and I would not be going back as it seems they are unable to accommodate dietary restrictions.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lee Gildemeester","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmwK5TPiyJO9K2BikS-yqaHifl8H0QHLdeDujEGzwKhWsKSXQ7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Love the homemade feel of the food but seriously lacking in ingredients. My tuna melt had twice as much bread as both tuna and cheese combined, and the potato salad, while enjoyable in its simplicity, needed more flavour. At $10 for a sandwich I expect more food than a minuscule line of tuna and so little cheese I need to closely inspect the sandwich to make sure the cheese is even there.

Also it’s rude when businesses prompt me for a tip on the machine when I didn’t sit down at eat in the establishment. I came in, ordered, and left to eat elsewhere. No service was provided so why am I being prompted to tip? Knocking a star off the review for greedy tipping prompt.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jordan Polgar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7C0SgKQzDvqRzNpQxit3us52V-jc-OQYXuRvCyoY-5Z6qHBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A quaint and unassuming little cafe, with fresh made soups, sandwiches, salads and hot beverages. Staff are friendly, and everything appears to be made in house. A wonderful spot for lunch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCHiNA59HmVj1yDQHkeoAwK4TBB3l1tp0-9OAO&fid=0x0:0xc46381d25939e8fe"],"When":"2017-3-4"},{"Name":"Mr Mckenzie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_BxPYDr2y3voCm_NUkWQ4KNhyyaNBjo_DUK5jjIu-c33iKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"If you like soggy a grilled sandwich - then enjoy, here it's microwaved and grilled, there's nothing gourmet about this place.
So disappointed","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Greg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEbsNJ3VwdzUJfJHVNQHq_iJl5Kf2D32xWuwwM8B1bnVunRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"great Chilli and cheese pasta salad ..nice litte coffee / tea shoppe. .sandwich s made to order ...great staff..and good beef barley soup","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Autin (RJ’s Custom Detailing)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6OJnMbuoaXAllJq-r8SXN2kVZVB-scSuLJA20qRNjh4A-4FzXSA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everything I have tried at Cafe de Gourmet has been excellent.  Generous portions of their baked goods, easily 5 stars!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Munro Stuff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj0Wcuk6ox5dfAeJ4fAaMbhX_F-nzzt3p5oc_f0hBd0NpbGSM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had planned to pop in for a beer....but the beers were so great that we had to try a few kinds. And it was an excellent Happy Hour so we had to try a pretzel with cheese sauce...which was so good that we ordered more food and made a dinner of it. Diverse menu, nice decor, great service by Ella. Will definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMy5Bm0nuTOpAnZjuPtygc4JvHf9agmWt4ashb-&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-11-7"},{"Name":"Omar Plascentia Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxFeUWXfP60KHwVYL9J3bKZi_XZdQMIDzH47BU49kMhclJbfIi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"_A Mixed Bag_
Gorgeous! The service? Friendly and attentive.
Unfortunately, the food didn't quite live up to the hype. I was genuinely excited to try, but they fell flat. Flavors were muted, presentation was lacking, and portions were small for the price .. feel sorry for the tip.. my wallet weeps, tho
It pains me to say it because the staff was lovely and the atmosphere was spot-on. But, the food – the main event – just didn't impress.
Rating:_ 2.5/5 stars
Maybe I just ordered wrong, that's it.. Try it for yourself, but temper your expectations
I'll stick to admiring their aesthetic, tho..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkaaDrGE4dtj-K58U9jeomSXuE_Rk55xky8d-z&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A great find in Ladner, Britannia Brewing has great tasting craft beer on tap, delicious food and spacious seating with a relaxing atmosphere. Great to sit, talk, eat or just enjoy a drink.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONkMoVTwjhUTGqFaFMRQ1gWr640QUWrNgAAOFE&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-10-28"},{"Name":"D. S. H.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJHQjUje9KisA5u93NxJkw1JL_FCRnXl3eZFy20rlaly3_hOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The dog-friendly patio was surprisingly nice considering it's a repurposed parking area covered in artificial grass. Lots of potted plants, nice umbrellas for shade and good room between tables.

Happy hour offered good food at great prices.

The servers were friendly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOmokuQHM_XU83F8EM7rYSQSwfgWmzkFYykNDfj&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-8-2"},{"Name":"Shirley Ann Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTufZ1O7YNqmevegFQNEbK68BixarB9ooeJyWD92O9OkSBiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Where do I begin? I was having a craving for fish and chips. I found the Britannia Brewing right across the street from my location. I walked into an inviting trendy at Chic restaurant. I was met by a lovely lady and taken to a table. I'm not someone who likes to try new things and when I notice the fish and chips wasn't the typical fish and chips I was skeptical. I spoke to my waitress and she explained the dish in detail. She knows her menu. Well. I found the staff to be dressed in comfortable yet professional manner making the place feel very relaxed and inviting. I did order the fish and chips and they were the best I've ever had. The batter was not thick and over breaded nor was it greasy. The flavor was delicious! They gave me two large pieces and french fries. I love the homemade tartar sauce. I ordered a pop as well and they even brought a slice of lime in there which I thought was a nice touch. I'm especially impressed with the fact that they have three bathrooms. One is wheelchair accessible tastefully decorated. In fact the whole restaurant is tastefully decorated!  I will not hesitate to go back in order to recommend this to as many people that are willing to listen.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXKShd1mPP3RLZleiMiBTr4WHfZNNwITCitKwe&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-5-13"},{"Name":"Ross McCutcheon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV17RLqBCwI7SSR47xRsCSTT37HMSG55hKmTlfuQXCdFOnVSNzm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best try this one before the lineups start. Enjoyed all four choices on our beer flight. The burger from Twin River's was terrific as was the salad with sockeye. Just a great place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWmkI8jn9zmctMJb1uWDQ6pD2gWWphsLmGV_iT&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-5-16"},{"Name":"Pongo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXT-qQCE1uUwfmES1FGLIpAmkroUlDIcsJZMXejhRkO1uA9CxO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Haven't had a chance to try the beers yet, but the food here is excellent. Each dish we tried were distinct and well-executed. Though a tad expensive, I would order the duck wings again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7eSyZTOJQBZhb93rXRUFU1y53HdqJ5fb_1qDy&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Sue Pierce","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFDZvp0iO8IycCL1mvjrCRyoXBO8oRqjr35u3xz-iSc5cOkePw6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loooooove this place! Amazing food, excellent service, and cozy atmosphere!  I ordered the Ladner Power Bowl, which was so fresh and full of flavor. Looking forward to eating here again soon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOV0Oeg17CocCmRjo6Ta6U0A7kbXigQD6Zu1XgT&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-11-30"}]

[{"Name":"July M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPev1MGk8g7gho65nL58g_fBB-niZ6_zdN_uI9W2I5IhKVkLnN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited this coffee shop for the first time and specifically requested a non-sweet cookie, which was absolutely delicious, along with a latte. Both were perfect. The service was friendly and welcoming. Great experience overall!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMa53cVS6ZTDGxR1kO5-W8J5i_Jb_w2UAp_CV2z&fid=0x0:0xe18a2afd96eb49d4"],"When":"2024-9-11"},{"Name":"Minji Co","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0cW7yUIGQwxewtq2t91XH-PweiJmGMnXmQUWs9lKXUa5ZbKC6vQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They have some unique drinks on the menu but I ordered the traditional flat white which was delicious!! 👍🏻

Servers were all friendly and lots of parking in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpHysWn-PBRZQB9dltxyGu8wCZgNxFQvDTNLXV&fid=0x0:0xe18a2afd96eb49d4"],"When":"2024-8-3"},{"Name":"Alicia Archer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU94NoAUo-reqA_8E5P1ww6vS09a_CWhkBDXdwTYWveC0MNK1Qi=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Mid at best.

Ordered two simple drinks. Both were super diluted and bitter. They also didn't put the flavor shot in we requested.

Got home and mentioned our lack luster experience to family. Without even mentioning the name of the shop they already knew who we were talking about.

Just sad because the location and atmosphere suggest they'd be better, and the place was empty when we ordered so there wasn't even the pressure of a rush to explain the bad product.

Staff was polite enough though.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christopher Cliff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX48zUpRrirDLCbbcO1JxvHVyUc21lKplohfJf2oB7SfkpzE0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great coffee shop in Ladner. Grab a coffee to go and hit up the thrift stores! That's what I do!

The layout of the coffeeshop makes sense, allowing for a lineup, a waiting area for orders, and a decent cafe / patio seating area.

I love the coffee, the selection of milk alternatives,  the vinyl that gets played, and rare these days: the washrooms are tidy and clean. (Though perhaps they are on the verge of needing a bit of TLC).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTAOSrxSaCOCACPaHfZJ7FuWXestAftlBtDHjz&fid=0x0:0xe18a2afd96eb49d4"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"Kelly Argue","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHguvt2mUYK3ZLLT7t42H3YMBdzPp4wF0FbC-_ZBGyrnECZG3faw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This place has a great location and wonderful courteous and helpful staff.
There wasn't a lot of vegetarian options for savory treats so I got the almond croissant, which is a personal favorite. There was a lot of sweet filling and it was huge, not necessarily my style but it was still good.
I got a decaf caramel oat milk latte and the coffee was quite bitter and I had to put extra sweet in it.
All in all it was a good experience and I'll go back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVS2sq4B4h1VNEAHPNyMb13fPFbu4xvPJGto5RC_j2_kf5ywyBT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I suspect they were having an off day the day we walked in for our one and only visit with them. We had the kind of experience that makes you regret pre-paying a tip that reflects great service.

It was not crowded or super busy in there. There were two tables free and no queue. A flat expressionless face greeted us and rang our order in. She promptly forgot our lemon loaf the minute we paid for it. Sat down thinking it might be brought to us but it wasn’t. Had to get up and ask for it. Got an apology. They gave us a dirty tea cup. Had to go up and exchange it. Got an apology. There’s no milk out for self-serve. Had to go up and ask for it.

I’m pretty low maintenance so it has to be exceptionally poor service for me to write this sort of review. Hoping this was a rare experience because otherwise it seemed like a great little cafe. Also, an unclaimed bag sat on the love seat the entire time we were there making us think someone was sitting there and perhaps just in the bathroom, but no. So there was a lovely seat left empty on a Sunday afternoon because staff were not really engaged.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nik Hik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8EtdPJeHnYK1rFp_5oxOZlQloWdY3g56lL9W_moBmlTS6JboP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Have the pleasure of working in Delta and stumbling across this charming little place. Outstanding coffee, hands down best traditional cappuccino I've ever tasted. Food is incredible (particularly the chicken club). Great staff, consistently awesome service and products. Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLuvf_-_rDZHj8RlHI0bzH9TQqwsze0353kjGC&fid=0x0:0xe18a2afd96eb49d4"],"When":"2023-6-2"},{"Name":"S R (RamRoad)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTuRXqijs8BhgMnzK7J9Ym7JABL4HcxpwlRMGaThlIPkDrCTk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Not sure what happened but the espresso was top notch for years here until recently.   I gave it another shot today and it was bitter , less than 2oz (double shot) and left a horrible after taste.      Shame because this was the best coffee house south of the Fraser for a long time.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Caleb Gallacher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHYEJtESOFHCZNx4k97gkuaJd71UDWV20zSPRKilwfYjkqKg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Not from here, yet I’m very impressed by their prices on beer. A 600ml beer is $6 - $8 which is nice on the pocket. The food here is good too. It isn’t renovated and not the most cozy place, but it’s the best place I’ve gone for a beer in a long time. Much better than the Rose and Crown and the Landing. The regulars seemed quite nice as well, along with the kind and honest staff. This place is a solid 8/10!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Holland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwojmWLax6tCAsluMeRYRcULAx9_6vDJad6FfkXbF3IYuaOOU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Speed's Pub in Delta is on the water, Fraser River, just up from the Ladner Harbour Boat Basin, by the Ladner Pier, in fact it is next door to Sharkey's Seafood Bar & Grille.
They served a respectable size piece of breaded cod, with the menu's listed fish & chips selection (cheaper as daily special on Tuesday).
A varied selection of both food choices and drinks. Draft beers included Guinness dark stout for a reasonable price!
The narrow patio by the water was pretty full when we arrived late in the lunchtime rush but as couples left, the two-tops by the water's edge became available for the 'later' lunch crowd or even happy hour guests.
Parking is available on the street and in front. With Sharkey's right next door, not certain how the parking is shared or gets too crowded?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJ6i4YMzV1jK5SNRM8YpvXPwFj0vp0OfziKADO&fid=0x0:0xe01f3ec377c88785"],"When":"2024-6-20"},{"Name":"Diane Leiter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyXk9fyDM9oMAi1nBBq-NeNkATe4RG0P2HwlXxGvuvY3BeYVaj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Neighborhood pub with great atmosphere, and right on the water. Food was wonderful, ample servings, and a good selection of beer. Accessible to all. Very friendly and helpful service. I didn't have the kind of ice tea I liked, so she made it for me. Awesome.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2BAgtq272CU8y8333I2_bkLbyO8DESAcahi0B&fid=0x0:0xe01f3ec377c88785"],"When":"2023-9-9"},{"Name":"Torchie 2010","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJqYIiPOFAtESxtEjn8bxUeO-DrBaKlnQ5IbOahr9roKXwkjwj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to the Ladner Farmers Market and walked around and saw this Pub by the Dease island slough.
Had Fish N Chips and Ceasers to drink.
Very nice, nothing fancy
Sunday Special Fish n Chips Cod 19.99 for 2 pc","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN-3gI3ZnaFLVa-A67RahtL_JNFL7INtgjKPwQc&fid=0x0:0xe01f3ec377c88785"],"When":"2023-7-23"},{"Name":"Dani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0rASNM3UoTaBI1w_-GDXRfdkjX2-OvaVRSoBQ9UJje7neMw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food & a great patio. So nice that they allow dogs on the lower part as well. Great weekly deals!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKSUIwA1TaFhQhv60qdC0vsN5A212uasvEAx5b&fid=0x0:0xe01f3ec377c88785"],"When":"2024-7-8"},{"Name":"Chris MacDonald","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUaD_C5C9feF_MEkQ2fFDc5cG1u4m6lAVed4bAYShNFRcTb6uI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Dined for two of us for happy hour. And the staff held out the food to go until it was beyond the happy hour time limit and so not to give the deal. When brought to the staff she said she had nothing to do with it. Unfortunate to offer the happy hour time but then to force a cold takeout meal. Staff must give leniency to the time when arrival and departure or you're going to lose the regular s that come there for the time that you're asking them to. Shame on speeds.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shawn B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIiLz_Fvu2Z_sAsud0kUXYcpIhrTzSkTDXj-dxi9MqAOVzC5A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Good drinks, fish and chips could be ALOT better. The servers are nice and the service is good. It is definitely a decent place during the summer for a quick bite or a beer on the patio, I would stick to the beer or drinks only, pass on the fish and chips","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"54sputnick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRGGRadB2kuHfTripjCMYlzqw93kIJfA9P_HvEu2OVglBQNcU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Went on Sunday for the prime rib dinner. While the beef was tender, the Yorkshire Pudding lovely, the so called mashed potatoes  were terrible! Not really mashed, large chunks of partially cooked potato, very little mash. The thickness of the meat served was in our opinion too thick. In all, was not the Sunday roast dinner we had been looking forward to.
The server did tell us the head chef was not on site, soooo could explain it, but won’t be running back for more soon.😕","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Dana Flores","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJk-5SV4AG-TBDxby4GTSu519jBHl91RfUXovRNMfylScOJDw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very tasty. Authentic Mexican (or at least my take on authentic Mexican)

The presentation of the food was amazing & super delicious. The quality of the food, you would think you were dining at a higher priced establishment.

Seems like a very popular spot with locals. Was very busy on a Thursday night. It was a full house! A table became available to us after a few mins of waiting.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNzYIzSgVKTk_RGTIP4B5wWVmH_1YW9Tuy9y9ZN&fid=0x0:0x1346437040852da0"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"Phil S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJiWEJLcqrXpHsLhKzG59Sc12cffA1IbqARgsoeTJJpctJaVQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Absolutely AMAZING!
This place was everything I had hoped it would be.  "Mom and Pop" style restaurant, with a big focus on quality food.  I had the chimichangas, but will be back to try everything on the menu.

HIGHLY recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfUPRtmFpB5b7Jtmy0y-aJtPma4f1tBLBXj2Qm&fid=0x0:0x1346437040852da0"],"When":"2024-11-8"},{"Name":"Sadman Hasan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1-E0x6j6iYhC4moEKHU2mbzBet2SDYA0iUiruX9Cj_jo750Zm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The service was quick and efficient, with staff being attentive and professional throughout. The tater tots and fries were particularly impressive—crisp, fresh, and perfectly cooked.

The Baja fish taco, complemented by fresh salsa, was a standout, offering a well-balanced flavor profile. However, the chicken tinga was underwhelming; the chicken had a boiled texture and lacked seasoning, which detracted from the dish. The carne asada torta, while flavorful, had slightly dry beef, though it still offered a satisfying bite. Compared to the price, I would say there is still room for improvement in terms of taste.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjSVq1m3NtVqoD-zHVlCkR62JyTauQqozYjhfn&fid=0x0:0x1346437040852da0"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Kaishin Chu (Kaī)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXj9wnE3m0__GlxpKfZ9aqATWnoMO7qf81wqy2GbvhG9f2N3RM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I greatly appreciated that here they don't over season or salt the food. Quality and fresh. Enjoyed the atmosphere, reminded me of authentic Mexican eateries in the southern US.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPoRwOTnoqhdXXDgEPG6fcYJu20Rtkg4_CtWsDb&fid=0x0:0x1346437040852da0"],"When":"2024-9-10"},{"Name":"Dan Lorenz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVa_eC-U0kV3zmKzI4E1osV8_z7ABPGLuq9fXQNAmdOuVhfXvuZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place has a great atmosphere with the music, lots of room to sit, and most importantly the food is fantastic! Fresh and full of flavor. The staff are very polite and friendly. It's a great spot to eat in between my trips to Mexico ❤️. Love this place and highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLmTmVzYz-gR3kdNi9mBcsI5WmtD1WPyhvXd_w&fid=0x0:0x1346437040852da0"],"When":"2023-10-11"},{"Name":"J. F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvnPrghjIIxyliVLQ5qdXC_aHHLxKWdRLtv7_c0XpUi4UfZmBiFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food was good, great menu, went on a friday night and was way too busy, came back a day or two later. The food was fresh, we like a tad more spice and wee bit more salt and heat but thats just us as we like spicy food...can always ask for hot sauce!
Fair prices too..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAapJL5aXN486AdWfRM03kKcdRxhFUHOIXLzOA&fid=0x0:0x1346437040852da0"],"When":"2024-4-29"},{"Name":"M Salem","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDyPcTCKM1nBReXiYdvf-fl3flLMVEDpSNvBvcjuZOTVSPbbo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was incredible here! some of the most authentic Mexican food I have had in Vancouver and it’s nestled inside a plaza where you would miss it if you weren’t looking for it, the service was great as well, and the staff went above and beyond! I would highly recommend trying it out if you’re in the area","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMR2ztmLVui_dQBMncQNmZZ7qn2EqEh1YsV6xUW&fid=0x0:0x1346437040852da0"],"When":"2024-6-14"},{"Name":"HT L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDfC_Anv2iX2nrBvcEl7ZLOFXp2Qf-wJNzJBcEdOwZe_APx_Ra=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious Mexican food. Reasonable prices! Clean and spacious. Will definitely come back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOw-xduOlTbW9GlZnJ7cjUjtu9PmqkmUlGgQO6V&fid=0x0:0x1346437040852da0"],"When":"2024-6-24"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"This food","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUaxcCslaGrcC0u202g67ni7XJGWWGyPYtSKkUjWo5gpcXXO0Yv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Enjoyed my meal here for lunch today. I ordered the House Pho and the popular dish with the vermicelli, spring roll, lemongrass chicken, the red meat, and spinach beef roll. It was all very delicious and they are very generous with their meat portion compared to other competitors I’ve been to in Vancouver. Friendly service and attentive. It wasn’t very busy for a Saturday afternoon. Since Ive been coming to Ladner often I think this will be my new spot for comfort food in this area. Thanks for the lovely experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3H8DgsTWL4bmzG-8oLEg7Fc8WaIkzy9n8uPJn&fid=0x0:0xa7336b586da3827f"],"When":"2022-8-14"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Service here was great. Had the beef stew noodle. The broth was rich, hot, and nice and clean tasting, and didn't taste like MSG broth but real broth. The downside here was that the beef placed on top was near ice cold...literally...no exaggeration. It was definitely below room temperature hard cold beef so I am assuming they refrigerate or freeze their precooked beef and just defrost or microwave it when someone orders the dish but reheat it unevenly. Other than that, overall this was a good experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-d8qptLejM7p-bMoElt1IDIx3tmqpkHStqVKu&fid=0x0:0xa7336b586da3827f"],"When":"2021-7-2"},{"Name":"Steven","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwhlFiHPSDGYcBNEBZjiV401CUR-8LRwpy-nj0JN_nYZzCJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The portion of the banh mi was quite small and looked like they cut the meatball in halves instead of full meatballs - not what the picture looks like on the menu. The chicken and pork flavor on the rice dish were not the tastiest and on smaller side portion as well. The spring roll was ok and fish sauce was good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNA1966FNZO9b3CoLj2SR7nPborYHKOZAKxyLB4&fid=0x0:0xa7336b586da3827f"],"When":"2023-6-12"},{"Name":"Carlos Miranda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUB4daJxQQkgICpxRva14F5-6b7EkrIChl-XMaudNJADEUdvdBstg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Quick and good service, the location has plenty of parking around and nearby and there is plenty of spaces in between tables. The food is good, the pork/beef was mostly fat so maybe that can improve? Aside from that, everything else was tasteful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNom3C5ExUbffhXXZV3pW0Z7hVyV2GUa-VPbfN9&fid=0x0:0xa7336b586da3827f"],"When":"2023-4-17"},{"Name":"Shun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7ONYhfPtFR7GegIR-TSpTU1q050DlVJptNGajTfP2cS0Xb_ovIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Rare steak & beef ball pho was decent, standard flavour. (***)

Bun cha vermicelli with grilled pork and spring roll is OK only (little oily). (***)

Single piece of overly-fried banana ~$4.50 was a lonely rip-off with hardly any 🍌 in it.(* one star) 👎","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8jul9XF7RJqs7iqklYcanZSlvdadnL-T6-Ogw&fid=0x0:0xa7336b586da3827f"],"When":"2020-11-13"},{"Name":"Wendy Kan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUUMkg9LUGDXoqYiP4Dz28YR3jha29JwaIMh-r1NAGkpgYpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"House vermicelli $16.5 portion is ok (not big) but taste soso. My friend had beef noodles and the soup base is very light. Pho in Richmond is much better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzi_RXrEZ8Djr0KLJNi4-CcwSxYhdwo0jQb07D&fid=0x0:0xa7336b586da3827f"],"When":"2020-8-3"},{"Name":"Cody R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhnerVAy8-Mum3GU2BWejFe6BzrPQX43sScD2H9dZeYGkgNg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered takeout from here. Food is pretty good. However the portion is extremely small compared to other Vietnamese restaurants. I ordered the sate pho rare beef and there was only 4 small slices of beef.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWZYEmN351J77FHP9efRYCAJf5QX16LRXfskSE&fid=0x0:0xa7336b586da3827f"],"When":"2022-4-2"},{"Name":"Jo Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1TqwVe-O5n1d06B2UdI-0JvwJ-TmiUkh94kPgCXIRbaD0Dlbo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Service was quick. Pho soup was okay and had generous portions of meat but it could use more noodles.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnCZi9m4Yefer3t3mOlq0dJiZa9gWehYKHThYW&fid=0x0:0xa7336b586da3827f"],"When":"2020-11-17"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Gina Grape","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjfpAS0e1J9DlXOCRvxRrfnAvo44TyYUw59aPp0ohD7GacQA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Taste and quality of the food is good. More than enough options to go with depending on what you are craving for.  I had lunch special that comes with miso soup - teriyaki chicken with  tempura; bro and wife went for udon soup, karaagi, and bento.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3yQOGXsG8u4WU7FyMwu-L-c4lQhpBL7mADw6f\u0026fid=0x0:0x88b0154276b56a25"],"When":"2023-7-22"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent quality salmon here! You can taste the difference. The dinner combo bento E includes a bit of everything such as tasty fresh terriyaki salmon, refreshing sunomono salad, two spring rolls, salmon and tuna sashimi, assorted nigiri, and crispy shrimp and vegetable tempura. Service was awesome! Well done!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKiWvOMfRJpaIwgkAQR2i3UCxKTE8N3lJIDTsT\u0026fid=0x0:0x88b0154276b56a25"],"When":"2021-7-3"},{"Name":"Joey Mullins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjA9hfj_Ijm7nk28n3Pwuv3ZUU8ObFM0Pq6x9qasT5gDb6RMN8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ladner sushi is the go to place when it comes to authentic food and great service. The cuts of sushi in the combos we ordered were fresh and tasty. We got more value then we expected for the money, especially with their after 4pm combo. The desert, which is either mango or green tea cheese cake, is too delicious for words. We will be coming again here soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMN7zU_C9vXdKIZ1MfrSexvGTrjwFQwULAnixE4\u0026fid=0x0:0x88b0154276b56a25"],"When":"2022-6-12"},{"Name":"Drd Cameron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxYa2qx-iJcYkg-8p-Wnm3pY-GsSAREUZ6W8RVzYEfVaabcA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I go here 2-4 times a month. She is vegetarian and I'm the fish lover. We love our food, service, and freshness, quality overall.  Plus reasonable prices. I'm always amazed at how many families eat here. The kids all seem to love their sushi.....","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImPOcJCm5CCEOa5wt5zZstcHUVRP_7OnV_asTIaMaNpvwXFw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Fast service and a good-sized sockeye sashimi plate. Reasonable prices - dinner for two $31. The place is a little run down - the tables need re-surfacing (linoleum was peeling off), and the washroom could use a renovation.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMenPblL06POMJfv-ZIyzGC3x65kPjxYGczwhXM\u0026fid=0x0:0x88b0154276b56a25"],"When":"2017-11-13"},{"Name":"Hamed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViJ9EznENDd1HeEqpUkYuqmZFdKwptQI-w0AYNvWdb_l07iQpU7w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The quality of food was great. The food arrived bit late cause they do a lot of takeout.\n\nA must try sushi place in Ladner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMvvi6PipUmbsi6I2Lmaa5OD3jlVYyWC8AxVg_5\u0026fid=0x0:0x88b0154276b56a25"],"When":"2024-2-27"},{"Name":"Simon Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1hOsKIoj9bFpzabsd3fL9vgr9Zy2VYnc2w3EE29msDfHdYeWL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This rating is less about the food than the exemplary customer service. I had left behind one of my personal belongings after eating there. As I was about to get into my car, the owner of the restaurant chased me down and returned my item. I was very grateful. Thank you, sir! I did enjoy the food;I ordered the beef bento box.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM2ocAt8PW0ZNqNOPyLO6JTSl-GjRNAejQ3I2GP\u0026fid=0x0:0x88b0154276b56a25"],"When":"2017-10-21"},{"Name":"Angie L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKwNm9A8ohrfnu_XFwYhP8N-ACXPuzjT8lHAp_d40ZyvMetcg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Portion is small. The bento sashimi combo was soso and a bit too cold. Sushi was okay. The wooden bento tray looks beat up and chipped. Should be changed. Service is good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0SIT6rqqwqz1JWv4VR2RSxIqtnCxne6Wbp74r\u0026fid=0x0:0x88b0154276b56a25"],"When":"2020-1-17"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Anjana Ramesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_u2BnNG3bLDugh5sSEw9Wh8vzwOrNIoCcKHn7L3I4N1E2ifrPEg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredible place with a fantastic atmosphere! The aesthetics are on point, creating a perfect vibe for a relaxing visit. Hands down, the best chai I've had — it’s absolutely worth traveling for, and they even offer a sugarless option, which is great. We also enjoyed the masala fries and the cheese chutney sandwich, both of which were delicious.

There’s plenty of seating, and the variety of food options is impressive. The masala chai was especially outstanding — very Desi. The washrooms were also clean and well-maintained, which is always a plus.

If you're in the area, this place is a must-visit. Totally worth it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLPaCeBUKXZhOOE95Hjo6pLsujz0pGjTmI7zEW&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-12-4"},{"Name":"Dr. Naresh.R. Thumati","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZe9i5l3lcphUrpMV7UIgJLbGmYTbI6xZPxyGLcsocFMCumCPI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Its been long time I wanted to visit Chaiwala since their entry into Canada. Today, I have had this chance to taste Chaiwala at Nordel for a casual business meeting. What a perfect place to hangout with friends,
Family and even for business meeting. Great ambience, service and food. It took me back to my back home days to see those Indian softdrinks, biscuits, and snacks. You can have Limca, fanta, Parley cookies and other snacks. Perfect desi feel.

We ordered Coffe, chai, Samosa cones and Bombay sandwitch. I must admit, I haven't found such a good Indian coffee in Surrey so far. Its exactly how we make coffee at back home. Luved it. Also meeting partners said the chai is awesome. Bombay sandwich is typical desi style how they make it in India on road side trucks. Good taste. Samosa are also good but I would say it could have been done better. But not disappointed. So awesome food. They have got many other items to taste but it was my business meeting and could not explore their full menu. Definitely a good place to hangout with friends and family for a tea/coffe and samosa, especially on a Rainy day in Vancouver. They also have special desi style frappuccinos .. must be good choice on a hot  sunny day. thank you Chaiwala for bringing this home experience to us in Surrey. keep growing and we want to see you like another Tim hortons or starbucks. Goodluck.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYwC-K6X0oE0sGxorjy_mho7HdP_IK4rpiK5ww&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-8-1"},{"Name":"Aditi Bhavsar-Vaidya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJfnrP4b6L_aruXJcdyMiWuTJNssQeB-jV5H_Q-V35MXID4oJu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good place to have a quick snack. Food portion is very small. If you are too hungry you might end up ordering 2 3 items!
Food is tasty! We tried Samosa cone, bun omelette, Malai boti naan, chicken tikka naan, breakfast meal, Falooda and chaai ofcourse!
The beans in breakfast meal had too much cinnamon in it so don't quite like the taste. Samosa cone was a hit for us!
Overall good place to hang out with family and friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNM-Yt5KLgPDcQ8s7GqiE3dyENduwpypnFKFWWR&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-7-23"},{"Name":"Ghazal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUxPjakfUDfUlOphLX0NHrhY3j03bOfl1WB2qtK88VIEBoxSUc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice cafe with creative drinks and street food options. It was our first time here and we ordered a cold drink and pani puri. We really like both. They also brought us samples of their hot drinks and we liked the karak chai as well.
Overall good food and great service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfnsfL2Nm3WOQdmooBqx3IgXytNFUdxXLGXMhY&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-6-19"},{"Name":"Rub Nawaz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVLuJJiE7dcIUD2Pb1gMI1AFYespjwRqrT-Gi7aOWncXuojQlYdw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Chaiiwala at their Nordel location while visitng Surry and had an absolutely fantastic experience! The food was incredibly tasty and authentic, with a wide variety of options to choose from. But what really made my visit stand out was the exceptional customer service - the staff were friendly, attentive, and made sure I felt welcome throughout my meal.

To top it all off, the music playing in the background was perfect - it added to the cozy and vibrant atmosphere of the restaurant without being too overpowering.

Overall, I would highly recommend Chaiiwala to anyone looking for delicious food and a great dining experience. I can't wait to go back and try more of their menu items!"","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwu93zLl2k-p5YXvBXflCSL-nFsRAUPjkTPRzl&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Zaheen Brayan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOOSuX6lFg8v7bPiDI_8nRyGbv6FQ4t_15QV-2mkB5F6R9lUcRUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Edit: Chicken in chicken tikka tasted stale. However, I’m not reducing the ratings as it never happened before. Please check and make sure that it doesnt happen.

Best chai in Surrey (or maybe in whole Vancouver!)
May be a bit difficult to find a space to dine in as they have limited seats.
Usually very busy in the weekends. Especially in the night.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYQrb6GZKEbA04tgV0ZPgtdg52bG-Nor7IaOXQ&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-8-21"},{"Name":"salman lalani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKzRjgMCbiCUsN80HctnqUaAn_unicELZ_9XdRGNU3d8EKl4w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had great dine in experience at Chai wala Nordel crossing. Loved the service and ambience was on point. Saleem sir made us laugh and gave us an excellent service. Will definitely recommend!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPb8ZDZ7mQOtEk_L9rUl_v0WfppODZz_tRH6Afj&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"V A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkmGVBCanJaIOvp8G-T0mVOXgfvSnBYnJwvPaqPMYfr6hZtLJeMw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fun little spot, with great food and drinks. The chai and the rose falooda were awesome.
We also got masala fries, samosa chaat and a butter chicken wrap. All of which were awesome.

The service was quick and great. You order at the front and can pick it up when it's ready.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNC_vuIu9ijidYtQ4C-wCtljGIULZLrhdschMOy&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-2-16"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Liana Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBd7Ss8Y7y3H5JQstWWjO4TKz3hKo9b4W72dyZfc4FSDaNq6e4-A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Was passing by and found this place. Tried my friend’s chowmein and it was delicious as well with slightly crispy noodles, a good amount of toppings and a lovely sauce! I would (and will) go back for both items 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSy0d9VBAZZ9sRo0blmHTtSiqxmIqdh9K84p4U\u0026fid=0x0:0x4c48d8ff5b6a58ca"],"When":"2024-5-17"},{"Name":"Nina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFTJTkcu4fmSUxBDu1STzFKa5Xg2-CR_8RBXSF9SW7RRkySC0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Got the Pad See Ew, total came down to $14.50. Good value and really tasty noodles. It was just the right texture and the sauce was flavourful but not too salty. Had that stir fry hot wok charred flavour that added this slight smokiness and was very good. I’ve been to the one downtown and it’s pretty consistent with the other location.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6Ta4mfnmbIarlgIk2hBzoQunkVifleCO3kFi6\u0026fid=0x0:0x4c48d8ff5b6a58ca"],"When":"2023-2-3"},{"Name":"Tony Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPKcy0N8L_e03kCanD-kbqBYJvghgec1_Wu16Qs-S8YjI-PLg2nw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Everything is delicious. That said, please add Thai Basil with Rice to your menu. Would love to have Thai Basil Beef or Chicken on rice. Tried the Kung Pao Chicken and loved it. The sauce is really delicious and is a must-try. The Pad See Ew is my favorite but the Pad Thai is good too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO6_XEm0w0U9VK67VZhJrYwpfn9Z_fHlrAwtg0Y\u0026fid=0x0:0x4c48d8ff5b6a58ca"],"When":"2023-10-24"},{"Name":"Tony Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf8VP49ZjSvgG0JnhT1tc6Tv6OzLL9YEi_yNvwH1rW_K8-7VE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This is an excellent place for an authentic meal. I wished there was one in Tsawwassen! It's fast because the wok is hot and everything is portioned control. You pick a dish, choose the protein and the heat level. I usually go with a 3 and my tongue is still intact. Tried a 5 once and it burned a hole on my tongue so watch yourself. Had almost everything on the menu and found the taste and quality to be excellent. They use fresh ingredients, and is not overly salty or greasy. Highly recommend #1, 2 and the Kung Pao Chicken.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Blessed\u0026lovely Lily Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBpM_hXxO2W4mWo2Apy4_LV_Yb0NKCg_EJ1ElrK-yH2X18sOCG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super clean and excellent service! The fried rice noodles was sweet and delicious for a cold day. Very grateful for the vegetarian options.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lucy Yep.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWyWEm1iVA5BhD52EO30x5805b5fs28qVCdlDvtJbrD1_d2ndv1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is great for dine in or take out. The staff is friendly and fast. The food comes in big portions and you have the option to select zero spicy or super spicy. It is the first time I see that option so I give an extra point to them. Easy to find parking. 100% recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtVl3uWPr57d13diDyAiPKyXCk3KCH5LRn2EYY\u0026fid=0x0:0x4c48d8ff5b6a58ca"],"When":"2023-4-25"},{"Name":"Ryan Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXemItCa5GMwKSxcqFJ30tQRTmnAIRcGqxKZfopnc7WWK0KUyAD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was the best pod thai ive ever tasted so far, affordable price but the amount of food i was given was dope, the restaurant was clean and even the employees were kind","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJyhAR4OHmJ3vHWCROHurGaMig1_qxZL5h2j1I\u0026fid=0x0:0x4c48d8ff5b6a58ca"],"When":"2024-2-4"}]

[{"Name":"Shakhawat Hossain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj82Rw5TJH3Le4DVawG-AUG1veXD6bQXDq6jJZAyEkjbjh2JO9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We tried the chicken biryani, which came with two pieces of chicken, shami kebab, and borhani for $14. The borhani had the authentic taste of Bangladeshi biye barir style, which was a lovely detail! We also ordered the half portion of tehari for $7, and it had a very generous serving. Both dishes were made with polaor Chal, which was well-cooked and full of flavor. Overall, we were very pleased with the quality and portion sizes. I really hope this Bangladeshi restaurant stays around!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfNRDthM_46JLy-Iv77N7g9kVaGZRsdZZTwTJ3&fid=0x0:0x6b762b8fb576daa"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"Md Khan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXC4M18l8R_PYe61dyUTvGkgpbVYIHk3kcsWiEyfOUQeATnQsh8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had great experience at Mia Mia this weekend as we went to taste Bengali food. We ordered beef tehari, chicken biriyani, kabab, burhani, and tea. It was not surprising that the food quality and taste was A class because one of the owners/partners of Mia Mia has international cuisine expertise with long experience in culinary art. Good portion of food, reasonable price and fast service. The server and other members were super friendly and very welcoming. Lots of free parking and very conveniently located at the heart of Surrey. A must try place. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP99ye11j2nxRnKi9jXjac4f_8u9Pg1HW9dJMuS&fid=0x0:0x6b762b8fb576daa"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Tanzina Islam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHin0i0PTPm3-Og3CIoFbjHaIuxwcsLJfLsXm1yQ5BTP0mNLM7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing amazing Bengali food!!! The breakfast is the best I have to say. The chicken platter is a sweet creamy korma and the beef is fabulously hot and spicy! 🔥The vegetable took me back to authentic Bangali hotel breakfast back home.  Generous portion, AND COMES WITH COMPLEMENTARY TEA. ☕️❤️ Must must visit. Breakfast only on weekends! Stays super busy, so plan ahead to go earlier in the morning!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNT4IHLRgQqr6gJEhiR9QBweV_Box5aLjxvjPV2&fid=0x0:0x6b762b8fb576daa"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Md Fazley Rabby Khan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJZ2YY4au-50gbKmHlxD0UPJJkXj3tZNawIy0kFw1LA5i-6tQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mia Mia Donair and Grill offers a cozy spot to enjoy authentic Bangladeshi flavors! The staff’s warm, friendly service makes you feel right at home. Each dish, from biryani to kebabs, is packed with traditional spices and freshness, showcasing true Bangladeshi culinary passion. With a comfortable seating setup perfect for small groups, it’s a go-to place for a delicious and welcoming dining experience. Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjVlC6ufFJdLqQQywjoI9rS0g-N0kK5FIpbHv4&fid=0x0:0x6b762b8fb576daa"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"fardin siddiky","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWyo_LdhLY6sNlHuJfc--o9yUN_PLiiTXo266yQGW1xSwxWvRuvxg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mia & Mia Donair - A Taste of Bangladesh in Every Bite

If you’re craving an authentic taste of Bangladeshi cuisine, Mia & Mia Donair is a must-visit. Recently taken over by new Bengali owners, this spot has infused traditional Bangladeshi flavors into every dish, bringing a refreshing and delectable twist to their menu.

The star of the show is undoubtedly their biryani, which is rich, fragrant, and deeply flavorful—each bite transports you straight to Dhaka. The chicken polaw is another standout, perfectly cooked with tender, juicy pieces of chicken amidst aromatic chinigura rice. And then there’s the borhani—a refreshing, tangy, and mildly spiced yogurt drink that’s simply the best accompaniment to the meal. It balances out the spices and adds a unique touch to the experience.

With warm hospitality and truly authentic flavors, Mia & Mia Donair is an excellent spot for anyone looking to indulge in Bangladeshi cuisine. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3ep9_3L3NlehQGn1y27pHa31XAM6HN1i-qR4F&fid=0x0:0x6b762b8fb576daa"],"When":"2024-10-27"},{"Name":"Arman fayez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiwEjBAM6WpabiC7--N7OzvDeuHSyddolaob94DM7qlsyyft0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food! Great place to eat!

Loved the chicken roast combined with pulao! The borhani hits the perfect spot! Its great to see how they represent authentic Bangladeshi cuisine ❤️ It’s a bit on the corner, would appreciate if they had more locations within the mainland.

Much love and support for the place!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3-KTrJCy1etLCYTXGI5KoPQV9XhJSO7IXF6dF&fid=0x0:0x6b762b8fb576daa"],"When":"2024-10-31"},{"Name":"Farhana Naznin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAnswi7rg7Kb6mxYG8xN1mxlcc2dAyL_EUItgQTqH6ko4OsY04=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing Bangladeshi food… went for breakfast… it was awesome and reasonable price. Also took the parcel for polao-roast combo, authentic Bangladeshi taste","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM--w1VcHStuiTgTNsMLd106TFa-f-onU3l7AX6&fid=0x0:0x6b762b8fb576daa"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"IR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ50LUWBgvjOkvHbu9_O-JapNBna7XhNHrv3aAnx1BeQzysxfE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Happy to have an authentic deshi restaurant. We ordered the Tehari meal combo and chicken biryani combo. The basmati rice in the tehari was slightly overcooked but the flavour of both dishes was good overall and the borhani was great. Service needs to be improved, we had to ask for everything cutlery, water, refills, napkins and extra plates.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN861xk2I5U7bppfwE0XRns35hlHKIeFrSxA5oD&fid=0x0:0x6b762b8fb576daa"],"When":"2024-11-5"}]

They used to be good but not anymore, there are way better places who will listen to customer.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcA1127hFqBgJ-ArQoqbpqkEtMstz2NLaw9a1a&fid=0x0:0xc34a4aa203c9f83d"],"When":"2024-12-7"},{"Name":"Sandra Tran Do","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9l6s1YZWB64Ki1thgUudvXKddmLpHe47fEzkyE5Wrayj1VfeG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I'm a Vietnamese foodie, when I heard about this place I just had to go try it

Would come back to try more food :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5O7eS0rSJ79idbDOoAiU1X15etmdm787GN3HV&fid=0x0:0xc34a4aa203c9f83d"],"When":"2024-12-5"},{"Name":"Pooja Jain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLoijTO-Lk55aRsErHcFNOKDM9e7vTR9eBb10OkJGOedR5BcA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered the chaat platter which had dahi puri, aloo tikki, papri chaat and bhel puri. I highly recommend everyone visit Desi Rasoi!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Akshay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGdG4K1g--zDRRQKvTXxJZtBDkS7hJ7B1hRUaBBg_pquB_7pU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Amazing place to eat the Indian street food. Their chaat items are second to none. We tried the pani puri and it’s a must try. One more thing which is totally worth it is the Paneer Noodle Burger.
