user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jay Swackhamer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoZ_wv1qiAi4KdqsYmTyxBMiU8sQ2GWvYO6Jr1f4H_xi_xiOM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It’s sushi. It’s “all you can eat” (*)

Every plate was good and well-presented. Service was friendly and fine. Quality was okay. Rolls were good, nice quality to the rice.

Sashimi was pretty small chunks — probably due to the “20 pieces per person” limit (*).

* typical state of the “sushi buffet” these days. Smaller portions, same price.

Nothing against Nordel Sushi, prices have gone up a lot (doubled!!) in just the last 3-4 years. Gone are the days of actually “unlimited” sashimi of high quality.  The quality of the AYCE menu here was “sufficient” but I wouldn’t say as good as times past. But since there’s such a dearth of quality sushi buffet places, I have no real complaints here, it is what it is now.

I would I come back? Not for the AYCE. I’d probably come back to try the a la Carte menu instead, which may be better value/quality.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMziNRaMe-l_3C-FfvzwLdwhenhvRjFx2mix0gZ&fid=0x0:0xbae6aeffcd1b7d0"],"When":"2024-9-10"},{"Name":"Denise Knauer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7AxkMI0ZXwyViMlCuoRJl_IXUEpXeOkBTeu91MLXTGLUteDj-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Unbelievably horrible customer service!  We've been coming here for years, and it's generally been pretty good. Today, however, was a different story.
We spent over $90 for dinner, and it was extremely disappointing and a waste of money, to say the least. We ordered a few items, including a Cali Roll Combo and Crunchy Cali Rolls with brown rice and real crab. The Cali Rolls in the combo had brown, old avocado and the Nigiri Tuna tasted off and very fishy.The Crunchy Cali Rolls tasted off, with a nasty sour taste.  Both left such a foul taste in our mouths, I'm waiting to see if we get food poisoning (fingers crossed that doesn't happen).
When I phoned and told them about our experience, I was told that there was nothing they could do for us. He said if there was anything significantly wrong with our order, he could give us a refund, but because it only tasted foul, he couldn't do anything for us.   They had apparently been serving these dishes all day, and no one else complained, so too bad. I said that was disappointing and we would find a new sushi place, to which he responded, "OK, bye."  Apparently they're not too upset or worried about losing faithful customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUZ33kEbtOjto5tIeikNPQK8mNCTxD11OAZ9RZ&fid=0x0:0xbae6aeffcd1b7d0"],"When":"2024-8-15"},{"Name":"Tess Hildebrand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJuanHbzMa_LrfMx102cX4d_u_8flJPfZXTrFCcVJCoyyvwDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Today was our third visit to this place, and I really love the aesthetic of the place and it was neat having a nearby AYCE place, but the food has been hit and miss and today was the most egrigious. We were served rancid salmon - I thought it had just been stained by the lettuce somehow but it was black on the inside and had a rancid smell. The staff was entirely unapologetic about serving me food poisoning on a plate. Honestly I regret tipping at all.
Needless to say we won't be back, as I'm now questioning the way their kitchen is managed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOp7dThPmP0zhCF9CJujWqfI3iLb_9AuQ037cN2&fid=0x0:0xbae6aeffcd1b7d0"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"Lala B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJgajmLwMBgGE9264N-jfBkh9m_ivt1oXmNtZY-maZnh6HJLU0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This was the smallest and worst nigiri I ever had. For $17, that's insane! It tasted awful too. You could get better at a grocery store :( to make matters worse, the lunch set next to it was $15.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPNPChAJDZyACVGgl430ozpSzMcIIesyaCgXb_a&fid=0x0:0xbae6aeffcd1b7d0"],"When":"2024-9-12"},{"Name":"Terrill Lyngen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVpaF5MBLC6tJzaPrc78Mx7uXvKYwG_JuMSyBlKDQ1ZzIUjgePG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Rotten avocado in my last order of California rolls, very disappointed.

I have eaten here many times in the past. It has been a while due to Skip the Dishes boycott, but I was in the area so I did a pickup order. The order was done on time, as it always has been. Service was fine. Prices are fine.

The food has always been a bit on the quickly made side but the prices were good enough so no complaints. Rolls are often a little inconsistent but portions were fine.

This time though, rotten avocado in multiple California rolls bought for my kids! Lots of dark spots and dark areas, some maybe from contact with nori but some clearly not. It was so bad I had to pick through everything to make sure food was safe to eat. It really ruined my experience and broke my trust. This much brown avocado would have been quite obvious to the chef, so no excuse IMO.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7qPOQfxHd_DOwx7Am8VoSQF0ADvVXOt4PxZZz&fid=0x0:0xbae6aeffcd1b7d0"],"When":"2023-10-15"},{"Name":"Victor Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMFE5BNhgNfk5RtFjElijU5COak-F8KWg7vkC2eOWy-GXpNlUM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been wanting to check this place out for a while. I finally got the chance and I'm not disappointed. Came here at 4pm on a Wednesday and got the AYCE Dinner menu.

I don't get why other reviewers had a bad impression about this place, but I didn't see anything that was a major concern. On the contrary, it's one of the better AYCE sushi places I've been too. Sure the sushi might seemed like it had more rice to them (not all rolls, but some), but this is a AYCE place. You won't find a AYCE/Buffet that doesn't add extra starch or whatnot to bulk up the food. The sashimi is limited to 20 pieces per person and a bit smaller then the usual gigantic pieces and the negiri is definitely half the size of a regular piece you'd find anywhere else; the fish/topping they don't skimp on either. The tempura is crispy/crunchy, the prawns are regular sized and the yam are half pieces. The gyoza was nicely crispy as well. Personally, I would get the chicken teriyaki. I was hoping for a more crispy skin, but it fell flat when it arrived to the table; it could've been the sauce though, but the chicken did seem a little dry/tough.

When I think of this place now, I think of sensible/petite pieces. Which is great because it gives you a chance to try other things on the menu. The service was quick and the servers are attentive. The best thing is they don't even skimp on your food. I've gone to many other AYCEs and when you order, you're missing a few items; hoping they you eventually forget. This place doesn't do that. They give you everything you order.

Overall, a very good experience and I recommend you check it out if you have a hankering for Japanese food. I'll definitely be back in the future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHVUVgNqPgi7AzBh04eT7xScIjalP8gqxI0wUE&fid=0x0:0xbae6aeffcd1b7d0"],"When":"2024-2-22"},{"Name":"Betty Orellana Murcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcu6WKHpuVOgrfNampCwsacpBebTY8L5h4jd9AMWFBpcWJweAvAA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of my families favourite restaurants! We plan our family gatherings there... have been going for as long as they have been open. Fresh delicious food and the quality is always on point... service is consistency great. 10☆'s time and time again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark Sousa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJL64vmJI8H6IV3Yj-EVNVpxIn9ywLLjw0dRXEkD0rjpQcC-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been coming to Nordal sushi for at least 20 years! That on its own says a lot, quality has been on point since day one. I live in Chilliwack now and still drive out to Surrey to go to Nordel Sushi.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM2-7ifbzx4OFpO5rIVtb-a2LN7x7W1rv_YdFwv&fid=0x0:0xbae6aeffcd1b7d0"],"When":"2024-6-18"}]

[{"Name":"Kaiti Luyt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6yOScSyx0mctSBHf70jnx-vlzy4EB9gjzKXJZfHbHC35asPNR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing meal at Ramie’s last night. This family-owned gem has recently opened a second location in Delta, and I’m so glad we gave it a try. Initially, I was a bit uncertain about the location, but it turned out to be absolutely worth it- and we’ll be back.

The food was delicious. The beef souvlaki was melt-in-your-mouth, and the portions were generous. My husband, who’s a big eater, had leftovers for the first time in history. The prices were very reasonable for the quality and quantity.

We also had the opportunity to take a peak at their newly renovated private room upstairs, which is available for rent. Seems like a great spot for a social gathering or work party.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNEF0bwypD9QGsSh6hZatC5Yo0vnPOchwPfmSXi&fid=0x0:0xa75fe21e2adf8a11"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"Leslie Gilker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmai_3H3HwS9svez3CowLlSmWqOxBDd7lXlUwqseaCZnolLw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Tasty meal, good portions and great prices on their wine. Nice to try a new place and close to home on a rainy cold evening.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPflYGuAZP_5gbsTfBuD06XdnsjiB36dR2DNnVR&fid=0x0:0xa75fe21e2adf8a11"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"L Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNXnB0qZV3V6VvXHSvI5L_5FB2A7crO3fFgJGGxEYx2B1_XBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This Greek restaurant has been here for a long time, but seems to be under new management as of late September. The food is excellent, the portions are generous, the service is great (shout-out to our server, Kirsten, for taking such good care of us), and the prices are quite reasonable. I have had two excellent business lunches there, and went initially on the recommendation of a family member who indicated her dinner experience was superb. The prawn souvlaki is excellent, but isn't on the list of dishes to recommend below.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jefray Magnusentosa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTJd1UTjgkSA4SqpXx8pkrkS04FkVspsUZlT_XZ-4g_PfSJA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"best Greek in lower mainland with best taste and best professional customer service, foods very fast to arrives. Restaurant ambiance is like in a fancy premium restaurant but with reasonable prices. Try their Greek style back ribs and it was top notch! Will definitely return to try their other menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMg0g0qrl1tNsM1E2cCgKmOOXyi-FFqMSQ610Uy&fid=0x0:0xa75fe21e2adf8a11"],"When":"2024-1-8"},{"Name":"Debbie Cullen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpXJDxvfJVaBFAt1Jx2Yts3y75HqDad13DwrvCEz8i2tpwAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was our 2nd visit to the Delta location & it didn't disappoint. Spanakopita dinner is so delicious, best I've ever had. Our waitress was Kirsten, an absolutely delightful & efficient server. Lovely atmosphere too, we'll be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"James Adegboye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZ0nofPFbCsKol6tk2QNNP_y98-xtP9FSoEHYf9Rz-7efyJ4xMDg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Seems like a family run restaurant because it felt homely. The food was good and affordable. I had the lamb souvlaki and I really can't complain. The waitress was very welcoming. The atmosphere was quiet so my friend and I could talk. They close early so you have to get there early","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2CIZz3koGf1MEVio-7buStyCPF0fgoiACkOEr&fid=0x0:0xa75fe21e2adf8a11"],"When":"2024-2-4"},{"Name":"Bella Marcellana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuNMsxjNQj4k3CDfGFcZW5BKv4g7-4u08Ctu57vopTUSMImPMH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We drove from Vancouver to Delta for this place and it did not disappoint. They were understaffed but we didn’t mind because we were just so excited to try something new. It was wednesday night so we got the date night special for only $65. The keftedes & calamari were so delicious and the ambiance was beautiful. Can’t wait to go back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPOnq3eamvECtfaqkkJFXiGkK1KfZh_TCtY-zUU&fid=0x0:0xa75fe21e2adf8a11"],"When":"2023-5-26"},{"Name":"Paul Yang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXn3m0AZWl28VYBOwUKfmGVllVddsvt-pe4tcU6-ebIHORKGYiIPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We arrived around 7:20 ish and were rejected to dine in since they said the restaurant closed at 7:30pm. The sign on the door and internet both shows 8pm to be the closing time.

Anyway, we ordered take out. The food quality and portions will have a solid 7/10.

PS: It seems like every 5 star review will receive a Starbucks gift card from the restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpHxqXnLGcWmkoMC4VuNna7Olf-S29OAvJnLeI&fid=0x0:0xa75fe21e2adf8a11"],"When":"2023-5-14"}]

[{"Name":"Sid.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMVJfFKKNH06AFhoNA4iVipFBVdseDesi9j-4WBkSI8OGEgbvW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I really appreciate the food they provide.
Every day, as I head home, I eagerly look forward to discovering what delightful dishes await in my tiffin.
Theirs food is consistently delicious and delectable.
I highly recommend for vegetarian and vegan to choose Bamon's","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adiba Muzaffar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuDQMjCZ29lDnoOzwczNSayn7fDGmqSVWxKC40X2KlmScasbtUTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm a new customer for Bamon's Kitchen, and I have opted for their 3 days/week meal plan. I have been very happy with their menu, their service and the responsiveness over email. For me some of these factors come first and foremost as I wanted a reliable meal delivery service.

Now, coming to the food itself- the dishes have all been consistently good. I'm happy to say that the food isn't greasy (as a lot of other options I tried would always be), it isn't overly spicy and each dish is distinct.

The options are all vegetarian, yet there is a diversity to the combinations of vegetables. The dals have also been a broad set, and they don't rely on intense flavours.

I can vouch for the fact that the chef at work really knows what he is working with. Thank you for the wonderful food and service so far, and good luck to the team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Suhas Uppin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkDnYjGkhzsKLus7CXaIsz06j3OfXzSUsbOHMLMnjxMQursLoF=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I’ve had multiple issues with deliveries not following instructions. Despite repeatedly requesting that the driver call me if there is no parking and that I would personally collect the food, my order was left near the buzzer without any notification. As a result, I missed the delivery and my food. This lack of attention to detail is frustrating and disappointing. I hope the company addresses this issue to improve their service, but as of now, I can't recommend them based on my experience.
I missed my food on last day as well( happened twice in a month) and didn't got compensation.
Food is average Delivery is pathetic.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4n_r8bRReeRi7_l48bM97OBnGItSUrozAb9PO&fid=0x0:0x338123af90eac97e"],"When":"2024-8-21"},{"Name":"tanmay Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-Lzy5G3y1H6AdFjPFiPmXao241cfX9ZL9p-jqo1yVfWMRmbR-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wanted to take a moment to express my gratitude for your amazing and delicious tiffin service. Among all the options I’ve tried, your meals stand out as the best! Whenever I have guests over, they always ask where I get such amazing food, and I never hesitate to recommend your service. In fact, several of my friends have started ordering from you as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yash Shah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUSrimn-algwsuH-Yup0zPJsAoS2ufT2Rn3OBkayXTmyhPdKMzmkw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food is great—less oily and just right. No complaints about the quality. However, I’m giving 2 stars less because our deliveries usually arrived after 2 PM, which was super late. This might be because I’m at the end of their delivery route, so not everyone might experience the same issue. Worth trying if the timing works for you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hari Kansal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZcEO19VQRatz9F93tFllkLlJuQuZnUsZAD7PNMg14xPUgkw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bamon’s Kitchen always delivers on great tasting and unique food, both on the tiffin and their newly launched UberEats takeout (or pickup yourself).

We bought 8 items from the take-out menu to eat in the comfort of our home in Burnaby and we loved them all. Veggie burger combo, Philly cheez sandwich (my favorite, see photo), Gujarati samosa, Punjabi samosa, Manchurian + fried rice, noodles with veggie pork, masala fries, and chilli chicken drumsticks (also incredible).

We had a wonderful variety meal, in great quantities, that tasted so delicious and was so fresh.

We will definitely be buying all these items again, and we still have more than 2/3rd of the menu to try!

Bamon’s Kitchen is a new family favorite 🎉","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgK9o2dnUI4gt6WSkJxF-HhZ1kGL46tLXO1fBQ&fid=0x0:0x338123af90eac97e"],"When":"2023-7-2"},{"Name":"Pratibha Umrariya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtPoZ5MQ8rRFy9qH3kxZi0RPs6yO2GrUhEks6wCD6V0nLdhIL6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently tried their lunch tiffin service and was very happy with the quality, variety and the portion sizes of the food. Everything is vegetarian and well made, home cooked food. I found their pricing is very reasonable and everything was well packaged in recyclable packaging. I am a picky eater but still found their food to be excellent. Definitely worth it to order from them instead of going through the hassle of cooking, especially if  you are a student or like me; recovering from childbirth.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jen G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_xHNPCGOksvG7r_6gmg3vstbGSF_01XgrdOGYFrYwwMYs7qQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious affordable home cooked meals delivered to your door step in Vancouver. This feels like a dream. The team is prompt and courteous, and are quick to correct any errors too. Thanks, team Bamon! I only wish I knew about you earlier!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"John Zak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiUYxjhD0zZyZkWLf0O-qFesnil2TXcRXcDvPfM5yIp3krrPI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I’ve been coming to Tidewaters Pub for about 3 years off and on with friends to watch UFC fights, but after today, I’ll never return. My partner and I drove all the way from Vancouver to watch the advertised UFC event, which you confirmed both on posters and over the phone. After sitting for 30 minutes waiting for the fights to come on, the waitress told us there was a “mistake” and that you may not be getting the fights after all. Soon after, she stood awkwardly by the entrance as the channel switched to football instead.

To the owner: Was saving $70 worth more than keeping loyal customers? The service was unprofessional, and your failure to honor your advertisement ruined what was supposed to be a great event. We had to leave and go somewhere else, only catching a few fights of what was an amazing card. You’ve lost three potential lifetime customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLAplmuqDRUo7m3Sjt7U6LXuOWAuAl0f_VTfGh&fid=0x0:0x8f42765e4e33be26"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Thomas Webb","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIG2rUdfdVayGjk-HyxI4bVkd14Qji7qcSfebB4nd2zWFS27w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"They had a prime rib special. I could not have fed it to my dog!
Tough and full of grizzle. Less than a half inch thick and tough as nails. We complained as did the folks around us. Left hungry. They took our meals off the bill but gave us a lame excuse about the meat.
A real cook would have refused to serve it.
Very disappointed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Proctor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUU4reTki5_DKZ68y-D-U91LkDlip7ln3Ocfw5-ZSYEfQqSejCW2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time here since it was rebuilt. Nice open modern concept, great staff. Food was exceptional. Our server Devyn was upbeat & friendly. Little hidden gem under the Alex Fraser Bridge. Most definitely return.
The old pub was more like a house. Had a great patio off the back with horshoe pits. Sundays were breakfast buffets. A perfect way to cure the cause 🍻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNeS9SMa0xH4FanDo3Ys67jJJR4Xf3rldX55leB&fid=0x0:0x8f42765e4e33be26"],"When":"2023-5-6"},{"Name":"Suman Bilkhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgOEqlVcR-SHJwu_c7T9FCQhKLIbhYsmGic_lANm34xi4hCfo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"No one seated us we were told to sit anywhere but there was no available seats..so we awkwardly waited around..sanitizing could be done better as well.. Calamari was good..wings were ok.  The burgers were underwhelming..the smallest underdressed burgers we have ever had at a restaurant!  1 slice of tomato and a single leaf of lettuce with a couple of onion slices..the smallest by and smallest piece of salmon..chicken from the chicken burger was nice and juicy though.. definitely not worth the price you pay..I make bigger better burgers at home :( do not recommend..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqV-99Wjro_MHA7jCBQRfL87u9aHr9e_kHplLI&fid=0x0:0x8f42765e4e33be26"],"When":"2020-11-24"},{"Name":"Crystal R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_nxdLIQfssGlpPXMfFbkpP82SZjuMBG0bae_WoDvcJnyOM6Eu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Nice pub with nothing else close by. Service and food was slow. Food was mediocre but typical pub food. Heard the pizzas were good though. Will try that next time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angela Jeffery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtGyld6d4wIU2Lb7oe7xsoiq4r77iaBdF6nkFQ8ek01eF1q7c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A bit difficult to get to especially when Google maps says turn right off the bridge. Lol. You need to exit for River Road.
Clean, bright, TVs weren't too loud so you could have a conversation, and nice server. Fries were amazing; fluffy inside and crispy outside. As a poutine they were good too, but had mozzarella cheese instead of true cheese curds. Hawaiian chicken burger was good. Reuben was great. Granville Island Winter Ale on tap is always a win.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMU9TiBvrrFknYUQJFcims3_TdAhpAXDC7YNztC&fid=0x0:0x8f42765e4e33be26"],"When":"2019-11-18"},{"Name":"Pixie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPQUjFSbkcAo6EvYOja47J4GX0ejm240O00cyAhKVz3-pSo_Qi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their nachos are delicious. Friendly staff, great service, always a pleasure.
Great variety of dishes. All so tastey.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN43dxSLSwjOzJ6h_zUH43anAgFblPMtfKM-eRr&fid=0x0:0x8f42765e4e33be26"],"When":"2021-9-12"},{"Name":"Monika Dean","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnFA3HgIab-NpASiEI9eKQ2eoN5GXH1ujtzJHiG3V4yJlOKpDG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service, and excellent happy hour menu 3-6 pm, with some items half price. The beer selection will hopefully improve, but I'm happy with the Stanley Park Amber. They've only been open 4 months, but hope to get things like trivia and live bands. Wednesday through Sunday nights can get really busy. It's nice to finally have a great pub back in this neighbourhood!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRYgZGyO8IxR-Gcx4M-ozmlYJv8I6EPmf2Ibjl&fid=0x0:0x8f42765e4e33be26"],"When":"2017-3-3"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Nathan Woods","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYlKwIGO9PHjqLgc7mRGN7qYIzJ_Yb1JOij4343pL12ye4fG4D-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Gotta say, hugely disappointed.

I ordered the simplest thing, Chicken Strips, in the 1st period. Halfway thru the 3rd, even after asking about them in the 2nd, I got nothing.

Funny thing is, against my anti tip culture for service that doesn't really provide service (this is walk up service) I gave 15% tip.

Exasperated, I asked for a refund, they gave it to me, but kept the tip...

Don't expect stellar service, perhaps don't even expect service...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNH2Djeiq8EVsLIRuJCr0QeP7Xt473HwWxw1stu&fid=0x0:0xd131c3be079520e"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Sarah HANNOU","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQX2z45WwD0hzxpFqSQJZOqDrOt1Df2EUd7mXfxRf0wpaAe9km=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time here and will be back!
The butter chicken was good, a little too spicy for me but the cook gave me some sour cream... I do appreciate the gesture and attentionate service!
Thank you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHJ2Rohb4LH74NNJrAAh0KKn3VXamOMyWxdZBi&fid=0x0:0xd131c3be079520e"],"When":"2023-11-1"},{"Name":"Amanda Blair","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBKFBw8SroBAGXNKvzouMmO8fdZe7vuOXyQlpvzAw4a6qHwY1MXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Muni* and staff are great. Great beer choices
(Four Winds IPA) food is good. Great place to watch the game of choice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN4FKHr2TcHuKVOzO6BbGNtbrOXoLfnEXoSgaDA&fid=0x0:0xd131c3be079520e"],"When":"2019-2-7"},{"Name":"Don Brecknell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIq7vPBaLZzmFmQYMVY4Zwrk3hZpaVy4f2Z65du7bJ40zsJ9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Waiter was brisk but cheerie but that’s where it ended meaning the food was looked unappealing with no taste or wierd flavor ie pizza then my fish was mostly batter little fish barely cooked so out of six orders only the chiken fingers n burger were without complaint
Very dissappointed","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Donna Vital","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWznp7NUh9jGhisskg6IpFyxqVxlW120LfYnoCoMKI2GOWNwmc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My daughter has played at Tilbury for years. For the last couple years we have regular scheduled practices on Tuesdays - which we (as adults) look forward to and call ‘Tilbury Tuesday’. The parents head upstairs for dinner, laughs and wait for our kids to join us after they practice. Patricia and her staff are fantastic - even remembering what we order and how we like it. BTW - BEST burger you’ll ever have! Thank you for years of outstanding service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brittany Malcolm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5LCsCjTHJvCCC_WseHPQJ4691cQzdvPUMY93TmU61PbfjyA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love this place! Warm and welcoming and go above and beyond for me and my kids every time we come in. We are in our 6th season of hockey and always look forward to our tilbury games and practices so we can eat and enjoy the atmosphere. The food is good and the staff is friendly, hard working and I continue to be impressed by how they handle the busy times and quick turnovers between ice times.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"charlie75meep","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKwYvvk-RDg2_p5lhcfW8LVi1SP7xOZdvvzXbcEScz3vOYSzpx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place for a good lunch/ dinner. Great staff, Owner is a very good guy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Morris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLwrINq5lT8oIFaKRsb9wQ5-qyPksj4ZX06EhtbdPd9WlY_AQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing staff! Go see Patricia and Muni. Great food and cheap prices! Also great atmosphere and authentic memorabilia hanging on the wall. Definitely a great spot to check out when you're in the area!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfLIEWYtQwvYysgCamZfUInt8VzNTZID_h0zCS&fid=0x0:0xd131c3be079520e"],"When":"2019-3-15"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Thomas Bailey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTKkME-Q5GL4N0GqIXgcKUsJmB0aY5YRo3WP6FidA2N4mL7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience at Bread and Cheese today, ordered the brie, fig and chicken sandwich with yam fries. Adrian was very friendly and personable. This should be your go-to stop when on Annacis Island.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mr. Beaver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWL3M8ZH3qEl_RyevO5nyLbhHPG0gb_f64YALWS11Pc92lQ0bBO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got the fried chicken and rice and honestly I think they cook better asian dishes than me and I'm Korean. Overall a solid restaurant and I can see myself becoming a regular.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqh3dT-ya9Vvaewhg26d5K0uAl219YYOgZOcCP\u0026fid=0x0:0x233d8126f42ef4a8"],"When":"2023-3-2"},{"Name":"Arshdeep Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBqu95-EQDC3uBV92WU-hjwJigkDkihleuzPYY1djx0k6ic2lz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Butter chicken poutine was okay. [{"Name":"Jimmy Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLtZ_12Qqd38lcoE8CQYPcOlH7Krj0MiA1S2C2AEdJbecnrCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Got chicken rice plate. Other than that i enjoyed it. Tasty. Top 5 donair of the 30+ places Ive had. Place is clean","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNrh_V4k-qjlehTyfrmMxyWteuq72KeYjATtnpL&fid=0x0:0x4a3cf0895297c2e6"],"When":"2024-8-1"},{"Name":"Harshul Madaan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmLcj7SjBXRN4Nzp-LRDsRqI6MSnBK5ZBjjAQbAqGg0QETrrI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have never had a better Donair . The new management has improved the taste of the food immensely. The customer service is top notch. Staff is friendly","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNeFmTFdE_SMkEYWP-1Vp1V9bj5ZdjuRffZ5aU&fid=0x0:0x4a3cf0895297c2e6"],"When":"2024-7-9"},{"Name":"Robinpreet K.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwt2iVvWAHle0yzZU372jAa2r2We_tqhFSCMEbHLTtc0ixfFM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had Donair Bite cater for our office, and the food was fantastic! The meats were tender, and everything was fresh and hot. We ordered rice platters, chips with hummus, and the portions were generous—our employees even took leftovers home. Great quality, great pricing, and highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"PARNEET KAUR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEEPVdBd7GknxoXFap1bv6Z6GMdOxFKTSHsdid7dxbpLUB3Zg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently ordered food from Donair Bite, and it was absolutely fantastic! The flavors were fresh, delicious, and perfectly seasoned.
The donair was packed with juicy, tender meat, crisp vegetables, and the sauce was perfectly balanced-not too sweet, not too overpowering. The portion sizes were generous, leaving me completely satisfied.
Beyond the food, the service was quick and friendly, and the overall experience was great. If you're craving a high-quality donair or any tasty meal, I highly
recommend checking out Donair Bite. I'll definitely be returning for more!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Priya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnPugMJUYNWTF7dVlrE9Cg4VZLyx474-PkMJW__55FAtcWkQU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I tried falafel and chicken platter of this place. I can say I never had this much good, fresh, and delicious food from a donair place. Chicken was crispy and juicy. Atmosphere and staff of this place also very nice. This place is highly recommended if you want good quality and quantity of food between $10-20.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Deep Gill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZVLGMHMUZAYCxMMueVKgssKT4TQJ5m_MkImESlHT-bTNh1ZWd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"16 dollar for this, subway is better than for this, you will get at least good quantity","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7O7GewuANrcpfORdIktovf0mvzt5VOOOB9Hkh&fid=0x0:0x4a3cf0895297c2e6"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Ramon Carfrae","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbjvo-PB7ZluRHdv76jBuAd7OTik1mTEXOQPMPuCJOV2Ov4A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time going to this place today and it was delicious. I really hope they keep their quality of food and service as time goes on because this place is on my route and I loved the food today. The woman working there was friendly and professional.

I have been checking out a lot of Donair places lately and this one is in my top 3!

mmm mmm!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A Z (futyh_ag)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5cJP6wFheKfz62vSlcPb207ZDQuO80KTxeX1k1o7FblbZGcZosQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Something definitely happened here. It used to be my favourite donair in Vancouver. I drove all the way back to get a chicken donair since I’m no longer working on the island. Unfortunately, it just tastes so not good as before. The chicken is dry, it’s not juicy and chewy anymore. I don’t know if it is overcooked or just the ingredients are not as fresh as before. Sauce is less. Lettuce are not well separated. Veggies, meat and sauce are not well mixed. The price is still the same, but quality is a lot lower. It definitely doesn’t deserve my time drive back.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Clam chowder that has no cream, crab wrap drown in wasabi. If you're open to spend a bit more, Hadis is right across the street. If you're not looking to spend more, canco gas station on the corner has heavenly pizza slices.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ps H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWZH4u5uxDfJNhnL_l8W1S4uIzr1H4HDeoj_eCHzg7xFQspTGN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ordered the Bibimbap - it was yummy, and very filling.  Good portions of each component.  The spinach was a little tough in the way that spinach sometimes gets.  I wish the egg had been over-easy, but that's just personal preference.  I have no similar bibimbap to compare this one too, but I will try there again.  They now also have something called "cup bob" on the paper menu - I look forward to trying that next time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIcOa3MBOm7S9gqsF3dyEze1473Y-01XRX--02&fid=0x0:0x81695ea7f6044254"],"When":"2021-1-27"},{"Name":"Greg Fong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJ0L0WZdGVzWI2qBiBqWQhdpTibGG4KMYCjzD-Xhn7xYWmDpA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"DISAPPOINTING!!!!!!

According to Google, "Divine" means "of God or god-like, heavenly" or, informally, "excellent, delightful" - the two sandwiches (club house and montreal smoked beef) were anything but!!! Barely enough content to cover the miniscule, cheap white bread (see photo with a pen as a reference to size) along with nothing but a microscopic and stale carrot stick!

Horrifically disappointing!!! A toddler would be left hungry!

A poor excuse for a sandwich shop / deli. Paid close to $30 for basically 5 slices of Wonderbread! Tim Horton's quality AT BEST, and that's really pushing to be complimentary. Website very deceiving.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNsDDULzFkfGuXHSV955_eB4VLStVwvy_hZc4dD&fid=0x0:0x81695ea7f6044254"],"When":"2023-5-12"}]

[{"Name":"Kumiko Murakami","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrzaF6KRvUp_QuDlErcjgBgm4H4mGAcgrFn7sjBqNDAMqeO3GY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Visited on a Friday night. Not too busy during dinner time but started to get busier around 9pm when the live band started playing.
Food wasn’t great but the drinks were good and decently priced.
I enjoyed the Artichoke Dip!
They have different bands play every weekend. The band that we saw was a lot of 70’s and early 80’s music which wasn’t really my cup of tea but a lot of other older customers were dancing and enjoying themselves which was nice to see.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtKFlCvBxQND4CN66eJaKqsarqRTYoEydu8FJx&fid=0x0:0x9c889cedda23104e"],"When":"2024-5-19"},{"Name":"ruishiro (taco bell tenma)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYdaLDrwUw5dQp4SH2Je4mYgR2AgtM7GnlEpZBeXUXn1aUfzR_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is good, our  favorite server is Lorry.. Bartender Wayne makes the best Margarita!
We often go dancing with co workers , love the live band.. was there june 29 and
First time to see  Coco Project Band - please
Make them your regular (just like electric ballroom and Famous players)
Coco Project is No 1- they have good fun energy, all their songs are great with No gaps between songs, love their music medley and their Happy Birthday song , in diferent languages ,extra touch to those celebrating their birthdays.. dance
Floor was packed and after they sang their last song, everyone shouted More More.. and they sang a bonus song.. they are the best
Looking forward to see them
Monthly! Please","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3iTWths184qZuE2l3vrWaxo7agDWV2DI-qm04&fid=0x0:0x9c889cedda23104e"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"Albert Leung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9Fv0yNGvtbx8QHQOR-NQBojnSXy-wOnKr-1lQp3bSnESE8g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Good service, friendly staff, but five shrimp at appetizer plate is too little.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4OrzE04CFlPy_z2oS15zs4Dv1RnU1xlQ_OqVg&fid=0x0:0x9c889cedda23104e"],"When":"2024-12-18"},{"Name":"Akiiiko 21","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJXlYcRvrwGjt6USpEiz5slZlftiMs6qJo8OGH4DRdSC5Laig=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience!
Not many places that provide free live entertainment & dancing!

A06 (chicken rice) 👍🏼👍🏼","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNX7xfpOLO2h-gJO3aAZ4pwxWwd6DxjIcG9g1Dw&fid=0x0:0xf30d517dcaa52bb9"],"When":"2024-4-5"},{"Name":"Aaron Sandhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIcyAqGvbQChyQNpoyohPaD5TZ1kNHz3Ec2QUUyAxk3O1LhJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good portions generally. Consistent. Decent lunch deals. Fairly filling. Good mixes of variety and flavors. Come here a lot. Reliable so far. Hope it stays that way","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ro The Artist","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPRGpSz5k6TBY-Jzwb0atPYYwnJkcdimPwAx5Kg-jHm18YMeZ0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Found this new spot while door-dashing. Amazing workers. I was greeted with big smiles. I got answers to my questions right away no barriers. Food smells amazing and prices are pretty good. I always say this though, check ‘em out for yourself!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_opsjjGatOLPo7jhWwQHxnZJTs2DJ0FGQSasn&fid=0x0:0xf30d517dcaa52bb9"],"When":"2023-11-25"},{"Name":"Macho Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWToXpU3H3YB3xkMOp6uUKU5gePr0KH9w6w89u7rGCD3siyx0IX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Their bento is excellent for lunch in this area~","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODmg0vIdvFgUSUkXhaG-OiZly0gavk6TKAUjfb&fid=0x0:0xf30d517dcaa52bb9"],"When":"2024-2-10"},{"Name":"Joey Chung Ming Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVYhcM9E4AVYkSMqsFZ4_g84iMZ5esvRAaqA4MOChKG5v569Xn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Authentic Asian convenience bento and side  with great portions.
Simple bento satisfies my craving with a lot of variety of dishes available.
3-stars for Atmosphere which is no big deal since it is a factory with takeout outlet.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ben Scoble","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIc4yAKxpC3bFlV1vXYnqNrLb5_rb5q0q0hWF66To7_4J_QPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Consistently great:)
I get my lunch from Bala Foods at least twice a week and the taste & quality is always excellent.
I have also catered meetings with clients and they have said the same thing about the various dishes Bala provided.
It should also be mentioned that the staff is really friendly and accommodating, offering suggestions and guidance if needed.
Thanks Bala!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Tou","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHzfYOOX8CBAX8aEEhbSM3yNYOaZp7oLI5XwrFFEIpeIaUwg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing pre-cooked and pre-packaged frozen Asian food, perfect for a camping trip. The ordering and delivery process was straightforward. Reheating instructions were very easy to follow (i.e. place in hot water for 10 minutes). Any questions we had were answered promptly. 100% for customer satisfaction. Portion sizes were accurate and the menu had a lot of variety. We had Taiwanese beef noodle soup, tomato pasta sauce, three spiced chicken, golden kimchi (must try!), curry beef brisket, and more. Would definitely order again, highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Akshita Sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6wgZMu-cjbsBT2ad4hC21-hyvycSFx7odboIAaezCz6WVHKsAug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Food tasted good. Our server was really nice!  I tried the nachos, fresh cut fries and crispy cauliflower. the Dipping sauces were amazing. One thing they can do is to add more vegetarian/vegan options in the main course! to make it a 5 start experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXkACHahvp6LxuL8gdEknOadadNytB8mwDyGkd&fid=0x0:0xcbf2a40a858564d2"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Daniel Shu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUS1jubu3BD_aebsu2emIDna5JPsgqM6RfMEVBMrW0qDYHu4mTv9A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a good location to have a drink, watch a game, good food and great service. Free parking and convenient.  Overall great!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdkzzSod2hwlt_7Z8vVPzY_b28cwRhFI9E9BcJ&fid=0x0:0xcbf2a40a858564d2"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"Jenn R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDkUzZ37cFKNTay406jwWU10ukeECQiRQ_-IcdaLTCc-zItVg3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was in a rush and our server Danielle was amazing yesterday. The food was so delicious. So fresh. So yum. Happy hour makes drinks affordable!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPW6foHIbGfcVXcqX6Y8DmNsJJy9boNuZ-o8RI4&fid=0x0:0xcbf2a40a858564d2"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Christina K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVjQInhnlTpctqjtKkyBuOFC73N2d82UYBNLgtyl-x2vd3fSs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Had a party of 12 for a Christmas get together on Dec 10. Place was not busy at all. After 20 minutes of being seated, no server came to take our drink order. I had to go to the front to find our server to ask for service (who was on her phone at the bar). Same happened when we were ready to order. She rarely came to our table. Had to leave the table several times to get our server. With an 18% automatic gratuity I guess she did not feel the need to put in the effort as she would be getting her tip no matter what. Food was good but service was poor. Tips should be earned for good service and not imposed. The service we received did not match the 18% gratuity that was imposed on us. For this reason alone, we will not be returning no matter how good the food was.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"sng1002001","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTfKdGFrJyL8jc4znhIMXimj1BkuJ1S_SEthxZmoeo2Gf8Rg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Have a late night family dinner at the restaurant. Glad to find a sit down restaurant late at night.

Menu items are pretty standard. Good selection of drinks with special on certain day and hours. Servers friendly and attentive. Only complaint is that the fries were a bit soggy. May be it was late at night or pre-fried from an earlier batch. Too hungry to complain at that moment.

Definitely a good place to hang out and serve as the neighborhood watering hole.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOf6Z9srvvfv7OjCTaU7EUDVUEl5_1wUnqDI6FG&fid=0x0:0xcbf2a40a858564d2"],"When":"2023-7-10"},{"Name":"Susan Flesher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZrGHunFEVWLl-Tmw-7Cvt3W7vP_TNBTYw4HVnyszqxmDXbqE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went for dinner a couple nights ago and Deshae was great. She says she's new but her serving was accurate, friendly and prompt. I had the Fish Tacos! Yum!
My husband had a burger, which he says is always,r reliably, good!
Thankyou!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nafisa Nazmul","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQ6V6OhfCWxPT6Qcukw2Lf3ApGG5qm9asyWHLVMjgu0yMiRWfw8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Personal and cordial!

My husband and I went there to celebrate his big career achievement. We were in mood for Mexican food and they had decent reviews. We ordered three items: Chicken Thai Soup, Small Nachos, and DRY RIBS.
We loved Nachos and soup but dry ribs was below average (for our tastebud).
Our lovely waitress was engaging throughout our dinner so she quickly noticed that we didn’t touch Dry Ribs. We didn’t even ask for a takeout container. Our waitress made sure that we knew how important customer service was to them.
Therefore to our utter surprise, she came back with the bill while saying, “We took care of the Ribs.”
We wanted to clarify and mentioned that they didn’t charge us for the Ribs, to which she said that their top priority was customer satisfaction!!!

We tried to tell her that it’s an issue of personal taste which has nothing to do with their food, but they were firm with their stance!
In my three years in Vancouver, we never experienced so much warmth from a place. Their food, atmosphere made our celebration joyful but their management team made it perfect ♥️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONTQZOgWBenIxiPe5qaFYUyvLEjIOLkqPmqK1r&fid=0x0:0xcbf2a40a858564d2"],"When":"2023-7-22"},{"Name":"Ebrahim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPIKcLlYsRXzj_NU-cKrILAfiV6rHoottOnSl1Co3QI6YN1537=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love the food here. Everything is so tasty here. The staff always take care of you so well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7JcTC2edGiOl8XSmPBQ3s6H66-JVOvNy1yS_y&fid=0x0:0xcbf2a40a858564d2"],"When":"2023-12-30"}]

[{"Name":"Ruchi Goswami","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI04e2H5hqwCeGVvc3c0VKFXD2k6itIeF8F85T09zlPQShP3g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Really poor service on Feb 21, 2024 at 7:45 am.
The sandwich artist girl was cutting something with scissors when I entered. I was the only customer and she did not like it because she had to leave her work, wash hands, wear gloves and attend me.
She was rude. Lettuce was all red. She did not even wrap my sandwich properly. When I asked her, she told me she wrapped it properly and I don’t know what a wrapped sandwich looks like.

$12 pasta special and $17.5 for wings.
The pasta seemed like a good deal and the wings in B.C--- crazy expensive.

The place wasn't too packed and the pints are about average in price for a respectable establishment!
Only suggestions I could make are to diversify the staff!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Randi Foulkes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoLXCTf8ZMlw2OJNLY_QrUyqBRUBWhNTjTSDcPwnhjldn_CBXGcw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love it! Great atmosphere and space! Food is delicious 👍 Waitresses were super friendly and very helpful. One of the only places I've found that serves Hopping mad cider!! Will be back for sure. They said they may start up a community shuttle service soon as well, pick up and drop off service. What could be better 😆","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNufSh_XFqa7dJfkA8t2x80hS2hHceVVKUKx7-n&fid=0x0:0xc6da18482b0cdfa7"],"When":"2018-9-15"},{"Name":"Tran Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9eULK8-7j2U9Ze3f3qd5XAYcn_cs8--Jdb91h4DDxVjShDzqIaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Came here on a sunny day and their patio is great. Drinks are good too. We ordered the nacho and beef sliders. Well, the food was not very good at all. The nacho was cold and not a lot of toppings. Cheese has congealed and did not have that classic stringy pull. Oh well. But the good news was that we brought it home added more cheese and banana peppers and warm it up in the oven, and it came out perfect. 👌 The sliders were very dry. The bread was like a few days too many in the freezer. Well again, we brought the sliders home, we swapped out for fresher buns and made our homemade beef patties, and the sliders turned out perfect 👌.  I want to like this place because it is only two blocks away from our house, but I rather walk 30mins to Match for better food or just cook at home. 🤷🤷🤷","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIymzm0hgCDF6KJmyCEiZzrJ2TVP_a_JereGCN&fid=0x0:0xc6da18482b0cdfa7"],"When":"2023-5-7"},{"Name":"Lorna Holmes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLGTiz7X8ca9yPQGHnezPpPq3Z134oRRYTfLLhiDOE2Wbgxc-9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always a pleasant experience in my lovely neighbourhood pub.  We were warmly greeted and our server, Ashley, was wonderful.  She took great care of us and our lunch was very tasty and perfectly portioned.  Will definitely be back.  Thanks Ashley!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lekha Reddy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmJGhl1-4gmLsjhODLv0EBv4db0I65Xj_LQ4N38nJXAbHQF354=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Located in Port Royal neighbourhood, this place gives all the cozy cabin vibes with good food and drinks. The nacho melts that were on special were just so so good. Red hot wings were on spot with perfect spicy flavour we wanted. The waitress was not really checking on and had to call quite a few times for cutlery, plates and more orders. Definitely going back for food and drinks","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQXuFR_yMLBpvZ4qwtFRGIVrRaXMUvFaxmjXXh&fid=0x0:0xc6da18482b0cdfa7"],"When":"2021-11-9"},{"Name":"Coffee Zombie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8RAVr6dsNMwjj0MLGbHc5BBD175kjOU3AHcl6iAJKIyIjRsJl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Just an average pub, nothing special.  It's in the middle of nowhere far from public transport which has its pluses and negatives.  If they setup a roadblock down the road Frankie's would give them some work.  Just straight down the middle average.  The food choices were okay with pizza and Yorkies and good size portions.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Maral H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXv9KWxZkzAlGbT8_izCalAvL5ZD65gRqiUFXh0ROKqHLjdrt07=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Not gonna lie . I was a little hesitant walking into Match (New West location) because it’s wasn’t busy but  I love how it was so  spacious ,I also noticed the different party rooms .
Glad I got to check it out tonight !
My Bartender “Ally” was very attentive and super friendly .  I trusted Ally with all the recommendations because Ally’s input was genuine and honest.  .

Had the Alfredo and shrimp dish and I wanted extra mushrooms and Ally was super accommodating and made it happen . Food was delicious and I got dessert to take home with me . I would definitely come back again. …
🤔 Maybe even book a private party there in the near future !!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOILSgSYR27Y7HUtI0rGuXDTKFvxY4WCYvVe0CB&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"Lydia Nathe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLN11wGOZlYbj2mxrkEpJC0C13ReaBejQPo_-hozaWwTeXumA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Food was terrible. The fact that there were so many different menus should have been the fist clue. I went for brunch and ordered a blackened shrimp benny. This consisted of 1 single tiny shrimp per Benny with the tiniest splash of hollandaise sauce, no flavor and dry. I couldn't even finish it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5Ofik1qCst-RcCDgqacobl-OdpLX4He1qrVJq&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Dan Peterson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbNeFUlLkRmjcX25zxpAW7H_0IDjY0P_SfdPGvxnigSNv-OQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We stopped in for dinner after an afternoon of shopping at Queensborough Landing and we were seated right away. Food is always reliable here and there are multiple sport screens for your entertainment. We ordered the Thanksgiving special turkey dinner and the 1/2 rack bbq ribs with chicken and subbed mashed potatoes for fries-both were delicious!
Service was efficient,food was hot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPy_FTWHqZosJkliAtnezYOU6EW6icdWxym65ZV&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-10-15"},{"Name":"Jordana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJvxqFr8nGL8vok-SCRwxhp2_EJmOiFDFc3qAUH70xw1rrHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went here for a Saturday lunch with my family. It was fairly quiet which was nice. We were seated right away and the server was attentive. Ordered nachos and the beef dip
The nachos tasted great, not too salty and just the right amount of toppings. The chips were placed on a piece of tortilla so once yoyu've eaten all the chips, you could fold the tortilla and eat it with toppings that fell into it. Thought it was a great idea. The chips however were not crunchy. It was like stale chips that have been re-baked.
The beef dip was good. Good size and flavor. Ordered it with a side of ceasar salad thinking who messes up salads. Well, if you like eating whole cloves of baked garlic, then this is for you. I was not expecting to find a whole piece of garlic clove when I took a bite off my salad and it threw me off. Not sure if it was intentional but not a fan. Who wants to walk around the casino with garlic breath anyway.
Being it was a slow saturday afternoon - there were only about 5 tables around us-' we expected the washrooms to be clean. The ladies room was kept clean but hubby was disgusted with the mens room, described it as if it was not cleaned from the drinking that occured the night before. We had to tell the host about it and while he was quick to call someome to clean it, it should have been done without us having to ask them to do so.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZplm2z0ayKrtqPeLabwFidkci-dviicRQiEx7&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"Lisa Avery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0uWvek94xw9hceZaor7-wGRHhxzIOVcSdxuCqWSKZC0HUDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly and efficient Gill was our amazing server and she was on top of everything. Super funny, very nice and fast-fast. Nashville Hot Chicken is my go-to here and it was as delicious as ever. The Tuna Bowl and the Heuvos Tacos were great. Thank you Gill!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPja0ZyExbuOpK6-_c4t4Ar2zI6M-Rrf0V76to&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-8-17"},{"Name":"Pam Delfino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVou97WNj_X-lZ_I6WAUZr7ELzzqVVEd-LYy7ydp9dEDslErRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely place to have a nice dinner and drinks! The fried ravioli is a must-try! So delicious. I was so happy to see Goose Island IPA on tap here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOKwXcakWHjZc55vrWM0xXJa9UZj-GGFoIyOPc6&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Lilian Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeGvMKjLmGYYsJTNuBD99YNR1QBuoPNEayiKi_IYfH8GzSOqXQSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Match Eatery and Public House is an underrated treasure that has much more to offer than your average pub. Everything is always fresh, delicious, and thoughtfully prepared.

The happy hour deals are great, and the service is always friendly and attentive. They have private rooms that can be used for hosting events, making this place very suitable for gatherings or celebrations. If you are in search of a great atmosphere, excellent food, and versatility in the available spaces, this is the place!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harmeen Grewal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6oMbvuFAad35H3E9C4dkq0m-eZv18ucrsWsuAfPgn07nMwE8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Horrible service! Asked the manager there who claims he’s the general manager for his name and he said he doesn’t need to share that. If you stand by your business, you shouldn’t need to hide your name. Very unprofessional. Just look at the picture of the water they service and instead of saying sorry about that and tries to explain the situation, he says I changed your water didn’t I? Very rude and unprofessional. Clearly too young to be able to handle the position he claims. The staffs are overworked and they need to do better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWh2R0zBT6XXtwHvK2q9AFBas0V51wghAawjKP&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-10-6"}]

[{"Name":"Darlene B.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJEzkJ_Cm9j6nle9JrD7D2YVUuFX857_POLo7FiF7FYoLYxKrd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"First time in, last time out. To be blatantly ignored not once but twice is atrocious, after an initial acknowledgement with eye contact previously too.

Eye contact was averted when I finally had the chance to walk up to the till, and there was no apology for the wait and disregard. No further assistance in finding the product I was looking for either, the guy was just looking down counting his cash while answering my questions with a shallow head shake.

How disappointing it is to live a life so pitiful you can’t even look up to a woman and answer her vocally. I hope for nothing but hell for people who treat other humans as such.

Good riddance.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObmD_2cmZ2E98IHNZwI45n6UTyzwwwZG-X0G0c&fid=0x0:0x51312d5b04b70939"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Hannah May","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLetJkR0Thx8it86V89uyU6ljDSDD0yhJgZe5esA_tgw0OqBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Grocery is okay, I’ve seen worse Indian grocers and I have definitely seen better ones. But their take out hot meat is terrible. First of all, all of it is burned and terribly cut. Leaving some pieces comically large and other super frail. But worst of all they are super skimpy with the portions. Ordered two pounds of chicken, I got about 600 grams INCLUDING the packaging, salad, and sauce. This is terrible. The same happened to my order of fish. I got a little more than half of what I was promised. Won’t return.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Prabhjot Kang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJyH3zPJaCJ3cRPkHT9uTIQJVWYrn0xibOYr5BwBPpSW_zPDMk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've had a fantastic experience shopping at Sunstone Supermarket & Meat Shop. The store is always clean, well-organized, and stocked with a great variety of grocery items.  The staff are friendly and helpful, making it a pleasant shopping experience every time. Highly recommend this place for anyone looking for quality groceries.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole L. Vaughan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8F2iuiy4vbxZWvjgNneYQuzYC5D2fbA7SRyi3iDD6FnvkaufTEg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Lacking general customer service they use to have... I went in on Thanksgiving Monday to get a loaf of bread and some bananas and it was absolutely pouring outside and I had to run around to the front entrance from the parking lot. When I was paying I asked why the back door is now locked and I was told it was because people are stealing. I was okay, but why should paying customers be punished and have to run around the whole building and get soaked. There was three people working in the store and and mainly just hanging out. I will not be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ansh Amandeep Sidhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdvYQ6Izr8bG-E2Pcz8US2uezHoloLOUV6PRNJR8hHzgFIpX1W=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to this store with my family. I loved the chicken. It was cooked very well. The staff was helpful. I have become a usual customer.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"DLH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNxoVJChN19TlxEyh2PqXcySZWcsWGp-pw0aGewSStRgeU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Located in Sunstone area of N.Delta, this new grocer carries a vast array of ethnic and otherwise items.

The meat counter has marinated meats (chicken wings) that they will cook for you.

The owner, Sukhjit Singh will ask for product suggestions you’d like to see them carry.
I suggested more (frozen) dim sum items as it would be nice to shop local for these things.

I took many more pictures than what is shared here as there is just so much.

Located in a still-in-progress small shopping/services centre visible from 84th/Delsom Cres.
Parking area is medium sized.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6OnbLN0kCRt8X6xJ-1W1tM8s7UjsCryecpzc&fid=0x0:0x51312d5b04b70939"],"When":"2022-4-15"},{"Name":"tanvi amba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUoTl8u2T9k7pR0A-ih2Ra9ecTGheWcoIgrl0dEhSq3vNqkS8I2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered leg and thighs from the store. They sent us burnt food. When i called the store and even sent them the picture of the food but they just bluntly deny and said that it is how it comes and all. And its not burnt. Worst experience at all.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1MFA3_VFF7bd1Z1COSdDzlBXzOfabIZ8KAKWX&fid=0x0:0x51312d5b04b70939"],"When":"2024-4-28"},{"Name":"Charanjit Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEcDVxhEub1WNaoO9foboMFTeh0I2MEyAmuqBsoNq1nmaKiFWj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Today bought cooked lemon chicken and salmon fish. [{"Name":"Edward Dolejsi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDxcmmjByq2PodkDyOmt0Pk9lStn4g7-jleRMZfYgkQApvrbl6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don’t drink much, but I enjoy Fat Tug IPA by Driftwood Brewery from Victoria, BC. Last summer, I had some business at the Shelter Island Marina & Boatyard.
It was lunchtime, and I noticed this neat pub, TugBoat Annie’s Pub & Grill, so I decided to go there for lunch. Boy, what a surprise! They serve Fat Tug IPA on the tap! I started going there regularly, first for the beer, then I discovered their excellent food selection and made friends with their friendly staff.
You guessed it, I love this pub. It is a hidden treasure if you enjoy great pub food, friendly staff, and a nice and relaxed atmosphere. This endorsement may be subjective, but I love this pub, and I highly recommend it. Look for it by the river at the south end of Graybar Rd, in Richmond.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steve Whalley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfD1baKjTO6OdWwruKgoRJEY7SRS7ivY7vqDVBaVOg96TYxNLDpg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great place to come to. The servers are attentive to your likes and needs, friendly and positive. This is a place to remember. If you feel like taking a walk along the road after your meal it's nice to enjoy viewing the boats in the marina.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kevin Bush","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCGxyYiPTdzevWdjSNVHFBYA6Syuv_fFL3qDuvq1li4-ZD_QE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just discovered this place today by accident and all I gotta say is I’m a fan.  I had Victoria as my server and she was super friendly and never skipped a beat. The Yorkshire’s were the best I’ve ever had and it’s just an awesome place to chill. Definitely be coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtykWQRgvOqAJPj2azweY_Q0rG7DqKsJSZUH_E&fid=0x0:0x94c83aa359d6149b"],"When":"2024-7-5"},{"Name":"Tricia Boneham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpaDZfQMP9gmE6Fd5t47ayR--tBtj_k7CI8MNtfWS-Z2f3dZ79=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Victoria is such a great server! Nice place for lunch","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgozaG-nvZLnYQ4T0-PosQj5UHQ3V9imETVawf&fid=0x0:0x94c83aa359d6149b"],"When":"2024-4-23"},{"Name":"D. James C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOgX71xwuGQJkLntlLXyDCHS3HWLYNhpDb8t2zmY-nv5R6n7gdew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Fast service.
When I asked the bartender how long the establishment had been open she replied a long time that goes to show how friendly the place is very unassuming yet approachable Right next to marina.
Server was great with menu option suggestions.
Opted for lobster sandwhich and fries .
Plenty of free parking. Big outdoor deck .
Spotless bar area. Big screen TV with live sports.
Plenty of tables.

She is caring, honest, friendly and very attentive to customers and the establishment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"JC Adriana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVCfhdkaI7AOgDnTNDdvsesQ8icy2R6P4uNP6C9EyexXUu4IVZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Limited menu options, but decent quality and good sized portions.

With your Encore Rewards Card you get a discount, or if you have a coupon from a promotion they have running, you can save a good amount.

Service is friendly and quick. You can eat in the Buffet seating area, which was quiet and very clean. Large spacious booths.

The BBQ pork fried rice was really good. I shared it with my husband, and it filled both of us up. With his 10$ off coupon, it was only 3$ or so.

Be sure to request soya sauce, as it doesn’t come with.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Greg Taylor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbVJlch04vVMx_cbcpxzS_cNOriY8-F6HogJO3bez1B971FeaC0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I had the BBQ pork fried rice and it was lack lustre. It's okay for a quick meal but I wouldn't pay full price.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Xiaoli-Lily Tang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYkrExj7ooFFdHjiqBkCf7b7y8BQsFdx5LydxtbNJnnz9Zfl3TaA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It's called Noodles to Go, so we thought we had to take out. Probably costs them 30 cents. Highway robbery. I must add that it tasted great (Buffalo Ranch chicken bowl) but it’s NOT great value for your hard earned money","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOa1Qm4SvbAtMoRqFu69_HjxByNhAWD0wn5_pNs&fid=0x0:0xe7bd2cc39b913d7c"],"When":"2024-10-2"},{"Name":"raman deep","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIanu3jVOnIw3LmNzV6WBEs69-hpHqXQHT34XbaaTkzrVJqOg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I stop by this Tim’s every day, and it’s always a great experience. The staff is very polite and  helpful , and they know my order, which makes each visit quick and easy. I appreciate how welcoming they are. There is a girl named Harman, she is very friendly and soft spoken. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Silvee Silv","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRPXjPLtMqvToVGVvrF5jMLaASHIAMq4ynKOu5YHIcuqc-vQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This is now probably the worst Tim Horton’s in the entire GVRD. They love to say no. I tried to order a farmers wrap at 4:30am on my way to work and the guy told me they don’t start breakfast until 5am. Instead I order a bagel with butter and cream cheese and they tell me I can only choose one or they charge extra. When I choose cream cheese, they put it so thin I can barely taste it.

Another time the girl took my order, there was a huge line in the drive thru that took over 15min to get through only for her to tell me they only accept cash. So why didn’t she tell me that before wasting both our time. She refused to give me food they already made because THEIR payment system failed.

Ive been going to this location for 15 years and the last two years their service and quality has become so bad I stopped going. They always make me late taking so long in the drive thru that I may as well wait for McDonalds to open at 5am anyway. These employees are truly miserable. Tim Hortons needs to do better. Be better.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Linda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIkmZBJIFrm1kwuZ59ZGf5ItaPQZcIu1O4ZDT12XKRdg5edAg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The drive thru ladies were rude, dismissive and screwed up my order.  I had to drive back and go into the restaurant to get it fixed, no apologies no acknowledgement just smirks and more rudeness.  Hasn't always been like this, the people in drive thru used to be great.  This encounter inspires me to also comment on the garbage in the restaurant.  It's not a clean venue at all

Got generic response from company and when asked to submit survey it won't go thru.  Minimal effort from tim hortons as with their customer service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gagandeep Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXBiBia4unoekoPOhCskrpGmZ7poG09ohD34hqaEc0cP6NEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I stop by on this Tim Hortons almost every day and the things are same i always ask them to put extra butter on Bagel but they don’t even put regular amount, either they are dumb or they can’t understand English","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPwAej2t16XjICW6vJUeriz2oguET1D75-CN02&fid=0x0:0xe7bd2cc39b913d7c"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"Kirandeep Mann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKwny5-M1s4iSn5SlWrgf0Ivt8xCxTpnjMcJwKdDU4t4ZfulQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I would have given zero if possible. All I want to say that if you don’t like your job just quit there is no point of throwing tantrums and showing bad attitude to the customers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Deep Khush","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqdNHVew6Q6-8q8FxSGipua5OrVIklzOOyMl55YoevVBLO9DLX=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had a very disappointing experience. Food is delicious. We ordered curry beef stew, stir fried vegetable, and pan fried shrimps. My favorite is the pan fried shrimps. They are really tasty. We also ordered the shrimp dumplings but I forgot to take a picture. The atmosphere is great too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8-vtXXRnLQjyEeAAuL35jbb-rsGBTqTSnPnNw&fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"minnie li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRoQOlIxvrw__7xun_s22_XplGfNg8u2NALefXOOF5MWkjHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience at this Chinese restaurant. The atmosphere is fantastic, with a spacious, high-ceilinged dining area that feels very comfortable. Unlike many other Chinese restaurants, the tables here are generously spaced, giving diners plenty of room without feeling cramped. The dim sum selection is excellent, offering a wide variety of tasty dishes. One of the standout features is that there is no extra charge for tea, which means you can save a bit and order an extra dish instead.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-elniB3Hl2xWWwsMV20UfYj7JPo45Q9rbfB5_&fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"Peter Powell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEWICjNsYatccfG8tJU6H4w44FxzrmrGxqQilpFtPRJqpzz2xy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Comfortable dining room and good service. Our group had a set dinner with suckling pig. All the food was very good. The pig was delicious, crispy skin that was delicate and crunchy. The meat was tender and moist. Enjoyed every dish although the chicken was a little dry (common problem) even the dessert was great, black sesame balls in almond flavour milk","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQwBTYDYQZcj-v30N7LNcD4G_NH0PQNi6H4BI0&fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Jenny Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgIEDkB2PzsQAjZtJxzL5NwawLrCpei_X1mvBSmllmI0Q-tBD5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Both the dim sum and service here are great! The location is kind of weird and a bit challenging to both find and navigate out of with so many blocked paths/streets. The har gao, har cheung, fung jow, and pai gwut were all tasty! We didn't have enough enthusiastic eaters to try more but I'd love to come back sometime to taste more of their menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-35rkTyMgdRaBUJ03HfzyFPeW_rVUCeeUzPA7&fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Kanako Sakurada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYybgPjG_d3LYq66Ui47Ocd_2PMrfkKaju5V_L0IyVTR19lQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Higher end Cantonese restaurant at starlight casino. Good food and great service!

We usually come here for suckling pig (pre-order needed). It’s like Peking duck but with crispier and thicker skin. I just felt a bit uncomfortable being stared at by the pig.
Other foods that came with the combo were very good. I liked rock cod with veggies dish and sesame ball dessert.

The restaurant is spacious and airy.
