[{"Name":"Avtar Jandoo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtqVZVFB4KITuYZn4EYBo6EU6YJR9xnC-0q2GysDYErKFlww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Got a gluten free VEGGIE Guac sub and there are no veggies.....1 tomato, No cucumber, No onions, no mushrooms, no green peppers.... Do not waste your money on this location. See photo for details.

What their website indicated for veggie gauc sub and FAILED to deliver:
The ultimate veggie sandwich made with creamy guacamole and piled with melted cheddar and provolone cheese, black olives, crisp cucumbers, mushrooms, green peppers, lettuce, tomatoes, onions, and zesty red wine vinaigrette, served toasted.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNf-a9wwuGAneaxwGJbKmV6eSGTESbSXk0zPWk&fid=0x0:0x6992cfa059154e2e"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Ro Pathak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBNxob9i7dnlw3FuvZB5SSvLQHxciIMmwlCg01QkpZXHz_7w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am a frequent customer, the girl who works in the evenings is very sweet and very polite always has a smile on her face. I stopped dining in as the AC unit has not been working. We feel really bad for the girl who works there she is always drenched in sweat from the heat must be so difficult to work in these conditions. I really hope these owners start treating their staff like humans  and not put them through poor work conditions.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joel Danyluk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5eXmHA_lPyDOlimkmP9F9MqU64f18kzpebj9BtbJ10ILR1A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Honestly the best quick food place in Queensborough. Always fresh and they remember my order!! Unreal customer service and they call you by your first name. Owner goes above and beyond always and she loves her store","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wairak Ritthikhun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlaeGm8tpuRF78gBQZsr5AMnn18Ecgap3GDGhV3JiYVpNm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered the Tuesday special, didn't ask me if it is takeout or eat here. Cashier Assumed it is take out and no takeout paper bag. Cashier told me extra charge on paper bag. The wrapping paper was oil and wet, made a mess in my car. Sub was super soggy, hate that. Taste too sour for me and will never go back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_Wg0yAR-HzbI3hrf4KgbWte4RhxPNwbEh7Tg&fid=0x0:0x6992cfa059154e2e"],"When":"2023-6-20"},{"Name":"FR Tum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNGpGc1C82qmMLlhqm6k9Twwd-Qrto2nhp0rZbmKdYw3fx1g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Lady preparing the sandwiches was unfriendly. So much for the world famous pepper bar, the lady has to personally put the banana peppers on our food tray. The pepper bar is empty.  No ice on the beverage machine, you have to pick up the ice on the side using a thong that everyone touched. So hygienic!?!? I'm not going back here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daljinder Bhachu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkeMDM9wZX9wW7qFnSGe0TV-HL4kghehP6AAdLPdt9StGuLgHz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Quiznos I’ve been to. Store is clean and the best part that brings me back every time is Rubalpreet. She is sooo sweet and kind.  Very good customer skills. Watched her treat other customers with politeness, the same as us.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2mZX0r7UdXrnZeHNR2BNzL0jndj00GVcb4XHd&fid=0x0:0x6992cfa059154e2e"],"When":"2023-6-10"},{"Name":"Ember N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAOVVSRZSBJ6e5O5jUUtiBAq23q-FcEx-8tVq1hmthlfDRNYcfgw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"UPDATE: Aug2020
Still liking how their bread is. They have deals for 2 sandwiches $10 and 2 drinks in Groupon. Bathroom needs to be cleaned a bit more but I understand there is only 1 employee sometimes. Hard enough to prepare, garbage, attend, and do everything at the same time. Same girl made our breads the last time.

-1 🌟 the turkey ranch looks sad. White meat and too much ranch not much veggies.

Old review:

It's not subway but it's better.

I'm a bit fed up with subway and this is the better version of the sandwiches. They have better choices for vegetarians as well.

I've been doing the Groupon deal for this place and I'm from Burnaby.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkTEg8sLPO__DthegDdb1sULzhu37JeqizHRrQ&fid=0x0:0x6992cfa059154e2e"],"When":"2020-8-4"},{"Name":"angelic malhi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3IkUa6zYyLxwPA685ZrhgpEJ4_wI0_6RBaNAgnj8Yt5XQe5yl3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This Quiznos location I have to say is my favourite. The staff and owner are really amazing and sweet.
I had two events where I had catering done from them and both times sandwiches were outstanding . Even our friends and family asked us multiple times these are so good where did you get them from.
We also had gluten free sandwiches made for people with allergies and those turned out amazing and knowing they took the allergy seriously and put extra effort into making sure everything was separate was amazing.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Hargun Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJgwC0-O0TWvCXmDyr1kOe2q8lPSxAmOdoXUIEi0ZLJsJnNsg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"It is very disappointing to order from here. Whenever we place an order they never press accept button after 10 mins it automatically get cancels I have tried 5 times ordering here no y accepts order and then called store back to back 10 times not even single person answer the call. Why u r in business if you are not accepting any orders or providing any services. It has made me so disappointing nd unhappy. I can’t say enough about how fresh and delicious the food was—it was incredibly fresh and tasty. Along with the meal, they served green tea and soup, which was also very flavorful. I highly recommend this place—great quality, reasonable prices, and excellent staff service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8AlmVD_atNRuqMGqN63gjYytl_5rksIknOdnQ\u0026fid=0x0:0xa96afa0fa7e894e8"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Harmeet Bhatia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNnAl78AOIxyt7c4IFDfDZa6TPcOoOsagwed_PuJK-JO6EfQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to get sushi for the first time. I wanted to try smoked salmon in mango but the owner wasn’t open to it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOd_YGpfu46uyO7Hv9bW0j_Wf_e3HLa1G1I4-Zk\u0026fid=0x0:0xa96afa0fa7e894e8"],"When":"2024-5-19"},{"Name":"Praneel Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUj4ZJPxV_Lcxat-Oj9_kCLqIHij2bPM9uJt9nJ993leu6gllF0g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The tempura was soggy, no utensils and sashimi was warm with only 1 soy sauce and minimal ginger and Wasabi","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2YeHDEsQ_Zb6OePOP5NlhvNe9GeIFpdR_5C6N\u0026fid=0x0:0xa96afa0fa7e894e8"],"When":"2024-12-18"},{"Name":"Ms. Tahir","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVO0mC0c5CUcMwi-TRQVPSrlxHoz9wAfFCPYNQLwJ5iZjJsjaxS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I went in 30 mins before they closed and I ate inside. They had such great customer service. I ordered one roll to eat at the restaurant and another roll to go. While I was there they had a few pick up orders placed and people came to pick up their orders. They were consistent with each person. My order was so so yummy","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPYcwnL4fgBN7Fx5_-lcW6uGycHJMDTOBKhk-cC\u0026fid=0x0:0xa96afa0fa7e894e8"],"When":"2023-5-29"},{"Name":"Bim S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZCEq-tjjAo_wFnCNX4kq5apTkVAiAoWVMqTwK5JG2VPcaBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Updated my review from 2 years ago with more pics from my recent visit.\n\nI ordered the dinner box. Great value! Great portions. The staff is always really friendly here. They were busy when I ordered during the dinner rush (which is an indication that this is the right place to go) I will definitely be back. Thanks for the great service and delicious food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJWxR6y4Wg19SdTEeXbGzGxC4y_I3V1CQAiBZp\u0026fid=0x0:0xa96afa0fa7e894e8"],"When":"2021-6-24"},{"Name":"Mirna Morales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAL0sLVOrVK-V-L8QMbAGcPidSGLmQTXXffM5Qr4sC484RkE6-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best sushi I've had in a long time. Fresh, delicious and service is fast and impeccable. Can't wait to come back!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOEsGM21Te0QMaRXHHtP64J6NKCY9SPhfxOtAml\u0026fid=0x0:0xa96afa0fa7e894e8"],"When":"2024-4-24"},{"Name":"Ben Moreno","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbXIQA5QNY2om_rvFeJhZDcAcErydWjpf8dpxFoZ8JJurbSZgE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing sushi and Japanese food, at very incredible prices, fast and friendly servers, very clean restaurant and washrooms,  or food order came to our table very fast and exactly what we ordered, well recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4ZzuJpZsa3nSHLZGq8bju4z27uXt-66hUzciA\u0026fid=0x0:0xa96afa0fa7e894e8"],"When":"2024-5-17"},{"Name":"Vikas Barvey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_ZNrRpPGfumHiqd6x5QeDUyjzH99IlKFoWvMPurV94dPcKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had an extremely disappointing experience at this restaurant. The food itself was far from impressive, tasting as though it had been reheated multiple times instead of freshly prepared. However, what really stood out and left a negative impression was how they treated delivery drivers. When a SkipTheDishes driver politely asked if they could use the restroom, the staff coldly turned them away. It’s unacceptable for any business to deny basic facilities to individuals who are out working tirelessly to deliver meals. Between the subpar food and the lack of consideration for hardworking delivery workers, I can confidently say that I will not be returning. I strongly advise against supporting a place that offers such poor customer service and shows such disregard for those who help their business operate.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Monster Alive","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBCwzV2fBW-aqNyUDo9PAn82ZOw7tIyMywMxsXRX6v-VhwqPEe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I recently visited Green Lettuce for the first time, and while the ambiance was lovely and inviting, the overall experience left me with mixed feelings.

We were excited to try the food, and I have to say, the dishes didn’t disappoint in terms of flavor. The Green Lettuce Hot and Spicy Tofu was tasty and beautifully presented. The Tofu with Eggplant in BBQ Sauce was flavorful, and the Manchurian Fried Rice with Vegetables was enjoyable too, though a bit oily. In fact, most dishes seemed slightly too oily, which might not suit everyone’s taste.

However, the service and overall professionalism left a lot to be desired. The server seemed rushed and lacked a welcoming attitude, which made us feel a bit overlooked. The kitchen team and staff were talking loudly in Tagalog, which felt unprofessional and made the environment uncomfortable. To make things worse, one of the staff members was eating at the front counter, which didn’t create a good impression.

To top it off, I was charged for takeaway containers and a bag without being informed beforehand. This was totally unacceptable, as I wouldn’t have agreed to pay for containers just to pack leftover food. Restaurants should always inform customers before adding such charges to the bill.

While the food was nice, these issues with service and hidden charges really need to be addressed for a better overall experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXAajGfM2sn3p8B-aFicLrj9Q-FcRifkxzO3pW&fid=0x0:0x7b3f087653f3c65"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"Liz Rahiman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLf_WAFTMczKN_GsPw8DV_ml7-UU2Elq3CK0W-VyX1oLU1MqQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Ok so I already know a lot of people aren't going to be happy with what I have to say.
We ordered take our from the surrey, the food was cooked in 30 mins for these dishes
Sweet and sour chicken
Mongolian beef
Sliced chicken with broccoli
Lamb with green onions
Beef fried rice
Black bean chicken

The food was good but the portion was awful and flavour betweenthe soy
sauce heavy dishes was minor. There was a total of 6 slices of beef in the Mongolian beef, it was just filled with veggies. The chicken with broccoli was a decent portion but the chicken was cut up to smaller than bite size portion to give the illusion of a full container. The lamb was also decent, but for the price tag it wasn't great. The fried rice had again a total of maybe 9 small slices of beef. The black bean chicken was again heavy with veggies and minimum chicken pieces.

This was the most disappointing take outs I have ever had. My guest was also pretty disappointed.

The person who we paid seemed upset that we didn't tip for our take out...it's take out! There was zero service.  To expect our food to be just cooked and us go and pick it up isn't service.

Overall, I gave it a 2 because this was awful and I felt embarrassed for our guest seeing the quality of surrey bc food.

Also, for some reason for their sweet and sour chicken they add onions and other veggies and its the palest colourive seen, its pink...I've never seen that but they seem to add veggies to avoid putting in more meat. So watch out for that. Ask for dishes that have more meat and less veggies.

Go in person and try it but skip the take out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOcd0i9QAnqVxW2ryWkhASOh80nZfB_TBegSKli&fid=0x0:0x7b3f087653f3c65"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Faheem Khan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-2fv3n7qJlJ30_bkfxp1JY6vmgP-HUHWGLsxX3k7aKrRSWliHIg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Best Hot & Sour chicken soup i’ve had in a while.. apart from that we ordered General Tsao chicken, Mongolian Beef, Schezwan chicken fried rice & Hakka noodles (chicken).. none of them were as tasty as I remember..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNJjfS8bxzjGLdKXSrvcccVMQRbppUVsksa02fu&fid=0x0:0x7b3f087653f3c65"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Lekha Reddy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmJGhl1-4gmLsjhODLv0EBv4db0I65Xj_LQ4N38nJXAbHQF354=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The quality of food has declined so much and won’t be going back. Visited after a long gap and ordered Kung Pao chicken and Manchurian chicken fried rice. There more peanuts and corn than chicken in Kung pao and a breaded frozen chicken in the fried rice. Absolutely no flavor whatsoever in the fried rice. The water glass had lipstick stains that were served to our table and it’s just so gross. Not worth a penny if the quality of food is this bad!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOq1sKeEj_aTorkLEOh90NZpudpHczjkskhX7os&fid=0x0:0x7b3f087653f3c65"],"When":"2024-7-22"},{"Name":"Lisa A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtp9kFla8zzSNpRqz_LPqmNlgZW0NyUdwjk_Pxaf3QrNv6aopq0g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of my absolute favourite places to eat in Greater Vancouver. As a non-pork eater I appreciate that they have no pork on the menu. Not only that: they have shrimp wontons. Big flavours. Great service. Fun music. Love it!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9aqJGZ0XhAPyLpG9pKIMGhocfmjuPuis8FvQ3Dm4rTWLBZg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Chicken was 70% batter! If u like batter more than chicken then u will love this place

To be fair, our server took 1 chicken item off the bill and was kind so I feel bad giving this review. But will not be back unfortunately","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPoOHtybNQqUISW01DVLGhC6hXjNIA-0jqnpPMK&fid=0x0:0x7b3f087653f3c65"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"Jay R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKagpkay_tyMiZJ290grAjrZOpOEgY41rzeVSw6eYBfxe4VIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is definitely one of our favorite spots to grab take out. The food is extremely tasty with an Indian and Chinese fusion. They have a great variety on their menu of different meal options. The staff are all so polite and very friendly. [{"Name":"Sarah Kosari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRKJF1Yntnp-zRLmumvc9e-i3Wwazxmkif9r_MkSiD9JZJ8ngfpA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I visited Lift a few weeks ago and was seated on the patio. Unfortunately, there were a couple of mice roaming around. When I mentioned it to the host, she said she’d inform the manager, but no one followed up or offered to move our table, which left us feeling uncomfortable. Our drinks and appetizers were decent but didn’t stand out. Overall, I expected a higher standard of service and quality for a place like Lift.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNGWppqgevsqLBUs9IIGQTc1uHEt2H1CKYtcICO&fid=0x0:0x311047961ea292e7"],"When":"2024-11-4"},{"Name":"C Alex","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwyIhy11vv6hkoEipoe6dXM4mdiw0k2lH2E1KOH_wFaJ6cgA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Overall a pretty good experience. Was just stopping in for a quick afternoon bite. Had the mussels with the garlic chili broth and I tried the red truck lager to drink. Mussels were pretty tasty. The broth was very good. I did ask the server for some bread to dip in the broth and she looked at me like I had two heads. She said she could bring me baguette. Great! 15 minutes later she came out with a full fresh baguette which was good, but not exactly what I was hoping for. It was an extra $8 just to soak up a little of the broth. Surely they could throw in a couple pieces of bread when charging 30 bucks for an appetizer.

The red truck lager was good but very light.

Great spot for people watching. It wasn't the nicest of days out, so not a ton of activity outside but I'm sure on a nice day that patio would be a great way to kill an afternoon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONoQdQ3PJywqDNcdtSs4MK21fZKoVlF52ATlwg&fid=0x0:0x311047961ea292e7"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"Ina Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqIKozAx8ntjuj5oZw4droqBVtaUlTOcOyWdmvwutABHppGwO0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We loved our experience here in Lift! They tried their best to accommodate our seating preference. The atmosphere and ambiance of the place was perfect to end our vacation. It had such a sophisticated and chill feeling. There’s also, of course, the nice view of Vancouver.

As for the food, we believe it’s priced reasonably. Our orders tasted good! We loved all of our orders. The service was excellent as well!!

- White Wine from Okanagan Valley, BC
- Tempura Prawns
- Calamari
- Grilled Octopus
- Scallop and Prawn Tagliatelle","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNktlrr0RBXAkXuWlioG4Rgq9DovMPiRUoG7hDr&fid=0x0:0x311047961ea292e7"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"Fancy Travel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_imMZ1lnmgEzmxvC-yMSzf-KAj7bJ9vdPxVLU3uTONK5sOgaO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Stopped in for a quick Happy Hour. The food was delicious. We tried the Salmon Flatbread, Tempura Prawns, and the Poke.

The stars of the show were the Prawns and Poke. The prawn batter was perfect, not oily, and the chutney dipping sauce was incredible. These are the top tempura prawns we’ve ever had.

The poke was really interesting. The rice was cubed and lightly fried, giving it a crunchy crust on the outside. It was fantastic.

Also, the views can’t be beaten.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKL6GJJxLYBFoP5TcdZivhNu0QUwbMogWjOVG0&fid=0x0:0x311047961ea292e7"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Happy Sunny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhrtA612fP6soH2c7PBaInHGNvnte3YNRS_qAs35pTYrJn3A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of our favorite spots to visit whenever we're in town. We love the atmosphere and the incredibly friendly staff. The food was good, though the drinks were a bit disappointing that day. We’ll definitely try something different next time!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9tQEMsrcGFQ7jVCFJUCDneY3szAtdRthdNSoN&fid=0x0:0x311047961ea292e7"],"When":"2024-9-9"},{"Name":"Cheryn Netz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIOfr0KygnJVuwTVj_W3-Xmm3bdmZoLu-8ib9KQLj2cd02wMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful views of the harbour. I had a crab eggs Benedict type entree and my partner had the veggie burger with fries. Both were delicious. We also each had a fruit plate. Best fruit plate I have ever had. So fresh, ripe and unique assortment of fruit including gooseberries. The staff was friendly and attentive. We sat on the water. Highly recommend","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHO2NfcpNttRPPHvkxbPlTfusT9tT7dnmoKXAs&fid=0x0:0x311047961ea292e7"],"When":"2024-9-20"},{"Name":"Hyunjun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmMVj9A7kkbF-ktWejUbqqrHSggH2FURXUUmkYlCk2YbG3-QF8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I liked the human IPA, but this place has more deliciois version. It looks they added something orange texture. The food was great. I ate the fish and chips, fries, cheese cake, and etc..
But, After they added an additional option that wasn't on the menu without discussion, I knew when I paid. I paid it. I had to confirm that I didn't order wrong. When the food I ordered comes out, I recommend that you check what's on the menu to see if there's anything else they've added without discussion. Please check the bill, too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOouwM5MaG709dko1rnncnapn_jR1dJ1-1Z03J3&fid=0x0:0x311047961ea292e7"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"Chan Owen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2m58ulSaNORbkm-gDhzx99iQT7v0dK1KjY8tZMsv_TprAr6-w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing dining experience. The food was excellent and the price was very reasonable. Chowder, Miso Sablefish, and Scallop Tag were fresh, flavorful, and worth every penny. The service charge was fair, and overall, $123.60 for such quality dining felt like a great deal. Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPs0yZAaB1XTBn6o_UYyWz9Tu80v5QoY4HAHR84&fid=0x0:0x311047961ea292e7"],"When":"2024-12-15"}]

[{"Name":"Angie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyUjdZQkz0bhaDppuQsySaOzrLROWSfhKe7zzOgxtMex30Fg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Haven’t been here in years and their quality still holds. The duck confit was really well done - orange sauce was a great compliment. I really like how they do their dessert “menu” - they take out the actual dessert to your table to choose from!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPaxXatkweyf6tDR4Mxs893zK4vE4VYx-3vMkwW&fid=0x0:0x5859b1fea94b4c88"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Lou Latil","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvQLHaU9CPptTsFc_Rq33iJ2lgKXoHFwLbBK6TnWLUHs249IqU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I really liked the ambiance and decoration of the restaurant. The service was great and the waitress was very friendly. The food tasted good but as a French myself I was a bit disappointed by the menu, a little bit too basic and pricey. The specials were really good however the Soufflé was small compared to how pumped it can be in Paris. I’d like them to have a more diverse and original menu. That’s why I only put 4 stars. There is always room for progress but overall it was  great experience !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_QABvS3wGLTG9PX3hsJWc9B8EWDeVQKq7cnKo&fid=0x0:0x5859b1fea94b4c88"],"When":"2024-9-21"},{"Name":"Maureen Reilly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfZ8XeI3ZdHWoZz2QYUC9iSK6dOGFb9EO33gAXdkAC6szM5E696Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We visited for the first time for lunch back in June 2024. The food was delicious, the service was excellent, the wine list is different and the wine we had was perfect. The atmosphere at Coquette is just like a French bistro and they have a great patio to boot! It's lovely to have a French restaurant on the west side. Can't wait to go back, in fact we're booked for tomorrow!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOv4jxo2anJl4RddS7v_-QqNbvTIReEr1IOimxO&fid=0x0:0x5859b1fea94b4c88"],"When":"2024-8-1"},{"Name":"P G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0fCU2Qc0a_c6EyAnrC9oWHMXOLKbAIpYaZPyN9xTdV9lbUoGm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Mediocre at best and overall disappointing. Trout didn’t taste fresh and desserts definitely weren’t - the tart pastry was totally soggy, but we never had a chance to tell our server because he was never to be found, and actually served our food smelling very strongly of smoke. Few customers so no atmosphere to speak of either","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkC6mNots7D2J5xA5-krU57DGBu9ThsQukH_Gr&fid=0x0:0x5859b1fea94b4c88"],"When":"2024-8-22"},{"Name":"Sophia Weng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-O2_b6sqvblFuBka3xyWeRr8eBkVZMFtu99msGWqtO5s4LN63=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the pleasure of dining at Coquette Brasserie today, and it was an unforgettable experience. The ambiance was a perfect blend of elegance and comfort, with beautiful decor that made us feel right at home.

From the moment we walked in, the service was impeccable. Our waiter was attentive and knowledgeable, providing excellent recommendations and ensuring our meal was perfect from start to finish.

The food was nothing short of spectacular. Each dish was beautifully presented and bursting with flavor. The wine list was impressive, and the cocktail we tried, French 75, was a perfect complement to our meal.

One of the highlights was the dessert – the crème brûlée was the best I've ever had, with a perfectly caramelized top and creamy interior.

Overall, Coquette Brasserie offers an outstanding dining experience that I highly recommend to anyone seeking delicious French cuisine in a warm and inviting atmosphere. I can't wait to return!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAWKz0t-AVfz-3zpOUQe_3pt2U5QAFeZ5C5lKS&fid=0x0:0x5859b1fea94b4c88"],"When":"2024-7-7"},{"Name":"Melissa Denise","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmPJUZyg5bbjNmbLw_9Zpw5GxBBDSB1XEPNgj4DHq-_lkoMwmALg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love French food, and Coquette has some of the best French food here in Vancouver!

First off, the spot is gorgeous and I love the interior decor and the patio that they have. We sat inside in the booth because it was so pretty!

We all opted for the tasting menu which is only $70 per person, and such a great deal compared to other restaurants. You get so many different dishes to try and we were so full by the time dessert came out. I liked how the dishes were a mix of meat and seafood. My favorite definitely had to be the chicken supreme because it was so creamy and decadent. I've been thinking of it nonstop since!

Our server was super kind and attentive. She refilled our bread multiple times when she saw it was almost done and also made sure our waters were always topped up. She knew we were there for a birthday so she also put a candle in one of the desserts for us!

It was also cool having the chef leave the kitchen to ask us how our dinner went. That is top notch service!

I will definitely come back here again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNo5oeom4PJ4gwmdLxdAjt3LZcGvc29VoSGQHAs&fid=0x0:0x5859b1fea94b4c88"],"When":"2024-5-16"},{"Name":"Tim Armstrong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ8OvraIt0sgHDywuWIL60bfKZ38dyuoGEJ1FlAPLzySD3NOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent experience for Brunch. First rate service, sensitive and made us feel comfortable, relaxed and civilised pacing. The Croque Monsieur with additional egg was cooked (and seasoned) absolutely perfectly. We'll definitely be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPOZU8uFbAnwQ_uwjz0BTQrNdN46gw9_k6VmUFK&fid=0x0:0x5859b1fea94b4c88"],"When":"2024-11-1"},{"Name":"tikki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzV_Y6bQFjodBKC8anq5nBVFmCTC7hA6Nh7xklFQuKGefK40A_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very lovely neighbourhood French restaurant! The food is always on point and the service is always very welcoming as well! The atmosphere is relaxing as well, making it a perfect place for friend and family to hang out and just enjoy some simple lunch or drinks!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQt8yhakYf5ySaRxMsVP60mteNpAkfpoAtrUNL&fid=0x0:0x5859b1fea94b4c88"],"When":"2024-7-9"}]

We enjoyed the experience overall and would definitely go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPD1mMDKeTW9VMD-sH4-P0ZXhHGK4VFfJv6kRs-&fid=0x0:0x123c41442fd65bfd"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Joon Park","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7wR-faZwpmFKcdH4M32IjjNX8F8dOrH-kcttpmJ5OZ4WEFi30-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved the atmosphere, service, drinks, and oysters. Oysters were served with cucumber puree-like things, which was super refreshing. Drinks were great with lots of options. The salad we ordered came with chunks of lobsters. Yum.  Overall, I recommend to come and enjoy your life at this bar.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOiGV2zUpysErw6ndmvPi3_98_EuwXQ8f6qqABT&fid=0x0:0x123c41442fd65bfd"],"When":"2023-11-25"},{"Name":"Alexandra L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXCrU6b78TWfWD0Vvy9Bo9t_SV0eMtnixMvgeYE0_6amVKCdKJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"What a great bar. Used to be my favorite in Vancouver. Until today when I was on a waitlist for 2 hours, only to be cancelled by them. We even went in after an hour wait, the hostess said it will be another hour. Then she cancels on the website, we were still only #7 in line. (Still, after 2 hours. Started #14)
Why cancel without notice or call, after making us wait this long? Sadly won’t be back…","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gia Dhillon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXt-wWmrFf5v4ElmZfQdGGB4prkhbT7axsOdXsHSggrDA2TsNU7YQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Our first experience here was great. So we decided to bring a guest here from out of town. we booked a month in advance. Reservation was for 5:00pm
We arrived 5:04, we called ahead letting them know we would be late as there was a 19 min slow down on the roads. The person I spoke to said it’s fine. Once we arrived We told the hostess my reservation name and party size, which was ignored.  She told us to  wait in the waiting area. Multiple tables were empty. We were seated twenty mins after arrival and not in the lounge which we booked, but in the lobby bar (table wasn’t even wiped down) By this point we just sat down because we were tired of waiting and had gotten valet parking. Hostess mentioned we have a hour and half, which I found so unprofessional when it’s listed upon booking and we would be out in a hour anyway for an event. Drinks and food fell short since our last visit. The young female Indian server was very attentive and gave us complimentary truffle fries. Which she didn’t have too, but was very sweet of her to do. Disappointed about the lack of organization.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katherine D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtDDpzard_Y4-DfAIGJ4daBYN_ISiZfYH7bUItfQO1ITLYog=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We were impressed with the unpretentious and friendly service from our waiter, Jason, wearing an ascot, whom we want to thank, again.  In a city with so little sartorial style anymore, it was so nice to see staff in well-fitting clothes in quality fabrics.  The Goan spiced prawns were very good and my non- alcoholic lemon cocktail was excellent.  The Christmas decorations in jewel tones are beautiful against the dark wood interior and there was a subtle scent of spice in the air.  It's obvious that a lot of thought goes into the live music. Also, the luxurious bathrooms with hand lotion are appreciated.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLyOJbL2Ya1fp4q-8DSGXuwE1QJXELdklxEbQ8lAilqa62IcLMT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic little lounge for breakfast and a great spot to stop in for afternoon tea while taking a break from exploring the city. It’s in the hotel lobby so the atmosphere isn’t anything remarkable, but they’ve done a great job making it a great area for a relaxing respite that is quiet without feeling secluded. Staff is amazing, and did a wonderful job at everything, and really went above and beyond. Note that it is overpriced for what you’re getting (omelette and bacon in particular) but everything was really delicious so I didn’t mind paying the de facto “hotel restaurant tax.”

The French toast (pictured) was REALLY great and would recommend anyone staying at the hotel to try that for breakfast.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLVvZ4dh8IQSxJ5x3YhLrc1J2_QNT7lvixf99h&fid=0x0:0x123c41442fd65bfd"],"When":"2023-9-16"},{"Name":"Shane Eaton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_agBuvtuLtmuC1xKO030XFkt4ff4uZuyg9JSmMnFCNqfVQepbNA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The classiest hotel bar I've found so far in Vancouver.

Update: the newly renovated lobby bar is breathtaking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwvwB_NGVvQpcIvvDMaEISIX3AuYM_AAU86PMz&fid=0x0:0x123c41442fd65bfd"],"When":"2024-4-17"},{"Name":"gemdelux","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbRzrhizyDLPGluXgc3AC6HZyx2rCZbB1Xi0qZ1641LtLPfA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We have been coming to this hotel bar every holiday season with friends.  We had reservations and still had to wait 15mins which we politely understood as it’s busy. We then saw the hostess give our table away to 5 guys who just walked in because they looked like high rollers.  When we asked about our reservations again they hostess basically confirmed they had given away our table and we’d get our table in minutes. Another 15mins goes by, we left. The customer service is so awful.  We would never come here again.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"L S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7Fs9Zln1Mi6KJj1r9xT5ZY-1fXZdBRHpZUBGr97nnpUmsTNiyFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had the best drinks here! They have the best theme drinks. I tried the gingerbread eggnog for Christmas and the Lavender Mist for Taylor Swift. Both were beautifully prepared and delicious! Obviously put a lot of thought into the creation of each drink and it was greatly appreciated!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjDuBG7FufuQt2A2MqxKmO3Y8jTcFf3bG0D-n7&fid=0x0:0x16340f11e1e0912"],"When":"2024-12-18"},{"Name":"Nisa Perera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJzdITsV8au6SEMMCTgqJQ8b9KRggb_KKbF_jkkqBjCntadl1c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We celebrated our anniversary here and had an incredible experience. The food was absolutely amazing, and the service was top-notch. A special thanks to Tori, who helped us throughout the evening and did a fantastic job making us feel welcome.

To make the evening even more special, the team surprised us with a delightful cheesecake and champagne on the house – a thoughtful gesture that we truly appreciated. Thank you!❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXiCd19BeZWfWShJg6vVtU9WH9Sau7H34dTWRH&fid=0x0:0x16340f11e1e0912"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Cleah Aguihap","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhAJulIMh5iFUSFcgbDJQDropQ32pWMlW2Rt6c68oRND7hVqlG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had our intimate wedding reception with family and closed friends at Glowbal on October 18 at 5 PM in the Executive Room, and the entire experience was absolutely incredible! Booking online was hassle-free, and communication with the team was smooth and easy from the start. Gabriel Martinez, the event coordinator, was fantastic from start to finish, ensuring that everything went smoothly and according to plan. One thing we really appreciated was that Gabriel placed no restrictions on the time we could use the Executive Room, allowing us to fully enjoy our celebration without feeling rushed.
The server, whose name I unfortunately forgot, was extremely attentive throughout the evening—constantly checking in, making sure our water glasses were always full, and providing excellent service.
The group menu we selected was fantastic, offering a great variety of delicious options that all our guests loved. We were also impressed by the wide selection of drinks available. Everything was perfect for our special day, and the atmosphere in the Executive Room made the event feel even more intimate and special.
The entire team at Glowbal made our wedding reception so special, and we couldn’t have asked for a better venue. Highly recommend for any event!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSTc4W-GUK73GoPCuxgolJa8NzR2k0MKfdatFk&fid=0x0:0x16340f11e1e0912"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Agnes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyqJcbJDbElC-RwU1sBP46by6tVeVGdJmv6s9B0kjpjwDghjdVVw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our server tonight for happy hour was Melody. Sweet and attentive service. She was also excellent in making sure our celiac friend had true gluten free food and thank you to the kitchen for ensuring top quality without gluten contamination.

The patio is a lovely spot and we had a booth which was so nice with the patio heaters.

The happy hour oysters were top notch. Would come here for dinner again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpre1U2Mps1YSEYXCz_wt6qcCUupdfADJ0d_TK&fid=0x0:0x16340f11e1e0912"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"Calvin Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8Z13zSu4pu6MVNdrUyY_r9hCMeQ4IyNWedet_35YGzsBEi3prVA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The brunch we had on remembrance was was fantastic - the food was amazing - love the beef tartare and the oysters - also the pork rib eggs Benny was amazing. Atmosphere is amazing as always but what stood out was our server - melody is fantastic. Very attentive and not intrusive but always making sure we had what we needed and kept checking on us. 5/5. We also had people coming late and one person had to leave early so it got complicated but the way she handled it with the flow and providing everyone consistent service was spotless. Fantastic experience","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmmJKfjbe_8X-CatJ9ZHI7tpK32VK9_4UnMaao&fid=0x0:0x16340f11e1e0912"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Louise Leung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdwxOP7IKmHv1pqr8CLOtOu012YQ5nKrrU0WlNL_Fs6Alv7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"To all who purchased the Glowbal Buy Up deal it's so worth it!!! The food was really good! Great flavours and the portions were amazing for two! The service was wonderful too! We talked with so many waiters all were so friendly and the manager overseeing that day made sure we were comfortable as well! We went there to celebrate our 15 year anniversary and had a very memorable and lovely time! Definitely recommend! Above and beyond thank you everyone at Glowbal!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMB0HOknSgSPsoa8RDjsoQcu-gQAGxE_7kBZ2bQ&fid=0x0:0x16340f11e1e0912"],"When":"2024-8-8"},{"Name":"Alison O","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUz_IgE1mnRz-WnhNgXMEVcP3ZoMA3o6t_4l4aHjMERP9icVBd7_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was such a lovely experience at Glowbal. Our server Melody was awesome and kept checking in to make sure we were doing alright. Food was really good! Would have been nicer if the food portion was a little more, but that’s because everything tasted so good and we wanted more! Dessert was also mouth watering delicious!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOaCjzRfHRqpbukgLwQK-9MVVVgnSQLb69NXpvt&fid=0x0:0x16340f11e1e0912"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Miriam pennington","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFKXIWFVnfNvTPzSbkTnMbu7J7X4PqEQcsIUjfmqvi5uxw9g_E=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great experience with our Buy Up deal. We arrived early for our reservation, but was seated right away. There was so much food included, and so delicious. Food and service was all amazing. Our server Omar C, was so attentive always filling our water glasses and checking on us. Would highly recommend this deal to all my friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNcSX7fcmd__LKS0F1P5DgqogD_eo1B6STmrl1-&fid=0x0:0x16340f11e1e0912"],"When":"2024-10-6"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Spike Luk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVljR41LewaD1cz5kVqUD3bmc9ybJSH00GIF-DrHusS8cKNejJe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We ventured over to Kove restaurant today.  If my wife did not venture to the end of the dock we would not have seen the nice patio and view Kove has.  We were greeted by friendly staff.  The drinks (Blue Kahuna and 33 Acres beer on tap) were cold and yummy.  The waffles and fried chicken were savory.   The batter on the generous 3 pieces of chicken were seasoned well.  Waffles were good.  The syrup brought it all together.   The fish and chips were good.   The pacific rougheye fish was moist and had good texture for a fried fish. The fries were well seasoned although I would prefer a thicker cut.  It seemed like I got a lot of ends.
Overall I highly recommend visiting here.  Dogs are allowed on the patio but they do limit one dog per table.
Cheers!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNyXPhVxVp-pgEA51kBSoVIeMWwIyGrpJN8HuxL&fid=0x0:0xacfcdfd6224879c3"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"Tony C. Leung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWg2hItphmDzADo6eJVMoupXSGu6cUX_5BRGxO8PmcjleCK5rzk2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Laid back burger joint at the waterfront with a Ukrainian touch. Our server was super friendly and keep offering us free beer samples. Burger was tasty","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7ollQH_UDw7N0mmOdCOSnAZkmlu4chG68IKv7&fid=0x0:0xacfcdfd6224879c3"],"When":"2024-10-12"},{"Name":"Ada Leung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZS31x788z5Sx39ClFe-nCKeE-yr0DOjemrNGL0Qgq3_eJnabT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Went for lunch with my mom, quick to seat us down. Amazing & attentive service! Mom ordered Steak & Frites and I got the Black Bean Veggie Burger w/ Impossible Patty. Meat was a little dry.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPO_L9iyFZkDfWHHT_KYN1afuxP5WEJTbee9gpB&fid=0x0:0xacfcdfd6224879c3"],"When":"2024-7-18"},{"Name":"Sarah K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWY-JgvN5-mznvqsAYHtcaVGAhVC2l-m6xd8sNXk8E9qqKEPNzX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The fish & chips was tasty, and their cheeseburger was very good. Their clam chowder soup had too much butter flavour though, which was not my favourite. There was nice seating outside the restaurant as well as inside.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyEkq7heCfMe5LF6EwliV3KnKvWg-1mYUL1y5R&fid=0x0:0xacfcdfd6224879c3"],"When":"2024-6-27"},{"Name":"Peter M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKk-rxpOq7GwruvLmSaB76J3zaSuKi4IDBOqoO6XW92wB2_VA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice little restaurant with a fantastic view of the water. Dog friendly patio.

Super friendly and efficient service.
We had the clam chowder soup, and the one of the egg breakfast brunch meals.
The food was great.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sam Grace","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiLWkBehUAoqecBLb-PR1WXkxDLUfUaNZAk5e7s-opHpmA48OSHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent food and service! Jennifer is amazing - my new favourite place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwcuvMEFfskdBh4LAkwtv_aqMQy08hOLHQdsaF&fid=0x0:0xacfcdfd6224879c3"],"When":"2024-10-12"},{"Name":"Alex Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI4m-RrKihCXXLVuygCulk_5TFxSVm8ArERd9VI1no5NHh65w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing! The sweetest, kindest people! Beautiful views! My husband got the butter chicken and was SO happy. I got the salmon burger it was delicious! Everyone shared the calamari and yam fries it was un-beatable!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuH6IHIwGhhE28_QO9nKYG61zRWEV4EGss3_7-&fid=0x0:0xacfcdfd6224879c3"],"When":"2023-8-2"},{"Name":"Azuki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDO580thEC_aOqQ6Ey2F5p_tJwlNUQNurFMEvymExhrUJyiE5I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"What a great restaurant for group gatherings!  A semi private area on the 2nd floor for a party as big as 20 with enough space to walk around.

- Private patio with seating overlooking the waters
- A decent menu selection for 2 or 3-course set menu between $50-75/pp + 18% gratuity
- Generous portions on shared plates
- Able to order off the regular menu in addition to the set menu

Their Butter Chicken Poutine is surprisingly a very nice combination of tender chicken, thick sauce and fries... and came in a big portion!

The only downside was there was no aircon on a hot summer day.

Perfect for family gatherings, grad dinners, company events or just a ladies night!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhQDPtosNzq3HCHmCJAwpg-an8UcGZN3EJqsoS&fid=0x0:0xacfcdfd6224879c3"],"When":"2023-9-5"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Alireza Mahdian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0UiNNVRyZjtmU8TuMFZWagjDEpOucA4a-KVpCiuYYILJ-rcBw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Mahony's at False Creek offers a unique ambiance that's on the darker side, which some might find appealing, though it’s not to my taste. Their cocktails are a highlight—I'd highly recommend the Spicy Mango Margarita; it's exceptional.

The appetizers are decent. The wings are tasty, but the fries are pretty standard, and the nachos are just okay. Unfortunately, the main course falls short. The pizzas, especially the Meat Lovers, were overly salty and perhaps some of the worst I’ve had in Vancouver. The fish and chips were disappointingly bland, and needing to request salt for a dish is far from ideal.

Overall, I wouldn’t recommend Mahony's for the main course. However, it’s a good spot to relax and enjoy some cocktails if that’s your focus.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPB4A8OcuCRBXYpSnVSR8Dv7mWlz-ocO5DOBjwp&fid=0x0:0xfee417e217dd63e7"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Alex MZ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFAZ3nTWliK_VtSenzw4uXoch_XcB3H6HxxbxlrUtcPTBIKY4A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A well located branch of a chain restaurant in Vancouver. This place has a beautiful patio which is lovely to dine in Summer time and enjoying the view. Besides of location, food and service is good. Spinach dip was so good. Calamari was so-so. Live music is performed in some weekend I guess, better to call and check.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2P_NgF2gS3QjuC0ex_msLtNPjerc7ok1-Ke1I&fid=0x0:0xfee417e217dd63e7"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Tay Cun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVISvV4V-lNqhgBJaNaxP5l32SM4_qpYYBDmmefTcVji7eDYTQz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food is delicious and portion sizes are decent.
They are pet friendly which is a plus although the pet friendly seating is right at the exit of the False Creek Ferry so it does get a little hectic.
We were entertaining family visiting from abroad and had a great time. It was a great spot for eats before hopping on the ferry to Granville Island.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMwTbG6b-2Vo4kXu2vbVX0mLPJq7M62VKG-5xpm&fid=0x0:0xfee417e217dd63e7"],"When":"2024-8-8"},{"Name":"Lizzie G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIs7GuwCphNV7dZ0l4sPc3kyk134hdt-GN0zf6584QBAaeg3IuS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Super cute spot! Would recommend for their patio on the water. Our server was so kind and the pretzel bites and calamari were tasty! I wish the pretzel bites came with cheese instead of the honey mustard but it hit the spot.

Great pit stop for some apps while on our bike ride.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMf_aokPJhzocD8ofeNeNnO5PfsJI9vQXUfYSm_&fid=0x0:0xfee417e217dd63e7"],"When":"2024-9-3"},{"Name":"Rachel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9HyW9EjTjpSgeCCza_X2_Hl91YZJNAaxmckSbsx6fdmko2g8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely spot along the water. We were outside for the view. The sun hits pretty strongly in the evening regardless of the sun shade, but I still would’ve sat outside. The food was terrific, appetizers and meal, as was the seasonal beer I tried. They are very doggo friendly with water bowls at every table on the patio. Would definitely go back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOmJ9NMkxKyV0s-sSg4wcwSRwcCu_jqM-8f1G8w&fid=0x0:0xfee417e217dd63e7"],"When":"2024-9-5"},{"Name":"Joey Lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIncJBLfbVzRO24PRdfxE4-hovZn6C_s4RV_vqsGslULP8YEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We live close by and have been here a few times. Their food is good and the patio is one of the best in the summer.

Today, we were only here to watch the COPA third place match between Canada 🇨🇦 and Uruguay 🇺🇾. I was a bit surprised to see not many people and staff seemed to care about the match. We were placed at the bar with a small TV in front of us. It almost felt like private area for us; however, it lacked of the atmosphere of a sports pub. Seemed like the staff only cared if we would have another drink.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO32VPVePp7ptRzdrUFo7dsbzy3f05Pjma9klW0&fid=0x0:0xfee417e217dd63e7"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Alexis desloges","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJYQj6LpCMziVYo3OUFRBQqqDtPhJlHOg8jlUwtFMDsEnodl3W=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Simply put it is an epic view of downtown. This is one of the place where I like bringing my friends from out of town. Obviously for the view from its terrace right on the water. The service is always great there. It is a bite pricy for what you get food wise, but on a sunny day the view and its atmosphere vastly compensate.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNUtagZLtsRrf4U9ycgs4qSdT4Xrsbg_1Aec60&fid=0x0:0xfee417e217dd63e7"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"June Tulips","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBB7orQoE65U9x6vCSwo7xnatdAueK1RLu0dqZ_yIaXcmiguus=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've walked by many times, and today I finally visited! The view off the patio was beautiful, the food was yummy, and the service was great. The aqua taxi was just below so very convenient as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-qytsJxZjjnwV4WsUkLWD9s8mBV5FKV4uPi5o&fid=0x0:0xfee417e217dd63e7"],"When":"2024-6-23"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jamie L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIsaaODpzZi62wV-93lE__3OFGYxafaFgdJgxMDBfyIfS_ESBX0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cute place, amazing food. I can't get over how good their focaccia was. Everything was flavorful, great balance. We had the meatballs and mortadella, I loved the flavor and texture. They didn't stinge on toppings. We will come back to try their pasta. Other tables' pasta looked so yum.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOzu69VsXsxcFYAcXp-WBjqLeTJ_4Nzps9QpOkz&fid=0x0:0xb07e2dc25b90f81b"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"Peter Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjFHpMfr2lFzpF8LvaoCh0yxlwbevy7_F6KFcqn7xzMqEEB9ZK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This place was very close to Capilano suspension bridge so that’s why we decided to eat here. The food is not bad, but also not spectacular. The pizza sauce was good. However, the crust was severely burnt and left a burnt taste in my mouth. The pasta flavor is very good, but we could tell the pastas were not homemade and for the price I think they should have been. So I’m giving this place about two or three stars out of five I think they can make some improvements.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN5KKuu-hDZcsnwxjdbMKktLjrMhM9l5tr3nwBb&fid=0x0:0xb07e2dc25b90f81b"],"When":"2024-10-22"},{"Name":"Lexie M.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVpseaTFLok5lMEaSxssXNB3jxoOaJUUw0Cvd3TEh7P8BdLMkS-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow! Ventured from East Van to try Nicli & it did NOT disappoint. 100000/10 would recommend this place. The most incredible service and team. We loved every single thing we tried. They did such a wonderful job making sure our gluten free & dairy free friend felt cared for. Delicious, creative & tasty. We will be back! Matt & the team are amazing. We were blown away.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gary Nijjar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7c94uvfJu43Q9g5Q4ou_CpS8D1rxE9zejnN_FsDe8kU6ATCbp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We found this restaurant by accident while looking for a pasta place.
The reviews had us wanting to try this little hidden gem.

Johnny was amazing as a waiter. Non rushed, super energetic and very passionate about the food and restaurant.

The food:
1 - focaccia was amazing. The bread was delicious and the oil/vinegar was perfect

2 - pesto pizza. Super flavorful and fresh.

3 - campanelle e funghi with chicken. Super creamy, delicious and made me wanting more.

Drinks:
Nicili lager. I am shocked this is not on the shelves in stores.  I will be back for this beer over and over.

Environment:
The restaurant is inviting and has an amazing ambiance when you enter and sit down.

The team working here clearly loves what they do and show their passion, not only in the food, but with their inviting attitudes about enjoying what they have created.

If you have not had a chance to visit here, I recommend this gem to everyone.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGeLv_VC07ffjIkJp5vMHT72hV1UUSPe97Rt9E&fid=0x0:0xb07e2dc25b90f81b"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"Philip Raymond Lim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5EIBAgpBLsauhPMdjXym7mJ4fA8mtryDtWQIJCZfJxYXxupU8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just had a lovely dinner with the family here at Nicli. Was helped by Michaela. Trust me, walking into this place is like in a Broadway house. They all have so much sense of humour plus good food, what can I ask for? I had a glass of wine and now I’m ready to go home. Happy. Will definitely come back when I’m in West Vancouver.

Recommending Il Bastardo Pizza, Burrata Classico, Campanella e Funghi, and Costamolino white wine that surely made my evening :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMssfnrq6j5kiMmDl_5zlZjR3zVJZvBNX2RRL4m&fid=0x0:0xb07e2dc25b90f81b"],"When":"2024-8-12"},{"Name":"Lynne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZCsf97y3t-Ppi4xqcVMVpZ9qy3abZg0k-7Vz9rSFc5K4h7Apj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The pizza was delicious, and the salad was refreshing. The tiramisu was just to my taste. Although the restaurant was quite busy during dinner, the service was excellent.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPkjBkmYcrarZm8AWW02fyRCHIkhm_dFRagx_bX&fid=0x0:0xb07e2dc25b90f81b"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"hosein jalali","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMRJ-zbypkRGZEGZDTSGd1l-_mo-EgMWxQxKDCxwplEVXPzYk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently visited Nicli for the second time for lunch, hoping my previous bad experience was just a one-off. Unfortunately, I was wrong. I ordered two pizzas, and both were burned. I was so hungry that I ate them anyway, but when I politely mentioned the issue to the staff at the end, I was rudely kicked out. The staff showed no professionalism whatsoever.

To make matters worse, the tiramisu I ordered wasn't fresh either. I should have trusted my first experience, where they also burned the pizza. Giving them a second chance was a mistake on my part.

I don’t recommend this restaurant to anyone. If you go, you’ll only be devaluing yourself, as they clearly don’t care about their customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNp98R9lxf0PN10xRXUrN4e7g6HT_zOwbqvnRws&fid=0x0:0xb07e2dc25b90f81b"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"Tara Elizabeth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWafp5-DbmdXd42lrIMIaPpUa4TG8IACFTFef3W9rqO44JjPcQgRg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We booked the private room for mom's 80th birthday. It had its own entrance and washroom. Food was delicious. We ordered an assortment of salad, pizzas and pasta for 17 people with wine. They let us bring in our own cake. We had a great night.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Davlynn Gundolff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXphGvLVdjUtvZy-Sdjqejg5MK9mAUc5Pw4LororIu2smvjqy174w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious! Exceptionally fresh seafood at a reasonable price - and happy hour is a steal. Our server even went out of her way to help us get our order in before happy hour ended. We loved the various oysters, the tuna was spicy and fresh, and the truffle fries were fantastic! They've also got a tank with fresh oysters and shellfish you can buy to go. Will definitely be stopping by again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2G5lbBn6bULKymWMhFoee7jK1vtX9JdF6pn4O&fid=0x0:0xf0d9da3a23633336"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Chanil Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUQGp1nrL9JxzAwqk4JQgTjHyMBxLETKa4reQFPABq175G_ZSPDw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fanny Bay Oyster Bar is a seafood lover’s paradise! The freshness and quality of their oysters are top-notch, with a wide variety to choose from, all sourced locally. The staff is incredibly knowledgeable, providing excellent recommendations and pairing suggestions. The atmosphere is relaxed yet lively, making it a perfect spot for both casual outings and special occasions. The rest of the menu is equally impressive, especially the chowder and crab cakes, which are packed with flavor. If you’re in Vancouver and love seafood, this place is a must-visit. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNLJBH68Xoly5pyHv_7PFEaytVW0jcrI-WuCJwf&fid=0x0:0xf0d9da3a23633336"],"When":"2024-9-21"},{"Name":"Marina Garvey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaQEZmQuInFCG4NBJpPjICbEG7y2Te3dnyglNmkqbq7FM8dlCz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This seafood restaurant absolutely deserves a 5! The food was incredible, featuring over 20 varieties of fresh oysters. Every dish we ordered was unbelievably delicious. The clam chowder had a slightly unusual flavor, but it was still very tasty, and I regretted not ordering a larger portion. The service was quick, and the prices were reasonable. We paid $130 for dinner for three, including drinks. Overall, a fantastic dining experience that I highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-eEqJ5kKf4JMzZIYhJxpENA6ZQEwkHZyrgZfe&fid=0x0:0xf0d9da3a23633336"],"When":"2024-9-21"},{"Name":"Will Heo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxT5MjFCA02DYcNMPq50pSW67aEzUVUKNG8pYBwikydiZxPhrd9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an amazing time eating more than a dozen oysters. Definitely recommend stopping by during happy hours. It was fun trying different kinds of oysters and tasting the difference. We didn't have to wait to be seated when we got there. Fast service, and fresh oysters. We even found a small pearl in one of these oysters!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPK2l0sbWAxDVius0cGJOI01YFK6KQZnJZLz0Ii&fid=0x0:0xf0d9da3a23633336"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Ivy Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1Q-mF_mtHVoTbjZB5Iec8jHkbku3Y97xK58QpvA0t95AOzA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Wonderful experience, not crowded. Happy hour oyster is perfect. Only CAD2. I like Fanny Bay and Olympics one. The staff is nice and helpful.  The cocktail tasted good","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPs1DO-yuKZmYehQKle3V5tKpgzwKt2awjG22h&fid=0x0:0xf0d9da3a23633336"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Percy Cheung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKpYfKBRmcbCv3QlJ6bZXmv0ly8_CocIf_lBOXCAlxRrZaEag=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really good place to go...especially during happy hour.   Everything was tasty and fresh.  We had the fish tacos, mixed clam and mussels in a white wine sauce with grilled sourdough, truffle fries, fried sable fish collars, lobster roll, a dozen premium features oysters (fat bastards) and tuna tartare.  The service was good and the other patrons were very talkative as well.  Good social atmosphere.  I will have to try the other menu items.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5i58FR32Beq69y6NlK_N-5UoRK7dBcEJ6224G&fid=0x0:0xf0d9da3a23633336"],"When":"2024-10-3"},{"Name":"Selina Brillantes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHan5bEmtfRw95p5-ef55mXLD788FU-inM5A0A8u5i6INTjg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had early dinner here (6pm) with 2 others and ot was outstanding. Oysters were fresh and very very good, as were the tuna and the mussels. Pavlova dessert also very good. Our server was amazing and great at recommending what to get ( she is a big reason we ended up ordering a lot).

Very highly recommended if you are in Vancouver.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOg1VwEqxcPdgennvZO2K3dHBKqAwtPTaaw3ECD&fid=0x0:0xf0d9da3a23633336"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Chloe Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0hSC9zRWfLvjPh4AZFB-wfg-EV8cZ_7vTxiFKPEG2gJ5fiKI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fresh and delicious oysters paired with horseradish sauce. Highly recommend coming during happy hours, as the tuna tartar, lobster roll, mussels & clams, and truffle fries are delicious as well.

Food came right away and there was very little wait time. The service was good but nothing special.

Good spot for a quick bite or a light dinner!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLuCvHNqkDYMw4gTCTII7ZbMMTS8dbAwlD7anV&fid=0x0:0xf0d9da3a23633336"],"When":"2024-8-28"}]

[{"Name":"Arturs Mons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVynJ4wFaO1n4O08x-FxTv1KPmlWKP1TXMDnyQPLz_hUxyhn-oQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Uva Wine and Cocktail Bar in Vancouver is a solid choice for a casual night out. We tried a few snacks, which were tasty and paired well with the drinks. The cocktails were well-made and enjoyable, showing good attention to detail.

The service was quick, and the atmosphere was nice—relaxed but with a bit of buzz. It’s a good spot if you’re in the area and looking for a place to grab drinks and light bites. Overall, a pleasant experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNH6eNheDLhmldePI0JJJiLxnwuyug0zu1o5Aw0&fid=0x0:0xe9f0fd5af77ef0ca"],"When":"2024-12-12"},{"Name":"PJLife","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWExxPLfiKH1wH-7GDM8WPUua0npwK45Ph-MlKP_DnWih5mHjztcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very nice place. Relaxed, casual, romantic atmosphere.
We had been here before for Martini's. I had the Irish cream one which was great.
Back again. Had a Dark matter, but it was disappointing that it came in a small glass :( every other place I had it before it came as a pint, for the same cost...
Bartender is very nice and knowledgeable. He made a great Vesper martini.
Sogar only had the meatballs which have a great flavour but a little bit a weird texture and could be softer.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMoRpUMr_7pdLt1_vxsGln9rl22GZZ0dJN_J3Rd&fid=0x0:0xe9f0fd5af77ef0ca"],"When":"2023-11-18"},{"Name":"Tay Cun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVISvV4V-lNqhgBJaNaxP5l32SM4_qpYYBDmmefTcVji7eDYTQz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This spot serves breakfast from 8am until 2pm. Tucked underneath the Moda Hotel breakfast is available not only to the guest but is also open to the public. While the menu consists of only a handful of items, the items offered caters to all dietary needs and tastes. The food came out fast. Everything tasted fresh and the presentation was fantastic. The pancakes were Soo fluffy it was amazing!  Hats off to the chef and our server. We definitely went back up to our suite with food coma!  Highly recommend.
Great job guys!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdXsD-gNqHCc5py2ocJXeT9J6QZ7VMBwmphxwd&fid=0x0:0xe9f0fd5af77ef0ca"],"When":"2024-3-30"},{"Name":"Anna Suki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKM0Vo8YWQUluNUfoUZdSZeGvp1rZfl9G9di0ffjBw-yWP8Js8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing cocktails and food. The waitresses were also very friendly.

The hostess told us we had to wait for 10-15 minutes for a table of 4 and it was such a smart move for her to give us the menu in advance so we could get a sense of what we want to order and also helped us kill time.

For cocktails, I highly recommend the Peach Fuzz and Snap Dragon! Both are very refreshing drinks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGnBQBII8wbxQlHilJESPHL5fQe0GP7Hm5iITr&fid=0x0:0xe9f0fd5af77ef0ca"],"When":"2021-12-16"},{"Name":"Jane Mathias","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWakchMa5EA_ldaZYAUYeq3qUdV97VOPMoh1kauhAqhJ048NXROsQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stopped by Uva for cocktails and this place was really good. There were barely any folks on a Sunday evening so we were seated promptly. The bartender is friendly and made amazing cocktails. We wanted to order the Pangea but they ran out of something so we ordered for Fireside Night Cap and One night Stand. Boy were these drinks delicious. Fireside night cap is served with a side of walnuts to enhance the taste of the drink and it truly does make a difference. The One night stand was one of my favorite cocktails with banana liquer and mind you I am not a fan of fruity cocktails. It was delicious. Highly recommend this cocktail bar in Vancouver.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOraJxOdhmyCQTzyTfMo0xsYLgh5wGoRkN8FegY&fid=0x0:0xe9f0fd5af77ef0ca"],"When":"2022-10-13"},{"Name":"Tegan Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhd8WcmMoJzrCTxjqUOompDgfhF2LCedWHn_fxFGFIAgklPsa_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The cocktails have been good each visit. Service is fine when they’re not busy, but bad when the place is full. The food is not great.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sharzi BD","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW288MzwFkWlfN4-hmCJwoI28tpVq0hWMFg6JZzbb5p0qpMwt_I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We tried just the cocktails before the concert near this bar. As a cocktail maker I can say All cocktails are so good 😊 🫢
Our server was super nice and attentive too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONuZdEgC_m0iGrVWEx0G0hsZCTecyz4eSJuBSg&fid=0x0:0xe9f0fd5af77ef0ca"],"When":"2024-1-22"},{"Name":"Courtney Fletcher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJrP6I-d4ImNGoDPD00RYdTOGYCfxqnJJUtbRFsPOzQuGBi0A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nikita’s style as a bartender was impressive as was his confidence to serve based on flavour complexities. He WILL tell you what is good 👍🏼 and does not hold back I love it. My “Ukrainian brother” much respect for this man and his trade! Tell him your favourite poison and flavours (sweet, bitter, savoury, floral…)  and he has you covered with his amazing magic!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPAooWHKh8pF4eIfKPIt3NDI3mjdWSk4JHRuHro&fid=0x0:0xe9f0fd5af77ef0ca"],"When":"2023-8-26"}]
